46003004	Kit nen yogo logonet, "An nogoba Pawulut. An nogoba Apolot," yinuk, yogwe ti paga nen, it aakumi nggween paga mendek yogo mengga kwak kit ndak-ndak agan nugwi nogo lek a?
46003005	An Pawulut kunduk, at Apolot kunduk, nit taani nduk, yogo ogotik? Lek~o. At nimbirak ti, Ala ayeloman mban aret me, ninowe nen eeriyak ninalitak lombok mban yo'nirage kenok, yokkira wogogurak paga kit abet mbareegutak nogo~o.
46003006	An nen awi yake, ndi, Apolot nen niyo kilike, eekwi niigak, Ala nen perak, awi yarak mbilanuwak nduk eereegerak.
46003007	Togop me, at awi yake inom, niyo kilike inom, ti iya lek~o. Ata, at awi yarak mbilanuwak nduk eeke menggerak Ala ti perak, mondok iya~o.
46003008	At awi yake inom, niyo kilike inom, ti imbirak ndak-ndak aret me, it nggwiirit-nggwaarit eeko logomenggaarak nogo, Ala nen it inalitak lombok onggo ndak-ndak wogoraagin~o.
46003009	Nit Ala ninom kunik logonet, eeko monggoorak me, Ala eyabu aago inom, at awi wurik inom, ti kit kineebe aret ogotik~o.
46003010	Ndi, an eerit nage logokit nduk, Ala iniki kunik nen unde eeppaneegerak nogo ndak-ndak eerit nage logonet, aap eenggi paalo aago o wuke menggi kwak, an o eyak liirogon wuppit nagagirak nogo paga, it aap alik nen eebe aret wukwi me, it inalitak eebe wukwi nogo nen ugun-ugun wukwi iyo, an eyak wuppereegirak nogo paga mban iniki liippunuk, eebe aret wuko logowak~o.
46003011	O eyak nu'lek wurabak nogo ti, Yetut Keritut alik aret me, alik ambi inom wuraburak mondok lek~o.
46003012	O eyak wurabak ti paga wuko logonet, it ando nen mbuti emas paga wukwi, ando nen mbuti perak paga wukwi, ando nen yugum onggo nggwok nogo mendek paga wukwi, ando nen eyo paga wukwi, ndi, ando nen iri'ngga-kale'ngga paga wukwi, eerit nogo logomenggaarak kwe,
46003013	peebi Keritut wage eyom paga it inalitak lombok wuko logomenggaarak nogo, "Op wukoorak a, maluk wukoorak a?" ineenu aruwak nduk, kani paga wakkage kenok, abu kin aret age kaagun~o.
46003014	It o wuko logomenggaarak kani paga wakkamenggerak nogo, nengga'lek kenok ti, onggo kolaagun.
46003015	Ndi, nengge kenok ti, ineebe kani nagun lek inagap ndarigin aret kwe, o wuremenggaarak nogo kani nengge kagak onggo kolaga'lek ineebe mban wundugun~o.
46003016	Kit Ala apuri kineebe lambuk togon ti, Ala awi wurik aret me, Aberiniki kinenggela'me kinom wonage nogo kineenggo'lek a?
46003017	Ala awi wurik mondok obeelom alik mbeenak nogo ti, kit kineebe aret me, aap ambi nen Ala awi wurik nogo maluk eeppege kenok, onggo Ala nen aap ti, mondok lek eerogo pigin aret~o.
46003018	Kit nen, "An abu neenu," mba'nuk, eekko'net nugwi paga kinambokan laganggologwe me, togop mbarugup~o. It aakumi nggween paga mendek nen, "Nit abok nineenu me, niniki warak aret~o," yinuk, mbakwi ndak-ndak, kit ambi togoti mbakwi kiinok, Ala nen kiniki warak kinombaruwak nduk, wi negen a'nuk, logonip~o.
46003019	It aakumi nggween paga mendek nen, "Abok nineenu me, niniki warak aret~o," yinuk, mbakwi nogo, Ala nen, "Yi wi negen aret agan nugwi," inombake menggerak. Aap ambi ari logonet, "Iniki ngget paga maluk eeriyak koonggwi nogo, Awo koonggwi iigak, Ala nen nggerok togon wagangge menggerak~o," yinuk, ari,
46003020	ndi, at ambi nen ari logonet, "It aakumi abok nineenu mbakak koonggwi nogo, Ala nen we aanom warogo aret koonggwi iige menggerak~o," yinuk, ari, yereegwaarak liiru mbanak wonage me,
46003021	-
46003022	ti kenok, it aakumi iniki nen mban koombunuk, eerit nugwi nogo wogoppiyaagup~o. An Pawulut inom, at Apolot inom, Kepat inom, yi mendek ndi mendek Ala nen wakkagagerak inom, nineenik wonogwe inom, kanggwi inom, yogondak wonage inom, peebi logorak nogo inom, yi mendek ndi mendek abok tigitogon ti, kit unde aret~o.
46003023	Ndi, kit kineebe ti, Keritut unde. Ndi, Keritut eebe ti, Ala unde aret~o.
46004001	Togop me, "It Ala wone kote kumaarak mendek unde eeppiyareegerak me, it at Keritut ayeloman mini aret iigo," ninombako logonip~o.
46004002	Inogobamini nen inayeloman mini eeriyak unde eeppiinok, eerit nogwe iigak, "An yoragarak liippunuk, eekwi iyaamun ilik lek a?" yinuk, inigen wogonako menggaarak~o.
46004003	Togop me, kit ilik, it aakumi inawone amburu mbanogo yorogo menggaarak mendek a, an eeke liippaninuk, yo'nugwi iinok, "Ti abet yaga," mbarigin lek~o. Ndi, an eeke kunduk, nawone amburu mbanogo nowak loonggolage lek mban~o.
46004004	An eerit mban nage logonet, maluk eekirak ambi niniki aberak wonage lek kwe, ambi wonage kagak, "Obeelom mban eeke minggirak," yukwak, noone yaga'lek puk wonage me, at nowe nen mban liippaninuk, yo'nirigin~o.
46004005	Ti kenok, it aakumi inowak looniyak koonogo pereegerak eyom awo panggoni waga'lek kagak, kit nen aakumi maluk ugun-ugun inoba lenggenogo piigo logorak mage~o. Ata, ninowe wage logomenggerik, nit aakumi ninikime kote koonggwi kumaarak wonage nogo kin paga pege, ndi, ninikime, "Alom ngge eeriyak," mba'nuk, koonggwi nogo nggwok paga paganogo yo'nirage, eeke kenok, Ala nen ninalitik-ninalitak eeko logomonggoorak nogo ndak-ndak ale'nggen ninoba pinanigin me, waga'lek kagak aakumi ugun-ugun maluk inoba lenggenogo piigo logogup~o.
46004006	Togop me noreewi~o. "Wone liiru mbanak kagak, alik eekwi mage~o," yogwe nogo, Apolot nimbirak eeko monggoorak kit mamunggolaabagip nduk, an wone yokkiragi ti, nit nineebe paga wakkagak yokkiragi~o. Mamunggologwe kiinok, kit nen, "At ambi iya, at ambi meek," yogo logonet, wogoppako logomunggup lek~o.
46004007	Nit aakumi tiyak-tebek logowok nduk, ta nen koonogo pinanege menggerak mbakop? At nen wokkiraga'lek kit nen mban kologogutak ambi ngge porogo ogotik? Ndi, at nen mban wokkiragagerak kagak, nonggop nduk, kinalik nen kologogutak negen eekko'nok iya-piya eekkologo ogotik?
46004008	Nit awo eeppinanega'lek kagak kit nduk obeelom aret eeppinagage, kit nduk kineenggi warak agago pinagage, kit aa'nduk kinendage nggwok agago tiyappinagage, eereegerak kenok op aret~o. Kit abet aret kinendage nggwok logonetak en, nit ninom ndak-ndak ninendage tiyanak logonetak kwe, lek me, "Ao," mbako ogoorik~o.
46004009	It Ala yonggo mbogut paga nugu menggaarak inom, aakumi nggween paga mendek inom, abok aret inigen iigak, eeppinanugwi me, aakumi abok inenggaanom paga aap kambuwak nduk, inooko logonet, inendage tebenak lombok kenok irip paga lombok mbigimbiinok, inooko mengga kwak, at Ala nen nit nappiigak nogo, mondok irip paga lombok mippinaneegerak kagi~o, obak!
46004010	Kit ti, Keritut kinom kunik me, kiniki warak wonogwe kiigak kwe, nit perak, Keritut wone yoranet nugwi paga wi negen aret ninombako agaarik~o. Kit kinomaawi ambik kwe, nit perak, ninomaawi lek lebenak aret~o. Kit tiyanak aret wonogwe kwe, nit perak, meek ninombako agaarik~o.
46004011	O maan nen yogondak kuli nit nggween paga yayi wonogo logonet, ninagi-ninambi abu ee'ninake, ninayum nibi-nibi aago kagak nugwi, yawi ninookwi, ninawi wurik lek me ugun ambime nogo yegak eerit nugwi, eerit nugu ogoorik~o.
46004012	Ti eerit nogo logonet, nineenggi paga nen mban nggik-palek eekko'net nugu monggoorak. Mbe'nirogwe iigak ninale'nggen inoba piigwi, piyak-payak eerogo pinanugwi iigak niniki yanggo yinuk, puk wonogwe,
46004013	miyuk-meya eerogo pinanugwi iigak, nit nen wone onggo obeelom mban yorogwe, eekwi niigak, aakumi nggween paga mendek inambeebuk laaguret munogo mbo nagako mengga kwak, o maan nen yogondak kuli paga togop aret eeppinanugo agaarik~o.
46004014	An wone liiru mbanggiragi yi ti, kinenggali wappinagakit nduk, mbanggiragi lek~o. Ata, kit an napuri niniki kunik me, we kinaruk wake agarik~o.
46004015	Kinarum logonet, Keritut eeke nagagerak wone mamunggirogo logorak nogo, ineebe apit sepuluh ribu negen logorak op aret kwe, abok kinogobamini lek~o. Keritut Yetut nen nappaneegerak kinenggela'me logonet, obeelom wone iyaalok yokkirage nagagirak nalik aret me, kinogoba an nalik aret~o.
46004016	Togop me, an eeke minggirak kit ndak-ndak eeko logobagip nduk, yokkiragi~o.
46004017	An eeke minggirak kit ndak-ndak eeko logobagip nduk, an naput niniki kunik mondok liippunuk, ninogoba wone mugurok nage menggerak Timotiyut nogo aret, kinowagam nappi wagarak kinenggela'me logonet, an Keritut Yetut nimbirak kunik logonet eeke, ndi, Ala apuri yi awi ndi awi kuwak eerit nogo menggaarak nogo yoranet nage, eeke minggirak wone nogo at nen yokkirage logogin~o.
46004018	Kit ando nen, "At niya woraagin lek~o," yinuk, wogoppakwi kwe,
46004019	ninowe nen, "An kiya woroorak op," nombake kenok, an mbet-mbet kiya woraakit mbake agarik~o. Kiya wage logominggirik, it aakumi nen, "An ndogop eekirak~o," yinuk, wogoppakwi nogo, "It abet aret eeko logonet yogwe ilik, we inoone paga mban agan nugwi a?" yinuk, liippiya woraagin~o.
46004020	Ala abu'me piige menggerak nogo ti, aakumi inoone ugun agan nugwi nogo liippunuk, abu'me piigeelik~o. Ata, at omaawi inikime eeppiige kagak, obeelom eerit nugwi iinok perak, abu'me piige menggerak.
46004021	Togop me, an kiya wage logonet, yawi wonok kiya woraagin ilik, niniki yanggonak kinabuwa mbake logonet, kiya woraagin a? Kit kiniki mban koonggo logonip~o.
46005001	Noreewi~o. Kit kinenggela'me time kumi ugun eeginabit nogwe konenggirak me, ambi yokkira~o. Aap ambi nen at ogoba akwe kagak, "Ndinggerak," konengge nagarik, yokkiragi. Wologo wae. It aakumi Ala wone konenggulik mendek nen kit eekotak ti, it ndak-ndak abu eekulik kagak, eekotak~o.
46005002	Kit Ala apuri nen aap nogo maluk eekerak paga kiniki wakkologo logonet, kinenggela'me nen nggiginogo wumbuurak op aret kagak, "Yi iya eekerak lek~o," yinuk, taganogo punuk, wogoppatit nugwi kiigi~o.
46005003	An nogo, an neebe kinom lek o nda yime neegak kwe, niniki kinom aret wonage me, neebe ninom kinenggela'me wonage negen logonet, aap eekerak ti, muk owak loonogo pigirak me,
46005004	wumbubagip nduk, ninowe Yetut endage paga yokkiragi~o. Ne ambi paga kit Ala apuri kuwak eekwi me, neebe kinom wonage lek kwe, niniki kinom aret kuwak eekwi me, aap ti yogo logonet,
46005005	"Ninowe Yetut woroorak eyom paga kiniki agap ndaruwak nen, yogondak keebe maluk eeppagage logowak nduk, ninowe Yetut awone kili'niragagerak nogo paga keebe apit aret Ibilit eenggi paga pagago~o," yinuk, yogo logomonggotik, mondok endekem wumbunu~o.
46005006	Kit wogoppakwi ti, maluk aret~o. Roti piike menggerak mendek mbuuluk roti enggela'me pugwi iinok, roti eebe abok aret piike menggerak nogo kineenggo'lek ya?
46005007	Kit time apit eeka'lek neenu aret kwe, roti piiruwak nduk enggela'me pega'lek kwak logobagip nduk, roti piike menggerak mendek kinengge-la'me wonage ti, mbo pinip~o. Laago Obaga Nagagerak ndomba ninake wariyak Keritut nogo ti, muk wareegwaarak me, nit laago noorak abu pipuk eerak wonage~o.
46005008	Pipuk eerak wonage me, laago nonggo logonet, roti piike menggerak mendek enggela'me punuk, larak nogo pogom, maan mendek nit abu maluk lombok ninggin-nanggin eeko nogogurak nogo kwak eeko logonet, nonggo logorak mage~o. Ata, roti piike menggerak mendek pega'lek larak pogom niniki abu obeelom kikak naka'lek, Ala inikilom mbaruwak nduk eeko logonet, nonggo logowok~o.
46005009	An aa'nduk liiru mbanggirage logonet, "It aap iniki kumi paga mban lunik logonet, eeginabit nugwi nogo kinom lambunik logogup~o," yinuk, mbanggiragagirak nogo ti,
46005010	it Ala wone konenggulik mendek nen iniki kumi paga mban lunik logonet, eeginabit nugu menggaarak mendek inom, uugwe-uugwe mbako menggaarak mendek inom, inageerok nggwok aruwak nduk, aakumi inambokan laganggo menggaarak mendek inom, kugiwak amili kunggo menggaarak mendek inom, kinom lambunik logorak lek nduk, liiru mbanggiroolik~o. Aap ti mendek kinom lambunik logorak lek nduk, liiru mbanggiranetak en, o nggween paga yime aakumi ti mendek mban wonogwe me, kit nggeeme logonetak mbakop?
46005011	An liiru mbanggiragagirak nogo ti, it nen, "Nit abok Ala apuri aret," mba'nuk, "Ninoreewi~o," yokkirogo logonet kwe, kumi paga mban iniki lunik logonet, eeginabit nugwi, uugwe-uugwe mbakwi, kugiwak amili kunggwi, aakumi inabok mbanggwi, amburu nonggo nagaatik, kumili negen agan nugwi, yogoot waganggwi, eekwi iinok ti, "Kinom lambunik logorak lek~o. Ndi, mbi makkirogwe iinok kunduk, noorak abu lek~o," yinuk, mbanggiragagirak.
46005012	-
46005013	It endekem mendek inowak looninaburak nogo ti, an nobaalombok lek~o. Ala nen mban inawone amburu mbanogo inowak loongge kaagun. Togop kwe, "Aap ambi maluk eeke nogo, kinenggela'me nen waganogo wumbinip~o," yinuk, liiru mbanak ndak-ndak, it Ala apuri kinom kuwak eeko monggotak mendek ambi nen maluk eeke kenok, kit nen at owak looniyak lek mbakop? Owak looniyak aret~o.
46006001	Aap kit mendek ambi nen ore imbirak wone wakwi iinok, it Ala apuri alik leenak nen alom kwaaruwak nduk, wogoren inowagam naga'lek logonet, nok-nok it Ala wone wagangga'lek mendek kagak, kinagabiti mbaka'lek inowagam piya nogo ogotik?
46006002	Nit Ala apuri alik leenak nogo nen it aakumi nggween paga mendek peebi inowak looninaburak nogo kit kobak ogotik? Ndi, peebi inowak looninaburak nit aret unde eeppinaneegerak kagak, yogondak yime logonet, wone mbuuluk age kenok, kooniyak meek me nduk, wonogo ogotik?
46006003	Nit nen it malayi-kat inawone amburu mbanogo inowak looniyak nogo, kit kobak logonet, yogo ogotik? Togop kenok, nit Ala apuri nen nggween paga yime yi wone ndi wone koonggo logorak meek mbakop? Lek~o.
46006004	Wone ambi age kenok, nit op aret koonggo logorak kagak kit nonggop nduk it Ala apuri kinom kuwak eekulik mendek nen koonggo logowak nduk, yorogo monggotak?
46006005	Kit kinenggali arubagip nduk, yokkiragi~o, noreewi. Aap iniki warak ambi nen oreewi maluk eekwi iinok, inawone amburu mbanogo yoroorak kinenggela'me wonage lek kenok, eeko ogotik ya?
46006006	Wonage kagak kwe, it Ala wone wagangga'lek nogo mendek nen koonuwak nduk, kinoreewi wogoren piya nogo monggotak me, iya lombok kiigi~o.
46006007	It aap abet mbaka'lek mendek nen inawone amburu mbanuwak nduk, kit kinoreewi aret kwe, wogoren piya nogo monggotak ti paga kit Ala apuri mendek kinayuk lek eekkologwe kiigi~o. Kit maluk eerogo pinagagwi, kinamendek ineengginabut waganggwi, eekwi iigak, kinendage op logorak nduk, onggo yoraga'lek puk logorak meek mbakop?
46006008	Puk logorak op aret kwe, at ambi amendek at ambi kolagak eekwi paga kit kinoreewi kinom aret maluk eekkologo ogotik~o.
46006009	-
46006010	Ndi, it maluk eeko menggaarak kenok, Ala abu'me piige menggim piyaagin lek nogo, kit kineenggo'lek a? It aap kumi paga mban iniki lunik logonet, eeginabit nega inom, kugiwak amili kungga inom, mbabi eeka inom, aap-aap wut-wut yaga inom, yogoot iyagalo inom, uugwe-uugwe mbaka inom, amburu nonggo nagaatik, kumili negen agan nega inom, aakumi inabok mbangga inom, inageerok nggwok aruwak nduk, aakumi inambokan lagangga inom, aakumi ti mendek ti, Ala abu'me piige menggim piyaagin mondok lek me, aakumi nen kinambokan laganggo logonet, alik yokkirogwe iinok, inoone koneniyak mondok mage~o.
46006011	Kit maan nen aap togop aret wonogogutak kwe, ninowe Yetut Keritut eereegerak paga ninogoba Ala Aberiniki nogo nen kinomaluk koorogo pinagage, Ala ake leenogo pinagage, ndi, "Aap yi, oba lek~o," yinuk, kiniki obeelom agago pinagage, eereegerak~o.
46006012	Yi mendek ndi mendek eeriyak mage lek abok ugun eeriyak op mban aret kwe, eerit nogo logonet perak, abok obeelom eekkoloorak nduk eekwi lek~o. Ando nit maluk ee'ninaburak kagak we aanom warogo aret eerit nogo monggoorak. Ndi, yi mendek ndi mendek ugun eeriyak op kwe, ti mban eeriyak ee'ninake kenok, eerit nogwe paga, ti ayeloman eerogo pinanege menggerak me, an togop eerogo paniyak mondok neebi~o.
46006013	Ninambi ti, ninaanogum ake, ndi, ninaanogum ti, ninambi ake aret kwe, peebi at Ala nen, ti imbirak lek eerogo pigin~o. Nineebe nogo ti, kumi ugun eeginabit nugu logorak nduk ake ti lek~o. Nineebe ti, ninowe ake aret, ndi, ninowe ti, nineebe ake aret wonage~o.
46006014	Ala nen ninowe eenik agago mippereegerak me, nit kunduk, at omaawi paga nineenik agago mippinanigin~o.
46006015	Kit kineebe ti, Keritut eenggi-iyok kwak li'luk agago kumbinagareegerak nogo kineenggo'lek a? Kit kineebe Keritut eenggi-iyok kwak at eebe paga kunik wonage nogo, werenogo kwe ya wukak oba nabenogo patiyak op mbakop? Abu mage~o.
46006016	At Ala nen ari logonet, "It imbirak ineebe mbere kwe, ambit aret logogun~o," yinuk, yereegerak liiru mbanak wonage me, ti kenok, aap ambi kwe ya wukak imbirak lambungge kenok, imbirak ineebe ambit aret arugun~o.
46006017	Aap ambit-ambi ninowe imbirak kunik wonage kenok perak, imbirak iniki ambit aago wonogwe~o.
46006018	Ti kenok, kumi ugun eeginaburak eekkinake kenok, "Eeriyak nineebi~o," yinuk, mbo pogo logonip~o. Yi maluk ndi maluk ando kiniki abe'nage kenok, kinagabolo paga nen ugun eeko monggotak kwe, kumi eeginabit nugu logonet, maluk eekwi ti perak, kinikime nen mondok aberogo punuk, eekwi me, kineebe mondok maluk eekkologo monggotak aret~o.
46006019	-
46006020	Kit kineebe ti, Aberiniki awi wurik wonage nogo kineenggo'lek a? At Ala nen onggo nggwok paga kinonggo mbangge nagagerik, Aberiniki wokkiragagerak kinikime wonage me, kit kineebe ti, kit unde lek~o. At Ala aret unde me, at endage tiyak yuwak nduk, kineebe paga obeelom mban eeko logonip~o.
46007001	Kit liiru mbanogo nappani wogogutak nogo, yogondak an wone onggo ambi yokkira~o. Aap nen kwe kolaga'lek we logorak ti op aret kwe,
46007002	aap nen kumi inom ugun maluk eekwi iyo, it aap inalitak lombok nen inakuwi kologwe, ndi, kumi nen kunduk inogonggelomini kologwe, eeko logowak~o.
46007003	Kologo logomenggaarik, imbirak nogo yugu logonet, eeriyak mbakwi nogo eeko logorak op aret~o.
46007004	At kwe eebe ti, at alik unde lek at ogonggelo unde aret wonage, ndi, aap ti, eebe at alik unde lek at akwe unde wonage, eekwi me, akwe nen eeriyak mbake kagak, ogonggelo nen at eebe ili yikkolage, ndi, ogonggelo nen eeriyak mbake kagak, akwe nen at eebe ili yikkolage, eeriyak mage~o.
46007005	Wone alik paga lek~o. Ata, tamban mban eeko logowak nduk, ogonggelo akweegelo imbirak wone koonggo logonet, "We luulu ne ndogop paga lambungga'lek puk logowok~o," yinuk, iniki ambit a'nuk, tayoppunuk, puk logorak ti, op aret kwe, elaambirik wonogwe iinok, Ibilit nen iniki nggagangge kenok, iniki nengge kero, logonuk lek mbet-mbet aret lambunuwak~o.
46007006	An wone yokkiragarak ti, noone omaawi paga lengganogo yokkirage lek~o. Ata, "Togop eeriyak op ilik?" yinuk, yokkiragi~o.
46007007	An wonage nogo pogom kit abok ndak-ndak togop logorak op mbake kwe, Ala nen eeriyak unde eeppinanege logonet, "Ambi yogop eeke logowak, ambi ndogop eeke logowak," yinuk, ninalitak lombok unde eeppinaneegerak me, eeko logowok~o.
46007008	It kumi tawe aap tawe inoreewi kolaga'lek inom, kumi togwe inom, nogo yorage logonet, "An wonage minggirak pogom kit ndak-ndak logorak ti op aret~o," yinuk, yorage minggirak kwe,
46007009	"Kinoreewi kolaga'lek logonet, aganggen nen kiniki nenet unggwage ti maluk, ndi, kinoreewi warak logorak ti maluk lek me, eeriyak eekkinake nogo tebenogo puurak meek kenok, kinoreewi kologo logorak op aret~o," yinuk, yorage minggirak.
46007010	-
46007011	Ndi, kit kinakuwi warak nogo perak, ambi yokkira~o. "Kit aap nen kinakuwi mbo piyoorak ti mage~o. Ndi, kit kumi kunduk, kinogonggelomini mbo piinok, mbaganiyak ti mage mban. Kit kumi nen kinogonggelomini mbo piinok, mbaganggwi kiinok ti, tawe aret logorak ilik, kiniyokan kinogonggelomini iya woroorak a, ti op aret kwe, aap alik koloorak ti perak, mondok lek~o," yinuk, yokkirage ti, an nen lek~o. Ata, ninowe nen yo'nege kenok wone lengganogo yokkiragi~o.
46007012	Ndi, ando yi yokkirage nogo ti, ninowe nen lek~o. Ata, an nen aret yokkira. Kit aap Ala apuri ambi nen akwe iniki abet mbaka'lek mendek kolegerak imbirak wonage logonet, kwe nogo nen, "Nogonggelo nimbirak logorak obeelom," mbake kagak, aap nogo nen, "Nakwe yi neebi~o," yinuk, mbo puurak ti mage.
46007013	Ndi, kit kumi Ala apuri mendek ambi nen ogonggelo iniki abet mbaka'lek mendek kolegerak imbirak wonage logonet, aap nogo nen, "Nakwe nimbirak logorak obeelom," mbake kagak, akwe nogo nen, "Aap yi, neebi~o," yinuk, mbo puurak ti kunduk, mage mban~o.
46007014	Aap iniki abet mbaka'lek nogo akwe abet mbake nogo paga Ala nen ore imbirak ale'nggen inoba piige, ndi, kwe iniki abet mbaka'lek nogo ogonggelo abet mbake paga Ala nen ore imbirak ale'nggen inoba piige, eeke menggerak. Imbirak ale'nggen inoba piyaanetak lek en, it inaagalogwe-inapuri ndarak nogo ti, we terak ndarak negen logonetak kwe, imbirak ale'nggen inoba piige ti paga Ala nen, "Yi an napuri aret~o," yinuk, inarum aret menggerak kogo~o.
46007015	Ndi, at ambi iniki abet mbaka'lek nogo nen, ore iniki abet mbareegerak nogo mbo puurak mbake kenok ti, iniki abet mbaka'lek nen, "Mbo pikit," koonggerak me, obaalombok koonuwak nduk mbo pinip~o. Ndi, kwe ilik, aap a, mbo pugu nogo ti, Ala nen iniki ambit ale'nggen paga lambunik logorak mbareegerak kwe, lambunik logorak meek kenok, inalitak logorak op aret~o.
46007016	Kwe Ala aput yi wae. Kogonggelo kimbirak logonet, kat eeremenggendak paga Ala nen kat kore agap ndarigin keenu me nduk, ari agandik? Ndi, aap Ala aput yi wae. Kat togop eeremenggendak paga Ala nen kakwe agap ndarigin keenu logonet, ari agandik? Lek me, inalitak logorak op aret~o.
46007017	Ala nen, "Aap ti, togop logowak~o," yinuk, koonogo pinagareegerak nogo togop aret logonet, ambi eeko logobagip nduk, unde eeppinagareegerak nogo ndak-ndak aret eeko logonip~o. It Ala apuri kuwak eerit nogo menggaarak nogo, wone ambit ti mban aret lengganogo yorage minggirak.
46007018	At Ala nen kit kinagabolo mbanak kagak wiigiragagerak kenok, kinagabolo mbanak aret logonip. Ndi, kinagabolo mbanak lek kagak wiigiragagerak kenok, kinagabolo mbanak lek aret logonip.
46007019	Kinagabolo mbanak inom, kinagabolo mbanak lek inom, ti iya lek~o. Ata, at Ala nen "Yogop ee'nu, ndogop ee'nu," yo'nirage menggerak nogo eerit noorak kenok perak iya~o.
46007020	Kit aa'nduk kinalitak lombok nonggop negen wonogwe kiigak, Ala nen wiigiragagerak nogo togop aret logonet, eeko logonip~o.
46007021	Aakumi inayeloman wonogwe kiigak wiigiragagerak kenok, ti wone aaninggin lek me, togop aret logonet, Ala mugurok nogo logonip~o. Ndi, kinogobamini nen wondet agago wumbinagagwi iinok, "Nanonggwan yo'nirogwe me, nawi~o," yinuk, nugu logomunggup~o.
46007022	Aap ambit-ambi aakumi inayeloman a'nuk, eeke kagak ninowe nen wiige kenok, at Ala aput wondet agago pereegerak aret wonage~o. Ndi, wondet aago wonage me, wiige kenok, aap ti Keritut ayeloman aret mbako logowok.
46007023	At Ala nen onggo nggwok nogo paga kinonggo mbaneegerak me, aakumi inayeloman arugup~o.
46007024	Noreewi~o. Kit aa'nduk kinalitak lombok nonggop negen wonogwe kiigak, Ala nen wiigiragagerak nogo togop aret at kinom kunik logonet, eeko logonip~o.
46007025	Kit komologwe tawe eeko logorak Ala nen wone ambi lengganogo yo'nirulik kwe, it aakumi Ala nen inabuwa mbake menggerak me, "Ninoone abet mban yogo logowok~o," yinuk, mbakwi nogo ndak-ndak an kunduk togop logonet, niniki mbakirak nogo ambi yokkira~o.
46007026	O yogondak aaninggin-paaninggin alik negen ninoba wonage me, an niniki nen, "Kit yogondak nonggop wonogwe nogo ti, togop aret logorak," mbakirak~o.
46007027	Kinakuwi warak kenok, mbo piyoorak mbarugup~o. Ndi, awo wagangga'lek wonogwe kenok, koloorak kiniki koonggo logogup~o, yinuk, yokkirage kwe,
46007028	kit ando kumi wogonakwi kenok ti, maluk lek~o. Ndi, kit tawe nen kinogonggelomini kologwe kenok ti kunduk, maluk lek mban kwe, kinoreewi wogonako logomonggotik, kinom logonet, aaninggin-paaninggin kinoba agago pakwi kiyo nduk, yokkiragi~o.
46007029	Noreewi~o. Yogondak o nggween paga yime kogo monggoorak nogo lek ariyak eyom abu koorok panggok yegerak me, yogondak nen, kit aap kinakuwi warak nogo nen kinakuwi lek negen a'nuk, wonogwe,
46007030	ndi, kit le yogwe nogo ti, le yogolik negen a'nuk, wonogwe, kit kiniki ale'nggen wonogwe nogo ti, kiniki ale'nggen lek negen a'nuk, wonogwe, kit yi mendek ndi mendek kunggwi nogo ti, yi mendek ndi mendek unde lek negen a'nuk, wonogwe,
46007031	ndi, kit nggween paga yi mendek ndi mendek waganggwi, onggo nggerenggologwe, eekwi nogo ti, kiniki kundugu lek negen eeppunuk, wonogwe, eeko logorak kinombakirak nogo ti aret yokkiragi~o.
46007032	Ti yokkiragarak paga kit kiniki piirik wonogwe kiyo, ambinom yokkira. Aap ambi akwe lek kenok, at iniki mbake logonet, "Nowe iniki ale'nggen nombaruwak nduk, at obaalombok mban eeke logokit," mba'nuk, eerit nage menggerak kwe,
46007033	at aap akwe warak nogo nen perak, "Nonggop togon nakwe iniki ale'nggen eeppumun?" yinuk, wone nggween paga wone mban mugurok nage logonet,
46007034	"Ambi yi, eeppi ilik, ambi ti, eeppi a?" yinuk, iniki koonit nage menggerak. Ndi, at kolaga ogonggelo lek tawe wonage kenok perak, "Niniki inom, neebe inom, maluk eeka'lek mondok ninowe ake leenak logokit nduk, ninowe obaalombok mban eerit nage logokit," mba'nuk, eerit nage menggerak kwe, at kwe ogonggelo warak nogo nen perak, ogonggelo iniki ale'nggen mbaruwak nduk, yi mendek ndi mendek nggween paga eeriyak mendek nogo mban iniki koonit nage menggerak~o.
46007035	An wone yokkirage yi, kit nen eeriyak mage me nduk, yokkirage ti lek~o. Ata, kineebe obeelom logobagip nduk, yokkiragi~o. Kit obeelom mban eerit nogo logonet, ninowe alik kinengga lolo agago punuk, mugurok nogo logobagip nduk, yokkiragi~o.
46007036	Aap ambi nen kwe yiindi pege nagaatik, "Mbet-mbet lambumbaniyak lek~o," yinuk, ari kwe, ti'nuk, kolaga nogo abu tawe age kenok, aap nogo iniki aganggen nen, "Nakwe nimbirak lambumbaniyak," mbake kenok, ti maluk lek me, lambumbiyoorak op aret kwe,
46007037	aap alik ambi nen yiindi pege nagaatik, iniki mondok nu'lek logonet, aganggen eeke nogo tebenogo punuk, at iniki nen, "Nakwe mbet-mbet lambumbaniyak lek~o," yinuk, mbake kenok, ti kunduk op mban aret~o.
46007038	Togop me, at aap akwe koloorak mbake nogo ti, maluk lek op aret kwe, tawe logorak mbake kenok ti perak, abu obeelom aret~o.
46007039	Kwe ogonggelo awo eenik wonage kenok ti, wone yugu paga imbirak lambunik wonage kwe, ogonggelo kangge kenok perak, nanu pemenggerak wondet aago wonage me, kwe nogo nen, "Aap alik kolaakit," mbake kenok ti, koloorak op aret kwe, kolage logonet, Ala aput kenok mban kolage logowak~o.
46007040	Aap kolaga'lek we logorak mbake kenok perak, iniki ale'nggen ambik kage logogin mbake agarik~o. An mbake logonet, yokkiragarak ti, Ala Aberiniki nen yo'nege kagak yokkirage mbake agarik~o.
46008001	"Wam kugi aanggo warak noorak ilik, mage a?" yinuk, wone ambi yokkira~o. "Nit abok nineenu~o," yogwe ti, abet aret yogwe kwe, it aap nen "Abok nineenu," mbakwi ti, wogoppako menggaarak. Ndi, aakumi inabuwa mbako logonet, obeelom eeppiigwi kenok perak, iniki kole eerogo piigo menggaarak~o.
46008002	Aap ambit-ambi nen, "An abok neenu," mbake kenok, at abe liirogon eenu ariyak mendek awo eenggo'lek kagak ari me, eenggo'lek nen aret ari mbariyak~o.
46008003	Ndi, aap ambi Ala imbirak iniki kunik wonage nogo Ala nen aap ti, eenu aret menggaarak~o.
46008004	Ti kenok, "Wam kugi aanggo warak noorak ilik, mage a?" yinuk, yogwe ti, at Ala alik ambit aret menggerak me, nggween paga yime kugiwak abe mendek ambi wonage lek ti, nineenu aret~o.
46008005	Mbogut paga nggween paga, "Ninagugi ambik wonogwe~o," yinuk, yogwe nogo ti, nit kunduk, "Nagugi nombo~o, nowogolo~o," yinuk, ambik inowak mbanit nogwe iigo monggoorak kwe,
46008006	nit perak, ninogoba ambit Ala aret wonage~o. At nen mban yi mendek ndi mendek abok aret wakkagagerak me, nit at ake aret nineenik ogoorik~o. Ndi, ninowe Yetut Keritut kunduk ambit aret~o. At eereegerak paga yi mendek ndi mendek warak eerogo pege nagagerik, nit nineenik logowok nduk, eeppinanege menggerak nineenu ogoorik~o.
46008007	Wone ti, nit nineenu aret kwe, it ando perak, awo liippega'lek aret agaarik~o. It nen maan kugi aanggo warak nonggo nogogwaarak me, yogondak iniki mari eeppunuk, wam ti, ugun noorak op aret kwe, iniki kole aga'lek me, "Inagugi aanggo wakaarak kagak, nonggo," yinuk, abeko nagaatik, "Maluk eekkologoorak kogo," yinuk, mbako menggaarak~o.
46008008	Nit yi mendek ndi mendek nunggwi paga Ala ninom kunik wonogolik~o. Nit nengga'lek puk wonogwe niinok, maluk eekkologwe, ndi, nunggwi niinok, obeelom eekkologwe, eekulik~o.
46008009	Togop me, kugi aanggo warak nogo kit nen ugun nenet noorak op aret kwe, kinoreewi ambi iniki abet mbakwi awo kole aga'lek nogo nggelenogo piyookwak, liippinip~o.
46008010	It kinoreewi ando iniki awo kole aga'lek mendek nogo nen, kugi aanggo warak kit ugun noorak kineenu me, ugun nunggwi kiinok, "It kugi aanggo warak kagak nunggwi me, nit togon nawi aret~o," yinuk, iniki maan mendek abeko logonet, nagun lek mbakop? Nunggwi aret iyoorak me,
46008011	it kinoreewi nogo abok inake Keritut kambeegerak kwe, kit alom abu kineenu logonet, kugi aanggo warak ugun namonggotak paga nen kinoreewi iniki awo kole aga'lek nogo maluk eeppiigwi kiyoorak me, liippunuk eeko logonip~o.
46008012	Ti eerumonggotak paga iniki warogo piigo logonet, Keritut kunduk inom aret maluk eeppumunggup~o.
46008013	Togop me, an nengge paga noreewi yigeebu wanggwi iinok, an nen aret nggelenogo piyookwak me, an wam mondok nengga'lek aret logogin~o.
46009001	An nogo, aakumi nen, "Yogop ee'nu, ndogop ee'nu," yo'nugwi iigak eeke minggirak mbakop? An nappiigak logokit nduk, Ala nen mippanulik mbakop? Ndi, ninowe Yetut an nenegen liirogon koolik nombako ogotik? Ninowe eyabu eeke minggirak nogo, anggen yugu negen kit aret wonogwe nogo lek a?
46009002	It aap ando nen, "Kat nappiigak mendek lek~o," yo'nugwi iigak kwe, kit nen perak, an yokkirage neegak, kit Ala apuri ogogutak ti paga liippaninuk nappiigak mendek abet aret wonage nombakwi nogo lek a?
46009003	It aakumi nen an kin wo'neego logonet, "Kat abet aret nappiigak mendek ilik?" yo'nugwi iinok, an nen wone onggo yorage logonet,
46009004	"Lek~o. An Ala eyabu eeke nogo onggo kinambi-kinagi ma'ninip~o," yokkiroorak meek mbakop?
46009005	It aap nappiigak mendek ando inom, at ninowe awurilogwe ambokan ndarak inom, Peterut inom, Ala wone wonok nugu logonet, inakuwi wogoren nugu menggaarak nogo ndak-ndak, nit togon togop eeriyak meek mbakop?
46009006	It ti, eerit nugwi iigak, an Mbaranabat nimbirak mban nit nineebe op logowok nduk, nineenggi paga mban nggik-palek eekko'net nugu logorak op mba'nuk, yogo ogotik?
46009007	It yigin unde nogo ineebe op logorak nduk, ineenggi paga mban nggik-palek eerogo nonggo menggaarak mbakop? It aap yabu eeka nen anggen yugu mbanogo ando it nunggulik mbakop? Ndi, it aap ndomba ndegeninaka nen ndomba inelak amburu toologo it ando noorak meek mbakop? Lek~o. It yabu eeko menggaarak abok aret onggo anggen mbanogo nonggo menggaarak aret~o, yinuk, yokkiragi~o, noreewi.
46009008	An wone yokkirage ti, nit aakumi abok eeko monggoorak nogo mban wakkagak yokkirage ti lek~o. Ata, maan Ala nen Muta wone yoreegerak nogo, togop aret liiru mbanak wonage nogo lek a?
46009009	"Lembu nen iniyok paga gandum anggen mbelanit nage kagak ando nunggwi iyo, inambe keele maarogo piigo logorak mage~o," yinuk, Ala nen wone Muta yoreegerak liiru mbanak wonage nogo ti, Ala nen lembu mban abuwa mba'nuk, yereegerak ilik,
46009010	nit togon, ninabuwa mba'nuk yereegerak a? Lek~o. Nit aakumi ninabuwa mba'nuk aret yereegerak me, it aap yabu wagangga inom, anggen mbilanit naga inom, imbirak nen, "Peebi nit aret nonggo logogun~o," yinuk, iniki lunik logonet, eeko menggaarak.
46009011	Togop ndak-ndak, nit nen Ala wone nogo kinikime awi yappinagareegurak me, yogondak anggen yugu kit kinamendek ando nit wo'niroorak meek nduk yogo ogotik?
46009012	It iyaalok Ala wone kinikime awi yappinagulik mendek nen, "It inamendek ando wo'niraagun," mba'nuk, kinoba aberak wonogwe iinok, wogorogo monggotak kwe, nit iyaalok yappinagareegurak nogo nen, "Wo'niraanip~o," yinuk, yokkiroorak meek mbakop? Yokkiroorak op aret kwe, obeelom wone Keritut yo'niragagerak wone nogo wiganit nage me, non mbambukwak nduk, "Wo'niraanip~o," yokkiraga'lek nineenggi paga nen mban eekko'net nogo ogoorik~o.
46009013	It Ala awi wurik me yabu eeko menggaarak nogo, yabu eekwi onggo negen mbi Ala ake pugu nogo aret kologwe, ndi, it aap Ala aanggo warogo wogogo menggaarak nogo, warogo wogogo logonet, ando it nunggwi, eeko menggaarak nogo kineenggo'lek me yogo ogotik?
46009014	Ti ndak-ndak it aap wone obeelom wone yorogwe nogo, ineebe obeelom logowak nduk, "It waganggo menggaarak nogo nen yi mendek ndi mendek wogorogo logowak~o," yinuk, ninowe nen koonogo pereegerak.
46009015	Koonogo pereegerak kwe, "Kinamendek ambi wo'ninip~o," yinuk, an yokkirage logolik~o. Ndi, yogondak kunduk, kit ambi eeppanubagip nduk, liiru yi mbanggirage lek mban. An kambuurak op aret mbake kwe, "An Ala ake pugu waagin abu lek~o," ari minggirak ti, iya lombok mbake me, aakumi nen lek eerogo paniyak lek aret~o.
46009016	An obeelom wone yoranet nege minggirak nogo ti, Ala nen, "Yoranet nege logot~o," ari kenok, yoranet nege minggirak ti paga an wogoppatiyak abu lek~o. An wone obeelom wone yoranet nege lek neenok, maluk eeppaniyak me, nagabiti mba'nuk, yoranet nege minggirak.
46009017	An niniki mba'nuk yorage logonetak en, "Onggo wo'niruwak," mba'nuk, niniki lunik logorak op aret kwe, Ala nen aret unde eeppaneegerak kenok, yoranet nege minggirak me, onggo lek we aret yoranet nege minggirak.
46009018	Togop me, an onggo koloorak ti, ngge mbakop? Lek~o. An yabu eeke onggo ti, wone yokkirage nogo paga, "Onggo wo'ninip~o," yokkiroorak op kagak, tebenogo punuk, obeelom wone onggo lek we aret kineenu eeppinagit nege minggirak nogo ti, an onggo kolage ti aret~o.
46009019	An aakumi inayeloman wonage lek we wonage minggirak kwe, Ala apuri eerogo piyaakit nduk, aakumi abok aret inayeloman eekko'nok nage minggirak.
46009020	An nen it Yakuri mendek Ala apuri eerogo piyaakit nduk, inenggela'me logonet, it Yakuri eeko menggaarak aret eerit nage, ndi, it wone Muta yoreegerak eeko menggaarak nogo, an togop eekeelik kwe, Ala apuri eerogo piyaakit nduk, inenggela'me logonet, Muta wone yoreegerak eeko menggaarak an ndak-ndak eerit nage,
46009021	ndi, it aap endekem mendek Ala nen wone Muta yoreegerak wone eekulik mendek nogo, Ala apuri eerogo piyaakit nduk, inenggela'me logonet, it eeko mengga kwak, an ndak-ndak eerit nage, eeke minggirak. Ti eeke minggirak nogo ti, Ala yereegerak wone nogo taganogo punuk eekeelik~o. Ata, Keritut yereegerak wone aret eeke logonet, eeke minggirak me nduk, yokkiragi~o.
46009022	Ndi, it aakumi iniki awo kole aga'lek mendek nogo iniki kole eerogo piyaakit nduk, it inenggela'me logonet, it eeko menggaarak an ndak-ndak aret eeke minggirak. An yi aap ndi aap abok inenggela'me nege logonet, it ambitak Ala nen inagap ndaruwak nduk, it eeko menggaarak abok aret an ndak-ndak eerit nage minggirak.
46009023	An eerit nage minggirak ti, abok aret it aakumi wone obeelom wone konembunuk, waganggo logonet, iniki ale'nggen mbakwi kwak, an togon nale'nggen kaakit nduk, yoranet nage minggirak.
46009024	It aakumi onggo koloorak nduk, nggare agan nogo logonet, ineebe apit aret nggare agan nogo menggaarak kwe, ambiret mban onggo kolage menggerak nogo, kit kineenggo'lek a? Togop me, onggo kolaabagip nduk, kit kunduk togop aret nggare agan togon nogo logonip~o.
46009025	Aap ambi it aakumi nggare agan nogwe nogo inom nggare agan aa'nduk wundi noorak mbake logonet, at yi mendek ndi mendek eeriyak mbake nogo tebenogo pege menggerak. At onggo nggare-nggare mendaarak we luulu lek ariyak mendek kagak yippanuwak mba'nuk, eeke menggerak kwe, nit perak, onggo nggare-nggare mendaarak mondok-mondok logorak mendek yippinanuwak mba'nuk, eekwi me,
46009026	-
46009027	ti paga an mondok nengga lolo nggare agan nage agarik~o. Wim namburuwok nduk, anggut-nggut wakkogo mengga kwak, an togop eekeelik~o. Ata, it ando, "Ninom mbe agan nogo logowok~o," yoraminggirak ninom mbe agan nogwe niigak, "Mbe agan noorak onggo kat koloorak lek me, puk logot~o," yo'nirukwak, nomaawi paga mbe agan nage logominggirik, onggo kolaakit nduk, yi mendek ndi mendek eeriyak ee'nake nogo tebenogo punuk, wakkagak mban eeke minggirak.
46010001	Noreewi~o. Muta nen nit ninombomini wogoren wage kagak, eereegwaarak nogo kobak ogwe kiyo, aberogo yokkira~o. It abok aret ndugwi nen tu nigiren wage, niyo mogongge kenok, it abok aret wunda wogwe, eereegwaarak.
46010002	Nit Keritut oone waganggwi mendek mbaruwak nduk, niyome wanggo monggo kwak, it Muta oone waganggwi mendek yelok iyaawak nduk, ndugwi nen nobaarogo piige, niyo mogonogo piige, eereegerak.
46010003	Roti mbogut paga nen wugira wagagerak nogo, it abok aret nunggwi,
46010004	ndi, yugum wareegerak nogo ti, Keritut kwak me, wake mbareegi, Ala nen niyo wogoragagerak nogo, it abok aret nunggwi, eereegwaarak kwe,
46010005	it ando nggwok nogo Ala ale'nggen inombarulik me, karume time kambit nogo logonet, inowak nggininit nagagerak nogo~o.
46010006	Ti eereegwaarak nogo it, "Maluk eeruwok," mba'nuk, eerit nogo nogogwa kwak, nit ndak-ndak, "Maluk eeruwok," mba'nuk eerit nogwe niyo, liippako logowok nduk, eereegwaarak.
46010007	It aakumi ando nen kugi eeko logonet, "Yi inom, mbi inom, nenok, mi'na'nuk, kwirabik-kwira-bok yogo logonet, kumi aap inom ugun-ugun eeko nogogwaarak~o," yinuk, liiru mbanak nogo ndak-ndak kit kugiwak amili kuniyak mage~o.
46010008	Ndi, it ando ndawi wappunuk, kumi ugun-ugun wurinabit nogo mbareegwa, ne ambit liingge ineebe ambik dua puluh tiga ribu aret kambit nogogwaarak nogo kwak, nit togop ee'ninabukwak, ugun aganabit nugu logorak mage~o.
46010009	It ando nen, "Ala nonggop ee'ninake kaamun?" yinuk, anini eeppogo mbareegwa, waalo nen eyak mbaninabit nage mbareegi, kambit nogogwaarak nogo kwak, nit togop aret kambit nookwak, "Nonggop ee'ninake kaamun?" yinuk, Ala anini eeppuurak mage~o.
46010010	It ando nen ineebi-ineeba yogo mbareegwa, at malayikat aakumi inoorit nega nogo nen inoorogo piinet wage mbareegi, kambit nogogwaarak nogo kokwak, nit togop aret ninooke kero, nineebi-nineeba yogo logorak mage~o.
46010011	It eereegwaarak nogo ti, in wakkagak nit nineenu aruwok nduk, eereegwaarak me, o age yobok eeriyak eyom panggoni wage kagak, nit yogondak wonogwe yi, niniki liippatuwok nduk, wone yi, liiru mbanniragagerak.
46010012	Ti kenok, aap ambit-ambi, "An Ala wone abu liippigirak me, maluk eerigin lek~o," mbake kenok, yigeebu wangge kero, iniki liippatinuk, logowak~o.
46010013	Kit kiniki nggagangginake menggerak nogo ti, alik mendek paga lek~o. Ata, yi aakumi ndi aakumi iniki nggaganinake menggerak nogo mendek paga mban aret kit kiniki nggagangginake kaamunggup kwe, at Ala nen nit ee'ninake nogo, mondok liippinanege menggerak me, kiniki nggagangginake kagak, kinomaawi lek arit unggwage logonet, maluk eekwi kiyo, Ala nen tu mbininogo pinagagin~o.
46010014	Ti kenok, noreewi~o. Kit an niniki kunik me, kugiwak amili kuniyak, "Nineebi lombok," mbako logonip~o.
46010015	Kit aap kiniki warak aret me, wone yokkirage yi, kit mban kiniki wakkogo logonip~o.
46010016	Nit niniki ambit lambunik logonet, at Keritut amiya wundeegerak nogo paga lambunogo pinaneegerak abeko logonet, amburu toolak waganogo, "Ala wa," yinuk, nonggo monggoorak nogo lek a? Ndi, roti karerogo nonggo monggoorak nogo ti, nit niniki ambit lambunik logonet, at ninake kambeegerak abeko logonet, nonggo monggoorak nogo lek a?
46010017	Roti ambit worarak wonage, ndi, nineebe apit aret kwe, roti ambit worarak ti aret karerogo mak-mak nunggwi me, nineebe ambit lambunik aret ogoorik~o.
46010018	It aakumi Iterali eeko nogogwaarak nogo liippinip~o. It Ala aanggo wonok wogwe inom, warogo Ala wogogo logonet, nunggwi inom, Ala nen ndak-ndak eeppiige menggerak lek mbakop?
46010019	An wone ti ngge nduk yokkirage mbakop? "Obeelom eekkolaabagip nduk, kugi aanggo warogo nonggo logonip~o," yinuk, yokkirage mbakop? Ndi, "Maluk eekkinake kero, kugiwak amili kunggo logonip~o," yinuk, yokkirage mbakop?
46010020	Mondok lek~o. An yokkirage ti, it aakumi endekem mendek nogo nen inagugi aanggo warogo wogogwi nogo ti, Ala ake warogo wogogwi lek~o. Ata, it inagugi inake aret warogo wogogwi me, inagugi kinoba age kero, kit kinom kunik eeko logorak an mondok, "Neebi," mbake logonet, yokkiragi~o.
46010021	Ninowe amiya kwak amburu toolak inom, kugi Tile agi toolak inom, imbirak lambunogo punuk nenggak yuurak mondok meek~o. Ndi, ninowe ambi larak inom, ti'nuk, kugi Tile ambi larak inom, imbirak lambunogo punuk, noorak ti kunduk, abu meek mban~o.
46010022	Nit ninowe anini eeppuurak op mbakop? Nit ninomaawi ambik, ndi, at omaawi lek mbakop? Lek aret~o.
46010023	Yi mendek ndi mendek eeriyak mage lek abok ugun eeriyak op aret kwe, eerit nogo logonet perak, nit ambi obeelom eekkoloorak nduk, eekulik~o. Ndi, yi mendek ndi mendek abok eeriyak ti, op aret kwe, apit op eeppinaniyak nduk, eekwi ti lek~o.
46010024	Kit kinobaalombok mban eekko'net nogo logorak lek~o. Ata, kinoreewi inikilom mbaruwak nduk inom aret eeppiinet nogo logonip~o.
46010025	-
46010026	"Nggween inom, yi mendek ndi mendek nggween paga wonogwe nogo abok aret inom, at Ala mban unde aret~o," yinuk, liiru mbanak wonage me, kit wam mbanak pasar paga onggo kumbunuk, alom kobak logonet, ugun nonggo logorak op aret~o.
46010027	It aap abet mbaka'lek mendek nen kinom mbi noorak nduk, wiigirage kenok, kinom na noorak mbakwi kiinok, larogo wokkirogwe nogo, "An op namun ilik, lek a?" mbaka'lek kagak ugun aret nonggo logorak op aret kwe,
46010028	-
46010029	aap alik ambi nen, "Yi kugi ake nggomoorak larak~o," yinuk, yokkirage kenok perak, kit ugun noorak op aret kwe, at yokkirage nogo nen, "An op namun ilik, lek a?" iniki aaninggin kenok, yokkirage me, at ake nen noorak lek mbo puurak aret~o. Mbo puurak op aret kwe, kit ando nen, "An ugun noorak op mbake neegak, at ambi noorak paga nonggop nduk mage yo'nirage,
46010030	ndi, an nobaalombok Ala, Wa, yinuk, nengge neegak, it aakumi nonggop nduk, nabok mbanggwi, eeko agaarik~o," yinuk, yogwe kiigirak me, noreewi~o.
46010031	Kinambi nunggwi, kinagi nunggwi, yi eekak ndi eekak abok aret eeko logonet, Ala endage tiyappuurak nduk mban eeko logonip~o.
46010032	-
46010033	An aakumi inale'nggen mbaruwak nduk, inake yi eekak ndi eekak eeke logonet, an obeelom logokit mba'nuk, eekkolage lek~o. Ata, Ala nen it inagap ndaruwak nduk, obeelom eeppiinet nage minggirak nogo ndak-ndak, kit togon, it Yakuri mendek inom, Yunani mendek inom, Ala apuri yi awi ndi awi kuwak eerit nogo menggaarak abok aret eeppiinet nogo logonet, non mbanogo piyookwak, liippunuk, eeppiinet nogo logonip~o.
46011001	At Keritut eeke menggerak an liippunuk, eeke minggirak pogom, kit nen an eeke nogo liippaninuk eeko logonip~o.
46011002	Kit nen kulinik-kalinik noba aberak logonet, yi wone ndi wone yokkirage nagagirak nogo, liippunuk eerit nogwe me, "Kit iya lombok," kinombake agarik~o.
46011003	At Ala abu'me ti, Keritut. Ndi, Keritut abu'me ti, aap. Ndi, aap inabu'me ti, kumi, togop aret monggoorak me, wone ti, liippubagip nduk, yokkiragi.
46011004	Togop me, nit Ala apuri kuwak eeppunuk, ninabetagi yirik kagak tamban eekwi, Ala wone yorogwe, eekwi niinok, nit ninirimbaga wonage Keritut nogo aret enggali eerogo pogo monggoorak me, nggoorogo punuk, eeko logowok~o.
46011005	Ndi, it kumi nogo nen inayum inomba nggoorak logonet, tamban eekwi, Ala wone yorogwe, eekwi iinok ti, we inagap mbelanak negen logonet eekwi me, it inirimbaga wonogwe inogonggelomini nogo inenggali eeppiigo menggerak me, inayum inomba langgunik logonet, eeko logowak~o.
46011006	It kumi inayum inomba langguniyak ineebi mbakwi kenok, it ineeruwak mbanogo pogo logowak~o. Ndi, it ineeruwak mbanggwi, inanobak puluk ko eerogo pugwi, eeremenggerak paga inenggali mbakwi kenok, inayum inomba langgunik logonet, tamban eeko logowak~o.
46011007	-
46011009	Ala nen aap ti, kumi inake wakkoolik~o. Kumi ti, aap inake wakkagagerak me, aap inalom ti, kumi lek~o. It kumi inalom ti, aap aret me, inayum langgunik logonet, inogonggelomini inabu'me tebe yinuk, inayuk wuko logowak~o. Ndi, aap perak, Ala nen, "An tiyappanugo logowak~o," yinuk, at etenggen pogom aret wakkagagerak me, aap ti, Ala abu'me tebe yinuk, inabetagi nggoorogo punuk, tamban eeko logowak~o.
46011010	Togop me, malayikat nogo nen it kumi liippiigwi me, aap inayuk wuko menggaarak iyaawak nduk, inayum inomba langgunik aret logowak~o.
46011011	-
46011012	Yi mendek ndi mendek wo'nirage menggerak alom ti, Ala aret~o. Ndi, it kumi inalom ti, aap aret kwe, it aap perak, kumi nen aret ndaganako menggaarak me, it kumi lek nen it aap wigannariyak lek~o. Ndi, it aap lek nen it kumi kunduk wigannariyak lek mban me, ninowe ninom kunik me, kumi aap ndak-ndak aret wonogo monggoorak~o.
46011013	Togop me, tamban nggwok paga eeko logonet, it kumi inayum nggoorogo punuk, tamban eeriyak op mbakop? Kit nen mban kiniki kooninip.
46011014	-
46011015	Ndi, it kumi nogo inanobak naberak logowak nduk, ineeruwak wogoragagerak me, ineeruwak nggorek kenok, "Nineeruwak nggorek ti, op aret kogo," yinuk, inale'nggen mbako menggaarak nogo lek a? Ndi, nit aap nen, "Nineeruwak nggorek kenok, ninobam lek~o," yinuk, mbaniyak ee'ninake menggerak nogo lek a?
46011016	Ti eekwi nogo paga it aap ando kinenggela'me nen, "Yogop eeriyak lek~o," yinuk, inoone nabenak mban yogwe iinok, "Nit yime inom, it Ala apuri ando yi awi ndi awi kuwak eerit nogo menggaarak inom, alik eekulik ti mban aret eeko monggoorak~o," yinuk, yoraanip~o.
46011017	Noreewi~o. Kit kuwak eeri wogo nogootik, "Obeelom eekwi lek, maluk eekwi~o," yinuk, yogwe konenggirak me, an wone yi yokkiraakit mbakirak nogo ti, wogoppinagage logonet, yokkiraagin lek~o. Mbekkirage negen logonet aret yokkiraagin~o.
46011018	Wone aa'nduk koonogo yokkiraakit mbakirak nogo yi~o. Kit Ala apuri kuwak eeko monggotak nogo, kuwak eeri wogo logonet, kit-kit aret ogoorik-ogoorak eekkologwe nogo naruk konengge nagarik, "Yi abet aret yogwe ilik?" mbakirak~o.
46011019	Kit wone-wone yogo logonetak lek en, taani nen wone liippunuk agan nugwi nogo, alom kin a'netak lek kwe, wone-wone yogo monggotak nogo paga alom kenom aga~o.
46011020	-
46011021	Kit kuwak eeppunuk, kinambi kinalitak lombok nonggo logonet, it ando nengga'lek abu wonogwe iigak, kit ando mban tiyaaket nunggwi, ndi, amburu nenok, kumili-kumili agan nugwi, eekwi konenggirak me, ninowe ambi inom, amburu inom, abe noorak nduk, kuwak eekwi lek ugun-ugun eeriyak nduk kuwak eekwi kiigi~o.
46011022	Wologwe! Kinagi-kinambi nonggo logorak kinawi wurik lek kenok, Ala awi wurik me ugun-ugun eeri unggwogo ogotik? Ndi, Ala apuri kuwak eeko menggaarak meek eerogo piigo logonet, it inamendek lek nogo inenggali kaawak nduk, eeginakwi lek mba'nuk yogo ogotik? Kit togop aret eekwi me, an nonggop yokkira? "Kit op aret eekwi~o," yinuk, yokkiroorak mbakop? Mondok lek~o.
46011023	At ninowe nen eeko logorak yo'nereegerak wagangge nagagirik, yokkiragagirak nogo eebe yi aret. At ninowe Yetut waruwok nduk awo pigagangga'lek iigak, ne ti eyom oonikiya paga roti mbi eenggime wagangge nagagerik,
46011024	"Ala wa," yinuk, karerogo wogorage logonet, "Yi an neebe negen aret me, kit kinake aret~o. An noba abeko logonet, nonggo logonip~o," yinuk, yorage mbareegi, nunggugwaarak.
46011025	Nonggo nogogwaarik, ti'nuk, mbi weelek larak ando nenok, amburu toolak togop aret eenggime wagangge nagagerik, "Ala nen kinom lambumbinagarak wone ngget mendek koonogo pereegerak nawoneninu kilikkirage nogo, kit abet mbarubagip nduk, namiya kinake wundigin amburu toolak yi kwak aret me, kiniki noba abeko logonet, nonggo logonip~o," yinuk, wogorage mbareegi, nunggugwaarak.
46011026	Nit Yetut woroorak tokkogo logonet, roti inom, amburu toolak inom, ne ambi nenggak, ne ambi nenggak eeko logonet, "Ninowe Yetut ninake abet aret kambeegerak kagi," yinuk, nggwok paga paganggo monggoorak.
46011027	Togop me, kit ninowe ambi larak inom, amburu toolak inom, we wuppagagi-perambagagi nunggwi kiinok, ninowe eebe inom, amiya inom, maluk eerogo pogo logonet, aret nonggo monggotak kiigo~o.
46011028	Kit aa'nduk kiniki liippatinuk, mbi inom, amburu inom, nonggo logorak ti op~o.
46011029	"Yi ninowe eebe negen aret~o," yinuk, liippega'lek logonet, kit mbi inom, amburu inom, nunggwi kiinok perak, "Ala anini ninoba pinanuwak," mba'nuk, nonggo monggotak kiigi~o.
46011030	Kit ti eekwi paga kinenggela'me time kineebe ambik andi eekkinake, ndeyak eerogo pinagage, ndi, ando kambit nogwe, eeko ogotik~o.
46011031	Nit aa'nduk, niniki liippatinuk maluk paganggwi niinok, peebi Ala nen nit eekwi liippinaninuk, maluk onggo ninoba pinanigin lek~o.
46011032	Peebi it aakumi nggween paga mendek abok aret inowak loonogo maluk onggo inoba piige logonet, nit ninom ninoba pinanege kero, yogondak at ninowe nen nit eekwi liippinaninuk, niniki koonogo pinanege menggerak.
46011033	Togop me, noreewi~o. Mbi amburu noorak nduk, kuwak eeri wogwe kiinok, ambugwi aret nabagip nduk, toginako logonip~o.
46011034	Ndi, mbi-amburu noorak nduk, kuwak eeko logonet, mbi abu nen ndonggok togon nunggwi kiinok, Ala nen maluk eerogo pinagage kero, kinambi weelek kiname nen mondok ndonggok togon nenok, wogo logonu~o. Wone ando ti, an pekkiya wage logominggirik, ninom logonet, yokkiraagin~o.
46012001	Noreewi~o. Aberiniki nen ninalitak lombok unde eeppinanege menggerak nogo, kit kineenggo'lek wonogwe kiyo, yokkira~o.
46012002	Kit aa'nduk, Ala wone konengga'lek wonogo logonet, kugiwak nebet-ndalok ariilik mendek kagak, "Ndogop yo'nirage kogo," yinuk, mugurok nogo nogogutak nogo, kineenu aret~o.
46012003	Ala Aberiniki kinikime wonage logonet, "Kat Yetut yi, kugi pulunogo pagagi~o," yinuk, yoriyak op mbakop? Ndi, Aberiniki kinikime lek logonet, "Kat Yetut nowe aret~o," yinuk, yoriyak op mbakop? Togop yoriyak mondok meek me, kineenu logobagip nduk, yokkiragi.
46012004	Aberiniki nen ninalitak lombok unde eeppinanege menggerak nogo ti, ambik wonage kwe, at eebe perak, ambit nen aret tumbu'nirage menggerak.
46012005	Ndi, nit Ala eyabu eeko monggoorak ti, alitak lombok wonage kwe, ninowe eebe ambit aret ake eeko monggoorak.
46012006	Ndi, eerit nogo monggoorak nogo ti, ninalitak lombok eerit nogo monggoorak kwe, Ala eebe ambit nen mban eeppinanit nage kagak eerit nogo monggoorak.
46012007	Aberiniki nen nit-nit mban obeelom eekko'net nogo logowok nduk, ninalitak lombok unde eeppinangge menggerak me, eerit nogo logonet, unde eeppinangge nogo, yelok aret kogo logogun~o.
46012008	Aberiniki ambit nogo nen aap ambi iniki warak logonet, wone koonogo yorage logowak nduk, unde eeppege, ambi, yi wone ndi wone alom neenu a'nuk, liirogon yorage logowak nduk, unde eeppege,
46012009	ambi, abet mba'nuk eeke logowak nduk, unde eeppege, ambi, aakumi andi iinok, obeelom eeginake logowak nduk, unde eeppege,
46012010	ambi, eerubok mendek eerit nage logowak nduk, unde eeppege, ambi, Ala wone yorage logowak nduk, unde eeppege, ambi, aakumi nen wone agan nugwi nogo abok aret, "Yi abet agan nugwi ilik, pilit agan nugwi a?" yinuk, yelok kage logowak nduk, unde eeppege, ambi, aakumi inoone nineenggo'lek kwe, lalin negen taati aret woppunuk, it inoone paga lombok yorage logowak nduk, unde eeppege, ndi, ambi, at ambi ari kagak, "Togop yigi~o," yinuk, abut laganogo yorage logowak nduk, unde eeppege, eeke menggerak~o.
46012011	Ti eeppinanege menggerak abok aret at Aberiniki eebe alik ambit nen at iniki mbaketak ndak-ndak aret ninalitak lombok unde eeppinanege menggerak.
46012012	Nineenggi-niniyok yeregerak-peregerak ti, ambik aret wonage kwe, nineebe ambit aret wonage ti kokwak, Keritut eebe ambit aret kwe, at eenggi-iyok negen nit apit aret ogoorik~o.
46012013	Togop me, nit Yakuri mendek inom, kit endekem mendek inom, kit aakumi inayeloman inom, inayeloman lek we wondet aago wonogwe inom, Aberiniki nogo paga nen nit abok aret nineebe ambit kumbinaneegerak me, niyo eneeri ambit nonggo monggo kwak, at Aberiniki eebe ambiret aret nit abok ninikime mambinaneegerak.
46012014	Togop me, nineebe alik mban wonage lek~o. Nineenggi-niniyok yeregerak-peregerak abok aret nineebe ambit paga mban kunik wonage~o.
46012015	Ti kenok, wone ogut wakkagak ambi yokkira~o. Aap ambi iyok nen ari logonet, "An ti, at eenggi mendek lek me, at eebe paga kunik lek aret agarik~o," ari kenok, at eebe paga kunik lek abet aret mbakop?
46012016	Ndi, aruk nen ari logonet, "An nogo, at enegen mendek lek me, at eebe paga kunik lek aret agarik~o," ari kenok, at eebe paga kunik lek abet aret mbakop?
46012017	Nineebe abok tigitogon ti, ninigen mban ogobakkigi'netak en nonggop togon ninaruk konenggo logonetak mbakop? Ndi, nineebe abok tigitogon ti, ninaruk mban ogobakkigi'netak en, nonggop togon yi mendek ndi mendek obari kogo logonetak mbakop? Togop logorak meek~o.
46012018	At Ala nen iniki koombege nagagerik, nineenggi-niniyok yeregerak-peregerak alitik-alitak ninanobak me nen ndegen-ndegen aret kumbinanit ogu niniyok me wambi nagagerak.
46012019	Nit nineenggi-niniyok yeregerak-peregerak mban logonetak en, nano paga kunik logonetak mbakop?
46012020	Lek~o. Nineenggi-niniyok yeregerak-peregerak ti, ambik aret kwe, nineebe ambit ti paga aret kunik menggerak~o.
46012021	Ti kenok, ninigen nogo nen nineenggi yoge logonet, "Kat nen ambi ee'naburak lek me, neebi~o," yoge, ndi, ninanobak nen niniyok yoge logonet, "Kat nen ambi ee'naburak lek me, neebi~o," yinuk, yoge, eeriyak op mbakop? Togop yuurak lek~o, noreewi.
46012022	Nit nineebe iya, ndi, nineenggi-niniyok yeregerak-peregerak nogo ti, meek mbakwi kwe, lek kenok, nineebe alik nen eeke logorak meek me, ti abu iya lombok aret~o.
46012023	-
46012025	Nit nineenggi-niniyok yeregerak-peregerak ando etenggen abe amuni mbanak kenok, liippugwi lek kwe, ando etenggen maluk kenok, ogobakkigirogo pugwi, ando ninenggali arukwak nduk, nobakkologwe, eeko monggoorak. Nineenggi-niniyok ambi nen ambi abuwa eekak, ambi nen ambi abuwa eekak, eeko logowok nduk, at Ala nen nineebe ogobakkigirogo pinanege logonet, nineenggi-niniyok ogoorik-ogoorak logokwak, etenggen maluk kenok, ogobakkigikkologo logowok nduk, koonogo pinaneegerak.
46012026	Togop aret kooneegerak me, kineenggi ambiriluk mbanggirage kenok, kineebe abok aret andi eek-kinake, ndi, kinetenggen abe me, aakumi nen, "Wi," kirogwe iinok, kineebe abok aret ale'nggen mbake, eeke menggerak.
46012027	Ti ndak-ndak, kit kineebe lambuk togon ti, Keritut eebe aret. Ndi, kit kinalitak lombok ti, Keritut eenggi-iyok aret ogotik~o.
46012028	Ndi, Ala nen at apuri kuwak eeko menggaarak inenggela'me nen aa'nduk nappiigak mendek leenogo piige, ti'nuk, it inabu'me Ala wone yorogo menggaarak mendek mippiige, ndi, it inabu'me Ala wone mamunirogo menggaarak mendek mippiige, ndi, it inabu'me eerubok mendek eekwi, aakumi andi obeelom eeginakwi, yeenggwaarogwe, wone koonogo piigwi, inoone lombok lalin yogwe, inalitak lombok eerit nogo logowak nduk, unde agago piinok mippiyareegerak me,
46012029	it abok aret nappiigak mendek logowak nduk, mippiyareegerak mbakop? It abok aret Ala wone yorogo logowak nduk, mippiyareegerak mbakop? It abok mamunggak logowak nduk leenogo piyareegerak mbakop? Ndi, it abok eerubok mendek eeko logowak nduk, kooneegerak mbakop?
46012030	It abok andi kenok obeelom eeginako logowak nduk, yoragagerak mbakop? It abok inoone lalin yogo logowak nduk, mippiyareegerak mbakop? Ndi, it abok aret inoone yogwe nogo, "Togop yigi~o," yinuk, yorogo logowak nduk, wogoragagerak mbakop?
46012031	Lek~o, noreewi. Ala nen ninalitak lombok unde eeppinaneegerak me, yokkiragi~o. "Ala nen aa'nduk iya lombok unde eeppiyareegerak nogo mendek unde eeppinagawak nduk, at yogo logonip~o," yinuk, yokkirage kwe, wone ambi mondok iya lombok eeko logorak nogo yokkira~o.
46013001	An aakumi inoone amburu ndik-ndik yogo mengga kwak ari, malayikat mendek inoone ari, eeke minggirak kwe, aakumi inabuwa mbaka'lek logonet ari neenok, an niyowak toolak lek me, oone lobale nggwok mban ari menggerak ndak-ndak aret ari minggirak kagi~o.
46013002	An Ala wone yorage logokit nduk, unde eeppanege, yi wone ndi wone alom neenu a'nuk, liirogon yorage, wone kote kumaarak mendek abok yelok kage, niniki abet mbake logonet, "Puut yi keebe tayo yu~o," yinuk, yoge neenok, tayo yi nage kage, eeke minggirak kwe, aakumi inabuwa mbaka'lek logonet eeke neenok perak, we aanom warogo aret eeke minggirak kagi~o.
46013003	An nen nayi mendek ndi mendek abok it aap ineenggi lek nogo tumburirage, ndi, Ala wone yorage paga onggo nggwok kolaakit mba'nuk, "Neebe inom noorogo kani kumbaninip~o," yorage, eeriminggirak kwe, aakumi inabuwa mbaka'lek logonet, eeriminggirak me, onggo an ambi kolaagin mondok lek aret~o.
46013004	It aakumi inabuwa mbako logonet eekwi nogo ti, wone onggo mbet-mbet yoraga'lek puk wonogwe, inobaabut yanggonak wonogwe, eeko menggaarak. Ti eeko logonet neebi-keebi yogwe, iniki wogoppakwi, an iya mbakwi,
46013005	inenggali lek eerit nugwi, nit mban obeelom eekkolaawok mbarit nugwi, inanini mbet-mbet wungge, maluk eeppiigwi nogo inikime abekwi, eerit nugwi ti mendek it aakumi inabuwa mbako menggaarak nogo ti, togop eekulik~o.
46013006	It aakumi inabuwa mbako logonet, eekwi ti, maluk eeriyak inikilom mbakulik~o. Ata, Ala ari menggerak eerit noorak mban inikilom mbako menggaarak.
46013007	It maluk eeppiigwi iigak kwe, inabuwa mbakwi, it-it yogo logonet, ambi ari kenok abet ari mbakak eekwi, iniki lunik nogo mondok eerigin aret mbakwi, eerulik kagak, "Eekotak~o," yinuk, inoone inoba piigwi iigak, yanggo yinuk, waganggwi, eekwi nogo ti, lek aga'lek mondok kundugu tit aret eeko menggaarak.
46013008	Ala nen yorage kagak yorogwe, inoone lalin woppunuk yorogwe, yi wone ndi wone alom ineenu ogwe, eekwi ti, lek arigin aret kwe, aakumi inabuwa mba'nuk, eeppiinet nugwi ti perak, lek arigin lek mondok aret logogin~o.
46013009	Yogondak Ala wone mbuuluk yelok kogo logonet, yorogo monggoorak kwe,
46013010	peebi abu obeelom eeppinaniyak eyom panggoni wage kenok perak, yogondak mbuuluk yelok kenok yorogwe nogo, lek age logonet, abok aret nineenu arugun~o.
46013011	An elege mbuuluk wonage logonet, it elege-aabologwe inoone yogwe pogom an noone ari, it eeriyak inikilom mbakwi nogo an togop aret mbake, iniki koonggwi nogo ndak-ndak an niniki koongge, eeke nagagirak kwe, an niniki warak age nagagirik perak, it elege-aabologwe inobaabut pogom logonet eeke nagagirak nogo mbo pereegirak~o.
46013012	Nit yogondak wukagi yumaak me, pekkogo logonet, ninetenggen liirogon kogolik nogo pogom, ninogoba etenggen agalu'mok mban kogo monggoorak kwe, peebi at eebe ninom lambumbunuk perak, at etenggen ninigen lik togon aret kaagun~o. Yogondak an ando mban neenu minggirak kwe, at nen an eeke minggirak abok aret liippaninuk eenu menggerak nogo ndak-ndak, an peebi at eeke nogo abok neenu arigin~o.
46013013	Ti kenok, niniki abet mbakwi inom, niniki lunik wonogwe inom, aakumi inabuwa mbakwi inom, wone alom kenagan wonage kwe, nabuwa-kabuwa mbakwi ti perak, mondok tiyanak aret wonage agaarik~o.
46014001	Ti kenok, nabuwa-kabuwa eeko logorak wone ti, kinengga lolo punuk, eeko logonip~o. "Ala eyabu eeko logorak unde eeppinanuwak lak ao," yinuk, at yogo logonet, Ala wone yorogo logorak inom aret unde eeppinagawak nduk, at yogo logonip~o.
46014002	It aakumi inoone lalin yogo menggaarak nogo ti, aakumi konengga'lek iigak yogo menggaarak me, aakumi inaruk koneniyak nduk yorogwe lek~o. Ata, Aberiniki it inikime lik yi unggwage kenok, wone kote mendek yogo menggaarak me, at Ala aruk koneniyak nduk, yogo menggaarak~o.
46014003	Ndi, it aap Ala wone yorogo menggaarak nogo nen perak, aakumi iniki kole eerogo piigwi, inaruk wakwi, iniki eyak wappiigwi, eeko menggaarak.
46014004	It aap wone lalin yogo menggaarak nogo ti, it inalik iniki eyak wakkologo logowok nduk, yogo menggaarak kwe, it aap ninogoba Ala wone yorogo menggaarak nogo perak, Ala apuri kuwak eerak abok iniki kole eerogo piyaawok nduk, yorogo menggaarak.
46014005	Kit abok nen wone lalin negen woppunuk, yorogo logorak ti, an nen op aret mbake kwe, an nen, "Ao," mbake ambi ti, "It abok nen Ala wone yorogo logowak lak, ao," kinombake minggirak. Inoone lalin yogo menggaarak nogo ti, it Ala apuri kuwak eerak abok iniki kole aruwak nduk, "Togop yigi," yinuk, yoroorak ambi lek kagak, yogo menggaarak ti, meek~o. It Ala wone konenggwi iigak yorogo menggaarak ti perak iya~o.
46014006	Togop me, noreewi~o. An kinowagam wage logominggirik, Ala nen paganogo yo'nege kagak, yokkirage, wone ambi liirogon kineenu eeppinagage, Ala wone yokkirage, wone mamunggirage, eeka'lek logonet, we noone lalin aret woppunuk, yokkiroorak mban kinowagam wage neenok, "Yi nano eeppinanikit nduk wagarak?" nombarumunggup nogo lek a?
46014007	Ti ndak-ndak nggawiiwak a, nggitat a, eeke logonet, oone abe lek kagak we lobale mban eeke kenok, aakumi nen, "Wone ti mendek ari," yinuk, nonggop negen liippuurak mbakop?
46014008	It aakumi wim namburuwok nduk, oone nggwok eeka trompet nogo oone pu abe eeka'lek kenok, nonggop togon it aap wim namburiyak nogo, inawuri lombok kuwak eeri woraagun mbakop?
46014009	Ti kokwak, kit kinoone we lalin yogo monggotak nogo liirogon yorogwe lek kiinok, kit yogwe nogo taani nen, "Wone ti aret yigi," yinuk, lik togon konenugun mbakop? Kit yogo monggotak ti, kineenggo'lek kagak, we aanom warogo nineenu mbaruwak agan nugwi kiigi~o.
46014010	Ndi, o nggween paga yime it aakumi inoone alitak lombok ambik yogo menggaarak kwe, wone yogwe konenggulik mendek yime ambi wonage mondok lek~o.
46014011	It wone yogwe iigak, an konengga'lek kenok, it nen, "Aap yi, nggiru nen ari," nombakwi, ndi, an nen kunduk, "Aap alik mendek inoone yogwe," inombake, eerugun~o.
46014012	Kit nen, "Ala eyabu eeko logowok nduk, ambi unde eeppanuwak lak ao," yinuk, mbakwi kiinok, Ala apuri kuwak eeko menggaarak nogo, iniki kole eeppiyoorak nogo mendek unde eeppinagawak nduk, at yogo logonip~o.
46014013	-
46014014	An ambi inoone lalin negen woppunuk, tamban eeke kenok, niniki nen abet aret eerigin kwe, "Ngge nduk yagarak," an kobak arigin~o. Togop me, aap ambit-ambi inoone lalin negen woppunuk, ari menggerak nogo nen, "An ari logominggirik, aakumi kobak ogwe iyo, Ti togop nduk yigi~o," yinuk, yorage logowak nduk, tamban eeke logowak~o.
46014015	Ti kenok, an tamban nonggop eeke logi~o? An tamban eeke kenok, niniki kobak logonet, ambi inoone lalin negen woppunuk, eerigin lek~o. Niniki nen abeppunuk, aakumi inoone paga aret eeke logogin~o. Ndi, ndawi ari kenok, aakumi inoone lalin negen woppunuk kobak logonet ari logogin lek mban. Niniki koombunuk nen aakumi inoone yogo menggaarak nogo paga kin aret ari logogin~o.
46014016	Ala alut eeko logonet, kiniki abe'naga'lek kagak, ambi inoone lalin negen woppunuk, tamban eekwi kiinok, it aakumi ando kinom kuwak eeppunuk, tamban eekwi nogo, kat ari it kobak ariyak me, nonggop togon, "Abet aret yigi~o," yinuk, "Amin," yugun mbakop?
46014017	Kit nen Ala mondok iya tit wogoppugwi kwe, it ando kobak iigak, ambi inoone lalin negen woppunuk, yogwe me, kit nen obeelom ambi eeppiyaamunggup lek aret kiigi~o.
46014018	Kit ambitak, ambi inoone lalin negen woppunuk, yogo monggotak ti, iya negen kwe, an perak, Ala wogoppege logonet, yi aap ndi aap inoone woppunuk ari minggirak me, an ari minggirak ti, iya lombok mbake logonet, "Ala wa," yoge minggirak.
46014019	Ala apuri kuwak eerak inenggela'me logonet, an ambi inoone lalin negen woppunuk, ari neenok, koneniyak lek me, an ambi inoone lalin negen woppunuk, noone nggorek mban yoroorak neebi~o. Ata, it liippuwak nduk, it inoone paga wone kuwagaluk yoroorak ti perak, op aret mbake minggirak~o.
46014020	Noreewi~o. Kit kiniki koonggwi nogo ti, it wologwe-mbuulogwe iniki koonggo mengga kwak, kiniki togop koonggo logogup~o. Ata, it aap iniki warak koonggo menggaarak pogom koonggo logonip~o. Maluk eeriyak eekkinake kero, elege awo ngget ndarak maluk ineenggo'lek menggaarak nogo pogom, kit togop aret logonip~o.
46014021	Ala nen ari logonet, "It aap inambik nen, inoone alik mendek nen, Napuri yi, an noone yoraawak nduk, nappiya woraminggirak kwe, Noone yorogwe nogo it liirogon inaruk konenugun lek~o," yinuk, yereegerak Muta liiru mbaneegerak wonage me,
46014022	it aakumi wone lalin yogwe nogo, it abet mbakwi mendek inake lek~o. It iniki abet mbaka'lek mendek nen ineenu agak ti, liippunuk, abet mbaruwak nduk, yogo menggaarak kagi~o. Ndi, it Ala wone yorogo logowak nduk, unde eeppiyareegerak nogo ti, it abet mbaka'lek mendek inake lek~o. Ata, it abet mbakwi mendek liippatuwak nduk aret yorogo menggaarak.
46014023	Togop me, it Ala apuri kuwak eeko menggaarak nogo abok ambit me kuwak eeppunuk, it abok nen inoone alitik-alitak lalin negen woppunuk, yogwe iinok, it aakumi weelek mendek a, Ala wone abet mbaka'lek mendek a, wogo logomenggaarik, it nen, "Aap yi, kumili negen agan nugwi kiraap," yinuk, yogo logogun lek mbakop?
46014024	-
46014025	Yogo logogun aret kwe, kit abok aret Ala wone yogwe me, it wogwe iinok perak, kit Ala wone yorogo logonet, wone it inikime kote kumaarak menggerak abok aret paganogo tena'me yorogwe konenggo logomenggaarik, "Wone ti, nit niinok, yo'nirogwe iigo~o," yinuk, iniki ndoguk togon wakkologo logonet, Ala abu'me tebe yinuk, Ala wogoppogo logonet, "Ao, Ala kinom abet aret wonogwe kiigo~o," yinuk, yokkiraagun lek mbakop?
46014026	Ti kenok, nit nonggop yuwok~o, noreewi. Kit kuwak eeppunuk logonet, aap ambi nen ndawi tiyaniyak mbake kenok tiyangge, ambi nen wone ambi mamuniroorak mbake kenok mamunirage, ambi Ala nen paganogo yoge kagak, yoroorak mbake kenok yorage, ambi, it ambi inoone lalin negen woppunuk, yoroorak mbake kenok yorage, ambi, "Togop yigi~o," yinuk, abut laganogo yoroorak mbake kenok yorage, yi eeriyak ndi eeriyak ti abok aret eeko logonet, it Ala apuri iniki nu'lek eerogo piyoorak kenok mban eeko logonip~o.
46014027	Kinoone lalin yogwe nogo ti, kit kineebe ambik nen yuurak lek~o. Ata, kineebe mbere a, kenagan a, nen mban yogo logonet, peebi-aa'nduk yogwe kiigak, at ambi nen wone ari kenok, at ambi nen, "Yogop yigi," yinuk, abut laganogo yokkiragak eeko logowak~o.
46014028	Ndi, aap, "Yogop yigi~o," yinuk, abut laganogo yokkiroorak Ala apuri kuwak eerak kinenggela'me time ineebe lek iinok ti, it lalin negen yogwe nogo inoone lek, puk aret logonet, inikime nen mban yogwe, Ala yogwi, eeko logowak~o.
46014029	It aap Ala wone liippunuk yorogo menggaarak nogo ineebe mbere a, kenagan a, nen aret wone yokkirogo logowak~o. Ndi, yokkirogwe iigak, kit ando nen, "Wone yo'nirogwe ti, abet aret yigi?" yinuk, liippako logomunggup~o.
46014030	It yokkirogwe iigak, aap alik ambi kwi'ndak wonage me, Aberiniki inikime lik ari logonet, paganogo yoge kagak yuurak mbake kenok, aa'nduk ari logomenggerak nogo, puk age kagak yokkiroorak op aret~o.
46014031	Kit abok aret mamunggologwe, abok aret kiniki eyak wat-wat yogwe, eeko logobagip nduk, Ala wone peebi-aa'nduk ndegen-ndegen yorogo logorak ti obeelom aret.
46014032	-
46014033	Ala ti, naalop-kaalop eerogo piiga lek~o. Ata, iniki lambunik ale'nggen logorak eerogo piiga at aret me, it Ala wone yorogo menggaarak nogo yoroorak aganake kenok, tebeppunuk logonuk, at aa'nduk yorage nogo puk age kagak, yoroorak mbake nogo peebi yoragak eeko logorak op aret~o.
46014034	At Ala nen ari logonet, "It kumi ti, inoone yuurak lek~o. Aap inabu'me tebe yinuk, inoone konenggo logowak~o," yinuk, Muta yoreegerak liiru mbanak nogo ndak-ndak, it Ala apuri alik leenak yi awi ndi awi kuwak eeppunuk, eeko mengga kwak, kit togon, kuwak eeppunuk logonet, it kumi ti, inoone lek puk logowak~o.
46014035	Ala apuri kuwak aago inenggela'me logonet, kumi nen wone yorogwe iinok, inenggali eekkolookwak me, wone ambi it kobak eekwi iinok, nggwok paga kin wogiyoorak lek~o. Iname na'nuk, inogonggelomini kin wogiigwi iinok, yoroorak op~o.
46014036	"Ala nen wone iyaalok lombok nit aret yo'niragagerak me," yinuk, yogo ogotik ya? Kit mban kinake yokkiragagerak me nduk, yogo ogotik? Ti lek~o.
46014037	Kit ambi nen, "An Ala wone yorage logokit nduk, unde eeppaneegerak kagi," yinuk, mbake, ndi, ambi nen, "An eeke logokit nduk, Aberiniki nen, Yi aret, wo'nireegerak kagi," yinuk, mbake, eekwi nogo nen, "Wone yi ti, ninowe nen Pawulut yoge kagak mbanniragagerak kogo~o," yinuk, kiniki liippinip~o.
46014038	Aap ambi nen an wone yogondak liiru mbanggirage yi, "Woorak neebi~o," yinuk, taganogo mbo pege kenok, kit togon, at oone taganogo mbo pinip~o.
46014039	Togop me, noreewi~o. It aap inoone lalin yorogwe nogo, "Mage~o," yinuk, yoraagup~o. Ata, "Ala nen paganogo yo'nirage kagak, yorogo logorak unde eeppinanuwak lak ao," yinuk, mbako logonip.
46014040	Kit yi eekak ndi eekak eeko logonet, mondok liirogon mot-mot mban eeko logonip~o.
46015001	Noreewi~o. Yogondak an wone obeelom wone aa'nduk yokkiragagirak waganeegutak paga kiniki panggombunuk wonogwe nogo aberogo yokkira~o.
46015002	Yokkiragagirak nogo kit nen mondok nu'lek porogo logomonggotak kenok, wone ti paga kinagap ndarigin kwe, abet mbaka'lek logonet we aanom warogo waganeegutak kwa?
46015003	Togop me, an wone waganeegirak kit mondok iya mbarubagip nduk yokkirage nagagirak nogo eebe yi~o. Ala wone liiru mbanak ndak-ndak, nit maluk eekwi niinok, at Keritut ninake aret kambeegerak.
46015004	Kangge mbareegi, at eebe waganogo ndoome mambereegwaarak. Mambogo mbareegwa, Ala wone liiru mbanak ndak-ndak, nogo mbere yinuk, eenik agago mippereegerak.
46015005	Mippege mbareegi, at Yetut nen Kepat enegen kaawak nduk, eebe nikkage nagagerik, ti'nuk, peebi it Duabelas nogo inigen kaawak nduk, eebe nigiyareegerak.
46015006	Nogo nigiige nagagerik, ti'nuk, peebi nen ninoreewi ineebe ambik lima ratus aret ambit me kuwak eerak wonogome, inigen kaawak nduk, nigiyareegerak. It aakumi nigiyareegerak nogo ti, ando muk kambeegwaarak kwe, ando ambik kangga'lek awo ineenik wonogwe~o.
46015007	Nogo nigiige nagagerik, ti'nuk, Yakobut nikkage, ti'nuk, it nappiyareegerak nogo abok aret nigiige, eereegerak.
46015008	Ti eeke nagagerik, an nogo, elege nda'nariyak eyom awo kagak aberak lek me, nda'nogo mengga kwak, an togop aret aberak lek me, nenegen kaakit nduk, age yobok togon an aret ni'neyareegerak.
46015009	An o maan nen Ala apuri kuwak eerit nogo menggaarak nogo piyak-payak eeginabit nege nagagirak me, "Nappiigak mendek," yo'nogo logonetak lek kwe, an nogo, it aap nappiigak mendek inabu'me negen logokit nduk, leenogo paneegerak~o, obak!
46015010	Togop me, at Ala nabuwa mba'nuk, eeppaneegerak nogo paga yogondak nobaabut alik eerit nage neego ogotik~o. Ala nabuwa mba'nuk, eeppaneegerak nogo ti, we aanom warogo eeppanulik~o. It nappiigak ando nogo ti, we mbuuluk iya negen eeko nogogwaarak kwe, an perak, mondok iya lombok eeke nagagirak. Ti eeke nagagirak nogo ti, an nen ta lek~o. Ata, Ala nabuwa mba'nuk, eeppanege kagak, niniki aganggen kerek togon eeke nagagirak me yagi~o.
46015011	It eeko nogogwaarak paga ilik, an eeke nagagirak paga a, ti iya lek~o. Ata, nit abok yorogo monggoorak eebe yokkirogogurak kit abet mbareegutak ti perak, iya~o.
46015012	At Keritut nogo kambunuk nogo menggam nen eenik eerogo mippereegerak wone nit nen yokkirogwe niigak kwe, kit ando nen yogo logonet, "Aakumi kanggwi nogo ineenik arugun lek~o," yinuk, nonggop nduk yogo ogotik?
46015013	"Nit peebi kambunuk, nineenik arugun lek~o," yinuk, abet aret mbako logonetak en, at Keritut kunduk, kambunuk, eenik a'netak lek abet aret mbako logonetak~o.
46015014	Ndi, at Keritut kangge nagagerik, eenik a'netak lek nen, nit wone yokkirogo monggoorak nogo ti, we aanom warogo yiluk-yiluk negen yokkirogo logonetak me, kit kunduk, kiniki we aanom warogo abet mbareegurak mba'netak~o.
46015015	Ndi, it aakumi kanggwi nogo ineenik agago mippiyoorak abet aret logonetak lek nen, Ala nen Keritut mippulik kagak, "Lek~o, eenik agago mippereegerak~o," yinuk, yokkirogo nogogurak me, nit yogwe nogo pilit aret ninombako logonetak.
46015016	Ndi, it aakumi kambeegwaarak nogo, peebi ineenik eerogo mippiyaagin lek mbakwi kenok, at Keritut kangge nagagerik, eenik agagerak nogo eenik arulik mondok-mondok kambeegerak mbako logonetak.
46015017	Ndi, at Keritut eenik eerogo mippenetak lek en, kit kiniki abet mbakwi nogo ti, we aanom warogo abet mbako logonet, kinomaluk mondok kinoba luurik aret logonetak.
46015018	Ndi, at Keritut eenik a'netak lek en, it Keritut inom kunik logonet kambeegwaarak nogo kunduk, kobak aago aret logonetak.
46015019	Ndi, nit togon we nggween paga yayi nen mban Keritut obeelom eeppinanigin mba'nuk, niniki lunik wonogwe niinok, "Kit abet mbaka'lek mendek kinabuwa~o," yinuk, yorogo monggoorak kwe, it nen, "Kit perak, kinabuwa nggwok lombok mbakkologo logonip~o," yinuk, yo'nirogo logonetak.
46015020	Togop kwe, at Keritut kanggo menggam nen eenik agago mippulik ti lek~o. Mippereegerak aret me, anggen iyaalok mbanak pogom, it kanggo menggam nen iyaalok eenik agago mippereegerak nogo ti, at aret~o.
46015021	Aap ambi nen maluk eereegerak nogo paga nit abok aret kanggo monggoorak ti kokwak, aap ambi eereegerak nogo paga nit abok kanggo menggam nen nineenik eerogo mippinanigin~o.
46015022	Nit abok Aram ninom kunik logonet, kanggo monggoorak ti kwak, nit aakumi abok Keritut ninom kunik logonet kanggwi kenok perak, mondok nineenik logowok nduk, mippinanigin~o.
46015023	Ti eeke logonet, mondok peebi-aa'nduk mippinanigin~o. At Keritut ti, anggen iyaalok mbanak kwak aa'nduk eenik eerogo mippereegerak me, at peebi wage logomenggerik, apuri ninom kunik monggoorak nogo, abok aret nineenik eerogo mippinanigin~o.
46015024	-
46015025	Mippinanege kenok, o age yobok paga ariyak nogo aret ari woraagin me, at Ala nen, "It ninom ogoorak wonogwe nogo tebenogo piiga'lek kagak, Keritut mban tiyanak logowak~o," yinuk, kooneegerak me, yi kugi ndi kugi inom, aap yo'nggok aakumi inarum menggaarak inom, inayuk warak menggaarak inom, it Ala inom ogoorak menggaarak mendek abok aret tebenogo piige logomenggerik, nit at Ala abu'me logowok nduk, at apuri ee'ninabeegerak nogo mban wo'niren Ala abu'me pinani nagin~o.
46015026	Ala inom ogoorak wonogwe nogo lek eerogo piige logomenggerik, irip paga lombok ti, kanggwi alom nogo mondok lek eerogo pigin~o.
46015027	"Yi mendek ndi mendek abok aret at abu'me logowak nduk pereegindak~o," yinuk, yereegerak liiru mbanak me, at Ala nen, "Yi mendek ndi mendek," yereegerak nogo ti, at yi mendek ndi mendek Keritut abu'me pege logonet, "An neebe inom aret Keritut abu'me tebe yinuk, logokit," mba'nuk, yereegerak lek~o.
46015028	Ata, yi mendek ndi mendek inom, yi aakumi ndi aakumi inom, abok aret Ala nen tebenogo Keritut abu'me piige mbaremenggi, ti'nuk, Ala alik mban tiyanak logonet yi awi ndi awi at oone mban mondok endak warak logowak nduk, aput nen ari logonet, "Kat nogoba yi mendek ndi mendek nabu'me paneegindak nogo, yogondak an kapuluk kabu'me tebe yinuk, logi~o, yinuk, yo'nirigin," mba'nuk, yereegerak kogo~o.
46015029	It kanggaatak ineenik agago mippiyoorak lek kenok, it aap kanggaatak inobaane'me yiime wuppiigo menggaarak nogo ti, nonggop nduk wuppiigwi mbakop? It kambeegwaarak nogo ineenik agago mippiyaagin lek kenok, nonggop nduk it inowe-inawot kanggwi iinok, "Inobaane'me yiime wuppinanuwak~o," yinuk, yogo agaarik, mbakop?
46015030	Ndi, nit togon nonggop mbakop? Ala nen nineenik agago mippinanigin lek kenok, nit ko'lu-kii'me ninooriyak eekwi iigak, ninogogumbuk puk aret logorak mbakop?
46015031	Lek~o. "At kambuwak~o," yinuk, ko'lu-kii'me nooriyak eekwi iigak, nagabiti lek logonet, eeke minggirak kit pilit nombarugup~o. Ninowe Keritut Yetut kinom kunik logonet, eekwi paga an nale'nggen mbake logonet, Ala wogoppege kit abet aret nombako monggotak nogo kwak, "At kambuwak~o," yinuk, ko'lu-kii'me nooriyak eeko menggaarak abet aret nombako logobagip nduk, yokkiragi~o, noreewi.
46015032	Aakumi kanggwi ineenik agago mippiyoorak lek kenok, an o Epetut yime logonet, nggeewo anini warak aakumi nibininake menggi kwak, it aakumi ninom ndugwi pereegirak ti paga an nano koloorak nduk eereegirak mbakop? Lek me, "Nit ko'lu aret kambugun me, yogondak mban amele nenet nogo logowok~o," yinuk, mbako logonetak.
46015033	"Kit kinobaabut obeelom wonogwe nogo nen aakumi maluk eekwi kinom nugwi kiinok, kinom maluk eekkolaamunggup~o," yinuk, yogo menggaarak nogo ti, abet aret yogwe me, aakumi nen wone alik yokkirogo logonet, kinambokan laganggwi iyo, kiniki liippinip~o.
46015034	It ando kinenggela'me Ala wone ineenggo'lek iigak, kit maluk eekwi me, maluk eeko monggotak nogo mbo punuk, kiniki warak a'nip~o. Wone yokkirage yi, kit kinenggali arubagip nduk, yokkiragi~o.
46015035	Kit ando nen yogo logonet, "Nit kanggwi nogo nonggop negen agago mippinanigin mbakop? Nineebe ninetenggen nano ndak-ndak agago mippinanigin~o?" yinuk, yogwe kiigirak me, wologwe.
46015036	Kit aap wi negen yogwebok. Mbato awi yakootak agabolo nggonenogo pega'lek kagak, eebe mbilanggeelik nogo, kit kineenggo'lek a?
46015037	Kit yi mendek ndi mendek awi yako monggotak nogo yako logonet, eebe apit awi yakulik~o. Ata, mbato a, yi mendek ndi mendek alik mendek awi a, yako logonet, anggen ambitak menenogo yako monggotak kwe,
46015038	mbilanikit nduk eeke logonet, eebe-etenggen alitak lombok mbilangge menggerak nogo ti, Ala nen mban iniki koombunuk, eeppege menggerak~o.
46015039	Yi mendek ndi mendek amiya warak ogobakkigirik nogo ti, agabolo-enete ambit mban wonageelik~o. Aap agabolo alik, wam agabolo alik, towe agabolo alik, ikan agabolo alik, wonage menggerak.
46015040	Ndi, mbogut paga yi mendek ndi mendek ogobakkigirik nogo inetenggen alitik-alitak kogwe, nggween paga kunduk, yi mendek ndi mendek ogobakkigirik nogo inetenggen alitak lombok kogwe, eeko monggoorak.
46015041	Oonegen abinak alik, tut abinak alik, laaluguragan abinak alik, ndi, laaluguragan ando inabinak alitak lombok aret menggaarak.
46015042	It kanggwi ineenik agago mippiyoorak ti, togop aret~o. Nit nabelan-kabelan eerogo pinanege logonet, aakumi nen awi yako mengga kwak, nit ninagabolo pili ariyak mendek yi, nggonenogo mbo punuk, obaane'me mondok logorak mendek yirippinanege,
46015043	ninagabolo maan maluk mendek nogo, nggonenogo mbo punuk, obaane'me ngget amuni mbanak mendek yirippinanege, ndeyak nogo mendek mbo punuk, obaane'me omaawi mondok logorak mendek wo'nirage.
46015044	ndi, nggween paga mendek nogo mbo punuk, obaane'me ngget mendek Ala etenggen ndak-ndak ogobakkigirogo pinanege, eerogo pinaninuk mippinanigin~o. Nit nggween paga yime logowok nduk, ninagabolo nggween paga mendek yippinaneegerak nogo kwak, peebi mbogut paga logowok nduk, ninagabolo mbogut paga mendek yirippinanigin lek mbakop?
46015045	"Aap Aram aa'nduk nggween mendek wakkage mbareegi, eenik a'nuk oone warak agagerak~o," yinuk, liiru mbanak wonage. Ti'nuk, Aram peebi mbogut paga mendek nogo perak, aakumi ineenik aganake logowak nduk, nappi wagagerak.
46015046	Ti kenok, mbogut paga mendek aa'nduk woroolik~o. Ata, nggween paga mendek aa'nduk wakkage nagagerik, ti'nuk, peebi mbogut paga mendek nappi wagagerak kogo~o.
46015047	Aap aa'nduk wakkagagerak nogo ti, nggween mendek aret wakkagagerak. Ndi, aap peebi mendek nogo ti, at awi alom mbogut paga nen aret wagagerak.
46015048	Aap aa'nduk nggween mendek wakkagagerak me, nit at apuri nggween paga mendek aret ogoorik~o. Ndi, aap mbogut paga nen wagagerak nogo, apuri aganabeegerak kenok ti, mbogut paga mendek aret~o.
46015049	Nit aap nggween mendek wakkagagerak etenggen wonogo monggoorak nogo kokwak, peebi at mbogut paga nen wagagerak etenggen nogo pogom eerogo pinanigin~o.
46015050	Noreewi~o. An wone yokkirage yi, kit liippatubagip nduk, yokkira~o. Ninagabolo nggween mendek yi, nggonengga'lek kagak Ala abu'me piige menggim unggwi nagun lek~o. Ndi, ninagabolo pili ariyak mendek nggonenogo mbo pega'lek kagak, ninagabolo ngget mondok logorak mendek yippinanigin lek mban~o.
46015051	-
46015052	Noreewi~o. Wone kote kumaarak wone ambi yokkira~o. Nit abok aret kambugun lek~o. Nu'lek me o yabok telanggage kenok, ninogut nage menggi kwak, o irip paga kuli oone nggwok eeka trompet nogo oone pu eeke kenok, nit abok nineebe alik negen eerogo pinanigin~o. Oone nggwok eeka trompet nogo oone pu eeke mbaremenggi, it aakumi kambeegwaarak nogo mondok-mondok inabelan waawak nduk, ineenik eerogo mippiige logomenggerik, nit abok nineebe alik mendek eerogo pinanigin~o.
46015053	Ninagabolo pili ariyak mendek yi nogo ti, nggonenogo mbo punuk, obaane'me mondok logorak mendek yirippinanege, ndi, kanggwi mendek nogo mbo punuk, nineenik mondok logorak mendek eerogo pinanege, eerigin~o.
46015054	-
46015055	Ndi, ninagabolo pili ariyak mendek yi, nggonenogo mbo punuk, mondok logorak mendek yirippinanege logonet, kambuurak mendek nogo mbo punuk, nineenik nabelan-kabelan agago pinanigin~o. Ti eeppinanege kenok, "Aap ineegin tiyak ari menggi kwak, kanggwi alom nogo mondok lek eerogo pigin~o," yinuk, yereegerak liiru mbanak nogo a'me lik yigin~o. Ndi, "Kanggwi alom unde yi, wae. Kat ngge eekendak paga keegin tiyak yuurak mbaken? Kanggwi alom unde yi, wae. Aakumi inooriyak kamburu andiigwi nogo ngge~o?" yinuk, yogo logogun~o.
