48002021	Wone Muta yoreegerak nogo, nit eekwi paga, "Aap yi, oba lek~o," yinuk, obeelom eerogo pinaniyak op mba'netak en, Keritut we aanom warogo ninake kambeegerak mba'netak~o. An mbo pereegirak nogo obaane'me eeke paga Ala iniki kunik en eeppinaniyak kooneegerak nogo, meek eerogo pukwak, an togop eerigin abu lek~o, noreewi.
48003001	Kit Nggalatiya mendek yi wae. Yetut Keritut eyo karo-karo paga kambeegerak wone nogo, kumaarak lek mondok kin paga aret paganogo yokkirage nagagirak konenggo nogogutak kwe, yogondak ta nen kugi pulunogo pinagagerak kenok, kiniki lek kumili negen agan nugu ogotik?
48003002	Kit wone onggo ambi yo'nirubagip nduk, yokkiraakit mbakirak nogo yi~o. Wone Muta yoreegerak nogo, kit eerit nogo nogogutak paga Aberiniki waganeegutak ilik, obeelom wone konembunuk, abet mbareegutak paga waganeegutak a? Mbet yo'ninip nda!
48003003	Kit kiniki ngget ndakkinabeegerak nogo ti, Aberiniki nen aret kwe, yogondak wone Muta yoreegerak nogo eerit nogwe paga, "Niniki kole eekkolaawok~o," yinuk, eeko ogotik ya? Kit kiniki lek wi negen aret eekwi kiigi~o.
48003004	Kit wone waganeegutak nogo paga mondok alik negen piyak-payak eerogo pinagagwi iigak, kiniki yanggonak logonet, waganggo nogogutak nogo ti, we aanom warogo waganggo nogogutak ya? An togop mbake lek~o, noreewi.
48003005	At Ala nen Aberiniki wokkirage, ndi, kinenggela'me eerubok mendek eeke, eeke menggerak nogo ti, kit wone Muta yoreegerak nogo ndak-ndak eekwi paga eeke menggerak ilik, obeelom wone konembunuk abet mba'nuk, waganeegutak nogo paga eeke menggerak a? Kit yinip nda!
48003006	"At Abarakam iniki Ala oba panggombunuk, abet mbake mbareegi, Ala nen, Aap yi, iniki koonak abu obeelom aret kagi~o," yinuk, yereegerak liiru mbanak nogo liippinip~o.
48003007	Liiru mbanak ti ndak-ndak, it aakumi abet mbakwi nogo mban Abarakam ombowologwe wonogo menggaarak kogo~o.
48003008	Obeelom wone awo kenom ari waga'lek kagak, at Ala nen, "Yi aakumi ndi aakumi o nggween paga yime abok aret kat paga inale'nggen kogo logogun~o," yinuk, Abarakam yoreegerak ti paga it aap Ala nen yorage kagak yoraga nen, "Aakumi endekem mendek abet mbakwi iinok, Ala nen, It yi, inoba lek~o, yinuk, obeelom agago piyaagin," yelok kaawak nduk, Abarakam yoreegerak me, yelok kogo nogogwaarik, liiru mbaneegwaarak.
48003009	Togop me, at Abarakam abet mbake mbareegi, Ala ale'nggen at oba pereegerak nogo ndak-ndak, nit togon abet mbakwi niinok, Ala nen ale'nggen ninoba pinanigin aret~o.
48003010	Ala nen ari logonet, "Aap ambi eeko logorak wone yugu liiru mbanak yi, porogo logonet, liirogon eeka'lek kenok, at pulinik aret logowak~o," yinuk, yereegerak liiru mbanak ndak-ndak it aakumi nen, "Nit obeelom agago pinanuwak nduk, wone Muta yoreegerak nogo ndak-ndak aret eerit nogo logowok~o," yinuk, wone ti paga iniki panggombunuk eeremenggaarak kwe, ndak-ndak eeriyak meek kenok, pulinik aret me, kambit nogo logogun aret kogo~o.
48003011	"It aap iniki abe koonak nogo perak, abet mbakwi ti paga, ineenik aret logogun~o," yinuk, yereegerak liiru mbanak ti paga, wone Muta yoreegerak ndak-ndak eekwi paga Ala nen, "Aap yi, oba lek~o," yinuk, obeelom eerogo piyaagin lek nineenu aret~o.
48003012	Eeko logorak wone yugu liiru mbanak panggombunuk, "Obeelom eerogo pinaniyak~o," yinuk, eekkoloorak wone ti, abet mbakwi paga ee'ninaburak wone ndak-ndak lek alom alik aret kagak kwe, "Eeko logorak wone nogo it mondok porogo logonet, liirogon eerit nugwi paga ineenik aret logogun~o," yinuk, liiru mbanak me, aap ambi wone ti, abu ndak-ndak eeke kenok, at abet aret eenik logogin~o.
48003013	Ndi, Ala wone mbanak paga nen ari logonet, "Aap ambi warogo eebe eyo karo-karo paga tugunogo pugwi kenok ti, Ala nen pulunogo pege menggerak~o," yinuk, yereegerak liiru mbanak ndak-ndak, wone Muta yoreegerak kagak alik eeko nogogurak ti paga, nit togon kambuwok nduk, pulunik aret wonogogurak kwe, lek aruwak nduk, Keritut ninobaane'me pulunogo pege mbareegi, eyo karo-karo paga tugunogo pereegwaarak ti paga, ninonggo mbambunuk, wondet eerogo pinaneegerak wonogo ogoorik~o.
48003014	Ti eereegerak nogo ti, nit abok aret niniki abet mbakwi paga Ala nen "Aberiniki wokkiraagin~o," yinuk, abok yo'niragagerak nogo, waawok nduk, Ala nen, "Nale'nggen koba pagagin~o," yinuk, Abarakam yoreegerak nogo ti, Keritut Yetut eeremenggerak paga it aakumi endekem konenggulik mendek ninom niniki ale'nggen mbaruwok nduk, eereegerak kogo~o.
48003015	Noreewi~o. Nit yogo monggoorak ambi wakkagak yuwok~o. Nit aap nggween paga mendek aret kwe, aap ambi ninom wone mbambunuk, "Mondok ndogop eeruwok~o," yinuk, nineenggi amburu pugwi niinok, aap alik ambi nen wone ti, taganogo mbo pege, ndi, at alik ambi nen wone alik ambi inom nabenogo pege, eeriyak mondok meek aret kogo monggoorak nogo ndak-ndak,
48003016	at Abarakam ombowologwe inom peebi eeriyak wone Ala nen Abarakam yoge logonet, ombowologwe ineebe ambik kenok, "Kombowologwe~o," yinuk, ti yoroolik. Ata, eebe ambit Keritut aret me, "Kombooluk~o," yoreegerak.
48003017	At Ala nen Abarakam imbirak wone mondok abuk nggaruk togon mbaneegwaarak kagak, tahun empat ratus tiga puluh eeppunuk, wone Muta yoreegerak me, peebi yoreegerak nogo paga nen, aa'nduk yugu nogo awo eeka'lek kagak, lek eerogo puurak op mbakop? Meek me nduk, yokkiragi~o, noreewi.
48003018	Ala nen eeppinaniyak Abarakam abok yoreegerak nogo, peebi wone Muta yoreegerak eekwi paga eeppinaniyak mba'netak en, aa'nduk at Abarakam ti, yo'netak lek kwe, iniki kunik eeke logonet, yoreegerak me, abet mbakwi niinok woorak nduk, yoreegerak kogo~o.
48003019	Ti kenok, Ala nen wone Muta yoreegerak nogo ti, nonggop nduk yoreegerak mbakop? Lek~o. Abet mbakwi paga woorak yoreegerak wone nogo, eebe kin ari waga'lek kagak, maluk aa'nduk kin kogo logowak nduk, wone Muta yoreegerak ti, inom nabenogo yoreegerak. Wone Muta yoreegerak nogo ti, Ala nen nok-nok aakumi Iterali yoroolik. Ata, it malayikat nen waganogo aap nggween paga mendek ambi yogo mbareegwa, at nen wonok aakumi yoragagerak.
48003020	Aap mbere nen, "E~o," yinuk, eeko logowak nduk ambi yegetak wonok ambi yogak eeko menggaarak kwe, Abarakam yoreegerak nogo perak, Ala eebe ambit aret me, alik nen iniki koombunuk nggaruk togon, "Eerikit," mbareegerak me, nok-nok Abarakam yoreegerak.
48003021	Togop kenok, wone Muta yoreegerak inom, ndi, Abarakam abok yoreegerak wone inom, ti alom alitak mbakop? Mondok lek~o, noreewi. Nit nineenik logorak nduk, wone yugu alom alik ambi logonetak en, wone ti woppunuk eekwi paga Ala nen, "Aap yi, iniki abe koonak aret~o," yinuk, yo'nirage logonetak kwe,
48003022	lek me, Ala nen eeppinaniyak yoreegerak nogo, nit niniki Yetut Keritut abet mbakwi paga eeppinanuwak nduk, tokkogo logonet, "It yi aakumi ndi aakumi abok aret maluk eeko menggaarak paga wam anggenogona narak negen wonogwe," mbaruwak nduk, Ala nen yereegerak liiru mbanak wonage.
48003023	Nit abet mbakwi paga woorak yugu nogo, wage kenok, "Abet mba'nuk, waganggo logowak~o," yinuk, awo kin ari waga'lek kagak, wone Muta yoreegerak paga, wam anggenogona nappiigo mengga kwak narogo pinaninuk wonagagerak.
48003024	Togop me, Keritut wage kenok, "Kit abet mbakwi paga, kinoba lek~o, yinuk, obeelom agago pinagarak," yo'niraawak nduk, wone Muta yoreegerak nogo nen we luulu aret ninarum wonagagerak kwe,
48003025	niniki abet mbakwi paga woorak nogo, muk kin ari wagagerak me, yogondak wone Muta yoreegerak nogo ninarum wonogwe lek~o.
48003026	Kit abok Keritut Yetut abet mba'nuk, kiniki at oba panggombereegutak me, kit Ala apuri aret ogotik~o.
48003027	Keritut kinom kumbinagage mbareegi, yiime wambeegutak me, Keritut obaabut ndak-ndak aret ogogutak~o.
48003028	Kinobaabut ambit Keritut mendek ogogutak me, yi Yakuri mendek yi Yunani mendek, yi aap inayeloman aago mendek, yi aap inayeloman aago lek mendek, yi aap yi kwe, togop yuurak mondok lek aret~o. Nit abok Keritut Yetut ninom kunik me, nineebe ambit aret ogoorik~o.
48003029	Ndi, nit Keritut apuri abet aret wonogwe kenok, Abarakam ombowologwe aret me, wone abok yoreegerak nogo, nit aret woorak nduk ogoorik~o.
48004001	Wone yokkiragarak nogo ando ambi yi yokkira~o. Aap ambi nen, "An namendek yi, napuluk tawe age kenok, unde eeppikit," mbaketak nogo abok aret ti, apuluk amendek aret kwe, apuluk nogo tawe aga'lek kenok, tokkage kagak aakumi inabu'me inayeloman negen aret menggerak~o.
48004002	Ogoba nen, "Ti eyom paga unde eeppikit," mbaketak nogo, awo panggoni waga'lek kagak wulaga nogo ti, eebe inom, amendek inom, ogobamini unde menggaarak me, it inabu'me logonet, inoone liirogon konengge menggerak.
48004003	Ti ndak-ndak nit togon tawe aga'lek wologwe-mbuulogwe negen ugun wonogwe niigak, it aakumi nggween paga mendek nen, "Yogop eeriyak ndogop eeriyak," iniki koonogo inapuri yoranet wundi wogo menggaarak wone nogo mendek mban konembunuk, eeko logowok nduk, keele maarak negen aret wonogogurak kwe,
48004004	-
48004005	wone Muta yoreegerak nit eeko logowok nduk, keele maarak negen wonogwe nogo, ninonggo mbambunuk, wondet eerogo pinanege logomenggerik, aap ambi apuluk maluk ngguungge menggi kwak, nit at apuri lombok logorak ngguunninabuwak nduk, Ala nen, "Ndiyom paga napuluk nappi woraagin~o," yinuk, kooneegerak nogo, abu aret panggoni wage mbareegi, kwe ambi nen aret ndareegerak. Ndake mbareegi, wone Muta yoreegerak eekwi nogo inom aret eerit nage nagagerak.
48004006	Ndi, yogondak kit Ala apuri aret me, Ala nen aput Yetut at Aberiniki nappi wagagerak nogo, kinikime logonet, "Kit kinogoba Ala aret~o," yinuk, ari menggerak.
48004007	Togop me noreewi~o. Kit aakumi inayeloman kokwak wonogwe lek~o. Kit Ala apuri lombok aret ogotik~o. Ndi, Ala apuri lombok aret me, amendek unde eeppiyoorak mbareegerak nogo kit aret~o.
48004008	Kit aa'nduk Ala kineenggo'lek logonet, kugi ti, abe mendek lek kagak, inayeloman a'nuk inoone konenggo logonet, kugiwak ogobakkigippunuk alut eeko nogogutak kwe,
48004009	yogondak perak, Ala kineenu ogwe, ndi, Ala nen kit togon kineebe eenu age, eereegutak me, kit nonggop nduk, wone abe yugu nogo mbo punuk, obeelom eekkinaburak lek kagak aanom warogo eeko nogogutak wone nogo, "Ambinom abu'me tebenak logowok," mba'nuk, kiniyok paga yungguninuk wa nogo ogotik?
48004010	"Ne yi paga yogop eeriyak mage~o. Tut ti paga togop eeriyak mage~o. O omarip paga kagak, o ame kagak, togop eeriyak mage~o. Tahun ti paga togop eeriyak mage~o," yinuk, yi eyom ndi eyom abok aret mage agago pit nogwe nogo, kit togon ndak-ndak liippunuk, eerit nugwi kiige nagagirik,
48004011	an kinake eeke nagagirak nogo ti, "We aanom warogo eeke nagagirak kulik?" mba'nuk, niniki aaninggin ee'nake~o, noreewi.
48004012	Kit nen an maluk eeppaneegutak kenok, yokkirage lek kwe, wone yugu liiru mbanak nogo, kineenggo'lek logonet, abet mba'nuk Ala apuri ogogutak nogo kwak, an togon, wone ti mbo punuk, abet mba'nuk Ala aput agagirak me, yogondak an eeke nogo kit ndak-ndak eeko logobagip nduk, noone nabek togon yokkiragi~o.
48004013	An andi ee'nabeegerak me, kinenggela'me ninom logonet, iyaalok togon wone obeelom wone yokkirage nagagirak nogo kineenu aret~o.
48004014	Andi ee'nabeegerak paga neebe abu maluk me, "Anggon lombok ndegeniyak yi, nineebi a," yinuk, nogole nen mbo paniyak op aret kwe kagak, "Yi Ala nappiige menggerak malayikat kwak, yi Keritut Yetut kwak," nomba'nuk, neebe wo'nako nogogutik, ndegennako nogogutak nogo~o.
48004015	Kiniki ale'nggen ambik eekwi kiyareegirak kwe, yogondak nonggop aga~o, noreewi? Nabuwa mbako logonet, "Ninigen kilirogo wogoriyak op nen, wogoruwok lak ao," nombakwi kiyareegirak kwe,
48004016	yogondak kit eeko monggotak an paganogo yokkirage paga kinawim negen ogoorogo panugwi kiigi~o.
48004017	It aap ando nogo ti, kiniki nomongginabuwok nduk, iniki aganggen kerek togon kwaakkinabit wogwe kwe, ti paga obeelom eeppinagawok nduk, kinabuwa nen kiya wogwe lek~o. Ata, "Ninoone konembunuk, iniki aganggen kerek togon, mu'neren nogo logowak," mba'nuk, kiya wogo menggaarak.
48004018	"Obeelom eeriyak mendek yi, ninom eeruwok," yinuk, iniki aganggen kerek togon aakumi wogonabit wogwe ti, op aret kwe, an neebe lek neegak mban wogonabit wogwe ti mage~o. Ata, neebe kinenggela'me wonage neegak wogonabit woroorak togon op mban aret~o.
48004019	Ai, napuri, kit an niniki kunik me, kumi elege enegen paganak yagan wako mengga kwak, kit Ala apuri arubagip nduk, an kinake yagan wake aret wonagagirak kwe, yogondak kit Keritut obaabut ndak-ndak arubagip nduk, ambinom yagan wake agarik~o.
48004020	An kinenggela'me logonet, kit eerit nugwi kiige logominggirik, noone yanggorogon yokkiroorak, "Ao," mbake kwe, kit eekwi an kiiga'lek me, niniki piirik togon logonet, noone alik negen aret yokkirage yi abet aret~o, napuri.
48004021	Kit wone Muta yoreegerak eeko logorak mbakwi nogo, wone Muta yoreegerak mbanak ambi yokkiraakit mbakirak me, konenggo logonip~o.
48004022	At Abarakam apuri mbere ndaganabeegerak nogo ti, ambi kwe at ayeloman nogo nen ndake, ndi, ambi at akwe abe wogo nogo nen ndake, eereegwaarak liiru mbanak kogo monggoorak nogo~o.
48004023	Kwe at ayeloman nogo nen ndareegerak nogo ti, it nggween paga nen ndaganako mengga kwak, ndareegerak. Ndi, at akwe lombok nen ndareegerak nogo perak, wone yugu paga nen aret ndareegerak.
48004024	Wone yi nogo ti, wakkagak aret~o. Kumi mbere yi nogo ti, wone mbere yugu nogo kokwak aret me, ambi puut Tinayi paga nen yoreegerak wone nogo ti, kwe Agat kokwak aret. Kwe Agat Abarakam ayeloman logonet, aagalogwe ndaganabeegerak nogo inom Abarakam ayeloman tebenak wonogogwaarak nogo kokwak, it wone puut Tinayi paga yoreegerak nogo waganggwi iinok, aakumi inayeloman kokwak tebenak aret menggaarak~o.
48004025	Ndi, puut Tinayi o Arap wonage nogo ti, kwe Agat kokwak aret me, wakkogo logonet, kwe Agat aagalogwe inom Abarakam ayeloman tebenak wonogogwaarak nogo kokwak, puut Tinayi paga, "Yogop ee'nu, ndogop ee'nu," wone yereegerak nogo, it o Yerutalem mendek nen awo eekwi me, aakumi inayeloman kwak, wone ti abu'me tebenak wonogwe iigo~o.
48004026	Ndi, o Yerutalem agi mbogut paga nogo ti, at akwe abe wogo nogo kokwak me, at Tara nen wone yugu abet mbareegerak paga aagaluk ndareegerak kokwak, nit kunduk, "Yogop ee'nu, ndogop ee'nu," yereegerak nogo eekwi paga lek~o. Ata, abet mbakwi paga o Yerutalem agi mbogut paga mendek ogoorik~o.
48004027	Ala wone mbanak paga nen ari logonet, "Kwe ogonggelo nen mbo pereegerak nogo aagalogwe ambik lombok wonage, Ndi, kwe ogonggelo warak aagalogwe mbereeluk wonage, eekwi me, At aagaluk ndaka'lek kwe wubili ti, iniki ale'nggen mbake, Kwe enegen paganak yagan waka'lek ti, ale'nggen inikime nggelok ari logonet, keyage wake, Eeke logowak~o," yinuk, yereegerak liiru mbanak nogo ti, nit abet mbakwi apit ninowogolo kwe Tara aret~o.
48004028	Ndi, noreewi~o. Kwe Tara nen wone yugu abet mbareegerak paga Itak ndareegerak nogo kokwak, nit togon Ala wone yo'nirage abet mbakwi paga at apuri aret nda'ninake menggerak~o.
48004029	Ti eyom it nggween paga mendek nen ndaganako mengga kwak ndarak nogo nen, Aberiniki nen wone yoreegerak paga ndarak nogo, miyuk-meya eerogo tebenogo pit nage nagagerak nogo kokwak, yogondak ti ndak-ndak, it puut Tinayi paga yoreegerak eekwi nogo nen, nit abet mbakwi nogo miyuk-meya eerogo pinanugo menggaarak kwe,
48004030	Ala wone liiru mbanak nogo ngge mbanak mbakop? "Kat keyate an kakwe abe wogo naagaluk wulaga Itak nogo kolage logonet, at kwe nayeloman Agat aagaluk Itamayen yi, inom wogoriyak lek me, kwe ti, aagaluk imbirak mbet mugogo wumbiyet~o," yinuk, Abarakam yoreegerak liiru mbanak wonage me,
48004031	nit kwe ayeloman nogo owowologwe lek~o. Nit kwe abe wogo nogo owowologwe aret~o.
48005001	Nit wondet aago nugu logowok nduk, Keritut nen wondet agago pinaneegerak me, eyo aaninggin tapi inuut paga pogo mengga kwak, aaninggin ambinom kinoba pinagawok nduk, "Yogop ee'nu, ndogop ee'nu," wone yugu nogo mendek ambi yokkira wogwe iinok, inoone konengga'lek mondok kinogogumbuk logonip~o.
48005002	Kit liippatubagip nduk, an Pawulut nen wone ambi yokkira~o. Kit kinagabolo mbaniyak mbakwi kenok, Keritut nen eeppinagarak mbake nogo, ambi eeppinagagin mondok lek aret~o.
48005003	Kit kinagabolo mbaniyak mbakwi kenok, wone, "Yogop ee'nu, ndogop ee'nu," yugu liiru mbanak nogo, ambiriluk ambi eeriyak lek ti lek mondok tigitogon eeko logorak ariyak me, mbo pubagip nduk, muk yokkiragagirak me, ne ambinom yokkiragi~o, noreewi.
48005004	Wone Muta yoreegerak nogo, eekwi paga, "Noba lek, neyaawak~o," yinuk, obeelom eekkoloorak mbakwi nogo, Keritut kinom ogookkologwe me, Ala iniki kunik nen eeppinagarak kooneegerak nogo lek eerogo pako ogotik.
48005005	Nit abet mbareegurak nogo paga Aberiniki nen eeppinanege kagak, Ala nen, "Aap yi, iniki abe koonak aret~o," yinuk, obeelom agago pinaniyak nogo, "Mbet-mbet eerogo pinanuwak lak ao," yinuk, niniki lunik logonet, tokkogo ogoorik~o.
48005006	Nit Keritut Yetut ninom kunik logonet, ninagabolo mbanak kenok, mbanak lek kenok, ti iya lek~o. Ata, niniki abet mbareegurak paga aakumi inabuwa nen obeelom eeppiinet nogo logorak nogo perak iya~o.
48005007	Ala abet aret ari menggerak wone nogo, kit aa'nduk, kiniki aganggen paga op aret mugurok nogwe kiige nagagirak kwe, Ala wone mbo pubagip nduk, ta nen kiniki nggagambunuk nomonggiren nage agaarik~o?
48005008	Ala wone mbo punuk, alik eerit nugwi nogo ti, at yonggo pinagareegerak nogo nen yokkiroolik~o.
48005009	"Roti piike menggerak mendek mbuuluk roti enggela'me pugwi iinok, roti eebe abok aret piike menggerak," nogo~o.
48005010	Nit ninowe ninom ambit kunik me, an mbake minggirak nogo, kit ndak-ndak mbako logonet, eerit nogo logorak abet aret kinomba'nuk yokkiragi~o, noreewi. Ndi, at nomonggiren nage nogo perak, Ala nen maluk onggo eeppigin me, agabiti mbake logowak~o.
48005011	Ndi, noreewi~o. An perak, alom ngge paga piyak-payak ee'nakwi mbakop? An, "Kinagabolo mbaniyak~o," agan nege logonetak en, piyak-payak agago paninetak lek kwe, Yetut eyo karo-karo paga kambeegerak wone yoranet nage logonet, "Kinagabolo mbaniyak lek~o," yinuk, non mbanogo piinet nage paga, inanini nombako logonet piyak-payak ee'nako agaarik~o.
48005012	It aap kiniki abut laganit unggwogwe nogo, inagabolo ti mban mbaniyak lek~o. Ata, eebe inom aret mbanogo nappako logowak nduk, teppiyaanip~o.
48005013	Noreewi~o. Kit perak, wondet aago nugu logobagip nduk, Ala nen miikkinabeegerak kwe, "An nanonggwan wondet agago paneegerak me, niniki nengge kenok ugun eerit nage logi~o," yinuk, yuurak ti mage~o. Ata, nabuwa-kabuwa mbako logonet, kinoreewi kinom yeenggwa-yeenggwa eeko logonip~o.
48005014	"Ineebe iniki kunik eekkologo menggaarak ti kwak, aakumi inom menggaarak ti togop aret iniki kunik aganako logowak~o," yinuk, yo'niragagerak nogo ti, wone yugu liiru mbanak eebe tigitogon eekwi ti aret~o.
48005015	Kit neyak-keyak yogo logonet, at ambi nibinogo nappegak eekwi paga kineebe lek eerogo pakwi kiyo, liippogo logonip~o.
48005016	Togop me, Aberiniki nen yokkirage kagak eerit nogwe kiinok, kiniki maan mendek nen maluk eeriyak eekkinake nogo, mugurok noorak eekkinabigin lek~o, yinuk, yokkiragi~o.
48005017	Niniki maan mendek nen Aberiniki warikit mbake, ndi, Aberiniki nogo nen niniki maan mendek warikit mbake, eeko logonet, imbirak wim negen ogoorak togon wonogwe me, kit eeriyak mbarumonggotak nogo, eeriyak meek aret kaamunggup~o.
48005018	Ndi, Aberiniki nen yokkirage nogo eerit nogwe kiinok perak, wone yugu liiru mbanak nogo abu'me logomunggup lek~o.
48005019	Iniki maan mendek paga eeko menggaarak nogo yi~o. Kumi ugun wurinabit nugwi, iniki kumi paga mban lunik logonet ugun-ugun aganabit nugwi, iniki nengge kenok mugurok nogwe,
48005020	kugiwak amili kunggwi, magagirak paga aakumi inookwi, iniki ogoorik-ogoorak wonogwe, wone wakwi, nuwa-kuwa yogwe, inanini mbet-mbet wungge, an eeke mban op mbakwi, an iya kat iya yogwe, iniki nen koombunuk pilit pugunogo agan nugwi,
48005021	neebi-keebi yogwe, amburu nenok kumili-kumili agan nugwi, kwaanggen wappunuk inoone amburu paga kumi ugun-ugun eeginabit nugwi, ti mendek abok aret it eerit nugwi iinok, at Ala abu'me piige menggim nogome unggwi nagun mondok lek aret~o, yinuk, aa'nduk yokkiragagirak nogo aret yokkiragi~o, noreewi.
48005022	Togop kwe, eyoonggen abe yi'nage menggi kwak, Aberiniki ninikime logonet, eerit nogo monggoorak nogo yi~o. Aakumi inabuwa mbakwi, niniki ale'nggen mban mbakwi, niniki ugun tayenak wonogwe, niniki aanaganggenggwi lek kwi'ndak wonogwe, ninobaabut abu obeelom wonogwe, aakumi obeelom eeppiinet nugwi, liippunuk mban eerit nogwe,
48005023	niniki yanggonak wonogwe, eeriyak niniki nengge kenok mbet-mbet tebenogo pugwi, eeko monggoorak ti aret~o. Ti eeko monggoorak nogo eeko logorak mage yugu ambi wonage mondok lek~o.
48005024	Nit Keritut Yetut apuri kenok, niniki maan mendek paga nen maluk eeriyak niniki nengge nogo, mondok warogo tebenogo punuk wonogo ogoorik~o.
48005025	Nit Aberiniki nen pi'niren noorak mbakwi kenok, at yo'nirage nogo mban aret eerit nogo logowok~o.
48005026	Kit wogoppako logonet, an iya kat iya yogwe, at ambi eeke paga at ambi iniki warogo pegak eekwi, obeelom eeppugwi iinok, nuwa-kuwa yogwe, eeko logogup~o.
48006001	Noreewi~o. Kinore ambi perak togon yigeebu wangge kenok, kit aap Aberiniki kinom kunik monggotak nogo nen, "Noreeluk iniki nggagangge mbaki, yigeebu wanggerak nogo kokwak, an togop wangge neyo nagabiti~o," yinuk, kinoone yanggorogon awone mbanggo logonip~o.
48006002	Aaninggin kinoba age kenok, yeenggwa-yeenggwa eerumonggotak paga Keritut nen, "Ndogop eeko logonip~o." yo'niragagerak wone yugu nogo ndak-ndak aret eeko logomunggup~o.
48006003	Kit aap iya lek kwe, "Nit iya~o," mbakwi kiinok, kit aret kinambokan laganggologo ogotik~o.
48006004	Kit ambi nen at ambi eeke wakkagak eeko logogup~o. Ata, kinalitak lombok eeko monggotak nogo wakkaanuk, op kenok kiniki ale'nggen mbakwi, ndi, maluk kenok mbo pugwi, eeko logonip~o.
48006005	Nit ninalitak ninobaalombok koonggologo logowok~o.
48006006	Nit Ala wone konenggo monggoorak nogo nen, ninamendek obeelom nogo mogonogo ninogobamini mamunnirogo menggaarak nogo wogorogo logorak ti op aret~o.
48006007	Ala ambokan laganggulik kagak, ambokan laganggwi kiinok, kit aret kinambokan laganggologwe me, liippako logonip~o. Aap ambi awi yaremenggerak nogo ti, anggen ti mendek aret mbanggolage menggerak me,
48006008	kit kiniki maan mendek nen eeriyak eekkinake nogo, eerit nugwi kiinok, anggen yugu maluk mendek mbanggologwe nogo kokwak, kineebe aret kambumunggup~o. Ndi, Aberiniki nen yokkirage nogo mban mugurok nogwe kiinok perak, anggen yugu abe mendek mbanggologwe ti pogom, mondok-mondok kineenik aret logomunggup~o.
48006009	Togop me, nit yi obeelom ndi obeelom eerit nogo logonet, anggon-panggon ee'ninake kagak, mbo pega'lek mondok aret eerit nogwe niinok, anggen yugu obeelom mbanggologwe nogo kokwak, nit onggo wo'niroorak nineenu me, ta'liila ee'ninake kenok mbo puurak mage~o. Kagak aret eerit nogo logowok~o.
48006010	It yi aakumi ndi aakumi abok aret obeelom eeppiyoorak, "Nanonggwan aga~o," yinuk, obeelom eeppiinet nogo logonet kwe, it ninom ndak-ndak abet mbakwi kenok perak, logorogon obeelom eeppiyoorak mondok aberak aret logonip~o.
48006011	An neenggi lombok paga liiru yo'nggok lombok mbanggiragi yi kaanip~o.
48006012	It aakumi nen, "Ia!" ninombaruwak nduk, wogoppatit nugwi nogo ti, Keritut eyo karo-karo paga kambeegerak wone yoranet nugwi paga piyak-payak eeginaburak inagabiti mbako logonet, "Kinagabolo mbaninip~o," yinuk, inoone omaawi paga yokkirogo menggaarak.
48006013	It inagabolo mbanak nogo nen wone Muta yoreegerak nogo ndak-ndak eeka'lek logonet kwe, kit mban eeko logobagip nduk, yokkirogwe nogo ti, "Nit ninapuri ambik aga~o," yinuk, wogoppatuwok nduk, yokkirogo menggaarak.
48006014	Ndi, an perak, ninowe Yetut Keritut eyo karo-karo paga kambeegerak wone nogo abet mba'nuk, waganeegirak ti paga, it nggween paga mendek nen eeko menggaarak ti, aap kanggaatak inoone yogolik nogo pogom me, it eekwi nogo an ambi eeke logokit nduk, yo'niriyak meek aret~o. Ndi, an kunduk kambeegirak negen aret me, it nen an yo'nugwi nogo kunduk, koneniyak meek me, an eeke minggirak paga wogoppatiyak lek~o. Ata, ninowe Yetut Keritut eyo karo-karo paga kambeegerak wone nogo mban tiyappege agarik~o.
48006015	Inagabolo mbanak kenok, mbanak lek kenok, ti imbirak iya lek~o. Ata, niniki ngget ogobakkigirogo pinanege logonet, ninobaabut koonogo pinanege ti perak, iya~o.
48006016	It wone ti paga panggombunuk, eerit nugwi nogo inom, ndi, Iterali mendek kwe, it abet mbakwi paga Ala apuri ogwe nogo inom, yi aakumi ndi aakumi abok aret Ala nen inabuwa mbake logonet, inomaluk mbo nappunuk iniki ugun tayenak ale'nggen logowak nduk, eeppiige logogin~o.
48006017	An Yetut wone yoranet nage paga ee'nabit nogo nogogwaarak nawin oban noba kunik yogobi wonage me, an mbo panubagip nduk, it kiniki nggagani wogwe nogo, inawone ambinom mbaniyak neebi me, mondok mbo piyaanip~o.
48006018	Ninowe Yetut Keritut iniki kunik en eeppinagage logonet, kinarum aret logogin~o. Wone ti abu aret yokkiragi~o. Noreewi wa.
49001001	Ala mbareegerak paga Keritut Yetut ayonggo nappiigak mendek agago paneegerak an Pawulut nogo nen kit Ala apuri at ake leenak Keritut Yetut kinom kunik logonet, obeelom wone liirogon mugurok nogo monggotak o Epetut wonogwe nogo, wone ambi yokkira~o.
49001002	Ninogoba Ala ninowe Yetut Keritut imbirak iniki kunik nen wokkirogwe, kiniki ugun tayenak ale'nggen logobagip nduk, eeppinagagwi, eeko logogun~o.
49001003	Ala wonage menggim mbogut paga mendek eeppinaniyak mbake menggerak nogo mendek abok aret, Keritut ninom kumbinaneegerak paga nen eeppinanege me, ninowe Yetut Keritut ogoba Ala mondok alut eeko logowok~o.
49001004	At Ala nen, "Peebi Keritut nen eeppiyamenggerak paga an napuri maluk inoba lenggenna'lek nenggaanom paga mondok alik leenak logowak~o," yinuk, o nggween yi, awo wakkaga'lek kagak mii'ninabeegerak.
49001005	Nit awo nda'naga'lek niigak, at Ala nen Yetut Keritut eeremenggerak paga, nit at apuri lombok logowok nduk wo'ninaburak inikilom mbareegerak nogo ndak-ndak, iniki kunik en, "Eeppiyaakit~o," yinuk, koonogo pereegerak nogo aret eeppinaneegerak.
49001006	Ninabuwa mbake logonet, at aput iniki kunik nen wo'niragagerak nogo paga, amendek mondok alik negen ngginu-ngginu eerogo wo'nirage menggerak me, nit mondok at alut eeko logowok~o.
49001007	-
49001008	At Ala ninabuwa mba'nuk, iniki warak lombok logonet, mondok liippinanege nagagerik, oba ngginik kagak eeppinanit wundi wage menggerak nogo ndak-ndak, at amiya paga ninonggo mbambunuk, keele piinogo pinanege nagagerik, ninomaluk mondok lek eerogo pinaneegerak.
49001009	"Keritut nen togop eeppiyaawak~o," yinuk, inikilom mbake nagagerik, koonogo pereegerak kote kumaarak wonage nogo aret paganogo yo'niragagerak.
49001010	At Ala nen, "An eeriyak mbareegirak nogo, ndiyom paga a'me lik yigin~o," yinuk, kooneegerak nogo ti, mbogut paga mendek inom, nggween paga mendek inom, yi mendek ndi mendek abok aret Keritut abu'me pege logomenggerik, at eebe mondok tiyanak logorak kooneegerak nogo ti aret~o.
49001011	At eeriyak koonggetak ndak-ndak aret eeke menggerak nogo nen, "An napuri ndogop obeelom eeppiyaakit~o," yinuk, o maan togon nit nda'naga'lek niigak, koonogo pereegerak nogo ndak-ndak, Keritut eeremenggerak paga nit at apuri aret miirogo pinaneegerak wonogo ogoorik~o.
49001012	Ti eeppinaniyak koonogo pereegerak nogo ti, "Nit nen, Keritut ndogop eeppinanigin~o," yinuk, aa'nduk abet mba'nuk, niniki at oba panggombereegurak nogo eerit nogwe paga Ala endage tiyak yuwak nduk, mii'ninabeegerak me, at alut eeko logowok~o.
49001013	Kit kinagap ndariyak Ala ari menggerak obeelom wone nogo, konembunuk, abet mba'nuk kiniki Keritut oba panggombogo mbareegup, wam yelok kaawak nduk, aruk nggaganggo mengga kwak, kit Ala apuri alik leenak yelok logobagip nduk, Aberiniki wo'niroorak koonogo pereegerak nogo, kit kunduk wokkiragagerak.
49001014	Ti wokkiragagerak nogo ti, peebi kit at apuri kinonggo mbanak me, kineebe abet aret wokkinaburak aberak logobagip nduk, kwe yiindi aa'nduk pogo mengga kwak, Aberiniki aret yilinogo wokkiragagerak me, Ala nen kit ninom ndak-ndak Keritut eeremenggerak paga aret mondok iya lombok koonogo pinaneegerak me, alut eeko logowok~o.
49001015	Togop me, kit nen ninowe Yetut abet mba'nuk, kiniki at oba panggombugwi, ndi, Ala apuri ake leenak abok aret kinom kiniki kunik aganakwi, eerit nogwe nogo, an konengge nagagirik,
49001016	tamban eeke logonet, kit eerit nogwe paga an puk aga'lek Ala mondok, "Wa," yoge minggirak.
49001017	At ninowe Yetut Keritut ogoba Ala mondok tiyanak menggerak nogo nen, kit kiniki warak eeppinagage, Ala eeke menggerak yelok kaabagip nduk, kineenu eeppinagage, eeke menggerak Aberiniki nogo, ambinom wokkiraawak nduk, kinake tamban eeke minggirak.
49001018	Ti eeke logonet, kit kola nabagip nduk kinayonggo pinagareegerak kiniki lunik wonogwe nogo inom, nit at apuri ake leenak kenok eyate mondok alik negen eerogo wo'niraagin kooneegerak nogo inom, ndi, nit abet mbakwi mendek Ala omaawi mondok iya lombok eeppinanege menggerak nogo inom, kineenu arubagip nduk, "Inikime eya eeginake logot~o," yinuk, Ala yoge minggirak.
49001019	-
49001021	Nit abet mbakwi niinok, at omaawi mondok iya lombok nogo paga eeppinanege nogo ti, Keritut kambunuk, nogo menggam nen eenik agago mippege nagagerik, kugi nggween abu'na mendek inom, eyonggaame mendek inom, mbogut abu'na o oolo yayi mendek inom, yi kugi ndi kugi inayuk wuko menggaarak o yogondak wonogwe inom, peebi logorak inom, it abok aret tebenak iigak, at Keritut alik mban Ala eenggi abe'nggan tiyanak logowak nduk, mbogut paga mippereegerak nogo ndak-ndak, nit yogondak at omaawi ti paga togop aret eeppinanege agaarik~o.
49001022	Yi kugi ndi kugi inom, yi aakumi ndi aakumi inom, yi mendek ndi mendek abok aret at abu'me piinok, nit Ala apuri yi awi ndi awi kuwak eerit nogo monggoorak nogo lambuk togon ninanobak kwak ninowe tiyanak logowak nduk, mippereegerak.
49001023	Ndi, nit Ala apuri yi awi ndi awi kuwak eeko monggoorak lambuk togon nogo ti, at eebe aret me, eebe ambit aruwak nduk, nit nineebe anobak nogo paga kumbinaneegerak me, yogondak at eebe yi awi ndi awi abok aret mondok endak warak menggerak.
49002001	-
49002002	Kit o maan aa'nduk nen it aap nggween paga mendek iniki nengge kenok mugurok nogo mengga kwak mugurok nogwe, it yi kugi ndi kugi mbogut abu'na o oolo yayi menggaarak inowe aakumi Ala wone taganggwi iinok iniki nggagangge menggerak nogo nen, yokkirage kenok konenggwi, eerit nogo logonet, Ala wone taganogo punuk, yi maluk ndi maluk eeko nogogutak paga kambak kwak aret wonogogutak~o.
49002003	It Ala wone taganogo punuk, maluk eeko nogogwaarak paga Ala anini inoba piyoorak wonogogwaarak nogo ndak-ndak, nit kunduk, togop aret niniki maan mendek nen yo'nirage kagak niniki nengge kenok mugurok nogwe, maluk eeriyak ee'ninake kenok eerit nogwe, maluk eeriyak mban koonit nugwi, eeko nogogurak paga Ala anini mondok ninoba pinaniyak aret wonogogurak kwe,
49002004	-
49002005	at Ala nogo nen aakumi maluk eekwi iinok, anini nen mbet-mbet inookeelik mondok inabuwa lombok mbake logonet, yanggo yinuk, torinake menggerak me, nit abok aret yi maluk ndi maluk eerit nogo nogogurak paga kambak kwak aret wonogwe niigak, Ala ninabuwa mbake nagagerik, Keritut eenik eeppege logonet, nit kunduk ninom aret nineenik eeppinaneegerak. Ala ninabuwa nen iniki kunik ee'nabeegerak ti paga ninagap ndareegerak kogo~o.
49002006	Ndi, at Keritut ninom kunik wonogwe niinok, Ala nen at ninom nineenik agago mippinanege nagagerik, Keritut Yetut tiyanak mbogut paga wonage nogo ninom ndak-ndak logowok nduk, tiyappinaneegerak.
49002007	Ti eeppinaneegerak nogo ti, ninabuwa mbake logonet, Keritut Yetut wo'niragagerak ti paga, o yogondak wonage inom, peebi logorak inom, at aakumi abok aret iniki kunik nen oba ngginik kagak ngginu-ngginu eerogo wogorage menggerak nogo, mondok-mondok nineenu logowok nduk, eeppinaneegerak.
49002008	Kit abet mba'nuk, kiniki at oba panggombugwi kiinok, kinabuwa nen iniki kunik eekkinake logonet, kinagap ndareegerak~o. Kit ambi eekkologogutak paga eeppinagulik~o. Ata, Ala nen onggo lek we aret eeppinagareegerak~o.
49002009	Kit nen ambi eekkologwe paga wogoppakwi kiyo, at nen mban onggo lek we aret eeppinagareegerak.
49002010	Ala nen aret ogobakkigi'ninabeegerak me, nit at amendek aret ogoorik~o. Nit nda'naga'lek niigak obeelom eerit nogo logorak Ala nen maan kooneegerak nogo, Keritut Yetut ninom kunik logonet eerit nogo logowok nduk, ogobakkigi'ninabeegerak.
49002011	Togop me, noreewi~o. It, "Nit ninagabolo mbanak mendek~o," yogo menggaarak nogo nen, "Kit kinagabolo mbanak lek mendek~o," yinuk, yokkirogo menggaarak kit endekem konenggulik mendek nda'nogogutak nogo, aa'nduk wonogogutak kiniki abeko logonip~o. "Ninagabolo mbanak~o," yogo menggaarak nogo ti, aakumi nen mbanak aret~o.
49002012	Nogo ne ti eyom paga, it aakumi Iterali mendek mban Ala apuri leenak wonogwe iigak, kit Keritut kinom ogoorak logonet, we aakumi nggiru negen aret wonogogutak me, at apuri iinok, wone abok yoragagerak nogo, kit koloorak meek aret wonogogutak. Kit aa'nduk kinogoba Ala lek me, kiniki lunik ambi lek
49002013	o nda negen aret wonogogutak kwe, Keritut amiya paga Ala kinom lambunogo pinagi wagagerak me, yogondak Keritut Yetut kinom kunik aret wonogo ogotik~o.
49002014	Nit aap Yakuri mendek inom, kit endekem mendek inom, at Keritut eebe paga paalungga negen warogo nineebe ambit lambumbinanege logonet, wim pak wurik pogom ninom ogoorak aret wonogogurak nogo, minogo mbo nappege,
49002015	ndi, nit aap ninanebunu mbere wonogogurak nogo, at eebe paga at apuri ninanebunu ambit a'nuk, ninom niniki lambunik logowok nduk, Ala nen, "Yogop ee'nu, ndogop ee'nu," yinuk, wone Muta yoreegerak nogo paga ninom ogoorak wonogogurak nogo kunduk, lek eerogo pege, eereegerak.
49002016	Ti eeke nagagerik, Keritut eyo karo-karo paga kambeegerak ti paga ninom ogoorak wonogogurak nogo, lek eerogo punuk, nineebe ambit lambumbinanege nagagerik, kit ninom lambunik logowok nduk, Ala abu'me pinani wagagerak.
49002017	Kit nda negen wonogogutak inom, nit koorok wonogogurak nogo inom, "Paalungga muk warak me, lambuninip~o," yinuk, yo'nira wagagerak.
49002018	Ndi, yogondak Keritut eereegerak ti paga, nit Yakuri mendek inom, kit endekem mendek inom, Aberiniki ambit nogo paga nen nit wo'niren ninogoba Ala owagam noorak op aret~o.
49002019	Ti kenok noreewi~o. Yogondak kit aap nggiru alik mendek wonogwe lek~o. Kit ninom ndak-ndak Ala apuri aret me, mbogut paga ninaworak aret ogoorik~o.
49002020	O wuruwok nduk, o eyak aa'nduk wurabak kwak ti, Keritut Yetut aret~o. Ndi, o eebe wurit laganggo logonet, abena pugu kwak ti, it nappiyareegerak mendek inom, it aap Ala wone yoraga mendek inom, nogo it aret. Ndi, ogumbaga pugwi kwak ti, nit abet mbareegurak Ala apuri nit nineebe aret~o.
49002021	Ala nen at awi mondok alik leenak obeelom lombok wukkolaakit nduk, nit nineebe alitik-alitak nogo, waganogo ninowe Keritut Yetut eebe ambit nogo paga panggombunuk, oba lu'luk wurit lagangge logonet,
49002022	kit togon, Ala eebe negen Aberiniki kinom logobagip nduk, kit kineebe nogo waganogo Keritut oba panggombinaganuk, at awi negen aret wukkolage agaarik~o.
49003001	Ti eeppinaniyak kooneegerak nogo abeke logonet, kit aakumi endekem mendek Keritut Yetut wone yokkirage nagagirak nogo paga keele maa'nabeegwaarak yime agarik~o.
49003002	At Ala nen iniki kunik ee'nake logonet, kit obeelom eeppinagawak nduk, unde eeppaneegerak nogo ti, kit muk kineenu~o.
49003003	Wone kote kumaarak wonagagerak lalin negen aret kin eeppaneegerak liiru kuwagaluk aginggwe mbanggiragarak nogo,
49003004	kit pekkogo logomonggotik, an Keritut agote wone nonggop togon liippereegirak nogo kineenu arumunggup~o.
49003005	Wone ti, it aakumi aa'nduk nda'narit wundi wogo nogogwaarak nogo, paganogo yoraga'lek aret wonagagerak kwe, yogondak perak, Ala nen at Aberiniki nappi wagagerak nogo paga nen it aap Ala ake leenak nappiigak inom, it aap Ala wone yoraga inom, abok aret ineenu eeppiyareegerak.
49003006	Wone obeelom wone waganggwi paga it aakumi endekem mendek inom, aakumi Iterali mendek inom, Ala apuri mban aret me, Ala nen obeelom eeppinaniyak kooneegerak nogo ndak-ndak aret kologwe, nineebe ando mogonak kit aret wonogwe, ndi, Ala nen Keritut Yetut eeremenggerak paga nit eeppinaniyak wone abok yo'niragagerak nogo, kit kunduk, ndak-ndak aret waganggwi, eekwi nogo ti, wone kote kumaarak yogondak iluk kin agaarak nogo ti aret.
49003007	At omaawi mondok alik negen eeke menggerak neenu eeppanege logonet, at ayeloman a'nuk wone obeelom wone yorage logokit nduk, iniki kunik nen unde eeppaneegerak.
49003008	-
49003009	It Ala apuri alik leenak nogo abok aret tiyanak wonogwe iigak, an abu inabu'me tebenak tit neegak kwe, Keritut oba ngginik kagak eeppinanit wundi wage menggerak wone nogo, kit aap endekem mendek yokkirage, ndi, at yi mendek ndi mendek wakkagagerak Ala nogo nen wone o maan koonak kote kumaapporogo wonagagerak nogo, nonggop eeppinaniyak koonogo pereegerak yi aakumi ndi aakumi abok ineenu eeppiige, eeke logokit nduk, iniki kunik ee'nake logonet unde eeppaneegerak.
49003010	Ndi, wone koonak kumaapporogo wonagagerak nogo ti, nit Ala apuri yi awi ndi awi kuwak eerit nogo monggoorak nogo nen, wone ti woppunuk eerit nogwe paga, it mbogut paga menggaarak malayikat inom, it inayuk warak o oolo yayi menggaarak inom, it abok nen, "Ala iniki mondok warak logonet, yi wone ndi wone koonogo eeppiige menggerak nogo, yogondak yi aret kogo~o," yinuk, ineenu aruwak nduk, kumaapporogo wonagagerak.
49003011	At Ala nen eereegerak nogo ti, ninowe Keritut Yetut nen eeppinanege logowak nduk, o maan togon koonogo pereegerak itok wonagagerak nogo ndak-ndak aret eereegerak~o.
49003012	Nit niniki Keritut oba panggombunuk, abet mbako mbareegu, at ninom kumbinaneegerak me, ninagabiti lek niniki teeluk aret logonet, Ala owagam unggwi nogo logorak op aret~o.
49003013	Togop me noreewi~o. An wone obeelom wone yokkirage nagagirak paga aaninggin noba agaarak wonage yi paga kinagabiti nen kiniki yungguppegak eerugup~o. Yi ee'nakwi nogo ti, kit ambi eeppinagarak nduk, eeppanugwi me, op aret~o.
49003014	-
49003015	Togop me, it aakumi mbogut paga mendek inom, nggween paga mendek inom, ninanebunu lombok abok aret, "Ninogoba Ala~o," yinuk, yogo monggoorak nogo, abu'me tebe yinuk,
49003016	"Kat mondok tiyanak logonet, koba ngginik kagak kapuri eeppiige menggendak nogo ndak-ndak, kat Kaberiniki nen eeppiige kagak komaawi paga iniki nu'lek eerogo piige logot~o," yinuk, kinake tamban eeke minggirak.
49003017	Kit abet mbakwi kiinok Keritut kinikime ye mbanggola unggwage, ndi, eyo omanggen nggween kole paga wuraketak nu'lek menggi kwak, kit togop aret kiniki nu'lek logonet, aakumi kinom kiniki kunik aganakwi, eeko logobagip nduk, kinake tamban eeke minggirak.
49003018	-
49003019	O oolo iniki agi-ogu, o irip aru-ogwe, agi-ogu ti, wakkogo menggaarak kwe, Keritut ninabuwa mbake alom nogo ti, mondok nggwok lombok me, wakkoorak meek aret kwe, it Ala apuri ake leenak kinom abok aret we mbuuluk liippugwi kiinok, Ala iniki-obaabut aago menggerak abok aret kit ndak-ndak eekkinabuwak nduk, kinake Ala yoge minggirak.
49003020	Nit eeppinanuwak nduk nggino yogwi, niniki koonggwi, eekwi nogo mban eeppinanege lek at omaawi ee'ninake logonet, niniki mbaka'lek nogo mendek inom abok aret eeppinanege menggerak nogo,
49003021	nit Ala apuri yi awi ndi awi kuwak eerit nogo monggoorak abok aret Keritut Yetut ninom kunik logonet, yogondak inom, peebi inom, at mondok-mondok alut eeko logowok~o. Amin!
49004001	Ti kenok, noreewi~o. Kit eeko logorak yonggo pinagareegerak Ala nen kit ndak-ndak aret eerit nogwe kiyaawak nduk, an ninowe oone wonok yoranet nege paga keele maa'nabeegwaarak nogo nen, "Ao," mbake logonet, yokkiragi~o.
49004002	Eerit nogo logonet, kiniki tebe yinuk yanggorogon eeppiigwi, kiniki aanaganggenggwi lek nabuwa-kabuwa mbako logonet, yeenggwa-yeenggwa eekwi,
49004003	Aberiniki nen kiniki ambit lambumbinagareegerak nogo kinom ogookkologwe kiyo, liippunuk wonogwe, eeko logonip~o.
49004004	Kiniki lunik wonogwe nogo ambit aret kolaabagip nduk, yonggo pinagareegerak nogo ndak-ndak, kit kineebe ambit lambunik aret. Aberiniki eebe togon ambit aret.
49004005	Nit ninowe nogo eebe ambit aret. Niniki abet mbakwi wone togon ambit aret. Ndi, yiime wuppinanugwi wone nogo kunduk ambit mban aret~o.
49004006	Nit aakumi abok ninogoba ti, Ala ambit aret logonet, oome-endekem at eebe mondok endak warak menggerak. Yi mendek ndi mendek abok aret at abu'me menggerak me, yi eekwi ndi eekwi abok aret at nen mban koonogo yo'nirage kagak eeko monggoorak.
49004007	-
49004008	Ala wone liiru mbanak paga nen ari logonet, "At agi tiyarogon lagi nage logonet, It aakumi keele maarogo piirogo wonogwe nogo, apit aret ndineren lagi nage nagagerik, At amendek onggo lek we aret tumburiragagerak~o," yinuk, yereegerak nogo ndak-ndak, nit togon, at eyabu eeko logowok nduk, Keritut nen, "At ti mendek eeke logowak," kooneegerak nogo, iniki kunik nen ninalitik-ninalitak togop aret unde eeppinaneegerak.
49004009	Ndi, "At lagi nagagerak," yereegerak nogo ti, ngge nduk yereegerak mbakop? Lek~o. At nggween abu'na wambi nage nagagerik, lagi wagagerak nogo kenok, yereegerak nogo lek a?
49004010	Ndi, at wambi nage nagagerik, lagi wagagerak nogo ti, yi awi ndi awi abok aret at eebe endak warak logowak nduk, mbogut irimbaga lombok lagi nagagerak nogo aret.
49004011	At nogo nen it ando nappiigak logowak nduk unde eeppiige, ando Ala wone yorogo logowak nduk unde eeppiige, ando obeelom wone yi awi ndi awi ambime yoragak nugu logowak nduk unde eeppiige, ando o ambit me Ala apuri liirogon inarum logowak nduk, eeppiige, ndi, ando Ala wone mamunirogo logowak nduk eeppiige, eereegerak.
49004012	Ti eereegerak nogo ti, nit Ala eyabu liirogon eerit nogo logonet, nit nineebe paga Keritut eebe mondok wigak yuwak nduk, nit Ala apuri abok aret mondok li'luk eerogo pinaneegerak.
49004013	Ti eeppinaneegerak nogo ti, nit abok aret Ala aput eeke menggerak nineenu ogo logomonggoorik, abet mbakwi paga niniki ambit a'nuk, Keritut iniki mondok koleewak obeelom wonage nogo kokwak, nit togop aret niniki kole eeppinanit wundi wage logowak nduk, unde eeppinaneegerak.
49004014	Togop me, noreewi~o. Yi kilaarak-mogonik eeke logonet, yi mendek ndi mendek piyanogo nippege, o wiya nen yi mendek ndi mendek wonok nage, eeke menggi kwak, elege-aabologwe ti, togop aret wonogwe me, kit kunduk togop logonet, it aakumi pilit wone yogo menggaarak nogo nen aakumi inambo'me laganuwok nduk, iniki koombunuk, inoone amburu paga nomoniren nawok nduk, agan nugwi wone ti mendek kit ugun konenggo logorak mage~o. Ata, Keritut iniki mondok kole menggi kwak, nit togop aret niniki kole eeppinanit wundi wage kenok, nit elege-aabologwe togop ti ndak-ndak logogun lek~o.
49004015	Ata, nit aakumi niniki kunik en Ala ari menggerak wone nogo mban yorogo logonet, ninanobak kwak Keritut iniki abu koleewak menggi kwak, nit togop aret niniki kole ee'ninabuwak nduk, eerit nogo logowok~o.
49004016	Nineenggi-niniyok yeregerak-peregerak abok aret eeriyak ake punik alitak lombok wonage kwe, nineebe ambit ninomanggen paga yinik-kunik eerak logonet, eerit nage kenok, nineebe mondok op aret menggerak nogo kokwak, nit Ala apuri ninanobak kwak Keritut ninom togop aret kunik me, niniki-kiniki kunik eeko logonet, ninalitak eeriyak unde eeppinaneegerak nogo ndak-ndak eerit nugwi niinok, Keritut eebe mondok obeelom aret logonet, nit nineebe paga wiganit nage logogin.
49004017	Togop me, noreewi~o. "It aakumi Ala wone konenggulik endekem mendek nen we aanom warogo koombunuk, eerit nogo mengga kwak, kit togop eerugup~o," yinuk, ninowe nen yo'nege kenok yokkiragi~o.
49004018	It iniki omaawi logonet, "Ala wone woorak nineebi~o," yinuk, yogwe paga it iniki o apit pogom wonogwe, Ala inom ogoorak wonogwe, eekwi me, Ala nen ineenik eeppiyoorak wone nogo, it mondok kobak aret wonogwe~o.
49004019	It maluk eeriyak inagabiti mbaka'lek kumi paga mban iniki lunik logonet, "Ugun-ugun eeruwok~o," mba'nuk, iniki nengge kenok ale'nggen paga eerit nogo menggaarak kwe,
49004020	Keritut eeke nagagerak wone nogo mamunggirogo logonet, kit eekwi ti mendek ambi inom mamunggiroolik~o.
49004021	At eeke nagagerak nogo mamunggirogwe niigak, Ala ari menggerak wone at Yetut ndak-ndak ari nagagerak nogo, kit liirogon konenggo logonet,
49004022	"Niniki nengge kenok mugurok nogo nogoorak nogo ti, maluk ee'ninaburak kagak mugurok nogo nogoorak kogo," yinuk, mamunggologogutak me, kinobaabut maan mendek nogo, nggonenogo mbo punuk,
49004023	kiniki ngget ogobakkigikkinabuwak nduk, Ala oone mban mugurok nogo logonip~o.
49004024	Ala maluk eekeelik obaabut abu abe koonak menggerak nogo kokwak, kit ndak-ndak kinobaabut mondok ngget mendek eerogo pinagawak nduk, yokkiragi~o.
49004025	Togop me noreewi~o. Keritut ninom kunik eenggi-iyok kokwak nit aret me, kit-kit aret pilit pugunggo monggotak nogo mbo punuk, kit abok aret wone abet kenok mban yogo logonip~o.
49004026	Kinanini nen maluk eeriyak ti mage~o. Ndi, kinanini wungge kagak oonegen kilu yi noorak ti mage mban.
49004027	Ibilit nen, "Nanonggwan aga~o," yinuk, kiniki nggagangginake kero, maluk mbuuluk kinikime kumaappunuk logogup~o.
49004028	Kit yogoot waganggo monggotak nogo, ambinom yogoot waagup~o. Ata, kineenggi paga nen mban eerogo nunggwi, it aakumi inamendek lek iinok yeenggwaarogwe, eeko logobagip nduk, yabu ambi eeriyak miippunuk, kineenggi omaawi paga eekko'net nogo logonip~o.
49004029	Wone maluk mendek kinambe paga nen wumbi woroorak ti mage~o. Ata, it konenggwi nogo nen, "Ninabuwa nen yo'nirogwe iigo~o," yuwak nduk, aaninggin ambi inoba age kenok, iniki kole eeppiyoorak wone mban yogo logonip~o.
49004030	Ala nen at apuri wogonabi wage logonet, nit ninom wo'ninabi woroorak nineenu logowok nduk, wam yelok kaawak nen aruk nggaganggo mengga kwak, Aberiniki wo'niragagerak me, Ala Aberiniki nogo, iniki maluk eerogo puurak mage~o.
49004031	Kinoreewi kinom ogoorak wonogwe, neebi-keebi yogwe, nanini-kanini yogwe, wone wakwi, miyuk-meya eerogo piigwi, kinoreewi maluk eeppiigo monggotak nogo mendek abok aret mbo pogo logonip~o.
49004032	Mbo punuk, kinom nabuwa-kabuwa eeko logonet, kiniki yanggonak paga at ambi obeelom eeppegak eeko logonip~o. Keritut eereegerak nogo paga Ala nen kit kinomaluk lek eerogo pereegerak nogo ndak-ndak, kit-kit aret maluk eekkologomonggotak nogo, mari eerogo mbo pogo logonip~o.
49005001	Noreewi~o. Kit Ala apuri kinom kunik me, at eeke menggi kwak, kit ndak-ndak eerit nogo logonip~o.
49005002	Ala ake warogo kani kunggwi iinok, Ala nen obari obeelom kage menggi kwak, at Keritut ninabuwa nen, "Inake kambikit," mba'nuk, ninake kambeegerak nogo ndak-ndak, nabuwa-kabuwa mbako logonet, at ambi obeelom eeppegak eeko logonip~o.
49005003	Kit Ala apuri ake leenak aret kagak, kumi ugun wurinabit nugwi, kiniki kumi paga mban lunik logonet, ugun-ugun eerit nugwi, uugwe-uugwe mbakwi, eerit nugwi kiinok, it aakumi ando nen, "Ala apuri aret kwe, maluk eekwi iyaanip~o," yinuk, kinombakwi iyo, liippunuk, eeko logonip~o.
49005004	Kumi inabok mban agan nugwi, elege negen ugun i'ndok kambuurak mban agan nugwi, iniki kumi paga mban lunik logonet, inoonewak agan nugwi, eekwi ti mendek abok aret yuurak lek maluk mendek kagak agan nugwi me, kit Ala apuri kenok togop yuurak mondok mage. Ata, Ala, "Wa!" mban yoge logonip~o.
49005005	It kumi ugun wurinabit nogo menggaarak inom, iniki kumi paga mban lunik logonet, inabok agan nugu menggaarak inom, ndi, it uugwe-uugwe mbakwi nogo ti, aap kugiwak alut eekwi ndak-ndak aret me, it ti inom, it aap ti eeko menggaarak abok aret Ala Keritut imbirak inabu'me piigo menggam unggwi nagun mondok lek mbako logonip~o.
49005006	It Ala wone tagambunuk, maluk ti mendek eerit nogwe iinok, Ala anini inoba piige menggerak me, it ugun kobak menggaarak nogo nen inoone amburu ndik-ndik agan wogo logonet, kinambokan laganggwi iyo, liippogo logonip~o.
49005007	It aap togop yogo menggaarak nogo ti, kinom kunggoloorak mage~o.
49005008	Kit aa'nduk o apit paga nogo nogogutak kwe, yogondak kinowe nen muk eya eerogo pinagareegerak me, Ala apuri eya paga logonet, eeko mengga kwak, kit togop aret eerit nogo logonip~o.
49005009	It eya paga logonet eerit nogo menggaarak anggen yugu nogo ti, aakumi obeelom eeppiinet nugwi, maluk eeka'lek Ala ari menggerak nogo ndak-ndak eerit nugwi, iniki mbere lek ambit logonet, inoone abet mban agan nugwi, eeko menggaarak me,
49005010	kit nen, "An eeke yi, Ala inikilom mbake menggerak ndak-ndak aret eeke ilik?" yinuk, liippako logonet, Ala apuri eya paga logonet, eeko mengga kwak, kit togop aret eerit nogo logonip~o.
49005011	-
49005012	It aap o apit paga logonet, obeelom ambi eekkoloorak lek kagak eerit nogo menggaarak nogo, kinom lambumbunuk eerit nagup~o. Ata, it kote eeko menggaarak inabok mbininiyak kineebi mbakwi kwe kagak, nggwok paga aret inenggali wappiigo logonip.
49005013	-
49005014	Aap ambi nen ari logonet, "Wologwe wae. Kit nogo yugwi nogo kineenik a'nip~o. Kineenik a'nuk, it aakumi mondok kambak wonogwe nogo, inenggela'me nen wundi wogwe kiinok, Keritut nen eya eekkinabigin~o," yinuk, yereegerak nogo ti, ndi wuninggwi iinok, yi mendek ndi mendek o apit paga wonage nogo kin kogo mengga kwak, it aap kote eeko menggaarak nogo, nggwok paga paganogo inenggali wappiigwi iinok, "Aap yi inobaabut togop aret menggaarak iigo~o," yinuk, yuwak nduk yereegerak kogo~o.
49005015	-
49005016	Togop me, kit eerit nogo monggotak nogo, mondok liippunuk eerit nogo logonip~o. O yi eyom paga aakumi nen maluk mondok alik negen eerit nogo logorak koonggwi me, kiniki lek we ugun eerit nogo logorak ti mage~o. Ata, kiniki mondok warak logonet, "O yogondak obeelom eeriyak ambi yi, nanonggwan agaarak me, eerikit~o," mba'nuk, eerit nogo logonip~o.
49005017	Kumili negen kiniki lek ugun eerit nogo logogup~o. Ata, ninowe nen eeriyak kooneegerak nogo mban liippunuk, eerit nogo logonip~o.
49005018	Ndi, anggur amburu nonggo logomonggotik, kumili kunit namonggotak paga maluk eekkinaburak me, mbo punuk, Aberiniki mban kiniki me liinik logowak nduk, eeko logonip~o.
49005019	Ndi, kit-kit aret kiniki mondok ale'nggen paga ninogoba endage alut eeko logonet, Ndawut ndawi pereegerak nogo inom, ki wone ndawi inom, Ala eeke menggerak ndawi inom, abok aret warit nogo logonip~o.
49005020	Warit nogo logonet, yi mendek ndi mendek apit eeppinanege menggerak nogo paga ninowe Yetut Keritut endage kunogo, "Ninogoba Ala wa," yinuk, keyage wako logonip~o.
49005021	Ninowe Keritut ayuk wuko logonet, kiniki tebe yinuk nabu'me-kabu'me logonip~o.
49005022	Kit kumi yi wae. Kit kinogonggelomini warak kenok, ninowe Yetut abu'me tebe yinuk, monggo kwak, kinogonggelomini inabu'me tebe yinuk, logonip~o.
49005023	At Keritut alik nen nit Ala apuri yi awi ndi awi monggoorak nogo, ninagap ndarogo at eebe paga ambit aruwak nduk, kunogo pinaneegerak me, ninanobak kwak Keritut wonage nogo pogom, kit kumi kinanobak kwak ti, kinogonggelomini aret~o.
49005024	Ndi, Ala apuri yi awi ndi awi monggoorak nogo ti, Keritut abu'me logonet, oone konenggo monggoorak nogo pogom, kit kumi togop aret kinogonggelomini inabu'me tebe yinuk, logonet, it inoone mban konenggo logonip~o.
49005025	Ndi, kit aap yi wae. Kit kinakuwi warak kenok, Keritut nen nit Ala apuri yi awi ndi awi monggoorak nogo, ninabuwa mbake logonet, "Inake kambikit~o," yinuk, ninake kambeegerak nogo kwak, kit kinakuwi togop aret inabuwa inombako logonet, obeelom eeppiigo logonip~o.
49005026	-
49005027	Nit Ala apuri yi awi ndi awi monggoorak ninake kambeegerak nogo ti, "An napuri inoba mili lenggenak yinik-pinik aago ineebe yinuk-punuk eerak iigak koloorak neebi~o. Ata, ineebe kikak naka'lek mondok alik leenak abe kigirikwe lombok iinok kolaakit~o," yinuk, ngguu'mo wappiigo mengga kwak, at oone waganggwi paga ninomaluk lek eerogo pinanege logomenggerik, Ala ake leenak logowok nduk, ninabuwa mbake logonet, ninake kambeegerak~o.
49005028	Ti ndak-ndak kit aap kineebe kiniki kunik eekkologo monggotak nogo kokwak, kinakuwi togop aret kiniki kunik aganako logonip~o. Aap ambi akwe iniki kunik eeke kenok ti, at eebe aret iniki kunik eekkolage menggerak~o.
49005029	-
49005030	Ndi, Keritut eenggi-iyok kwak nit aret me, Keritut nen at apuri yi awi ndi awi monggoorak nogo, iniki kundugu ee'ninake logonet, liirogon ndegenninake menggi kwak, nit aap nineebe ti, nineebi mbakulik~o. Ata, niniki kunik eekkologo logonet, liirogon ndegenggologo monggoorak nogo pogom, kit kineebe ando nogo ti, kinakuwi aret me, kiniki kunik aganako logonet, liirogon aret ndegeninako logonip~o.
49005031	"Togop me, aap nen agalo-ogoba mbo piinok, Akweeluk imbirak ambit a'nuk, it imbirak ineebe mbere kwe, ambit aret logogun~o."
49005032	Ala nen wone yereegerak nogo ti, wone alom abu kumaarak negen aret yereegerak mbake logonet, Keritut apuri yi awi ndi awi monggoorak nogo ninom nonggop togon ambit kunik logorak wakkagak yokkirage kwe, ti mban yokkirage lek~o.
49005033	Ata, kit aap kineebe kiniki kunik eekkologo monggotak kokwak, kinalitak lombok kinakuwi inabuwa mbakwi, ndi, kit kumi kunduk, kinogonggelomini inayuk wuko logonet, inabu'me tebe yinuk, inoone konenggwi, eeko logobagip nduk, inom aret yokkirage agarik~o.
49006001	Wologwe-komologwe yi wae. Kit Ala apuri aret me, kinagalomini-kinogobamini inoone yokkirogwe iinok, konembunuk eeko logorak nogo ti, Ala nen aret kooneegerak me, liirogon eeko logonip~o.
49006002	-
49006003	Ala nen wone, "Yogop ee'nu, ndogop ee'nu," ari logonet, "Kinagalo-kinogoba inayuk wuko logonet, inoone liirogon aret konenggo logomunggup~o," ari nagagerik, ti'nuk, "Nggween paga yime yi wone ndi wone kinoba aga'lek, kineebe obeelom li a'nuk, kanggo logomunggup~o," yinuk, yereegerak nogo ti, wone, "Yogop ee'nu, ndogop ee'nu," yoragagerak eekwi iinok, onggo koloorak wone aa'nduk lombok yoragagerak nogo ti aret.
49006004	Kit aap kinapuri wonogwe kenok, inanini aruwak nduk, eeppiyaagup~o. Ata, Ala wone mugurok nogo logowak nduk, inaruk wakwi, Ala wone mamunirogwe, eeko logonet, tawe eeginako logonip~o.
49006005	Kit aakumi inayeloman monggotak yi wae. Kit nen, "Nogoba yi, Keritut kwak me," yinuk, kinagabiti mbakak inayuk wuko logonet, kiniki obeelom yanggonak paga inoone konembunuk, inake eeko logonip~o.
49006006	Eerit nogo logonet, inikilom kinombaruwak nduk, inigen iigak mban eeko logorak ti lek~o. Ata, "An Keritut ayeloman aret me," yinuk, Ala iniki mbake menggerak nogo, "Eerikit~o," yinuk, kiniki obeelom yanggonak paga eeppiinet nogo logonip~o.
49006007	-
49006008	Nit aakumi inayeloman wonogwe inom, aakumi we ugun wonogwe inom, abok aret obeelom eerit nogwe niinok, ninogoba nen onggo ndak-ndak aret wo'niraagin nineenu me, "Yi aakumi inake eeke lek~o. Ata, nowe ake aret eeke~o," yinuk, kineebi mbaka'lek kiniki ale'nggen paga eerit nogo logonip~o.
49006009	Ndi, kit nogobamini yi wae. Kit kinayeloman wonogwe kenok, "Nit ninogoba ambit mbogut paga wonage nogo nen ninayeloman inom, inogobamini nit inom, ninetenggen liippinaninuk wo'niraagin lek, eekwi onggo ndak-ndak wo'niraagin," mbako logonet, kinoone omaawi paga yoraagup~o. Ata, it kinayeloman nen iniki ale'nggen paga eeppinagago mengga kwak, kit ndak-ndak kiniki yanggonak paga obeelom eeppiigo logonip~o.
49006010	Wone abu aret yokkiragarak me, age yobok ambi yi yokkira~o. Kinowe omaawi ambik nogo paga kiniyok panggombunuk, kinogogumbuk logonip~o.
49006011	Ibilit nen iniki koombunuk, kinambokan lagani wage kero, mugogo nappegak eeko logobagip nduk, Ala nen at eegin-omaale li'luk eerogo pinagareegerak nogo, waganggo logonip~o.
49006012	Wim ninom nambuko logonet, perenggologwe nogo ti, nit aap nggween paga mendek ninom nambukwi lek~o. Ata, it inayuk warak o oolo yayi nugu logonet, aakumi nggween paga yime iniki o apit aago pogom wonogwe nogo, maluk eeruwak nduk, iniki nggaganggo menggaarak Tile inom, at awuri yi kugi ndi kugi inom, abok aret ninom wim nambuko logonet, perenggologwe me,
49006013	-
49006017	maluk eekkinabuwak nduk wogwe iinok, mondok mugogo nappiigo logonet, kit mban kineegin tiyanak logobagip nduk, inagabee'le mbam nggerenggologo mengga kwak, Ala ari menggerak wone kinikime nggerorogon waganggwi, tin yikkologo mengga kwak, Ala obaabut obeelom menggerak nogo yikkologwe, sepatu omaawi mendek yikko'nok nogo mengga kwak, Ala ninom lambumbinaniyak obeelom wone nogo pipuk ee'nuk nogwe, eeko logomonggotik, at maluk lombok eeke menggerak nogo nen omaale kani kunik negen namburi wage nogo, mbeenogo nappogo logobagip nduk, nggeemu langgunggologo mengga kwak, abet mba'nuk kiniki Ala oba panggombugwi, petagi langgunggologo mengga kwak, kinagap ndariyak wone aberogo kologwe, tege wooluwak kwak ti, Aberiniki nen Ala wone wo'niragagerak nogo waganggwi, eeko logomonggotik, Ala nen at eegin-omaale wurogo pinagareegerak nogo, li'luk eeppunuk, kinogogumbuk nu'lek logonip~o.
49006018	Kinogogumbuk mondok kinom perenggologo logonet, Ala nen yeenggwaagiraawak nduk, Aberiniki nen yokkirage kagak, puk aga'lek Ala nggino yogwi, nogo yigin eekkinaka'lek kineenik logonet, it Ala apuri ake leenak abok aret inake tamban eekwi, eeko logonet,
49006019	-
49006020	an kunduk, obeelom wone kote kumaarak wonagagerak nogo, yoranet nege logokit nduk, Ala nen aret leenogo mippaneegerak kagak keele maarogo mambaneegwaarak yime logonet, nagabiti nen noone puk logorak ti lek~o. Ata, wone nogo yoraakit nduk, eeke neegak, Ala nen, "Togop yoret~o," yinuk, yo'nege kenok, nagabiti mbaka'lek noone teeluk paganogo yorage logokit nduk, it Ala apuri abok aret inake tamban eeko logonet, an kunduk, nake tamban eeko logonip~o.
49006021	At ninawot niniki kunik ninowe eyabu liirogon eeke menggerak Tikikut nogo nen, an neebe nonggop logonet, eeke minggirak wone nogo, abok aret kineenu arubagip nduk, yokkira woraagin~o.
49006022	Kineenu eeppinagarak nduk, kinowagam nappi woraminggirak wage logomenggerik, nit abok nineebe nonggop wonogwe nogo, ninabok yokkirage, ndi, kiniki eyak wappinagage, eeri woraagin~o.
49006023	Kit ninoreewi Ala apuri abok aret abet mba'nuk, kiniki ugun obeelom ambit lambunik logonet, nabuwa-kabuwa mbako logobagip nduk, ninogoba Ala ninowe Yetut Keritut imbirak nen eeppinagago logowak~o.
49006024	Ninowe Yetut Keritut kit kiniki kunik eekwi nogo, lek aga'lek mondok kundugu wonogwe kiinok, kinabuwa mbake logonet, kinarum logogin~o. An Pawulut nen abu aret yokkiragi~o. Noreewi wa!
50001001	Kit Keritut Yetut kinom kunik Ala apuri ake leenak o Pilipi wonogwe inom, Ala apuri inarum monggotak inom, aap yeenggwaaragak inom, kit abok aret Keritut Yetut ayeloman mini an Pawulut Timotiyut nimbirak nen wone ambi yokkiraawi~o.
50001002	Ninogoba Ala ninowe Yetut Keritut imbirak iniki kunik nen wokkirogwe, kiniki ugun tayenak ale'nggen logobagip nduk, eeppinagagwi, eeko logogun~o.
50001003	An niniki kinoba abe'nage kenok, nogoba Ala, "Wa," yoge minggirak.
50001004	-
50001005	Tamban eeke logonet, o aa'nduk nen nok-nok yogondak kuli aret, obeelom wone kit ninom ndak-ndak eerit nugwi nogo, abe'nage kenok, niniki ale'nggen mbake logonet, kinake tamban eeke minggirak~o.
50001006	"At Ala nen obeelom eekkinaburak nduk, aa'nduk eereegerak kuli nogo nen, kinikime eekkinake tit kagak, o age yobok Keritut Yetut woraagin," an abet aret mbake logonet, yokkiragi~o.
50001007	An yogondak keele maarak wonage neegak inom, aa'nduk nawone mbanuwak nduk, mippanugo mbareegwa, obeelom wone mondok nu'lek logowak nduk, yorage neegak inom, kit mbo panulik me, Ala iniki kunik nen unde eeppaneegerak nogo, "Kat ninom ndak-ndak eeko logowok~o," yinuk, kit abok aret eeko nogogutak nogo paga, an niniki mondok kit ninom kunik wonage me, kinoba abe'nage kenok, niniki ale'nggen logonet, kit kinake Ala, "Wa!" yoriyak ti, op aret mbake agarik~o.
50001008	At Keritut Yetut nen kinabuwa mbake logonet, iniki kunik eekkinake menggerak nogo kokwak, an togon kit ninom niniki mondok kunik me, "It iyaakit lak, ao," kinombake nogo ti, Ala eenu aret~o.
50001009	Kit yi wone ndi wone alom liirogon kineenu ogwe, ndi, kiniki warak logonet, yi mendek ndi mendek eraambe yelok kogwe, eeko logonet, it kinom kiniki kunik aganakwi nogo, ambinom nggwok arit wundi nage logowak nduk, kinake tamban eeke minggirak~o.
50001010	-
50001011	Kit ti eeko logobagip nduk, kinake tamban eeke minggirak nogo ndak-ndak eekwi kiinok, yi mendek ndi mendek abut mbambunuk, abe kenok mban eeko logomonggotak me, Keritut woroorak eyom ti paga Ala endage alut eerak tiyanak logowak nduk, eyo anggen abu abe yi'nage menggi kwak, Yetut Keritut eeppinagage kagak obeelom mban eeko logomonggotak nogo paga at enegen kiige logomenggerik, "Kit maluk eerulik obeelom mban eeko nogotak~o," yinuk, oone kinoba pinagagin lek~o.
50001012	Ai noreewi~o. An ee'nabeegwaarak nogo paga obeelom wone mondok nggwok wigak yereegerak me, kineenu arubagip nduk, yokkiragi~o.
50001013	An keele maarak wonage yi paga, aap endagembogut awuri apit inom, it aakumi weelek ugun mendek inom, abok aret, "Pawulut nen Keritut wone yoranet nage nagagerak nogo paga, keele maarogo mambiigo menggam time wonage~o," yinuk, ineenu ogogwaarak.
50001014	Ndi, ninoreewi ninowe inom kunik wonogwe ando apit nogo ti, an keele maa'nabeegwaarak nogo paga iniki ninowe oba panggombunuk logonet, yogondak Ala wone yoroorak inagabiti lek mondok inogogumbuk logonet, yoranet nugu agaarik~o.
50001015	It ando nen, "Nit togon ninoone konenggo logowak~o," yinuk, abet aret ineebi nombako logonet, "Tebembuwok," mba'nuk, Keritut wone yorogo menggaarak kwe, it ando nen perak, iniki obeelom paga yorogo agaarik~o.
50001016	Wone obeelom wone Keritut nen yo'niragagerak nogo, amburu mbanogo yorage logokit nduk, Ala nen aret mippaneegerak yime wonage ineenu me, ninom niniki kunik logonet aret yorogo ogoorik~o.
50001017	Ndi, it ando nogo nen perak, iniki obeelom paga Keritut wone yorogwe lek~o. Ata, "An ari mban konenuwak~o," yinuk, an keele maarak neegak, aaninggin ambinom noba paniyak mba'nuk iniki laakot mbako logonet, yorogo menggaarak~o.
50001018	Togop agan nogwe iinok ti op mban aret~o. It iniki laakot nombako logonet yorogwe a, iniki obeelom paga yorogwe a, nogo ti, Keritut wone mban aret yorogwe me, "Op mban aret~o," yinuk, niniki ale'nggen mban mbake minggirak me, yogondak togon niniki ale'nggen aret agarik~o.
50001019	Kit nen nake tamban eekwi, ndi, Yetut Keritut Aberiniki nen niniki eyak wappanege, eekwi ti paga keele piinogo wumbanugun an neenu me, niniki ale'nggen mban mbake agarik~o.
50001020	An eeke logokit nduk unde eeppaneegerak nogo, ando eeka'lek neenok, nenggali wappaniyak neebi me, "Ao," mba'nuk, an neebe paga Keritut tiyappuurak mbake minggirak nogo, yogondak ndak-ndak mbake logonet, kambuurak kenok, neenik logorak kenok, "Op mban aret~o," yinuk, nagabiti mbaka'lek yoranet nege logorak uugwe lombok mbake agarik~o.
50001021	Neenik logorak kenok ti, Keritut ake aret~o. Ndi, kambuurak kenok ti, an ambi kola noorak me, neenik logorak kenok, kambuurak kenok ti, op mban aret~o.
50001022	An neenik logorak kenok, Ala wone yoranet nage paga ambi anggen yippiyoorak kagak eerukwak me, an nggaruk togon, "Kambi a, neenik logi a?" yinuk, miikkoloorak ti meek~o.
50001023	-
50001024	An Keritut nimbirak logorak ti, op lombok mbake logonet, nggween paga yime mbo punuk, ka noorak, "Ao," mbake kwe, kit ninom logonet eeppinagarak ambi wonage mban me, niniki abu mbere ee'nake~o, noreewi.
50001025	Kit eeppinagarak ambi wonage aret mbakirak me, kit abet mbareegutak nogo paga kiniki kole arit unggwage kagak, ale'nggen mbako logobagip nduk, ninom aret logorak mbake agarik~o.
50001026	An keele piinogo teppanemenggaarak paga kiya wage neenok, Keritut Yetut kinom kunik logonet, kiniki ale'nggen mbako monggotak nogo nggwok lombok wiganggo logobagip nduk, kiya woraagin mbake agarik~o.
50001027	An yime wonage neegak eekwi konenigin a, time kiya wage neenok eekwi kiyaagin a, kit obeelom wone abet mba'nuk waganeegutak nogo, mbo pega'lek kiniki ambit a'nuk, nu'lek logonet, eerit nogwe neenu arigin me, obeelom wone Keritut nen yo'niragagerak nogo, ndak-ndak liirogon aret eerit nogo logonip~o.
50001028	It kinom ogoorak wonogwe nogo ineebe paga kinagabiti mbarugup~o. Kinagabiti mbaka'lek nugwi ti paga, it kinom ogoorak wonogwe nogo nen, "Ia! It abet aret yogwe me, nit perak, lek eerogo pinaniyak kagi," yinuk, yugun~o. Ndi, kit perak, Ala nen abet aret kinagap ndakkinabeegerak kineenu arumunggup~o.
50001029	At Ala nen kinabuwa mbake logonet, eeriyak kooneegerak nogo ti, kit kiniki Keritut oba panggombunuk abet mbarubagip nduk mban koonulik~o. Ata, at eeke nagagerak obeelom wone yoranet nugwi paga aaninggin-paaninggin inom kaabagip nduk kooneegerak me, kiniki ale'nggen mbako logonet waganggo logonip~o.
50001030	Piyak-payak eerogo panugwi iigak, Ala wone lek age kero nduk, nggwiirit-nggwaarit yorage neego nogogutak nogo inom, ndi, yogondak eeppanugwi iigak, nogogumbuk logonet, eerit nage konenggwi nogo inom, kit ninom ndak-ndak aret eeppinanggo agaarik~o.
50002001	Keritut kinom kunik me, kiniki eyak wappinagage, at kinabuwa mbake logonet kiniki yanggongginake, eeke kagak, Aberiniki kinom kunik wonogwe, kit mban-mban niniki-kiniki kunik eeko logonet, obeelom eeppiinet nugwi, eeko logorak eekkinake kogotak kenok,
50002002	an ambinom niniki ale'nggen nggwok lombok kaakit nduk, kit togop aret kiniki ambit eeppunuk logonet, Keritut iniki kunik eekkinake nogo kokwak, kinoreewi kinom niniki-kiniki kunik eekwi, kiniki lambunik logonet eeriyak ambit koombunuk eekwi, eeko logonip~o.
50002003	Kit yi mendek ndi mendek eeko logonet, ambi koloorak nduk eeppiigwi, ndi, "Tiyappinanuwak," mba'nuk eekwi, ti eerugup~o. Ata, kiniki tebenak logonet, "An ti, meek, ndi, nore perak, iya~o," mbako logonet, eeppiigo logonip~o.
50002004	Kit kinalitak kinobaalombok mban koonggologo logogup~o. Ata, kinoreewi inobaalombok inom koonggo logonip~o.
50002005	At Keritut Yetut iniki wonagagerak nogo kokwak, kit togop aret logonip~o.
50002006	At Keritut nogo ti, Ala iniki menggerak kokwak, Keritut iniki ndak-ndak aret wonagagerak kwe, "Ala nimbirak ndak-ndak tiyanak aret me, an tiyanak logokit," ti mbarulik.
50002007	Ata, at iniki nen aret tebeppatinuk, "It aakumi inayeloman kokwak eekkola~o," yinuk, aakumi nit pogom aret nda'nagagerak.
50002008	Nda'nage nagagerik, aakumi nit pogom aret nege logonet, eyo karo-karo paga kambuurak ti, meek aret kwe, Iniki tebeppatinuk, "Ti paga kambuurak op aret~o," yinuk, kambeegerak.
50002009	Togop aret eeke mbareegi, at Ala nen mondok agi lombok tiyappereegerak. Yi aakumi ndi aakumi abok inendage tebenak iigak, at mban endage tiyanak logowak nduk, mondok tiyappereegerak wonage me,
50002010	It mbogut paga mendek inom, nggween paga mendek inom, nggween abu'na mendek inom, it abok aret Yetut endage kumbunuk, abu'me tebe yinuk, ayuk wukwi,
50002011	Ndi, aakumi inanebunu lombok abok aret ninogoba Ala endage tiyak yuwak nduk, "Yetut Keritut ti, ninowe aret~o," yinuk, nggwok paga paganggwi, Eeruwak nduk, Tiyappereegerak~o.
50002012	Togop me, noreewi~o. Kit an niniki kunik me, wone ambi yokkira~o. Aa'nduk kit ninom time logonet, an noone yugu ndak-ndak eeko nogogutak nogo kokwak, yogondak neebe yime neegak, kinagap ndakkolaabagip nduk, kinagabiti nen kinaganak wake logonet, ambinom nggwiirit-nggwaarit eeko logonip~o.
50002013	At Ala nen eeriyak inikilom mbake menggerak nogo, kit nen, "Eerikit," mbakwi, ti'nuk, eebe aret eekwi, eekwi nogo ti, Ala nen mban aret koonggirage menggerak.
50002014	-
50002015	It aakumi o yogondak ndarak wonogwe nogo inobaabut nggolo iniki mondok maluk mban koonggo menggaarak inenggela'me laaluguragan pindan-pindan eeke menggi kwak, kit togop logonet, inoone kinoba pinagaga'lek Ala apuri kiniki kikak naka'lek abu obeelom mban logonet, eerit nugwi kiyaawak nduk, kit yi mendek ndi mendek eeko logonet, kinoone laakit-laakot yogwe, wone wakwi, eerugup~o.
50002016	At Keritut woroorak eyom paga, "An mbe agan nage, anggon-panggon ee'nake kagak eerit nage, eeke nagagirak nogo ti, we aanom warogo eerulik ambi kolaakit nduk eereegirak kagi," mba'nuk, niniki tiyappake logonet, nale'nggen kaakit nduk, wone nineenik ee'ninake menggerak wone nogo, kit nggirik-nggerok agago porogo logonip~o.
50002017	Kit abet mba'nuk kineebe apit Ala wogo'nuk, at ake eerit nogwe nogo ti, Ala ake warogo wogogo mengga kwak aret me, ambinom eerit nogo logobagip nduk, kinake eeke neegak, ndomba warak amiya obaga kilippogo mengga kwak, "An yogondak togop eeppaniyak op aret," mba'nuk, niniki ale'nggen mbake me, kit togon kiniki ale'nggen mbako logonip~o.
50002018	An niniki ale'nggen mbake minggi kwak, kit ndak-ndak kiniki ale'nggen mbako logobagip nduk, yokkiragi~o.
50002019	Kit nonggop wonogwe nogo liippinaganuk yo'niri woramenggerak neenu age logominggirik, niniki ugun tayenak logokit nduk, ninowe Yetut nen niniki koonnege kenok, Timotiyut mbet-mbet pekkiya woraawak nduk, kinowagam nappi woroorak mbakirak~o.
50002020	-
50002021	It aakumi yime abok aret Yetut Keritut obaalombok eerit noorak mbaka'lek, it inobaalombok mban koonggo'net nogwe iigak kwe, at Timotiyut alik nen perak, kit nonggop wonogwe nogo, mondok abet aret kinoba abeke menggerak me, at aret nappi woraagin~o.
50002022	Aap ambi apuluk nen ogoba yeenggwaage menggi kwak, an obeelom wone yoranet nage neegak, at ko'lu-kii'me yeenggwaanege nagagerak ti paga, at obaabut kineenu aret me,
50002023	nonggop togon eeppaniyak nawone mbanggwi nogo, neenu age logominggirik, mbet-mbet kinowagam nappi woraagin mbake agarik~o.
50002024	Ndi, an togon, mbet-mbet kiya woroorak nogoba Ala nen tu koonogo panigin abet aret mbake kwe,
50002025	waga'lek neegak, niniki eyak wappanuwak nduk, aap ambi awot imbirak ndak-ndak wim nambuko mengga kwak, Ala wone wigak yuwak nduk, nimbirak ndak-ndak eeko monggoorak nore Epapororitut kit nappi wogotak nogo, iyokan kinowagam nappi wage ti~o.
50002026	At nogo nen, "An andi ee'nakerak noreewi muk konenggaarak me, nonggoti mbakwi iigak logokwak, pegiya na ilik?" yinuk, iniki piirik eeke kage nagarik, at aa'nduk kinowagam nappi wagi ti~o.
50002027	At andi kambuurak abet aret eereegerak kwe, Ala abuwa mbake logonet, obeelom eeppereegerak. At mban abuwa mbareegerak lek~o. At andi eereegerak nogo paga an togon niniki ambinom aaninggin logonet, wakko'net unggwage logokwak, niniki teeluk logokit nduk, obeelom eeppereegerak.
50002028	Togop me, at kiya wage kenok, kiniki ale'nggen paga keyage warogo waganggwi kiinok, an niniki piirik wonage nogo, tayok ari logonet, niniki ale'nggen mbarikit nduk, mbet-mbet kinowagam nappi wagi ti~o.
50002029	-
50002030	Ndi, kit an eeppaniyak mbareegutak nogo obaane'me at aret eeppani wage logonet, "Keritut ake eerit nage logonet, kambuurak op aret~o," yinuk, agabiti nen eebe ili yikkoloolik aret neya wagagerak me, yogondak kit kiya wage ti, "Ninore Keritut imbirak kunik nogo niya wage yi~o," yinuk, kiniki ale'nggen paga keyage warogo wanip~o. It aap togoti mendek ambi kiya wogwe iinok, keyage warogo wogonako logomunggup~o.
50003001	Noreewi~o. "Kinowe kinom kunik logonet, kiniki ale'nggen aret logonip~o," yinuk, wone irip paga yokkiragi ti aret~o. An aa'nduk liiru mbanggiragagirak nogo ndak-ndak, peebi mbanggiroorak neebi mbakeelik~o. Kit kiniki nu'lek logobagip nduk, mbanggiroorak op aret mbake agarik~o.
50003002	It aap nggeewo negen maluk lombok eeko menggaarak nogo, kiya wogo logonet, "Kinagabolo mbaninip~o," yinuk, yokkira wogwe iyo, liippunuk kiniki tum wako logonip~o.
50003003	"Neebe ndogop eeppaneegwaarak~o," yinuk, niniki ti paga panggombunuk, tiyappugwi lek~o. Ala Aberiniki nen ninikime yo'nirage kagak, Ala alut eekwi, Keritut Yetut ee'ninabeegerak nogo tiyappugwi, eeko monggoorak nogo ti, ninagabolo abe mbanak nit aret~o.
50003004	It ando nen, "Neebe ndogop eeppaneegwaarak~o," yinuk, ti paga iniki panggombunuk, tiyappatiyak mbakwi nogo ti, mbuuluk eeppiyareegwaarak kagak mbakwi, ndi, an perak, iya lombok eeppaneegwaarak me, niniki ti paga panggombunuk, tiyappatiyak op aret kwe, "Ti paga nen ambi eekkoloorak lek," mba'nuk mbo pereegirak nogo yi aret~o.
50003005	An ndarak neegak nogo 7 yippunuk, 8 paga nagabolo mbaneegwaarak. Neebe ti, Iterali mendek aret kwe, nanebunu perak, Mbeniyamin mendek aret~o. Nagalo-nogoba kunduk, Iberani mendek aret. Ndi, Muta wone yugu liiru mbanak li'lak eeka an Pariti mendek aret wonagagirak.
50003006	Wone ti nogo, niniki kundugu lombok logonet, Ala apuri kuwak eerit nogo menggaarak nogo piyak-payak eerogo inoorit nege nagagirak. Obeelom eekkolaawak nduk, Muta wone ndak-ndak eeko menggaarak nogo, an togon ndak-ndak aret eeke nagagirak me, aakumi ambi nen inoone noba panega'lek aret wonogogwaarak.
50003007	Ti paga an ambi op eekkolaakit nduk, eeke nagagirak kwe, yogondak Keritut wone wagangge nagagirik, "Wone aa'nduk nogo ti, we aanom warogo eerit nage nagagirak kagi," yinuk, mbo pereegirak.
50003008	-
50003009	Ndi, an nowe Keritut Yetut neenu ariyak ti mondok iya me, "Yi mendek ndi mendek eeriyak abok aret we aanom warogo eerit nage logorak kagi," mbake nagagirik, Muta wone ndak-ndak eeke nagagirak nogo paga obeelom eekkoloorak ti, neebi~o. Ata, Keritut abet mbakwi paga Ala nen nit obeelom eerogo pinanege nogo mendek, "Muk eeppagagirak me, Keritut kimbirak kiniki kunik wonage keegi~o," yinuk, yo'niruwak nduk, Keritut kolage nagagirik, an yi eekak ndi eekak eeke nagagirak nogo abok aret, "Yi inambeebuk pogom aret kagi," yinuk, mbo pereegirak.
50003010	-
50003011	At Keritut eebe inom, ndi, Keritut ninake kangge mbareegi, Ala omaawi paga eenik agago mippereegerak nogo inom, "Liippatikit lak ao," mbake logonet, an kambunuk nogo menggam nen neenik agago mippanuwak nduk, at Keritut iniki yanggonak kagak, aaninggin-paaninggin oba punuk, wako mbareegwa, kambunuk, eenik agagerak nogo kwak, an ndak-ndak neegak, eeppaniyak op aret mbake agarik~o.
50003012	An niniki muk kole ee'nake, ndi, wone agan wagarak nogo abu eeppanege, eereegerak me nduk yokkirage ti lek~o. Ata, Keritut Yetut nen ee'nabikit nduk kwaa'nabeegerak nogo, "Aret kolaakit~o," yinuk, nengga loolo aret mugurok nage agarik~o.
50003013	At nen eeppaniyak nduk, mii'nabeegerak nogo ti, muk eeppaneegerak me nduk, yokkiragi ti lek~o, noreewi. Ata, an aa'nduk eeke nagagirak nogo, nggonenogo nambokan mbo punuk, ngget mendek eeppaniyak koonogo pereegerak nogo, kola naakit nduk eeke logonet,
50003014	Keritut Yetut eereegerak paga at Ala nimbirak mbogut paga logokit nduk, yonggo paneegerak nogo mban nengga loolo agago punuk, mbe agan mugurok nage agarik~o.
50003015	Kit kiniki muk kole agaarak kenok ninom togop aret mbe agan nogo logowok~o. Ndi, kit ando togop eeriyak mbaka'lek kenok, eeko logobagip nduk, Ala nen aret eekkinabigin me,
50003016	nit abok niniki ambit eeppunuk, kola noorak nduk, wone aa'nduk waganeegurak nogo mbo punuk, niniyok paga yungguninuk woroorak ti mage~o. Ata, abeko logonet, mondok mugurok nogo logowok~o.
50003017	-
50003018	Noreewi~o. It aap ando apit nogo nen, "Keritut eyo karo-karo paga kambeegerak wone woorak nineebi," mba'nuk, iniki alik koonit nogo menggaarak me, "Ala inom wim mbanak wonogwe~o," yinuk, ko'lu-kii'me yokkirage minggirak nogo, yogondak ambinom le ari logonet yokkiragi~o. It aap ti, togop eerit nogwe me, an eeke minggi kwak, kit ndak-ndak eeko logonet, it kinoreewi ando nen nit eeko monggoorak nogo kokwak eekwi iinok, liirogon aret inarum logonip~o.
50003019	It aap ti nen nggween paga mendek mban abekwi, inaanogum ake mban tiyappugwi, inenggali ariyak kagak wogoppakwi, eeko menggaarak me, Ala nen mondok lek eerogo piyaagin kwe,
50003020	nit perak, ninawi ninaworak mbogut paga wonage me, ninagap ndaka ninowe Yetut Keritut mbogut paga nen, "Mbet-mbet woraawak lak, ao," yinuk, tokkogo ogoorik~o.
50003021	Wambi wage logonet, at omaawi paga yi mendek ndi mendek abok aret at abu'me logowak nduk, tebemborogo menggerak nogo paga nen ninagabolo maluk pili age menggerak mendek yi, nggonenogo mbo punuk, obaane'me at agabolo mondok alik ngget mendek nogo aret yippinanigin~o.
50004001	Togop me. noreewi~o. Kit an niniki abu kunik me, kinoba mondok aberak mban wonage~o. An nanggare-nggare mendaarak inom, niniki ale'nggen mbake inom, ti, kit kineebe aret me, ninowe kinom kunik logonet, wone ti mondok nu'lek porogo logonip~o. Ai, noreewi niniki kunik wa!
50004002	Kit kumi Ewuworiya kunduk, Tinitike kunduk, kimbirak ninowe kinom kiniki kunik logonet, kiniki ambit lambunik logobagip nduk, noone yanggorogon yokkiragi~o.
50004003	Ndi, kat nore Tundogot nimbirak Ala eyabu ndak-ndak eeke menggendak me, it kumi ti, obeelom wone wigak yuwak nduk, nggwiirit-nggwaarit eeko nogogwaarak me, yeenggwaarage logot~o. Ndi, aap Kelemen kunduk, it an noreewi ando inendage mbuku ineenik aganaka paga mbanak wonage nogo kunduk, togop aret ninom eeko nogogurak me, inom yeenggwaarage logot~o.
50004004	"Ninowe kinom kunik logonet, kiniki ale'nggen mban mbako logonip~o," yinuk, ne mbere paga yokkiragi~o, noreewi.
50004005	Ninowe woroorak abu panggo yegerak me, it aakumi abok nen, "Iniki abe paga aakumi obeelom eeppiinet nugwi iigo~o," yinuk, kinombaruwak nduk, eerit nogo logonip~o.
50004006	Aaninggin nano mendek ambi kinoba age kenok, kiniki piirik logogup~o. Ata, "Aaninggin ndogop noba agaarak~o," yinuk, tamban eekwi, ndi, kinamendek ambi lek kenok, wokkiraawak nduk, "Ala wa," yinuk, nggino yogwi, eeko logonip~o.
50004007	Ti eekwi kiinok, niniki piirik lek ugun tayenak ale'nggen logowok nduk, eeppinanege menggerak alom nit kin kaga'lek niigak kwe, eeppinanegak mban eeke menggerak Ala nogo nen, Keritut Yetut kinom kiniki kunik me, kineebe-kiniki abok aret liirogon kinarum logogin~o.
50004008	Noreewi~o. Wone irip paga ambiriluk yi, yokkira~o. Wone abet mban agan nugwi, iya eeriyak kenok mban eerit nugwi, a'me nggelok mban eeppiinet nugwi, kumi inabok yaga'lek wonogwe, kinoone abe kigirikwe mban agan nugwi, "Wone abe yigi," yuwak nduk agan nugwi, eekwi ti mendek abok aret eekwi kiinok, aakumi nen, "Yi abu obeelom aret eekwi iigo~o," yinuk, tiyappogo logorak aret me, ti mendek mban eeko logobagip nduk, kiniki koonggo logonip~o.
50004009	An wone mamunggirage neegak, waganggo nogogutak inom, ari neegak kinaruk konenggo nogogutak inom, eeke neegak kinigen neego nogogutak inom, nogo abok aret eerit nogo logonip~o. Ndi, niniki ugun tayenak ale'nggen logowok nduk, eeppinanege menggerak Ala nogo nen kinarum aret logogin~o.
50004010	Aa'nduk noba kiniki abe'naka'lek wonogogutak kwe, yogondak iluk kiniki abe'nakwi kiige nagarik, nowe nimbirak kunik logonet, niniki ale'nggen ambik mbake agarik~o. Aa'nduk we noba aberak wonogogutak kwe, yeenggwaaniriyak eyom awo aga'lek kenok, puk wonogogutak me nduk yokkiragi~o, noreewi.
50004011	An yi mendek ndi mendek abok aret noba age kagak, niniki ugun tayenak logorak mamunggolagagirak me, an namendek lek kenok, "Ambi wo'negabok eekaarak ao," yinuk, yokkirage lek~o.
50004012	An namendek lek kenok, wonage kenok, ti neenu aret~o. An mbi ndonggoppanege, abu ee'nake, ti neenu mban. Ndi, namendek ka'let age, namendek lek age, yi mendek ndi mendek op-maluk abok aret noba age nogo kagak niniki ugun tayenak logorak mamunggolagagirak.
50004013	Keritut nimbirak kunik logonet, omaawi eeppanege kagak, an yi eekak ndi eekak abok eeriyak op aret kage minggirak~o.
50004014	Op aret eeriyak kage neegak kwe, an aaninggin noba age mbareegi, kit nen yeenggwaanereegutak me, "Wa," yokkiragi~o.
50004015	Kit Pilipi mendek yi wae. An maan aa'nduk obeelom wone yi awi ndi awi yoranet nage logokit nduk, o Makendoniya mbo punuk o alik me nage neegak, Ala apuri kuwak eerit nogo monggoorak kenok ti, yeenggwa-yeenggwa eeko monggoorak kwe, it abok aret puk iigak, kit Ala apuri o Pilipi nen mban yeenggwaanereegutak nogo kineenu aret~o.
50004016	An o Tetalonika wonage neegak, kit nen ne mbere paga yeenggwaanereegutak nogo kunduk aberak aret wonage~o.
50004017	Kinamendek ambi wo'nirubagip nduk, an nggino yokkiraga'lek neegak, wo'nereegutak waganeegirak nogo ti, Ala nen peebi onggo nggwok wokkiraawak nduk, eyo anggen yi'nage menggi kwak, kit togop aret anggen nggwok yikkologwe kiyaakit nduk, waganeegirak~o.
50004018	Kit nappani wogogutak nogo, abok aret waganeegirak me, lek aga'lek wonage aret~o. Ala ake pugu kani kunggwi obari obeelom kenok Ala nen, "Op wo'nega~o," yinuk, iniki ale'nggen mbake menggi kwak, kit an nake pugu aap Epapororitut nen wo'niruwak nduk nappi wogogutak nogo, wonok niri wage mbareegi, wagangge nagagirik, ndiinik-piinik agago pereegirak lek aga'lek wonage aret~o.
50004019	Nit eeriyak ambi mendek lek age kenok, Keritut Yetut eereegerak paga at Ala nen oona ngginik kagak wo'nirage logogin~o.
50004020	"Ninogoba Ala endage mondok-mondok tiyappogo logowok~o," yinuk, abet aret yokkiragi~o. Amin.
