50004021	Ala apuri ake leenak Keritut Yetut kinom kiniki kunik wonogwe nogo abok aret keyage wappiigo logonip~o. Ndi, an noreewi ninom yime wonogwe nogo nen keyage wappinagaga~o.
50004022	Ala apuri ake leenak o yime wonogwe abok nen keyage wappinagagwi iigak, it Kayitat apuri logorogon nen kunduk, keyage wappinagaga mban~o.
50004023	Ninowe Yetut Keritut iniki kunik en eeppinagage logonet, kinarum aret logogin~o. An Pawulut Timotiyut nimbirak nen abu aret yokkirogo~o. Wa.
51001001	Ala iniki mbareegerak paga Keritut Yetut ayonggo nappiigak mendek agago paneegerak an Pawulut ninawot Timotiyut nimbirak nen
51001002	kit abet mbareegutak Keritut kinom kunik ninoreewi Ala apuri ake leenak o Kolote wonogwe nogo, wone ambi yokkiraawi~o. Ninogoba Ala iniki kunik nen wokkirage, ndi, kiniki ugun tayenak ale'nggen logobagip nduk, eeppinagage, eeke logogin~o.
51001003	-
51001004	Kit Keritut Yetut abet mba'nuk, kiniki at oba panggombugwi, ndi, it Ala apuri ake leenak abok aret kiniki kunik aganakwi, eekwi nogo, kinabok ninaruk konenggo nogootik, kinake tamban eeko logonet, kulinik-kalinik ninowe Yetut Keritut ogoba Ala mondok, "Wa," yogo monggoorak.
51001005	Ala ari menggerak wone obeelom wone yokkirogo logonet, "Kit abet mbakwi kiinok, kinake aago mbogut paga wonage~o," yinuk, aa'nduk yokkirogogwaarak nogo konembunuk, mondok kola noorak kiniki lunik logonet, kiniki abet mbakwi, kinoreewi kiniki kunik aganakwi, eekwi yogwe konenggo nogoorik, yokkirogo~o.
51001006	Obeelom wone kinaruk konenggwi, Ala abet aret iniki kunik en eeppinagage menggerak wone nogo liippugwi, eeko nogogutik, abet mba'nuk, waganeegutak kuli nen, yogondak awo aret kinenggela'me nen wiganinuk nage me, eyoonggen yi'nage menggi kwak, yi o ndi o abok togop aret wiganinuk nage logonet, anggen abu alik negen yi'nage agaarik~o.
51001007	Wone obeelom wone ti nogo, at ninom niniki kunik Ala ayeloman logonet, ndak-ndak eeko monggoorak Epaparat nogo nen aret mamunggiragagerak~o. At Keritut ayeloman logonet, nit kinake eeriyak meek kenok ninobaane'me at aret kulinik-kalinik eeke menggerak me,
51001008	Aberiniki nen eeppinagage kagak, niniki-kiniki kunik eeko monggotak nogo, at nen aret yo'nira wagagerak.
51001009	Kit togop eerit nogwe ninaruk koneneegurak kuli nen puk aga'lek kulinik-kalinik kinake tamban eeko logonet, Ala nen eeriyak mbake menggerak abok aret Aberiniki nen kineenu eeppinagage logonet, yi wone ndi wone alom abok aret yelok kogwe, ndi, kiniki warak eeppinagage, eeke logowak nduk, Ala yogo monggoorak.
51001010	Kinake tamban eekwi ti, ninowe inikilom kinombaruwak nduk, ndak-ndak eerit nogo logonet, eyoonggen abe yi'nage menggi kwak, obeelom eerit nogwe, ndi, Ala eeke menggerak kineenu ogo logonet, kiniki kole ogwe, eerubagip nduk, kinake tamban eeko monggoorak.
51001011	-
51001012	It Ala apuri ake leenak nogo, Ala abu'me eya aago menggim logonet, pipuk eerogo piyareegerak kolaawak nduk, kooneegerak nogo, ninom ndak-ndak kolaawok nduk, niniki koonogo pinaneegerak me, aaninggin-paaninggin kinoba age kenok, kinaanaganggenggwi lek kiniki kwi'ndak nu'lek logonet, kiniki ale'nggen paga, "Ninogoba Ala wa," yinuk, waganggo logobagip nduk, tamban eeko monggoorak. Kit kiniki kwi'ndak logonet, waganggwi kiigak, at mondok tiyanak logonet omaawi paga yi mendek ndi mendek eeke menggerak nogo nen, kit ndak-ndak omaawi eeppinagage logowak nduk, kinake tamban eeko monggoorak.
51001013	At o apit aago unde menggim nit keele maarak negen wonogwe me, Ala nen ninagap ndarogo at aput iniki kunik nogo abu'me pinani nage mbareegi,
51001014	ninonggo mbambunuk, wondet aago nugu logowok nduk, aput nogo nen ninomaluk lek eerogo pinaneegerak.
51001015	Ala etenggen ninigen kaga'lek kwe, at etenggen ndak-ndak ti, Keritut aret me, liippogo ogoorik~o. Ala aput manggu ndarak Keritut aret me, yi mendek ndi mendek wakkagagerak nogo, tebenak kagak, at mondok tiyanak aret agaarik~o.
51001016	Ala nen eeriyak yoge kagak, mbogut paga mendek inom, nggween paga mendek inom, ninigen kogwe mendek inom, ninigen kaga'lek mendek inom, yi mendek ndi mendek abok aret aput nen mban wakkagagerak. Wakkage logonet, kugi nggween abu'na mendek inom, eyonggaame mendek inom, mbogut abu'na mendek inom, yi kugi ndi kugi yi mendek ndi mendek abok aret, at mban endage tiyappogo logowak nduk, ogobakkigirogo piyareegerak.
51001017	Yi mendek ndi mendek awo wakkaga'lek kagak at aa'nduk wonagagerak. At nen mban yi mendek ndi mendek wakkage nagagerik, unde wonage me, oone konenggo menggaarak.
51001018	Ala apuri yi awi ndi awi kuwak eerit nogo menggaarak lambuk togon Keritut eebe negen nit aret me, ninanobak kwak ti, at aret. Ndi, yi eekwi ndi eekwi alom unde nogo ti, at mban aret me, yi mendek ndi mendek abok aret tebenak kagak, at mban tiyanak logowak nduk, kambunuk nogo menggam nen aa'nduk at aret eenik agago mippereegerak.
51001019	At Ala nen, "An neebe nitok li'luk aago minggi kwak, naput mondok ndak-ndak aret logowak~o," yinuk, inikilom mbake logonet,
51001020	"Naput eyo karo-karo paga kangge kenok, yi mendek ndi mendek abok aret, an ninom ogoorak wonogwe nogo, amiya paga inonggo mbambunuk, an ninom lambuni woraagun~o," yinuk, kooneegerak me, at eereegerak paga mbogut paga mendek inom, nggween paga mendek inom, abok aret at amiya paga ninonggo mbambunuk, Ala ninom lambunogo pinaneegerak.
51001021	Kit aa'nduk maluk eeriyak mban kiniki koombunuk, eerit nogo logonet, Ala kinom ogoorak nda negen aret wonogogutak kwe,
51001022	Keritut nen wokkiren Ala enggaanom unggwi nage mbaremenggi, Ala nen, "Kit an napuri nake leenak logonet, maluk eeka'lek obeelom aret monggotak me, an noone kinoba pinagagin lek~o," yinuk, yokkiraawak nduk, at eebe aap aret age nagagerik, ninake kambeegerak nogo paga lambunogo pinaneegerak me, yogondak lambunik aret ogoorik~o.
51001023	Keritut ti eereegerak nogo paga, Ala kinom lambumbinagareegerak me, wone obeelom wone kit konenggo nogogutik, abet mbako logonet, "Ala nen togop eeppinanigin kagi," yinuk, kiniki lunik wonogwe nogo, mbo puurak mage~o. Ata, o eyak wurabak kwak Keritut paga kiniki panggombunuk, wone abet mbareegutak nogo, kiniki nu'lek logonet, mugurok nogo logonip~o. Ndi, obeelom wone yi awi ndi awi abok aret wiganinuk nage nogo ti, an Pawulut ninom aret yorage logokit nduk, Ala ayeloman agago paneegerak aret~o.
51001024	An andi-pandi eeppanugwi nogo ti, "Kit kinake aret eeppanugwi," mba'nuk, niniki ale'nggen mbake agarik~o. Ndi, "Ala apuri yi awi ndi awi kuwak eerit nogo menggaarak lambuk togon ti, Keritut eebe aret me, iniki nu'lek logowak nduk, Keritut wako logonet, it ando nen warulik mbo pereegwaarak nogo, Ala apuri inake an neebe paga eeppaniyak op aret," mba'nuk, niniki ale'nggen mbake agarik~o.
51001025	-
51001026	Wone o maan nen yogondak kuli kote kumaarak kagak, aakumi nda'narit wundi wogo nogogwaarak kwe, yogondak iluk, it at ake leenak Ala apuri iinok, kin eeppiyareegerak Ala wone kit yokkirage logorak unde eeppaneegerak nogo ndak-ndak, it Ala apuri yi awi ndi awi kuwak eerit nogo menggaarak abok aret inake eeke logokit nduk, inayeloman agago paneegerak~o.
51001027	Wone alik negen mondok iya lombok eeppinaniyak kagak kumaarak wonagagerak nogo, at Ala nen, "Peebi aakumi endekem konenggulik mendek inom ineenu eeppiyaakit," mbareegerak nogo, yogondak iluk aret it at apuri ineenu eeppiigerak~o. Wone kumaarak wonagagerak eebe nogo ti, Keritut ninom kunik wonogwe nogo aret. Ndi, ninom kunik me, peebi at ninom ndak-ndak tiyanak logowok nduk, eeppinaniyak niniki lunik wonogwe abet aret kola nagun nineenu ee'ninake niniki me wonage nogo ti, Keritut aret~o.
51001028	Togop me, noreewi~o. Kit ninapuri abok aret Keritut kinom kunik logonet, kiniki muk kole agaarak kenok, "Ala owagam wokkiren pinagi nawok," mba'nuk, Keritut eeke nagagerak wone yokkirogo logonet, kinaruk wakwi, niniki abu kwippunuk, eekkinake mugurok mamunggirogwe, eerit nogo ogoorik~o.
51001029	Kiniki mondok kole ogwe kiyaakit nduk, Keritut omaawi mondok alik negen eeppanege kagak, an puk aga'lek kit kinake mondok nggwiirit-nggwaarit eeke agarik~o.
51002001	It Laworikiya mendek inom, it ando an neebe ineenggo'lek inom, kinom abok aret obeelom mban eeko logobagip nduk, aaninggin tit kagak kwe, kinake nggwiirit-nggwaarit eeke minggirak nogo, kineenu arubagip nduk, yokkiragi~o.
51002002	Kit abok kiniki ambit a'nuk, niniki-kiniki kunik eekkologo logonet, Ala wone kote kumaarak wonagagerak nogo ti, Keritut aret me, at eebe liirogon kineenu ogo logomonggotik, "Peebi ndogop eeppinanigin~o," yinuk, yugu nogo abok aret kineenu me, kinagabiti nen kiniki yungguppegak eeka'lek kiniki ale'nggen lombok logobagip nduk, kinake eeke minggirak.
51002003	Ala iniki warak nen mondok liippinaninuk, eeppinaniyak alom inom, yi wone ndi wone nineenu ariyak alom inom, kumaarak wonage nogo, kin kaawok nduk, tu paake menggerak kunci nogo ti, Keritut eebe aret~o.
51002004	It aakumi inoone amburu ndik-ndik agan wogo logonet, nomonggiren tu alik paga nogwe iyo, wone ti yokkirage agarik~o.
51002005	An neebe kinom time wonage lek kwe, niniki perak, kinom aret wonage me, kit kiniki Keritut oba panggombunuk, abet mbareegutak nogo nu'lek porogo logonet, mondok ndak-ndak eerit nogwe kiinok, an niniki mondok ale'nggen mbake agarik~o.
51002006	Kit aa'nduk nen, "Keritut Yetut ti, nit ninowe aret~o," yinuk, waganeegutak me, yogondak at kinom kunik logonet, yokkirage nogo konembunuk, mondok ndak-ndak aret eerit nogo logonip~o.
51002007	Eyo omanggen nggween me yarak nu'lek logonet, mondok mili kwit agan lagangge menggi kwak, kit togop aret Keritut paga kinomanggen yarak logonet, kiniki kole ogwe, ndi, abet mbareegutak nogo nu'lek porogo logobagip nduk mamunggirogogwaarak nogo, ndak-ndak porogo wonogwe, eekkologo logonet, kiniki mondok aganggen kekererak lagi wage logonet, Ala, "Wa!" yogo logonip~o.
51002008	It aakumi ambi eeppiyoorak lek kagak we inambokan laganuwok nduk, iniki koonogo yorogo menggaarak nogo ti, Keritut wone lek~o. Ti, it inombomini wandek inom, it kugi inayuk wuko menggaarak nogo inom, inoone mamunik aret agan nugwi me, keele maarak negen it inabu'me logonet, inoone mban konenggo logobagip nduk, kit kinambokan laganggwi iyo, tum wakkologo logonip~o.
51002009	At Ala eebe itok li'luk aago menggerak nogo abok aret, Keritut oba lenggenak logonet, aakumi aret nda'nage nagagerik, nege nagagerak.
51002010	Ndi, kit Keritut kinom kunik wonogwe me, at Ala eebe li'luk aago menggerak nogo, kit kunduk kinoba li'luk agago pinagareegerak wonogwe me, alik ambi inom eeppinagarak mondok lek aret~o. It wone lenggangga inom, inayuk warak inom, o oolo yayi menggaarak abok aret Keritut abu'me logonet, at oone mban aret konenggo menggaarak.
51002011	Ndi, at kinom kunik logonet, kinagabolo mbanogo pinagareegerak negen aret ogotik~o. Ti eereegerak nogo ti, it aakumi nen eekkinabulik~o. Ata, aakumi inagabolo mbanogo piigo mengga kwak, kit maluk eeriyak mban eekkinake menggerak alom nogo, at Keritut nen muk omaawi lek eerogo tebembereegerak me nduk, yokkiragi~o.
51002012	Keritut kinom kunik logonet, kambunuk ndoome mambiigo menggam nen kinom kineenik agago mippinagareegerak nogo kwak, yiime wanggo nogogutik, lagi wogogutak nogo~o. Kit kambunuk ndoome mambiigo menggam negen wonogwe me, Ala nen Keritut kambunuk nogo menggam nen at omaawi paga eenik agago mippereegerak me, "At omaawi ti paga at ninom nineenik agago mippinanigin kogo~o," yinuk, abet mbareegutak paga kineenik agago mippinagareegerak wonogo ogotik~o.
51002013	-
51002014	It aakumi inagabolo mbanogo nappogo mengga kwak, kiniki maan mendek nen maluk eeriyak eekkinake alom nogo omaawi awo lek eerogo pega'lek logonet, yi maluk ndi maluk eerit nogo nogogutak paga kambak kwak aret wonogogutak kwe, "Yogop ee'nu, ndogop ee'nu," wone yugu liiru mbanak ndak-ndak nit eeka'lek niinok, Ala nen, "Maluk onggo ndogop eeppiyaakit~o," mba'nuk, eenggi lingginogo liiru mbaneegerak aaninggin kinoba wonagagerak nogo, "Mondok mbo pikit~o," yinuk, liiru mbanak nogo Keritut inom eyo karo-karo paga nabenogo punuk, kinomaluk tigitogon lek eerogo pege nagagerik, Keritut kinom kineenik agago mippinagareegerak.
51002015	Ti eereegerak nogo ti, it wim nambuppunuk, "Nit nineegin tiyak yigi~o," yinuk, "Wi!" iraawak nduk, aakumi ineebe kugun wogoren wogo mengga kwak, at Keritut nen, "An neegin tiyak yegerak neyaawak~o," yinuk, at Tile inom, at awuri yi kugi ndi kugi inom, abok aret inomaawi lek eerogo piinok, inenggali aruwak nduk, ineebe nggwok paga o oolo yayi wogoren nege nagagerak.
51002016	Togop me noreewi~o. Kit yi mendek ndi mendek nunggwi, Ala wone yugu mugurok laago lakwi, tut ambi penengge kenok lakwi, nogo 6 yippunuk, ko'lu yonggonggologwe paga eekwi, eekwi kiinok, it iniki ugun koombunuk, "Ambi yi maluk kagak eekotak~o," yinuk, yokkiroorak ti abu lek~o.
51002017	Ti eekwi nogo ti, peebi abe eeppinaniyak we ogut negen eeko nogogwaarak nogo, eebe muk eeppinaneegerak kagak eekwi me, tiyappugup~o. Yogondak niniki ale'nggen eeppinaniyak eebe nogo ti, Keritut aret me, at mban tiyappogo logonip~o.
51002018	It aakumi nggween paga mendek mban iniki koonit nogo menggaarak nogo nen, it aap iya lek kagak iniki wogoppako logonet, "Nabinggaanggo paga wone yo'nege menggerak me, an iya~o," yinuk, inabi kagaatak mbinuk-mbenak agan wogo logonet, inoone omaawi paga, "Malayikat inalut eeko logonip~o," yinuk, yokkirogwe, ndi, iniki tebenak nege mbaruwak nduk, inagabiti nggo-nggo nugwi, eerit nogwe nogo, kit liippugwi kiinok, Ala nen wokkiroorak kiniki ale'nggen mbakwi nogo, lek eerogo pakwi kiyo, inoone konenggo logogup~o.
51002019	Ninomanggen ambit paga nineenggi-niniyok yeregerak-peregerak abok aret ninanobak inom yinik-kunik aago logonet, nineebe tawe ogo monggo kwak, nit ninanobak Keritut ninom togop aret kunik me, at Ala nen, "Keritut eebe wigak yuwak," mba'nuk, ee'ninake menggerak nogo kagak, it aakumi ti, iniki wogoppako logonet, inanobak Keritut nogo mbo punuk, inom kunik lek ugun nugwi me, inoone konenggo logogup~o.
51002020	Kit Keritut kinom kunik logonet, kanggo mbareegup, yi kugi ndi kugi inayuk wuko logonet, inoone konenggo nogogutak nogo tebembiinok, wondet eerogo pinagareegerak kagak, nonggop nduk, wondet eerogo pinagulik inoone awo konenggwi negen eekko'net nogo ogotik?
51002021	It aap ti nen, "Yogop ee'nu ndogop ee'nu," yogo logonet, "Ti mbaanggoorak mage~o. Ti noorak mage~o. Ti pigoorak mage~o," yinuk, yokkirogwe nogo, nonggop nduk, "Yi abet aret yo'nirogwe iigo~o," yinuk, inoone konenggo ogotik?
51002022	"Ti noorak mage," yokkirogwe nogo ti, nit nonggo nogootik, muk lek age menggerak mendek kagak nonggop nduk yogo agaarik? It agan nugwi nogo ti, aakumi iniki koombunuk, "Yogop eeriyak mage, ndogop eeriyak mage," yinuk, wone mamunik aret yokkirogo agaarik~o.
51002023	Inoone omaawi paga, "Malayikat alut eeko logonip~o," yinuk, yokkirogwe, iniki tebenak nege mbaruwak nduk, inagabiti nggo-nggo nugwi, ndi, "Aap yi, iya," inombaruwak nduk, inagabolo paga andi-pandi eerogo pakwi, eerit nugwi iinok, "Yi iniki warak nen eekwi," mbarumonggotak kwe, wone ti waganggwi paga kiniki nengge mugurok noorak eekkinake nogo ti, tebenogo pogo logorak eekkinabigin lek me, mugurok nogo logogup~o.
51003001	Keritut eenik agago mippege logonet, kinom kineenik agago mippinagareegerak me, Keritut Ala eenggi abe'nggan paga kwi'ndak menggim mbogut paga eeko menggaarak wone nogo mban kiniki panggombunuk, logonip~o.
51003002	-
51003003	Kit kanggo mbareegup, Ala nen kineenik agago mippinagage nagagerik, Keritut kinom Ala iniki me kumaappinagago wonage me, kiniki nggween paga mendek paga panggombunuk logogup~o. Ata, kiniki agi mendek paga mban panggombunuk logonip~o.
51003004	At nineenik ee'ninake menggerak Keritut nogo, wage eyom paga kit kinom ndak-ndak tiyanak wonogwe kiyaagun~o.
51003005	-
51003006	Togop me, noreewi~o. Kumi ugun wurinabit nogwe, kiniki kumi paga mban lunik nugwi, kiniki nengge nogo mugurok nogwe, maluk eeriyak mban kinikilom mbakwi, yi mendek ndi mendek koloorak uugwe mba'nuk, tiyappugwi nogo ti, kugiwak alut eekwi ndak-ndak me, uugwe-uugwe mbakwi, eeriyak mage~o. Ti eerit nogwe kiinok, Ala anini abet aret kinoba pinagarak me, ti eeriyak eekkinake nogo abok aret mondok warogo wuppogo logonip~o.
51003007	Kit aa'nduk maluk mban eerit nogo logonet, ti mendek abok aret eerit nogo nogogutak nogo mbo pereegutak kwe,
51003008	yogondak, nanini-kanini yogwe, neebi-keebi yogwe, maluk eeppiyoorak koonggwi, miyuk-meya eerogo piigwi, wone yuurak lek mendek kagak yorogwe, eekwi ti mendek abok aret mbo pinip~o.
51003009	-
51003010	Nit niniki ngget ogobakkigika Ala nogo nen, at eeke menggerak kineenu arubagip nduk, at iniki pogom kit kiniki ngget ogobakkigirogo pinagage kagak, kit kinobaabut maan mendek paga maluk eeko nogogutak nogo, nggonenogo mbo punuk, kinobaabut ngget mendek eekkologogutak me, kit-kit aret pilit pugunggwi ti mage~o.
51003011	Nit niniki ngget ogobakkigirogo pinanemenggerak nogo paga eerit nogo logonet, "Yi Yakuri mendek yi Yunani mendek, yi inagabolo mbanak yi inagabolo mbanak lek, yi aap ineenggo'lek mendek yi aakumi nengga mendek, yi aap inayeloman aago mendek yi aap inayeloman aago lek mendek," yinuk, togop agan nogo logorak lek~o. Ata, at yi o ndi o abok aret endak warak menggerak Keritut nogo, nit abok ninowe aret me, at mban tiyappogo logowok~o.
51003012	Togop me, at Ala nen kinabuwa mbake logonet, at apuri maluk eeka'lek alik leenak logobagip nduk, miikkinabeegerak me, yum yikkologo mengga kwak kinobaabut ngget mendek eekkologo logonet, aakumi inabuwa mbakwi, kiniki yanggonak paga obeelom eeppiigwi, kiniki tebenak logonet nugwi, kinoone omaawi lek yanggorogon yorogwe, inoone kinoba pinagagwi iinok liippunuk yorogwe,
51003013	yeenggwa-yeenggwa eekwi, eeko logonet, at ambi nen at ambi omaluk mari eerogo pegak eeko logonip~o. Kit kinore ambi nen maluk eeppinagage kenok, ninowe nen kit kinomaluk mondok lek eerogo pereegerak nogo ndak-ndak, kit togop aret at maluk eeppinagage nogo, mari eerogo mbo pogo logonip~o.
51003014	Yokkiragarak ti abok aret eerit nogo logonet, kit kiniki ambit lambunik ale'nggen nggwok logorak alom nogo ti, yum yippunuk inobate keele nggerenggologo mengga kwak niniki-kiniki kunik aganakwi nogo aret me, ti inom aret eerit nogo logonip~o.
51003015	Keritut kinom kunik kineebe ambit a'nuk lambunik logonet, kiniki ugun tayenak ale'nggen logobagip nduk, Ala nen kinayonggo pinagareegerak me, nit op eekwi niinok, Keritut nen niniki ugun tayenak logowok nduk, ale'nggen eeppinanege menggerak nogo, kit ndak-ndak, yi mendek ndi mendek eeriyak kiniki koonggwi kiigak, op eeriyak kenok ale'nggen eekkinake, ndi, maluk eeriyak kenok, kiniki aaninggin eekkinake, eeke logowak~o. At togop eekkinake menggerak me, Ala mondok, "Wa," yogo logonip.
51003016	Keritut ari nagagerak wone abok aret kiniki me mondok yagabit eerogo waganggo logonip~o. Waganggo logomonggotik, kiniki warak a'nuk, Ala wone mamunirogwe, kiniki eyak wat-wat yogwe, ndi, Ala keyage wako logonet, "Nogoba wa," yinuk, Ndawut nen ndawi pereegerak inom, ki wone ndawi inom, Ala eeke menggerak ndawi inom, abok aret warit nogwe, eeko logonip~o.
51003017	Keritut kinabuwa nen kinake eeke menggerak me, kinogoba Ala, "Wa," yinuk, keyage wako logonet, kinoone yogo monggotak inom, eerit nogo monggotak inom, abok aret ninowe Yetut endage tiyak yuwak nduk mban eerit nogo logonip~o.
51003018	Kit kumi yi wae. Kit Ala apuri aret me, Ala apuri eeko mengga kwak, kinogonggelomini inabu'me logonet, inoone konenggo logonip~o.
51003019	Ndi, kit aap yi wae. Kinakuwi inabuwa mbako logonet, kinoone andiigwi yorogo logogup~o. Ata, kinoone yanggorogon yorogo logonip~o.
51003020	Kit wologwe-komologwe yi wae. Kit kinowe inikilom kinombaruwak nduk, kinagalomini-kinogobamini inoone yokkirogwe abok aret liirogon konembunuk, eeko logonip~o.
51003021	Ndi, kit aap kinapurilogwe warak yi wae. Iniki wakkologo logonet, inogogumbuk ogwe iyo, kinoone panggok togon kinapurilogwe inaruk wakak yuurak mage~o.
51003022	Kit aakumi inayeloman monggotak yi wae. Kinogobamini inikilom kinombaruwak nduk, inigen wonogwe iinok mban eeko logorak ti mage~o. Ata, ninowe ayuk wuko logonet, it yokkirogo menggaarak nogo abok aret, "E~o," yinuk, kiniki abe paga inake eerit nogo logonip~o.
51003023	Yi mendek ndi mendek abok aret eerit nogo logonet, "Yi aakumi inake eekwi lek~o. Yi ninowe ake aret eeko ogoorik~o," mba'nuk, kiniki aganggen kerek togon inake eerit nogo logonip.
51003024	-
51003025	At Ala nen aap ambi iya, ambi meek, mbakeelik nit eekwi onggo ndak-ndak wo'niraagin nineenu me, kit nen, "Nit ninowe ambit Keritut ake aret~o," yinuk, kinogobamini inake eekwi kenok, it maluk eekwi onggo wogorage logonet, at apuri obeelom eekwi iinok inake pipuk eerogo piyareegerak nogo, "Nit kunduk ninom ndak-ndak wo'niraagin," mbako logonip~o.
51004001	Ndi, kit nogobamini wae. Kinayeloman wonogwe iinok, "An kunduk nogoba mbogut paga wonage kagi," mbako logonet, it kinayeloman mini kinake eekwi ndak-ndak kiniki obeelom paga a'me nggelok eeppiigo logonip~o.
51004002	Ko'lu-kii'me nogolumok yega'lek tamban mban eeko logonet, Ala, "Wa!" mban yogo logonip~o.
51004003	-
51004004	Tamban eeko logonet, an Keritut awone kote kumaarak nogo yorage nagagirak paga keele maarogo mambaneegwaarak yime logonet, nagabiti mbaka'lek paganogo yorage logorak Ala nen tu koonogo panege, ndi, yorage neegak, aakumi nen, "Yi abet aret yo'nirage kogo," mba'nuk, waawak nen eeppiige, eeke logowak nduk, Timotiyut nimbirak ninake tamban eeko logonip~o.
51004005	It aakumi abet mbaka'lek mendek kinom eerit nogo logonet, "Ala abet mbaruwak nduk, wone yoroorak nanonggwan aga~o," yinuk, kiniki mondok kwippunuk, eerit nogo logonip~o.
51004006	Yi aakumi ndi aakumi inoone yokkira wogwe iinok, onggo yorogo logonet, mbiingga ombat abe kaawak nduk, mayu eeko mengga kwak, kit togop aret kinoone ale lek inabuwa mbako logonet, yanggorogon yorogo logonip~o.
51004007	At ninoreeluk Tikikut ninom niniki kunik me, ninowe ayeloman logonet, nit ninom ndak-ndak Ala ake liirogon eeke menggerak nogo nen, an yime eeke minggirak nogo, abok aret yokkira woraagin~o.
51004008	Kineenu eeppinagawak nduk kinowagam nappi woraminggirak wage logomenggerik, nit abok nineebe nonggop wonogwe nogo yokkirage, ndi, kiniki eyak wappinagage, eeri woraagin~o.
51004009	Kinawot Onetimut kunduk ninom niniki kunik me, ninowe Keritut wone mondok liirogon mugurok nage menggerak nogo, imbirak nappiya woraagin me, wogo logomenggaarik, nit yime niigak eeppinanugwi nogo, abok aret yokkira wogwe iyaamunggup~o.
51004010	-
51004011	At ninoreeluk Aritarukut keele maarak nimbirak yime wonage nogo nen keyage wakkinake~o. Ndi, aap ambi endage aa'nduk toonak Yetut, ndi, peebi toonak Yutut nogo kunduk, aap Mbaranabat amboko Marakut imbirak nen kunduk, keyage wakkinaka~o. At Marakut eereegerak yokkiragagirak nogo kagak kiya wage kenok, keyage warogo eebe waganggo logonip~o. It aap mbere ti, inagabolo mbanak mendek aret kwe, Ala abu'me piyoorak wone ninom ndak-ndak eerit nogo logonet, niniki mondok alik negen eyak wappanegaarak me, yokkiragi~o.
51004012	Ndi, at kinoreeluk Epaparat inom keyage wappinagage~o. At Keritut Yetut ayeloman aret me, kit abet mbareegutak nogo mondok nu'lek porogo logonet, kiniki kole ogwe, ndi, "Ala nen nit eeriyak ninombareegerak nogo yi aret~o," yinuk, abet mbako logonet, eerit nogwe, eekwi kiyaawak nduk, abuwa warak nggo-nggo logonet kinake tamban eeke menggerak~o.
51004013	It aakumi o Laworikiya mendek inom, o Kiyerapolit mendek inom, kinom eeppinagarak iniki kinoba mondok aberak wonage kage minggirak me nduk, yokkiragi~o.
51004014	Ndi, at Lukat niniki kunik ndotet nogo inom, aap Ndemat nogo inom, imbirak nen keyage wakkinaka~o.
51004015	Ndi, ninoreewi Ala apuri o Laworikiya mendek inom, kwe Nimipa inom, Ala apuri at ame kuwak eeko menggaarak nogo inom, "Pawulut oreewi inom nen keyage wakkinaka~o," yinuk, yoret~o.
51004016	Liiru mbanak yi, kit kinaa'nduk pekkogo logomonggotik, it Ala apuri o Laworikiya kuwak eeko menggaarak nogo, pekkaawak nduk, nappiya wa'nu~o. Ndi, an liiru mbanogo Ala apuri Laworikiya nappiige logonet, "Kit aa'nduk pekkogo logomonggotik, Ala apuri o Kolote wonogwe nogo, pekkaawak nduk nappiyaanu~o," yinuk yoragarak me, nappinagi wogwe iinok, ti inom aret pekkogo logonu~o.
51004017	Ndi, aap Arikiput nogo, yogo logonet, "Ninowe nen unde eeppereegerak nogo, ndak-ndak eeke logowak nduk, liippege logowak," yegerak, yo'nu~o.
51004018	Ai, noreewi~o. An keele maarak yime wonage nogo, noba abeko logonip~o, obak. Ndi, ninogoba Ala iniki kunik en eeppinagage logonet, kinarum aret logogin~o. An kinogoba Pawulut nen, "Kit napuri abok aret keyage wakkinaki~o," yinuk, liiru irip pagaluk ti mban neenggi lombok paga mbanggiragi~o. Napuri wa.
52001001	Noreewi~o. Kit Ala apuri ninogoba Ala ninowe Yetut Keritut kinom kunik o Tetalonika kuwak eeko monggotak nogo, an Pawulut kunduk, Tiliwanut kunduk, Timotiyut kunduk, nen wone ambi yokkiraawi~o. Ala iniki kunik nen wokkirage, kiniki ugun tayenak ale'nggen logobagip nduk, eeppinagage, eeke logogin~o.
52001002	Nit tamban eeko monggoorak me, eeko logonet, kit abok kiinok kulinik-kalinik Ala, "Wa," yogo monggoorak.
52001003	Kit abet mba'nuk eerit nugwi, aakumi kiniki kunik nen nggwiirit-nggwaarit obeelom eeppiinet nugwi, ndi, ninowe Yetut Keritut paga kiniki lunik wonogwe me, aaninggin kinoba age kagak kinogogumbuk logonet waganggwi, eekwi nogo ti, aberak logonet, ninogoba Ala yogo monggoorak~o.
52001004	Noreewi~o. Ala iniki kunik eekkinake logonet, miikkinabeegerak ti, nineenu aret~o.
52001005	Nit nen wone obeelom wone yokkira wogogurak nogo ti, we nit ninoone paga mban lek~o. Ata, Aberiniki omaawi eeppinanege kagak, yokkirogogurak paga kinikime nen, "Ie! Wone yi, mondok abet aret yo'nirogwe iigo~o," yinuk, waganeegutak nogo~o. Kit mamunggolaabagip nduk, nit kinenggela'me logonet, nonggop eerit nogo nogogurak nogo ti, kineenu aret~o.
52001006	Maluk eeppinagagwi iigak, Aberiniki nen kiniki ale'nggen eekkinake kagak, wone waganggo nogogutik, nit ninowe ninom eeko monggoorak nogo ndak-ndak aret eeko nogogutak.
52001007	Togop eeko nogogutak me, it aakumi abet mbakwi o Makendoniya inom, o Akaya inom, abok aret kit paga in wakkagak eeko agaarik~o.
52001008	Kit eekwi paga ninowe wone nogo o Makendoniya inom, o Akaya inom, time mban wiganinuk noolik~o. Ata, yi awi ndi awi abok aret kit Ala abet mbareegutak nogo wiganinuk nagagerak me, nit wone ambi yorogo logorak lek aret kogo~o.
52001009	Nit kiya wogo mbareegu, wo'ninabeegutak nogo inom, kugiwak eeko nogogutak nogo mbo punuk, Ala abet aret eenik menggerak nogo mugurok nogo logobagip nduk miikkologogutak nogo inom,
52001010	ndi, Ala nen at aput Yetut kambunuk nogo menggam nen eenik agago mippege mbareegi, peebi anini nen nit maluk eeppinanege kero, ninagap ndareegerak Yetut mbogut paga nen wambi woroorak nduk, kit tokkogo monggotak nogo inom, abok aret nit yo'nirogo menggaarak.
52002001	Noreewi~o. Nit we aanom warogo kiya woroolik nogo ti, kit kineenu aret~o.
52002002	Nit o Pilipi wonogwe niigak, aaninggin-paaninggin ninoba pinanugwi, miyuk-meya eerogo pinanugwi, eereegwaarak kineenu nogo kwe, kagak, Ala nen yo'niragagerak wone obeelom wone nogo it apit aret, "Nineebi~o," yogwe iigak, Ala yeenggwa nirage me, ninagabiti mbaka'lek yokkirogo nogogurak nogo~o.
52002003	Nit kinaruk wako logonet, yokkirogo monggoorak nogo ti, nit nineenggo'lek logonet yokkirogwe, nit ambi kolaawok nduk yokkirogwe, kinambokan laganuwok nduk, pilit wone yokkirogwe, eekulik~o.
52002004	Ala nen ninabut mbambunuk, obeelom wone unde eeppinaneegerak nogo ndak-ndak aret yokkirogo monggoorak. Kit kinikilom mbarubagip nduk yokkirogwe lek~o. Ata, at niniki lombonninake menggerak Ala nogo inikilom mbaruwak nduk, yokkirogo monggoorak.
52002005	Niniki laakot logonet, ninoone yokkirogo logolik ti, kineenu aret~o. Kit kinageerok ambi kolaawok nduk, ninoone, "Ai-ao," yogwe ti, at Ala eenu me, yuulik mban.
52002006	-
52002007	Ndi, Keritut ayonggo nugu logowok nduk nappiigak agago pinaneegerak me, ninoone omaawi yokkiroorak op aret kwe, kit inom, it aakumi alik inom, nit ninendage tiyappinanuwak nduk, woroolik~o. Ata, kwe ambi at aagaluk abuwa nen ogome lamoppunuk oone yanggorogon yoge menggi kwak, nit kinenggela'me logonet, togop aret ninoone yanggorogon aret yokkirogo nogogurak nogo~o.
52002008	Kinabuwa lombok mbako logonet, kit niniki kunik eekkinabeegurak me, obeelom wone ti mban yokkiroorak mbarulik~o. Ata, kinake lombok kambuurak kenok perak, op aret mbareegurak.
52002009	Noreewi~o. Nit eerit mban nogo logonet, ndeyak eerogo pinaneegerak nogo ti, kiniki abe'nip~o. Ala nen yo'niragagerak wone obeelom wone nogo yokkirogo logonet, "Kit mban ambinom aaninggin kinoba pinagukwak," mba'nuk, nit nen liingge inom, oonikiya inom, eekko'net nogo nogogurak nogo~o.
52002010	Kit abet mbareegutak nogo nit kinenggela'me logonet, Ala wone liippunuk eekwi, ndi, maluk eeka'lek abu obeelom eereegurak paga kinoone ambi ninoba pinanega'lek wonogwe, eerit nogogurak nogo ti, Ala niige, kit kunduk niigwi, eereegutak~o.
52002011	-
52002012	Ala mondok tiyanak logonet, "Kit tiyappinagakit nduk, nabu'me woraanip~o," yinuk, ayonggo pinagareegerak nogo, iniki mbake ndak-ndak eerit nogo logobagip nduk, aap ambi apuri kenok yorage nogo kokwak, nit togop aret niniki aganggen kerek togon kit kinalitak lombok kinaruk wakwi, kiniki eyak wappinagagwi, kini wuppinagagwi, eeko nogogurak nogo kineenu aret~o.
52002013	Togop me, Ala wone yokkirogogurak konenggo logonet, "Yi we aakumi inoone lek~o. Yi Ala wone nit abet mbakwi ninikime koonninake menggerak wone abet aret~o," yinuk, waganeegutak me, nit puk aga'lek kulinik-kalinik, "Ala wa," yogo monggoorak.
52002014	-
52002015	Noreewi~o. It aap Yakuri nogo nen it Ala yorage kagak yoraga nogo inookwi, ninowe Yetut warogo pugwi, ndi, nit kunduk mugogo nappinanugwi, eeko nogogwaarak nogo nen it Ala apuri Keritut Yetut inom kunik logonet, o Yureya yi awi ndi awi kuwak eerit nogo menggaarak piyaginabit nogo nogogwaarak nogo ndak-ndak, it kinowe-kinawot nen kit togop aret eeppinagagwi iigak kinogogumbuk logonet, waganeegutak me, it inogogumbuk logonet, waganggo nogogwaarak ndak-ndak, kit togop aret waganggwi kiigi~o. It Yakuri eereegwaarak nogo ti, it aakumi abok ineebi mbako logonet, inom ogoorak wonogwe me, Ala kunduk, inikilom inombakeelik mondok eebi inombake menggerak~o.
52002016	It aakumi endekem mendek Ala nen inagap ndariyak wone, "Kit yorogo logorak lek~o," yinuk, non mbambinanogo menggaarak me, it maluk ambi nabek mban eerit wogoga, wogoga, "Ti kuli ari nawak," koonak nogo paga ari nage kenok Ala anini inoba piige menggerak nogo ndak-ndak, yogondak anini mondok it inoba piige agaarik~o.
52002017	Ndi, noreewi~o. Nit perak, niniki kinoba aberak mban wonogwe kwe, ne ambiriluk nineebe alitak wonogogurak me, mbet-mbet pekkiya woroorak, "Ao," lombok mbako logonet, wakkagak mban eereegurak kwe, meek aret agagerak~o.
52002018	Noreewi ninom pekkiya woroorak mbakwi, ndi, an nalik ne ambit paga lek~o. Ata, kulinik-kalinik pekkiya woroorak mbake, eereegurak kwe, Ibilit nen non mbanogo pinanege kenok, wonogo ogoorik~o.
52002019	Nit niniki lunik inom, niniki ale'nggen mbakwi inom, obeelom eekwi niinok nggare-nggare mendaarak yippinanege kenok, wogoppatiyak nogo inom, ti taamini mbakop? Lek~o. Nit ninowe Yetut wage kenok eeppinaniyak nogo ti, kit abet mba'nuk eerit nugwi paga aret~o.
52002020	Nit tiyappinanugwi, niniki ale'nggen eerogo pinanugwi, eeriyak ti, kit kineebe paga aret~o.
52003001	Togop me, ambinom puk logorak abu meek ee'ninake mba-reegi, an nalik o Atina taati neegak,
52003002	-
52003003	at ninawot Ala ayeloman Keritut eeke nagagerak obeelom wone ninom yorogo monggoorak Timotiyut nogo nen, it aakumi aaninggin kinoba pinagagwi paga wone ti, "Nineebi~o," yinuk, mbo pugwi kiyo, kit abet mbakwi nogo nu'lek agago pinagage, kit kiniki eyak wappinagage, eeke logowak, mba'nuk, at kinake nappi wogogurak. Nit togop aret eeppinanogo logorak Ala nen koonogo pinaneegerak kineenu aret~o.
52003004	Kit ninom logonet, awo eeppinanega'lek kagak, "Aaninggin eeppinanogo logogun~o," yokkirogo nogogurak nogo, a'me aret agagerak ti, kineenu aret~o.
52003005	Togop me, an ambinom puk logorak abu meek ee'nake mbareegi, at niniki nggagangge menggerak nogo nen kit kiniki nggaganiyak kagak nit aanom warogo wone yokkirogo nogogurak kero, niniki piirik logonet, kit kiniki abet mbakwi nogo nonggop wonogwe an neenu arikit nduk, aap Timotiyut kinake nappi wagagirak nogo~o.
52003006	Ndi, yogondak perak, at Timotiyut muk kit wonogome nen nit niya wagaarak~o. Ndi, niya wage nagaarik, wone obeelom wone kit kiniki abet mbakwi wone inom, aakumi kinom kiniki kunik aganakwi wone inom, ndi, nit nen, "Kit kiyaawok lak, ao," mbakwi kwak, kit nen, "It iyaawok lak, ao," ninomba'nuk, kulinik-kalinik ninoba abeko logonet, kinale'nggen mbakwi nogo inom, yo'nira wagaarak~o.
52003007	Togop me, noreewi~o. Aaninggin-paaninggin ninoba pinanugwi iinok, niniki aaninggin ndugu agan koonit nogwe me, kit abet mba'nuk eerit nugwi nogo yo'nira wage mbaki, niniki kwi'naga~o.
52003008	Ndi, yogondak kit kinowe kiniki kunik logonet, mondok nu'lek wonogwe kiinok, nit aaninggin nen niniki wakkolaagun lek~o. Ninale'nggen logonet, eerit nogo logogun aret~o.
52003009	Kit eerit nogwe paga nit niniki ale'nggen ambik ee'ninake me, "Ala wa," yinuk, at yogo monggoorak nogo ti, at eenu aret kwe, iya negen ambi ngge mendek yorubok ee'ninake agaarik~o.
52003010	Nit kinetenggen kiigo logomonggoorik, kit abet mbakwi wone nogo ambi yobok ari kero, yokkiraawok nduk, ko'lu-kii'me ninoone aganggen kerek togon kinake tamban eeko monggoorak.
52003011	Nit pekkiya woroorak nogo ninogoba Ala lombok ninowe Yetut imbirak nen tu mbininogo pinani woraawak nduk, tamban eeko monggoorak.
52003012	Nit nen kit niniki mondok kunik eekkinakwi nogo kokwak, kit-kit inom, aakumi abok inom, ambinom niniki-kiniki kunik aganako logorak ninowe nen eekkinake,
52003013	ndi, ninowe Yetut at apuri ake leenak inom wogo logomenggaarik, "Kit kiniki nu'lek logonet maluk eeka'lek abu obeelom eeko nogootak me, nogoba Ala oone kinoba pinagagin lek aret kiigi," yinuk, yokkirage, eeke logowak~o.
52004001	Ndi, noreewi~o. Wone irip paga iluk ambi yokkiroorak mbakoorak me yokkiraawi~o. Ala inikilom kinombaruwak nduk, "Nonggop eerit nogo logorak?" mamunggirogogurak nogo, muk eerit nogwe aret kwe, ambinom mondok nggwok togon eerit nogo logobagip nduk, ninowe Yetut nen yo'nirage kenok lengganogo yokkirogo~o.
52004002	Ninowe Yetut nen, "Yoret~o," yinuk, yo'nirage mbareegi, wone, "Yogop ee'nu, ndogop ee'nu," yinuk, lengganogo yokkirogo nogogurak ti, kineenu aret~o.
52004003	At Ala nen kit maluk eeka'lek at ake leenak logorak mbake nogo ti, kit kumi ugun wurinabit noorak mage nduk, yereegerak~o.
52004004	-
52004005	It aakumi endekem mendek nogo nen Ala ineenggo'lek logonet, aganggen aganake kenok kumi ugun-ugun eeginabit nugwi nogo kwak, kit togop eeko logorak mage~o. Ata, kinalitak lombok kinendage op logobagip nduk, "Ala endage paga lambumbinanuwak~o," yinuk, maluk eeka'lek inabuwa mbako logonet, kologo logonu~o.
52004006	-
52004007	Nit maluk eerit nugu logowok nduk, at Ala nen mii'ninabulik~o. Ata, maluk eeka'lek at ake leenak logowok nduk, mii'ninabeegerak me, nit aa'nduk ninoone omaawi paga yokkirogo nogogurak nogo ndak-ndak, maluk togoti eekwi iinok, Ala nen onggo koonogo eeppinanege menggerak me, kinoreeluk ambi maluk eeppege logonet, at akwe kote wuriyak mage~o.
52004008	Togop me, aap ambi nen, "Wone yi, Ala nen yegerak lek~o. Aakumi nen aret yagaarak~o," yinuk, taganogo mbo pege kenok, at nen aakumi mbo piige ti lek~o. Ata, at Aberiniki wo'nirage Ala nogo aret mbo pege menggerak~o.
52004009	Kinoreewi kinom kiniki kunik aganabit nugwi nogo ti, Ala nen muk mamunggiragagerak me, wone ti mendek ambi liiru mbanggiroorak lek aret kagi~o.
52004010	Kit kinoreewi abok o Makendoniya menggaarak nogo, abet aret kiniki kunik aganakwi kwe, ambinom kiniki kunik aganako logobagip nduk, lengganogo yokkirogo~o.
52004011	-
52004012	It aakumi abet mbaka'lek mendek nen kit liirogon eerit nugwi kiinok, kinayuk wuko logowak nduk, at ambi eerit nage paga kiniki panggombegak eerit nagup~o. Ata, kit kinendage op logobagip nduk, kiname liirogon logonet, kit kinobaalombok mban eerit nugwi, ndi, kineenggi omaawi logobagip nduk, nit aa'nduk kinaruk wareegurak nogo liirogon aret eekwi, eeko logobagip nduk, wone lengganogo yokkirogo~o.
52004013	Noreewi~o. It aakumi kambunuk nonggop ogo menggaarak wone nogo, kineenggo'lek logorak ti, nineebi~o. Aakumi ando iniki lunik ambi lek me, inore ambi kangge kenok iniki wakkologo mengga kwak, kit kiniki togop aret wakkologo logokwak, mbininogo yokkiraawi~o.
52004014	At Yetut kangge nagagerik, mi'nagagerak nogo nit abet mbakwi kenok, it aakumi Yetut inom kunik logonet, kambeegwaarak nogo at Ala nen ineenik agago mippiyaagin abet aret mbako logowok~o.
52004015	Ninowe yereegerak ndak-ndak, at wage kenok, it aakumi kambeegwaarak nogo wonogwe iigak, nit awo nineenik wonogwe nogo ninaa'nduk lagi nagun lek~o.
52004016	At ninowe lombok kuum ari, yonggo mbogut paga inowe nogo oone ari, Ala amendek oone nggwok eeka trompet nogo oone eeke, eeko logonet, ninowe mbogut paga nen wambi wage kagak, it aap Keritut inom kunik logonet, kambeegwaarak nogo, at Ala nen inaa'nduk mippiyaagin~o.
52004017	Mippiige logomenggerik, ti'nuk, nit nineenik awo wonogwe nogo, it ninom ndugwi enggela'me oolo taati ninowe ninom lambunuwok nduk, wo'niren nagin~o. Wo'niren nage kenok, ninowe ninom mondok-mondok aret logogun~o.
52004018	Wone ti, ninowe nen aret yo'niragagerak me, ti paga kiniki eyak wat-wat eeko logonip~o.
52005001	Noreewi~o. Yi eeriyak wone yokkirogoorak nogo ti, "Ndi eyom paga woraagin a, o lagi nage, wambi wage, eeke paga woraagin a?" kineenu arubagip nduk, liiru mbanggiroorak lek~o.
52005002	At ninowe woroorak eyom nogo ti, aap yogoot wagangga nen oonikiya wogo menggaarak nogo pogom woraagin ti, muk kineenu aret~o.
52005003	It aakumi nen, "Wone ambi ninoba aga'lek nit abok obeelom aret me, niniki ale'nggen aret ogoorik~o," yogwe iigak, kwe abila aagaluk nda'nariyak eenggo'lek me, enegen pagak ari nogo pogom, ninowe abera'lek me wage logonet, mondok lek eerogo piya woraagin me, it ambi mbo nagun abu lek aret~o.
52005004	Togop me, noreewi~o. Kit perak, kiniki o apit pogom kobak wonogwe lek~o. Aap yogoot wagangga nen o ambime unggwage kenok, inogut nage nogo kokwak, kit togop kinogut nagin lek~o.
52005005	Kit abok aret aakumi o apit paga logonet eeko menggaarak nogo pogom lek~o. Ata, eya paga logonet eeko menggaarak mendek kit aret~o. Ndi, it aakumi oonikiya paga eeko menggaarak pogom kit lek mban. Ata, it liingge eeko menggaarak nogo pogom kit aret me,
52005006	it aakumi ando nogo yugu menggaarak nogo pogom nit togop nogo yugu logorak lek~o. Nit nogolumok yaga'lek tum wako logowok~o.
52005007	It aakumi nogo yugu menggaarak nogo ti, oonikiya aret nogo yugu menggaarak. Ndi, it amburu kumili aganabuwok nduk, nonggo menggaarak nogo ti, oonikiya aret nonggo menggaarak kwe,
52005008	it liingge eeko menggaarak nogo mendek nit aret me, nit nogolumok yaga'lek tum mban wako logowok~o. Tum wako logonet, nit niniki abet mbakwi, aakumi niniki kunik aganakwi, eekwi nogo paga ninarin pogom yirikkologwe, ndi, aap wim nambuka anobak me warukwak nduk, petagi mbuti mendek yirikkolage nogo kwak, ninagap nda'ninaburak niniki lunik wonage nogo abekwi, eeko logowok~o.
52005009	At Ala nen anini ninoba pinanikit nduk, leenogo pinanulik~o. Ata, at ninowe Yetut Keritut nen ninagap ndaruwak nduk, leenogo pinaneegerak~o.
52005010	At ninom nineenik mondok logowok nduk, nit ninake kambeegerak me, nineenik wonogwe kenok, kanggwi kenok, op mban aret~o.
52005011	Togop aret me, kit kiniki eyak wat-wat eekwi, ndi, at ambi nen at ambi iniki kole eekak eekwi, eerit nugwi nogo yogondak ndak-ndak aret eerit nogo logonip~o.
52005012	Noreewi~o. "It aap kinenggela'me nabenak mban eeppinagagwi, ninowe inom kunik logonet kinarum wonogwe, ndi, kini wuppiigwi, eekwi nogo liippiigo logonip~o," yinuk, yokkirogo~o.
52005013	It eerit nugwi ti paga kit kiniki kunik eeginako logonet, tiyappiigo logobagip nduk, yokkirogo. Kit kiniki ambit lambunik logonip~o.
52005014	Ndi, noreewi~o. It aap iniki nen alik eerit nugwi iinok, inaruk wakwi, aaninggin inoba age kero, inagabiti mbakak nugwi iinok, iniki kwippiigwi, iniki awo kole aga'lek kenok, eyak wappiigwi, ndi, aakumi abok kinoone yanggorogon yorogwe, eeko logonip~o.
52005015	Maluk onggo-onggo eekwi iyo, liippiigo logonip~o. Kit-kit inom, it aakumi abok inom, obeelom mban eekak yuwak nduk, liippogo logonip~o.
52005016	Kiniki ale'nggen mban mbako logonip~o.
52005017	Puk aga'lek tamban mban eeko logonip.
52005018	Keritut Yetut kinom kunik logonet, eerit nogwe kiinok, yi mendek ndi mendek eeppinagagwi nogo ti, Ala mbareegerak paga aret eeppinagagwi me, "Wa," mban yogo logonip~o.
52005019	Kani noguk ari menggi kwak, Aberiniki nogonogo puurak ti mage~o.
52005020	Ndi, Ala nen yorage kagak, yokkirogwe wone nogo, miyuk-meya eerogo pugwi ti, mage mban~o.
52005021	Yi wone ndi wone yogwe nogo abok aret abut mbambunuk, abe kenok mban nggirik-nggerok agago porogo logonip~o.
52005022	Yi eekak ndi eekak eerit nogo logonet, maluk eraambe yelok kenok, mbo pogo logonip~o. Wone yokkirogoorak ti, abok aret eeko logonip~o.
52005023	Ndi, yogondak niniki ugun tayenak ale'nggen logowok nduk, eeppinanege menggerak Ala nogo nen, kit kineebe at ake leenogo pake logonet, kinomaluk abu lek eerogo pinagage, ndi, ninowe Yetut Keritut woroorak eyom paga maluk kinoba pinagage kero, kiniki-kineebe abok aret enaani nggelorogon pinagago wonage, eeke logowak~o.
52005024	At yonggo pinaneegerak nogo nen, yegetak alik mbeyok ariilik, abok liirogon aret eeke menggerak me, "Eeke logowak~o," yogoorak nogo aret eeke logogin~o.
52005025	Noreewi~o. Ninake tamban eeko logonip~o.
52005026	Keyage wat-wat yogo logonet, kiniki kunik paga linggik-kambuk yogo logonip.
52005027	Nit liiru mbanggoorak yi, ninowe nen, "Yoret~o," yinuk, yo'niragaarak me, noreewi apit inenggaanom paga mbininogo yoraanip~o.
52005028	At ninowe Yetut Keritut iniki kunik en eeppinagage logonet, kinarum aret logogin~o. Noreewi wa!
53001001	Noreewi~o. Kit Ala apuri ninogoba Ala ninowe Yetut Keritut kinom kunik o Tetalonika kuwak eeko monggotak nogo, an Pawulut inom, Tiliwanut inom, Timotiyut inom, nen wone ambi yokkiraawi~o.
53001002	Ninogoba Ala ninowe Yetut Keritut imbirak iniki kunik nen wokkirogwe, kit kiniki ugun tayenak ale'nggen logobagip nduk, eeppinagagwi, eeko logogun~o.
53001003	Noreewi~o. Kit eekwi paga nit puk logorak meek ee'ninake kenok, Ala mondok, "Wa," yogo monggoorak. Kit abet mbakwi nogo piyok ari lek omaawi arit unggwage, ndi, niniki-kiniki kunik aganakwi ti, nggwok arit nage, eeke me, "Ala wa," yogo monggoorak nogo ti, op aret eeko monggoorak~o.
53001004	Togop me, kit piyak-payak eerogo pinagagwi, aaninggin kinoba pinagagwi, eekwi kwe kagak, kinogogumbuk logonet waganggwi me, kiniki mondok nu'lek logonet abet mbakwi nogo, Ala apuri yi awi ndi awi kuwak eerit nogo menggaarak nit yoranet nogo logonet, tiyappinagit nogo monggoorak.
53001005	Kit Ala abu'me logorak miikotak kenok, maluk eeppinagagwi nogo ti, Ala nen, "Kit obeelom aret me, nabu'me logorak op aret~o," yokkiraawak nduk, kinogogumbuk logonet, waganggwi me, Ala nen koonogo pinanege nogo ti, maluk lek obeelom aret koonogo pinanege menggerak nineenu ogo~o.
53001006	At Ala iniki koonak a'me nggelok eeke menggerak me, it nen aaninggin kit kinoba pinagagwi nogo, onggo at nen it aaninggin inoba piyaagin~o.
53001007	Ndi, yogondak aaninggin kit kinoba wonage nogo, peebi nit ninom niniki tayenogo pinanigin~o. It waka'ngget mondok tiyanak menggaarak malayikat nogo ninowe Yetut inom mbogut paga nen kani omoonuk enggela'me wambi wogo logonet,
53001008	it aakumi Ala ineenggo'lek obeelom wone ninowe Yetut eeke nagagerak wone nogo wagangga'lek iinok, maluk onggo wogora woraagin eyom nogo paga niniki tayenogo pinanigin~o.
53001009	-
53001010	Ti eyom paga nit at apuri ake leenak nogo nen at eebe tiyappugwi, ndi, nit wone paganogo yokkirogogurak paga abet mbareegutak me, kit ninom abet mbakwi abok aret, "Wi!" ugwi, eeruwok nduk, woraagin~o. Wage kenok, it Ala ineenggo'lek Yetut eeke nagagerak obeelom wone wagangga'lek mendek nogo, maluk onggo mondok-mondok aganabuwak nduk, at Ala nen, "An nomaawi paga eeppiinet nage neenok, aakumi nen, Wi! nugu menggam nenggaawak paga yayi logorak lek~o," yinuk, ogoorogo endekem wumbiyaagin~o.
53001011	At ninogoba Ala nen obeelom eerit nogo logobagip nduk, kinayonggo pereegerak nogo ndak-ndak eerit nugwi kiinok, "Op eekotak~o," yinuk, yokkirage, kit obeelom eeriyak mbakwi nogo eerubagip nduk, omaawi eeppinagage, ndi, at abet mba'nuk eeriyak mbakotak nogo ndak-ndak eerubagip nduk, omaawi eerogo pinagage, eeke logowak nduk, kinake tamban mban eeko monggoorak.
53001012	Ninogoba Ala at ninowe Yetut Keritut imbirak iniki kunik nen eeppinagagwi iigak, kit togop aret eerit nogo logonet, at tiyappugwi kiinok, at nen kit kunduk tiyappinagage logogin~o.
53002001	At ninowe Yetut Keritut wage kenok, nit at ninom kuwak eeriyak wone nogo yokkiraawi~o.
53002002	Ninoreewi~o. It aakumi nen, "Ninowe woroorak eyom abu panggoni wagaarak~o," agan wogo logonet, at ambi nen, "Ala nen wone yo'nege kenok, yokkiragi~o," ari, ndi, ambi nen, "Lek~o. Pawulut nen liiru mbaneegerak me, yokkira~o," yinuk, ari, agan wogwe iinok, kinagabiti nen kiniki ma'nogwe kiyo nduk, yokkirogo~o.
53002003	It aakumi pilit togop agan wogo logonet, kinambokan laganukwak, liippiigo logonip~o. Ninowe woroorak nogo ti, aakumi nen Ala wone, "Nineebi~o," yinuk, mbo pugwi, ndi, at mondok maluk eeka lek eerogo puurak ake lengganak nogo, kin ari wage, eeka'lek iigak, woraagin lek~o.
53002004	It aakumi nen yi mendek ndi mendek mippunuk, "Ninogoba Ala aret~o," yinuk, ayuk wukwi, kugiwak ogobakkigirogo punuk, alut eekwi, eeko menggaarak abok aret, at mondok maluk lombok eeka nogo nen tebenogo piinok, at alik tiyappake logonet, Ala awi wurik me mi'nari unggwage logomenggerik, "Kinogoba Ala an aret~o," yinuk, yorage logogin~o.
53002005	An aa'nduk kit ninom logonet, wone yi apit yokkiragagirak nogo abeko ogotik ilik, lek a?
53002006	At maluk eeka nogo ti, mbet-mbet woraagin lek~o. Ndiyom paga kin ari woroorak koonak wonage nogo paga mban woraawak nduk, at ambi nen tebemborogo wonage nogo kineenu aret~o.
53002007	At kumaat-kumaat maluk eerit nage menggerak nogo ti, muk eerit nage kwe, at tebenogo pege menggerak nogo wonok lagangga'lek kagak, maluk nggwok wigak yigin lek~o. At tebenogo pit nage me, tebenogo pit nage logogin aret~o.
53002008	-
53002012	Wonok lagi nage kenok perak, at maluk lombok eeka nogo kin ari woraagin~o. Kin ari wage logomenggerik, at Ibilit eeke menggerak ndak-ndak at omaawi paga eerit nege logonet, "Ala omaawi paga eeke," mbaruwak nduk, inagabiti worak mendek eeke, eerubok mendek eeke, tam warak negen eeke, eeke logonet, it aakumi Ala nen inagap ndaruwak nduk, wone abet aret ari menggerak inikilom mba'nuk wagangga'lek logomenggaarak paga maluk agago piyoorak nogo, inambokan laganikit nduk, oone alik negen pugunogo yoranet unggwage logogin~o. It aakumi Ala ari menggerak wone wagangga'lek maluk eeriyak mban inikilom mbarit nugwi nogo abok aret, at Ala nen, "Inowak loombunuk, maluk inoba piyaakit~o," yinuk, pilit wone agan wage nogo abet mbaruwak nduk, iniki apit agago piyaagin~o. At maluk lombok eeka ti nen togop eerit wage me, ninowe Yetut mondok tiyanak ayuk worak wage logonet, ambe aagi paga eebe mondok warogo lek eerogo pi woraagin~o.
53002013	Kit noreewi~o. Nit ninowe nen iniki kunik eekkinabeegerak nogo kit aret kiinok, "Ala wa," yoriyak mban ee'ninake menggerak. Kit Ala ari menggerak wone abet mbakwi kiinok, Ala apuri logobagip nduk, Aberiniki nen leenogo pinagage kagak, Ala nen, "Kinagap ndarikit~o," yinuk, kit kinaa'nduk togon miikkinabeegerak me, "Ala wa," yoriyak mban ee'ninake menggerak.
53002014	Kit togop aret eekkinabuwak nduk, nit obeelom wone yokkirogwe niigak, wiigiragagerak nogo~o. Nit ninowe Yetut Keritut mondok tiyanak menggerak kit kinom ndak-ndak tiyanak logobagip nduk, wiigiragagerak.
53002015	Togop me, noreewi~o. Ninoone paga yokkirogo nogogurak inom, liiru mbanak paga yokkirogo nogogurak nogo inom, kiniki nu'lek logonet, wone ti, nggirik-nggerok agago porogo logonip~o.
53002016	-
53002017	Kit obeelom eerit nugwi, wone obeelom mban yoranet nugwi, eeko logobagip nduk, at ninabuwa mba'nuk iniki kunik ee'ninake logonet, niniki mondok-mondok eyak wappinanege, niniki lunik abe nogo mendek wo'nirage, eeke menggerak ninogoba Ala nogo inom, ninowe Yetut Keritut inom, imbirak nen kit kiniki eyak wappinagagwi, kinomaawi eerogo pinagagwi, eeko logowak~o.
53003001	Ndi, ninoreewi~o. Wone abu aret yokkirogoorak kwe, irip paga iluk ambi yi aret me, yokkiraawi~o. Nit ninowe wone waganggo nogogutik, wiganinuk wundi nogo logonet, tiyappit nogo nogogutak nogo ti kokwak, nit togop aret yi awi ndi awi wiganinuk mbet-mbet nogo logowok nduk, ninake tamban eeko logonip~o.
53003002	Ndi, it aakumi abok aret abet mbaka'lek me, it aap maluk eeka abu maluk lombok eerit nugwi ti nen, nit maluk eerogo pinanukwak, ninogoba nen ninagap ndaruwak nduk, ninake tamban eeko logonip~o.
53003003	At ninowe perak, mbo pinanegeelik mondok liirogon ninake eeke menggerak me, at nen kinomaawi eeppinagage, ndi, at maluk eeke menggerak nen maluk eeppinagukwak kinarum wake, eeke logogin~o.
53003004	Kit eeko logorak wone lengganogo yokkirogo monggoorak nogo ti, muk eekwi nineenu aret kwe, ambinom eeko logobagip nduk, ninowe nen eeppinagagin abet aret mbako ogoorik~o.
53003005	At Ala nen yi aakumi ndi aakumi iniki kunik aganake menggerak nogo kokwak kit ndak-ndak eeppiinet nugwi, ndi, Keritut maluk mendek oba age kagak, yanggonak wonagagerak nogo kokwak, kit togop aret yanggonak wonogwe, eeko logobagip nduk, Ala nen eeppinagage logowak lak, "Ao," kinombako ogoorik~o.
53003006	Ndi, ninoreewi~o. Wone, "Ndogop eeko logonip~o," yokkirogo nogogurak nogo, kinoreewi ando eeka'lek ineenggi tanep we nugwi iinok, kinom nugu logorak mage~o.
53003007	Kit ninom logonet, nit we logolik nggik-palek eerit nogogurak nogo kineenu lombok aret me, eerit nogogurak nogo kit ndak-ndak eerit nogo logonip~o.
53003008	Ninom logonet, kinambi onggo lek we ambi nonggo logolik~o. Nit time wogo nogogurik, kit aaninggin ambinom kinoba pinagukwak, ko'lu-kii'me eerit mban nogo logonet, ndeyak eerogo pinaneegerak nogo kineenu aret~o.
53003009	Kinamendek wo'nirogwe we noorak op aret kwe, nit eerit nogwe paga ninowakkagak kit ndak-ndak eeko logobagip nduk, eereegurak.
53003010	Ninom logonet, "Aap ambi yabu eeka'lek kenok, mbi magariyak mage~o," yokkirogo nogogurak nogo~o.
53003011	Kit ando kit kinobaalombok eekkolaga'lek aakumi inobaalombok mban eerit nugu logonet, yabu eeka'lek we ugun-ugun eerit nugwi yogwe iigirak me nduk, yokkirogo.
53003012	"It aap togop eekwi ti, ineyabu liirogon eekkologo logonet, it inambi mban nonggo logowak~o," yinuk, wone ti abok aret ninowe Yetut Keritut nen yo'niragagerak me, lengganogo yokkiragi~o.
53003013	Ndi, ninoreewi~o. Kit perak, obeelom eeppiinet nogwe paga anggon eekkinake kenok, "Nineebi," mbarugup~o.
53003014	Nit wone yokkirogwe liiru mbanak yi, at ambi nen, "Eeriyak, neebi~o," ari kenok, aap ti, eebe liippogo logomonggotik, enggali aruwak nduk, kinom nugu logorak mage~o.
53003015	"Ninawim kwak me," nduk, eeppuurak ti lek~o. Ata, "Ninore aret me," mba'nuk, we aruk liirogon aret wa'nip~o. Wone yokkirogoorak yi abok aret ninowe Yetut Keritut nen yo'nirage kagak lengganogo yokkirogo~o.
53003016	Ndi, yogondak niniki ugun tayenak ale'nggen logowok nduk, eeppinanega ninowe nogo nen yi eekak ndi eekak abok aret eerit nogwe kiigak, kiniki ugun tayenak ale'nggen logobagip nduk, kinarum logonet, eeppinagit nage logogin~o. Kit abok aret ninowe kinom logogin~o.
53003017	"At Pawulut nen aret liiru yi mbanggerak kagi," yinuk, yelok kaawak nduk, irip paga keyage wappiige wone ti, an nen aret mbangge minggirak me, liiru yi, "At nen aret yo'niragaarak," mbarubagip nduk, irip paga keyage wappinagage wone yi, an neenggi lombok paga nen aret mbanggiragi~o.
53003018	At ninowe Yetut Keritut iniki kunik nen kit abok aret eeppinagage logonet, kinarum logogin~o. Wa!
54001001	-
54001002	Naput Timotiyut wae. At ninagap ndaka Ala inom, niniki lunik Keritut Yetut inom, imbirak nen wone lengganogo yo'nereegwaarak paga an Pawulut Keritut Yetut ayonggo nappiigak mendek agago paneegwaarak nogo nen, nit apit abet mbakwi nogo paga an naput lombok agagindak me, wone ambi yokkiri~o. At ninogoba Ala ninowe Keritut Yetut imbirak iniki kunik nen wokkugwi, kabuwa nen obeelom eeppagagwi, ndi, kiniki ugun tayenak ale'nggen logonok nduk, eeppagagwi, eeko logogun~o.
54001003	-
54001004	An o Makendoniya woraakit nduk, wage logonet, "Kat o Epetut yayi logot~o," yinuk, noone nabek togon yokkereegirak nogo ti, "It aakumi timbayok mbininggwi, ndarak alom mbininggo logonet, puk aga'lek niikkenok nogwe, eekwi iinok, niniki abet mbakwi paga Ala nen ee'ninaburak kooneegerak nogo nineenu ariyak nduk yo'nirogwe lek we wone alom kwaako logonet, noone-koone yogwe me, liippugup~o," yinuk, yorage, ndi, it aakumi ando wone alik agan nugwi nogo, "Mamuniroorak mage~o," yinuk, yorage, eeke logonok nduk, "Yayi logot~o," yinuk, yokkereegirak nogo~o.
54001005	An wone lengganogo yokkereegirak nogo ti, it iniki abe paga aakumi inabuwa mbakwi, iniki obeelom koonnage kenok mban eekwi, ndi, iniki abu abet aret mbakwi, eeko logowak nduk, "Yorage logot~o," yinuk, yokkereegirak nogo~o.
54001006	An wone yokkege yi nogo ti, eeriyak kagak aakumi ando nen nomonogo mbo punuk, wone lek ariyak mendek mban aanom warogo mbininggo menggaarak.
54001007	It aap ti nen, "Ala yereegerak wone yugu liiru mbanak mamuniraga mendek nit aret logowok," mbako menggaarak kwe, it yogo menggaarak inom, ndi, inoone omaawi paga, "Ti ndogop kaamunggup~o," yinuk, yogo menggaarak nogo inom, it iniki we ugun kobak mban logonet, yogo menggaarak.
54001008	Ala yereegerak wone yugu liiru mbanak nogo ndak-ndak eeruwok nduk, waganggwi kenok ti, obeelom aret kogo monggoorak.
54001009	Ala wone yugu liiru mbanak nogo ti, aap iniki obeelom wonogwe iinok yoroolik. Ata, it aap Ala wone yugu tagangga inom, inogobamini inoone koneniyak ineebi mbaka inom, Ala ayuk wuka'lek meek eerogo pega inom, it maluk eeka inom, iniki liirak lek ugun-ugun eerit nega inom, inagalo-inogoba inooka inom, aakumi ugun-ugun inoorit nega inom,
54001010	kumi ugun wurinaka inom, aap-aap wut-wut yaga inom, aakumi inapuri kumaarinaka inom, pilit pugungga inom, pilit wone inoba pega inom, ti eekwi abok aret Ala wone kole wone kagak alik eekwi iinok, inake aret yoragagerak nineenu aret~o.
54001011	Ala wone kole wone nogo ti, nit alut eeko monggoorak tiyanak menggerak Ala nogo nen obeelom wone an unde logokit nduk, eeppaneegerak nogo aret~o.
54001012	An nomaawi eeppanege menggerak nowe Keritut Yetut nogo nen, "Aap yi, ambi eeke logowak nduk, unde eeppege neenok, liirogon aret eeke logogin," nombake nagagerik, an yabu ambi eeke logokit nduk, unde eeppaneegerak me, "Wa," yoge minggirak.
54001013	An aa'nduk noone maluk at yoge, nanini wulo logonet, at oone waganggwi mendek inoorit nage, at miyuk-meya eerogo pege, eeke nagagirak kwe, abet mbaka'lek ugun neenggo'lek logonet, eeke nagagirak me, Ala nabuwa mba'nuk, teppaneegerak~o.
54001014	Ninowe Keritut Yetut ninom kunik me, iniki kunik nen obeelom eeppanegak mban eeke logonet, an Ala wone abet mbarikit nduk ee'nake, ndi, aakumi niniki kunik aganabikit nduk ee'nake, eereegerak.
54001015	"Aakumi maluk eeko menggaarak nogo inagap ndaruwak nduk, Keritut Yetut o yime wambi wagagerak~o," yinuk, yogo menggaarak wone nogo ti, abet aret me, woorak op aret~o. "Aakumi maluk eekwi~o," yogo menggaarak nogo ti, maluk eeka abe iyagalo an aret kwe,
54001016	alom ti paga at nabuwa mba'nuk teppaneegerak. Peebi it aakumi ineenik mondok logorak mbaremenggaarak nogo nen iniki at oba panggombunuk, abet mbakwi paga waganggo logorak nogo, in wakkagak eeko logorak an neebe aret~o. Nit nen Keritut Yetut maluk eeppugwi kwe, onggo mbet-mbet eeppinanege lek liippunuk eeppinanege menggerak nogo, maluk eeka abe iyagalo an neebe nogo paga kin aruwak nduk, nabuwa mba'nuk, teppaneegerak.
54001017	Ndi, yogondak, naput~o. Yi o ndi o aakumi aa'nduk wonogogwaarak inom, yogondak wonogwe inom, peebi logorak inom, ninogoba endagembogut kanggeelik mondok itok eenik menggerak ninigen kogolik alik menggerak Ala nogo endage mondok-mondok tiyanak ayuk warak logogin~o. Amin!
54001018	-
54001019	Ndi, naput Timotiyut wae. Wone lengganogo yokkigirak ti, mondok unde logonok nduk, yokkigi~o. Kat awo eeka'lek keegak, "Peebi ndogop eeke logomunggun~o," yinuk, yokkereegwaarak wone nogo ndak-ndak aret yokkigi~o. Kiniki abet mbariyak inom, kiniki obeelom koonnage kenok mban eeriyak inom, mondok nggirik-nggerok agago porogo logonet, aap wim waka'ngget menggi kwak, kat togop aret kalilaakwi eerit nage logot~o. It aap ando iniki obeelom koonnage nogo taganogo punuk, alik eerit nugwi me, yiiro eyo paga lik ari logonet, yigirik-noonom age menggi kwak, it abet mba'nuk waganeegwaarak wone nogo togop aret yigirogo mbo pereegwaarak me nduk yokkigi~o.
54001020	It aap Kimeneyut kunduk, aap Alekandet kunduk, togop eereegwaarak me, an nen Ala endage miyuk-meya eerogo pugwi inagabiti mbaruwak nduk, Ibilit unde eeppereegirak aret~o.
54002001	Wone aa'nduk yokkiriyak mbakirak nogo yokkiri~o. Yi aakumi ndi aakumi abok aret inake Ala nggino yoge, tamban eeke, aakumi inake yoge, eeppagage nogo, "Wa," yoge, eeke logonok nduk, noone nabek togon yokkege agarik~o.
54002002	It aap inendagembogut inom, aap yo'nggok abok aret inom, nen ninarum abe wonogwe iigak, niniki warak a'nuk, Ala liirogon mugurok nogo logonet, niniki ugun tayenak ale'nggen logowok nduk, it inake tamban eeke logot~o.
54002003	Togop eekwi kiinok, ninagap ndaka Ala inikilom mbake menggerak me, ti eeko logorak op aret~o.
54002004	At nen yi aakumi ndi aakumi abok aret inagap ndappunuk, at ari menggerak wone nogo ineenu aruwak lak, "Ao!" inombake menggerak.
54002005	At Ala ambit aret menggerak. Ndi, aakumi inom, Ala inom, terak inake yonggo nappegak aap ambit Keritut Yetut aret~o.
54002006	Yi aakumi ndi aakumi abok aret at eebe paga inonggo mbambunuk, wondet agago piyareegerak. Ti eereegerak nogo ti, Ala nen yi aap ndi aap abok eeppiyoorak kooneegerak pagak yuurak eyom panggoni wagagerak me, aret pagak yereegerak.
54002007	Ala nen yi aakumi ndi aakumi abok eeppiyoorak kooneegerak nogo, it aap endekem mendek Ala ari menggerak wone ineenu a'nuk, abet mbariyak wone nogo, agan nage logokit nduk mippanege, ndi, yi awi ndi awi yoranet nege logokit nduk, nappiigak agago panege, eereegerak~o. Wone ti, pilit lek abu abet aret yokkigi~o.
54002008	Togop me, it aap yi awi ndi awi abok aret inanini mbakwi, wone wakwi, eeka'lek obeelom mban logonet, ineenggi nippunuk, tamban eeko logowak nduk, "Ao!" lombok inombake minggirak.
54002009	Ndi, it kumi iniki warak nen inayum-inagali liirogon yikkologo mengga kwak, yi kumi ndi kumi abok aret iniki warak a'nuk, togop aret inayum-inagali nggirik-nggerok liirogon aret yikkologo logowak~o. Ineeruwak awi wuppunuk laanggwi, mbuti abinakwi mendek yirikwi, eyoonggen laambu kigirikwe nogo mendek yikkologwe, ndi, yum onggo nggwok kenok mban kunogo yirikwi, eekak yuurak ti mage~o.
54002010	Ata, it kumi Ala wone liippunuk, mugurok nogo menggaarak mendek nen inayum-inagali liippunuk yikkologo mengga kwak, yi obeelom ndi obeelom eeriyak nogo ti, ndak-ndak aret liippunuk eerit nogo logowak~o.
54002011	It kumi nogo ti, inoone lek aap inabu'me kwi'na'nuk wone mamunggologo logowak~o.
54002012	-
54002014	At Kawa aa'nduk lek~o. Aram aa'nduk wakkagagerak me, kumi ti, inoone lek logonet, inoreewi inoone liirogon konenggo logowak~o. Ibilit nogo nen aap Aram ambo'me laganulik. Ata, kwe ambo'me lagangge mbareegi, kwe nogo nen maluk eereegerak me, "Kumi nen aap mamunirogwe, ndi, it kumi nen aap inabu'me piinok, Yi eeri nak, ndi eeri nak, yorogwe, eeko logorak ti mage~o," yinuk, ari minggirak.
54002015	Kwe nogo maluk eereegerak ti kwe, it kumi nogo iniki warak logonet, Ala wone abet mbakwi, aakumi iniki kunik aganakwi, ndi, maluk eeka'lek Ala ake leenak wonogwe, eekwi iinok perak, it inaagalogwe ndaganakwi iigak, Ala nen inagap ndaganake logogin~o.
54003001	"Aap ambi nen, An Ala apuri unde logokit, mbake kenok, at mbakerak nogo ti, op aret~o," yinuk, aakumi nen yogo menggaarak nogo ti, abet aret yogo menggaarak~o.
54003002	Aap ambi Ala apuri unde logorak mippuurak mbakwi kenok ti, aakumi inoone at oba pugulik kenok, akwe ambit wogo kenok, iniki tum waka kenok, iniki warak kenok, li'lak mban eeke menggerak kenok, inanoniya laka kenok, aakumi op mamuniroorak kenok,
54003003	amburu kumili aganake ndonggorogon nenggeelik kenok, anini mbet-mbet wunggeelik iniki yanggonak kenok, yawi pegeelik kenok, wu inikilom mbakeelik kenok, aap togop mendek ti, Ala apuri unde logorak mippiyoorak op aret~o.
54003004	Aap ambi Ala apuri unde logorak ti, ayuk warak logonet, at apuri liirogon ndegeninake menggerak kenok mban mippuurak.
54003005	Aap ambi nen at apuri lombok liirogon kooninake logorak kobak menggerak kenok, Ala apuri ti, nonggop togon kooninake logogin mbakop?
54003006	Aap awo ngget iluk Ala miikerak kenok mippuurak lek~o. Ibilit iniki wogoppake mbareegi, maluk eeppereegerak nogo kwak, aap ti, togop iniki wogoppatemenggerak paga maluk eeppege kero, mippuurak lek~o.
54003007	Mippugwi iinok, maluk eeremenggerak paga aakumi nen abok mbanggwi iinok, pagi keele pugu enggaanok nggerok ari menggi kwak, Ibilit nen aap ti, togop aret iniki nomongge kero, it aap endekem mendek nen at eeke abok mbanggo logonet, "Aap ti, obaabut koonak aret~o," yogwe iinok mban mippuurak~o.
54003008	Ndi, it aap yeenggwaaragak nogo, togop aret it inayuk warak logonet, inoone mbere lek ambiret mban yogo menggaarak kenok, anggur amburu kumili aganake menggerak ndonggorogon nunggulik kenok, wu kolaawok nduk aakumi wi-wi eeginakulik kenok,
54003009	ndi, wone kote kumaarak wonagagerak niniki abet mbakwi wone nogo porogo logonet, iniki obeelom koonnage kenok mban eekwi kenok, aap ti mendek mippiyoorak op aret~o.
54003010	It aap yeenggwaaragak logorak ti, aa'nduk inabut mbambunuk, inoone inoba piigulik kenok, mippiyoorak op~o.
54003011	It inakuwi ti togop aret inayuk warak logonet, wone inambe irip paga wonok nugulik kenok, iniki warak kenok, ndi, yi eekwi ndi eekwi ineenggi omaawi eerit nugwi kenok, kumi togoti mendek iinok, it inogonggelomini aap yeenggwaaragak mippiyoorak op aret~o.
54003012	It aap yeenggwaaragak ti, inakuwi ambit wogo kenok, ndi, inapuri inom, it at inom menggaarak inom, ndegeninako logonet, wone liirogon lengganogo yorogwe iinok mban mippiyoorak op aret~o.
54003013	It aap yeenggwaaragak eerit nugu menggaarak nogo abe koonak eekwi iinok, inendage warak aret logogun~o. Ndi, nit niniki Keritut Yetut oba panggombunuk abet mbakwi wone nogo, it inagabiti mbaka'lek logonet, yoranet nugu logogun aret~o.
54003014	An mbet-mbet keya woraakit nduk, niniki lunik logonet, wone yi, liiru mbanggege kwe,
54003015	ambi yiluk ari kagak eerukwak, Ala apuri inenggela'me logonet, nonggop eerit nege logorak keenu a'nok nduk, liiru yi mbanggege agarik~o. Wone Ala ari menggerak wone o eyak nu'lek wuraberak ti, Ala mondok eenik menggerak apuri kuwak eeko menggaarak nogo aret.
54003016	Nit Ala wone abet mba'nuk waganggo monggoorak kote kumaarak lombok wonagagerak nogo yi~o. "At aap aret kin ari wage mbareegi, Yi Ala aput, mbaruwak nduk, Aberiniki nen kin eeppereegerak. Kin eeppege mbareegi, it malayikat nen at eebe inigen kogwe, Ala wone ineenggo'lek mendek wonogome yoranet nogwe, it aap abok aret at abet mbakwi, eeko mbareegwa, Wi, ugwi iigak, wonok laganeegerak~o," yinuk, yogo menggaarak nogo mondok abet aret kogo~o.
54004001	At Aberiniki nen kin paga ari logonet, "O age yobok kuli paga it aap ando nen aakumi inambokan laganuwok nduk, pilit pugunogo yorogwe, Ibilit nen yorage kagak mamunirogwe, eekwi wone nogo liippunuk, mugurok nogo logonet, Ala wone abet mbareegwaarak nogo kobak eerogo mbo aret pugun~o," yinuk, ari menggerak.
54004002	It aap wone ti mendek agan nugwi nogo ti, aakumi inambokan laganuwok nduk, pilit pugunogo yorogo menggaarak aret. Ninagabolo togum agaatak me, kani nengge kagak andi lek menggi kwak, it aap ti, inikime togop aret me, wone yoragaatak kwe, konengga'lek inogogumbuk aret menggaarak~o.
54004003	It aap ti nen, "Kumi wogonako logorak mage~o," yinuk, yorogwe, ndi, it aap Ala ari menggerak wone ineenu a'nuk abet mbakwi nogo nen, "Ugun noorak nduk Ala nen wakkagagerak me, Wa, yinuk, ma'mak noorak op," mbakwi iigak, "Noorak mage~o," yinuk, mamunirogwe, eeko menggaarak.
54004004	Yi mendek ndi mendek Ala nen wakkagagerak nogo ti, obeelom mban aret wakkagagerak me, nit niniki nen, "Wa," mbako logonet, waganggwi kenok ti, mage lek~o.
54004005	Ala wone waganggwi, tamban eekwi, eekwi paga obeelom age menggerak me, yi mendek ndi mendek ugun noorak op aret~o.
54004006	Wone ti, koreewi mamunirage keenok, kat Keritut Yetut ayeloman abe mendek aret logomunggun~o. Ndi, niniki abet mbakwi wone inom, wone kole wone mamunik mugurok nage menggendak inom, waganogo aberit nage paga kiniki nu'lek kole aret logomunggun~o.
54004007	It kumi inanggok inariimbayok mbininggo mengga kwak, yi wone ndi wone abe mendek lek kagak aanom warogo mbininggo menggaarak nogo ti, liippugun~o. Ala wone perak, ndak-ndak eeke logonok nduk, nabenik-nabenak mamunggolage logot~o.
54004008	Nineebe omaawi eeriyak wakkagak eekwi paga nineebe ninomaawi ee'ninake ti, we mbuuluk op ee'ninaburak nduk eeko monggoorak kwe, Ala wone yugu ndak-ndak eeruwok nduk, wakkagak eekwi niinok perak, Ala nen yogondak inom, peebi inom, ee'ninaburak nineenu me, mondok nggwok togon obeelom ee'ninaburak nduk, eeko monggoorak kogo~o.
54004009	Togop me, "Wone ti abet aret~o," yinuk, kiniki mbere lek nggaruk togon waganggo logorak op aret~o.
54004010	Yi aakumi ndi aakumi abok inagap ndarikit mbake menggerak kwe, nit niniki at oba panggombunuk abet mbakwi ninagap ndaka mondok itok eenik menggerak Ala nen, "Nit yorogwe niigak eeppiyaagin," mba'nuk, niniki lunik mondok nu'lek monggoorak me, nit lin wako logonet, nabenik-nabenak mban eerit nogo monggoorak.
54004011	Wone yi nogo lengganogo yorage, mamunirage, eeke logot~o.
54004012	Kat keebe awo tawe aret me nduk, aakumi nen tebenogo pagarak ti mage~o. Ari menggendak inom, eeke menggendak inom, aakumi kiniki kunik aganake menggendak inom, Ala wone abet mbake menggendak inom, maluk eerukwak, kenegen tebenak nege menggendak nogo inom, eeke ti paga it aap abet mbako menggaarak kat in wakkagak logonet, eeke logot~o.
54004013	An awo waga'lek neegak, Ala wone mbuku paga mbininirage, inaruk wake, wone mamunirage, eeke logonet, liirogon eeke logot~o.
54004014	Ala eyabu ambi eeke logonok nduk, it Ala apuri unde nogo nen kanobak tebenggo logonet, "Kat peebi togop eeke logomunggun~o," yinuk, nggwok paga aa'nduk unde eeppagareegwaarak nogo, kobak eerogo puurak ti mage~o.
54004015	Kiniki kole age aakumi abok yelok keyaawak nduk, yokkigirak ti paga mban panggombunuk, eerit nage logot~o.
54004016	Kobaabut eeke menggendak inom, wone mamunirage menggendak inom, liippege logot~o. Wone yi, mondok liirogon porogo logot~o. Porogo logonet, liirogon eeke keenok, it aakumi kat koone konenggwi nogo inagap ndake, ndi, kat kunduk kagap ndakkolage, eerumunggun~o.
54005001	It aap inanggok iinok, koone omaawi paga mberiraagun~o. "Yi nogobamini kwak me," yinuk, iniki eyak wappiige logot~o. It aap tawe ti, kat kawuri kwak,
54005002	it kumi inanggok ti, kagalomini kokwak, ndi, kumi tawe ti, kat kiriwi kokwak me, it paga kiniki me maluk mondok abeka'lek logonet, yorage logot~o.
54005003	It kumi togwe inaagalogwe inarum liirogon wonogwe lek iinok, liippiige logot~o.
54005004	Kumi togwe inaagalogwe-inowowologwe wonogwe iinok perak, it nogo nen Ala wone ndak-ndak eeruwak nduk, inagalomini- inowogolomini it inaa'nduk yeenggwaarogo logowak~o. It inagalomini-inowogolomini nen inaagalogwe-inowowologwe ndegengginako nogogwaarak nogo onggo yogondak it togop aret ndegeninako logowak~o. Togop eekwi iinok, Ala inikilom mbake menggerak.
54005005	Kwe ambi togwe aret kwe, aagalogwe nen yeenggwaaga'lek kenok, "Ala nen yeenggwaanege logowak~o," yinuk, iniki Ala paga lunik logonet, ko'lu-kii'me Ala nggino yoge, tamban eeke, eeke menggerak kenok, kwe ti, abe togwe aret~o.
54005006	It kumi ineenggi eekwi lek amburu warak mban na mbarit nugwi iinok ti, ineenik wonogwe kwe, kambak negen aret wonogwe~o.
54005007	Kumi togwe togop eekwi iinok, aakumi inoone inoba piyookwak, wone ti, kulinik-kalinik koone omaawi paga inaruk wake logot~o.
54005008	Aap ambit-ambi at owe-awot ndegeninakeelik ti, maluk aret kwe, at apuri lombok ndegeninaka'lek kenok perak, it aakumi abet mbaka'lek mendek ti, we maluk mbuuluk negen kwe, aap ti perak, maluk mondok nggwok aret eeke menggerak~o. At abet mbareegerak nogo ti, mbo pereegerak aret wonage~o.
54005009	Kwe ambi nda'nagagerak kagak tahun 60 eeka'lek kenok, endage mbaniyak lek~o. Ata, ogonggelo ambit wogo kagak togwe pugu kenok,
54005010	"Yi obeelom ndi obeelom eeke menggerak," yogwe iinok, aagalogwe liirogon tawe eeginaka kenok, aap nggiru inanoniya laka kenok, it Ala apuri ake leenak iniyok koorinaka kenok, it aakumi aaninggin inoba agaatak iniki eyak wappiiga kenok, ndi, yi obeelom ndi obeelom eekwi abok aret, "An unde~o," yinuk, eeke menggerak kenok, endage mbaniyak op kwe,
54005011	it kumi togwe awo ndugum iinok perak, inendage mbaniyak lek~o. It kumi ti, iniki nengge kenok, Keritut wone waganeegwaarak mbo punuk, aap alik koloorak koonugun me, inendage mbaniyak mage~o.
54005012	It aa'nduk mugurok noorak miireegwaarak nogo mbo pugwi paga maluk aret eekkologo logogun~o.
54005013	Ooluk-ooluk nogo yit nogo logonet, ineenggi lebenak eekko'net nugu menggaarak. Ti mban eerit nugwi ti lek~o. Ata, wone inambe irip paga wonok nugwi, ambi me wok yagak nugwi, eerit nugu logonet, wone yuurak lek nogo mendek kagak ugun agan nugu menggaarak.
54005014	Togop me, it kumi ti nen ambi eeremenggaarak paga it ninom ogoorak nogo nen ninenggali wappinanukwak, it kumi ndugum me togwe piyamenggerak nogo, inogonggelomini kologwe, inaagalogwe ndaganakwi, inamelak wogo eekwi, eeko logorak op aret mbake agarik~o.
54005015	Kumi ando perak, Ibilit mugurok nugu logowok nduk, muk iniyok paga yungguninuk nogo agaarik~o.
54005016	Kwe iniki abet mbake ambi nen agalo togwe wonage kenok, it Ala apuri abunuk aaninggin inoba piyookwak me, at aagaluk nogo nen yeenggwaage logowak~o. Ndi, it kumi togwe aret kwe, inaagalogwe lek iinok perak, it Ala apuri nen yeenggwaarogo logowak~o.
54005017	-
54005018	Ala nen ari logonet, "Lembu nen iniyok gandum anggen mbelanit nage kagak ando nunggwi iyo, inambe keele maarogo piigo logorak mage~o," ari, ndi, ambi, "It aap yabu eeko menggaarak yabu onggo woorak op aret~o," yinuk, ari, yereegwaarak liiru mbanak wonage me, it aap Ala apuri unde menggaarak inendage tiyanak kwe, obeelom lombok inarum wonogwe me nduk, inendage ambinom tiyappuurak ti op aret~o. It Ala wone nggwok paga yorogwe, wone mamunirogwe, mondok nabenak mban eekwi iinok ti, abunuk ambinom inendage tiyappiigo logonet, liippiigo logowak~o.
54005019	Aap mbere ilik, kenagan a, nen, "Togop eekerak~o," yinuk, yogwe lek iigak, at ambiret nen mban aap Ala apuri unde menggaarak ambi oone oba pege kenok, at oone koneniyak ti, lek~o.
54005020	Aap ambi nen maluk mban eeke kenok, it aakumi abok inagabiti mbaruwak nduk, nggwok paga aruk wake logonu~o.
54005021	An nogo, Ala inom, Keritut Yetut inom, it Ala ake leenak malayikat nogo inom, abok inenggaanom paga an wone yi, lengganogo yokkigi~o. An wone lengganogo yokkege yi, abok aret eeke logonet, kat kinom kunik kenok eeko logorak yoraga'lek mbo piige, ndi, aakumi ugun kenok eeko logorak yorage, eeke logogun~o. Ata, aakumi abok aret ineenu a'nuk, eeko logowak nduk, yorage logot~o.
54005022	Ala apuri unde logowak nduk, inanobak mbet-mbet tebeniyak mage~o. It ambi maluk eekwi iinok, kat kinom nabenggoloorak ti mage mban~o. Kat kiniki kikak naka'lek mondok alik leenak logot~o.
54005023	Kat kaanogum andi eekkake, keebe kuluk-kuluk ndeyak eekkake, eeke menggerak me, kat niyo mban nengge logogun~o. Ata, anggur amburu mbuuluk inom nenggak eeke logot~o.
54005024	It aap mippiyoorak nduk, inabut mbangge logonet, aap ando maluk eekaatak kenom age kenok, mbo piigo menggaarak kwe, it aap ando perak, inomaluk nobarak kagak, mippiigaatak me, peebi inomaluk kenom aret age menggerak.
54005025	It obeelom eekwi ti, togop aret iigo monggoorak. Ndi, it ando obeelom eekwi ambi nobarak wonage kenok, kumaarak togop mban logogin lek~o. Kin arigin aret~o.
54006001	Ala endage inom, nit wone mamunirogwe nogo inom, miyuk-meya eerogo pukwak, it aakumi inayeloman nen, "Ninogobamini aret~o," yinuk, inoone konenggo logonet, inayuk wuko logowak~o.
54006002	Ndi, it aakumi inayeloman nogo nen inogobamini abet mbakwi iinok, "Nit kunduk abet mbakwi me, Ala apuri ninom ndak-ndak aret~o," yinuk, inoone taganogo punuk, tebembiyoorak mage~o. Ata, it nogo nen, "Ninogobamini yabu eeppiigwi ti, aakumi inambik ti lek~o. Nit ninom ndak-ndak abet mbakwi aret me niniki kunik aret~o," yinuk, ambinom inake nggwok togon eerit nugu logowak~o. Wone yokkege yi nogo abok aret mamunirage, inaruk wake, eeke logot~o.
54006003	Aap ambit-ambi wone kole wone ninowe Yetut Keritut wone nogo inom, ndi, nit Ala wone liippunuk, mugurok noorak mamunirogwe wone nogo inom, eebi mbake logonet, wone alik mamunirage kenok,
54006004	-
54006005	at nen, "An neenu~o," nduk, wogoppatit nage kwe, kobak kagak we ugun agan nege~o. At aap ti nen wone, "Yi ndogop me, ti ndogop me," ari logonet, wone wake, ndi, wone mbuuluk yugu kagak ndugwi pege, eerit nage logorak ti, inikilom lombok mbarit nage menggerak. At togop eerit nage kenok, it aap ando Ala ari menggerak wone nogo mondok kobak logonet, maluk mban koonggwi nogo nen, "At ari kenok mban koneniyak, yo'nirogwe me," yinuk, neebi-keebi yogwe, "An iya, kat iya," yogo logonet ndugwi pugwi, at meek ombako logonet abok mbanit nogwe, ndi, inom wone mondok wakak mban eekwi, eeko menggaarak. It aap ti, "Ala wone liippunuk eerit nogwe niinok, nineenggi warak eekkolaawok," mbako menggaarak kwe
54006006	nit perak, Ala wone liippunuk, eerit nogo logonet, niniki tayenak wonogwe nogo ti, onggo iya tit kologwe ti aret.
54006007	Ninagalomini inikime nen nda'nogo logonet, iri'ngga ambi nineenggime wonok wundi woroolik me, kanggo logonet kunduk, ambi wonok nagun lek mban.
54006008	Ninambi-ninayum ambiriluk ambi wonage kenok, "Yi abu aret~o," yinuk, niniki tayenak logowok~o.
54006009	It aap, "Nineenggi warak eekkolaawok," mbakwi iinok, Tile nen, "Nanonggwan aga~o," yinuk, iniki nggagangge kagak, pagi keele pugu paga enggaanok nggerok togon wake menggi kwak, it aap ti togop aret perak togon maluk eekwi, ndi, "Yi an neebe paga maluk eekkolage," mbaka'lek iniki ugun nenet nugwi, eerit nugwi paga yobok togon yigeebu wanggo logonet, ineebe mondok wakkolaagun aret~o.
54006010	Yiluk-maluk alom lombok ti, wu mban uugwe mbarit nugwi ti aret~o. It aakumi ando nen uugwe nduk, kwaarit nugu logonet, wone abet mbareegwaarak nogo mbo punuk, tu alik nomoninuk nogwe me, aap togowa paga ndanunggologo nagaatik, andi kogo mengga kwak, it aap ti, togop aret wakkologo menggaarak.
54006011	Kat perak, Ala aput aret me, eekwi ti mendek mamunggolookwak, ogole nen mbagangge logot~o. Obeelom kenok mban eekwi, Ala wone liippunuk eekwi, iniki abet mbakwi, aakumi iniki kunik aganakwi, aaninggin inoba age kagak, inogogumbuk logonet waganggwi, iniki yanggonak paga yorogwe, ti mendek eeriyak kenok mban mugurok nage logot~o.
54006012	Nit abet mba'nuk mugurok nogwe nogo, kat kunduk mugurok nage logonok nduk, mondok wakkagak eeke logot~o. Ndi, keenik mondok logonok nduk, kayonggo pege mbareegi, kat abet mbareegindak aakumi ambik inenggaanom paga paganeegindak nogo, nggirik-nggerok agago porogo logot~o.
54006013	Yi mendek ndi mendek ineenik aganake menggerak alom at Ala inom, ndi, at iniki mbareegerak Pondiyut Pilatut enggaanom paga paganeegerak Keritut Yetut nogo inom, imbirak inenggaanom paga noone omaawi yi yokkege agarik~o.
54006014	Wone lengganogo yokkereegwaarak nogo ambi wuppega'lek abok enaani porogo logonet, eerit nage me, "Ninowe Yetut Keritut kin ari woraawak~o," yinuk, wone ti lengganogo yokkigi~o.
54006015	Ala nen ninowe Yetut Keritut, "Ndiyom paga kin eeppi woroorak," koonogo pereegerak nogo ndak-ndak aret kin eeppi woraagin~o. Nit alut eeko monggoorak mondok alik omaawi menggerak ti, Ala aret~o. Aakumi inoweewi inogoba at aret. Yi aap ndi aap inendage warak inowe endagembogut ti, at mban aret~o.
54006016	At kanggeelik mondok-mondok eenik menggerak aret~o. At wonage me time eya ambik me aakumi at owagam wok yi noorak meek~o. Aakumi nen aa'nduk at eebe inigen koolik me, yogondak kunduk inigen kogwe lek mban aret. "At endage mondok tiyanak yi aakumi ndi aakumi abok at abu'me tebe yinuk, at oone mban konenggo logowak~o," yinuk, amin.
54006017	It aakumi o yogondak ineenggi warak wonogwe nogo ti paga iniki wogoppako logonet, yi mendek ndi mendek lek ariyak kagak, iniki ti paga lunik logokwak, yorage logot~o. Nit ale'nggen mbaruwok nduk, at yi mendek ndi mendek ngginu-ngginu eerogo wo'nirage menggerak Ala paga mban iniki mondok lunik logowak nduk, yorage logot~o.
54006018	Obeelom eeppiinet nugu logonet, yi obeelom ndi obeelom eekwi paga ineenggi warak eekkologwe, iniki lek ndoobu aakumi wogoroorak mban inikilom mbakwi, eeko logowak nduk, mamunirage logot~o.
54006019	Ti eekwi iinok, ko'lu o eebe wuruwok nduk, yogondak o eyak nu'lek wurakwi nogo kokwak, it peebi ineenik mondok abe mendek kologo logorak iniki piirik lek, "Eeppinanigin aret," mba'nuk, inageerok abe kunggolaawok nduk, inawu kuwak eeko mengga kwak, yogondak yi obeelom ndi obeelom mban eerit nogo logowak nduk, yorage logot~o.
54006020	Timotiyut wae. Wone liirogon yogwe lek inoone amburu puk-puk agan nugwi, pilit wone aret kwe, "Wone ngget mendek yi aret~o," agan wogwe paga wone wakwi, eekwi nogo mendek liippugun~o. Ata, kat unde logonok nduk, mippagareegwaarak nogo liippunuk eeke logot~o.
54006021	Wone ti mendek agan nugwi paga aakumi ando abet mba'nuk waganggo nogogwaarik, Ala wone abet mbareegwaarak nogo mbo punuk, tu alik paga nomoninuk nogo agaarik~o. Yogondak abu aret yokkigi. Ninogoba iniki kunik en eeppagage logonet, karum aret logogin~o. Wa.
55001001	Timotiyut wae. Kat naput niniki kunik aret me, at Ala mbareegerak paga nit Keritut Yetut ninom kunik logonet, nineenik mondok logorak wone abok yo'niragagerak nogo yorage logokit nduk, Keritut Yetut ayonggo nappiigak agago paneegerak an Pawulut nogo nen wone ambi yokkiri~o.
55001002	At ninogoba Ala inom, ninowe Keritut Yetut inom, imbirak iniki kunik nen wokkugwi, kabuwa nen obeelom eeppagagwi, ndi, kiniki ugun tayenak ale'nggen logonok nduk, eeppagagwi, eeko logogun~o.
55001003	An ko'lu-kii'me tamban eeke minggirak me, eeke logonet, kat koba aberak wonage me, "Nogoba Ala wa," yinuk, yoge minggirak. An nombomini maluk abeka'lek logonet iniki abe paga Ala ake eeko nogogwaarak nogo kokwak, an ndak-ndak aret eeke minggirak~o.
55001004	Kat le yereegindak nogo abe'nage kenok, an niniki ale'nggen nggwok lombok kaakit nduk, "Keya woraakit lak ao," mbake minggirak.
55001005	Kat abu abet aret kiniki Yetut oba panggombunuk abet mbareegindak nogo, an neenu aret~o. Kowogolo Lowit inom, kagalo Ewunike inom, imbirak aa'nduk abet mbareegwaarak ndak-ndak, kat kunduk abet mbareegindak me, niniki aberak agarik~o.
55001006	Togop me, an neenggi kanobak tebembagage neegak, Ala eyabu ambi ee'nok nduk, unde eeppagareegerak nogo, kani noguk ari kenok ambi kunggwi nogo pogom ambi abeke logonok nduk, yokkigi~o.
55001007	At Ala nen niniki ninagabitinggut mendek wo'niroolik~o. Ata, Aberiniki omaawi eeppinanege kagak ninagabiti lek logonet yorogo logorak mendek inom, aakumi niniki kunik aganaburak mendek inom, niniki warak mendek inom, wo'niragagerak~o.
55001008	Togop me, ninowe eereegerak wone nogo yorage logorak kagabiti mbarugun~o. Ndi, an Ala wone yorage nagagirak paga nen keele maa'nabeegwaarak nogo kunduk, kagabiti mbarugun mban. Obeelom wone yorogwe paga aaninggin-paaninggin ninoba pinanugwi iinok, ndak-ndak woorak nduk, Ala omaawi wo'nirage menggerak me, an nalik lek~o. Nimbirak ndak-ndak aaninggin kogo logowok~o.
