55001009	At Ala nen ninagap ndake nagagerik, nit at apuri at ake leenak logowok nduk, ninayonggo pereegerak. Nit ambi eekkologogurak paga ti lek~o. Ata, at ee'ninaburak kooneegerak nogo ndak-ndak, iniki kunik nen eeppinanege logonet, ninagap ndareegerak. At iniki kunik nen eeppinanege menggerak nogo ti, o yi awo wakkaga'lek kagak, "Keritut Yetut abet mbakwi paga woorak~o," yinuk, koonogo pinaneegerak nogo, pagak yaga'lek wonagagerak kwe,
55001010	yogondak iluk ninagap ndaka Keritut Yetut kin ari wage nagagerik, kambuurak ninoba lenggenak wonogogurak nogo, lek eerogo punuk, wone obeelom wone waganggwi paga nabelan-kabelan ee'ninaburak wone nogo nggwok paga pagak yereegerak.
55001011	Wone obeelom wone ti, mamunirage, yi aakumi ndi aakumi yoranet nege, nappiigak logonet, yi awi ndi awi, "Nak~o," yo'nege kenok nage, eeke logokit nduk, leenogo mippaneegerak.
55001012	Mippaneegerak me, eerit nage neenok, aakumi nen aaninggin eeppanugwi kwe, nenggali mbaka'lek aret agarik~o. An niniki at oba panggombunuk abet mbareegirak eebe nogo ti, an abu neenu aret~o. Ndi, an eeke logokit nduk, unde eeppaneegerak nogo ninowe waga'lek kagak, lek arigin ti lek~o. "Yorage logogin aret~o," yinuk, abet aret mbake agarik~o.
55001013	Wone kole wone kat nen it in wakkagak eeke logonok nduk, yokkege nagagirak nogo porogo logot~o. Keritut Yetut ninom kunik logonet, wone kole wone yi, abet mbake, ndi, aakumi kinom kunik aganake, eeke logonet, porogo logot~o.
55001014	Abe mendek unde eeppagareegerak nogo, Aberiniki ninikime menggerak nogo nen omaawi eeppagage kagak, liirogon unde logot~o.
55001015	It o Atiya menggaarak aap Pigelut kunduk, aap Eromogenet kunduk, abok aret an mbo paninuk mbaganeegwaarak nogo ti, kat keenu aret~o.
55001016	At aap Onetiporut perak, an mbuti keele maarak neegak, agabiti nen mbo panulik nabenak mban niniki eyak wappani wagak mban eeke nagagerak me, at apuri inom abok aret ninowe inabuwa nen obeelom eeppiige logogin~o.
55001017	At o Oroma nen mbet-mbet kwaa'nabit nege logonet, kwaa'neyareegerak.
55001018	At o Epetut logonet, yeenggwaanege nagagerak nogo kat abu keenu me, o age yobok eyom paga ninowe nen aap ti, abuwa mba'nuk obeelom eeppigin aret~o.
55002001	Naput kat perak, Keritut Yetut ninom kunik me, Ala iniki kunik nen omaawi eeppagage kagak, nu'lek logonet, eerit nage logot~o.
55002002	Aakumi apit inenggaanom paga an yi wone ndi wone yokkege koneneegindak nogo, it aap abe mamumbunuk aakumi liirogon mamuniroorak op iigendak kenok, unde logowak nduk, mamunirage logot~o.
55002003	Maluk eeppanugwi iigak, nogogumbuk logonet wagangge minggi kwak, kat Keritut Yetut awot yigin unde abe kwak logonet, nimbirak ndak-ndak waganggo logowok~o.
55002004	Aap ambi nen, "Nowe wim mamunnegerak inikilom nombaruwak~o," yinuk, yi mendek ndi mendek eeriyak mbo punuk, wim eeriyak mban iniki lunik logonet eerit nage menggerak nogo~o.
55002005	Ndi, aap ambi, "Ta aa'nduk onggo kolamenggi?" yinuk, wakkogo logonet, "Ndogop eeru~o," yinuk, wone yugu nogo ndak-ndak eekeelik kenok, onggo kolageelik~o.
55002006	Aap yabu eenggi omaawi eeke logomenggerik, anggen iyaalok yugu nogo nggwok mbanggoloorak op~o.
55002007	An yokkege yi nogo ti, yi wone ndi wone yelok kaanok nduk, ninowe nen keenu eeppagagin me, liippege logot~o.
55002008	At Ala nen Ndawut ombooluk Yetut Keritut kambunuk nogo menggam nen mippereegerak wone nogo ti, an obeelom wone yorage minggirak ndak-ndak aret me, abeke logot~o.
55002009	An wone ti aret yorage neenok, maluk eeppanegak mban eerit wogoga, wogoga, irip paga, "Aap abu maluk eeka~o," yinuk, keele maarogo paneegwaarak yime wonage kwe, Ala wone perak, keele maariyak meek me, wiganinuk nage agaarik~o.
55002010	Togop me, it aakumi Ala miirinabeegerak iniki Keritut Yetut oba panggombunuk, abet mbakwi iinok, inagap ndappunuk mondok-mondok inom tiyanak logowak nduk, maluk eeppanugwi iigak, it inake nogogumbuk logonet wagangge minggirak~o.
55002011	"Nit at ninom kambeegurak kenok, at ninom nineenik arugun~o.
55002012	Maluk eeppinanugwi iigak, ninogogumbuk logonet, waganggwi niinok, at ninom tiyanak logonet, aakumi inarum logogun~o. Nit nen at mbo pugwi niinok, at kunduk nit mbo pinanigin~o.
55002013	Nit yogootak kagak alik eekwi kwe, at yegetak perak, alik ageelik yegetak ndak-ndak aret eeke menggerak~o," yinuk, yogo menggaarak nogo ti mondok abet aret~o.
55002014	Wone yokkege yi nogo ti, aakumi nen abeko logowak nduk, yorage logot~o. Wone mbuuluk yugu kagak wone wakwi nogo paga obeelom eekkologwe lek it konenggwi nogo iniki mi'nage me, "Togop eerugup~o," yinuk, Ala enggaanom paga koone omaawi paga yorage logonok nduk, yokkigi~o.
55002015	Aap ambi yabu abe eeke logonet, agabiti mbakeelik nogo pogom, kat Ala ari menggerak wone mamunirage logonet, kiniki nen koonogo alik inom nabenogo yoraga'lek at oone mban liirogon yorage keenok, Ala nen inikilom kombaruwak nduk, liippunuk, eeke logot~o.
55002016	Wone liirak lek inoone amburu puk-puk agan nugwi paga obeelom eekkoloorak lek maluk eeriyak mban ee'ninake logorak me, mbo puurak aret~o.
55002017	It aap inawin maaluget ambit me kungge nagaatik, ineebe paga nggwok wigangge menggerak nogo pogom, it aap ti, inoone togop aret wiganinuk nage menggerak. Wone ti agan nugu menggaarak nogo ti, aap Kimeneyut Piletut imbirak it inom a'nuk agan nugu menggaarak.
55002018	It aap ti, Ala ari menggerak wone nogo nomonogo mbo punuk, "Aakumi kambunuk nogo menggam nen muk ineenik agago mippiyareegerak~o," yinuk, yogo logonet, it abet mbareegwaarak nogo ando iniki abut laganggo menggaarak kwe,
55002019	o wurik ili agago liiru mbanogo pogo mengga kwak, Ala eeriyak kooneegerak nogo, "Mondok logogin," mbaruwak nduk, ari logonet, "An napuri kenok ti, neenu aret minggirak~o." Ndi, ambi, "Yi aap ndi aap abok aret, An Ala aput aret~o, yogwe iinok, It maluk eekwi nogo mbo pogo logowak~o," yinuk, yereegerak me, it aap ti togop aret eeko menggaarak kwe, Ala nen, "Eeriyak," kooneegerak ti, o eyak wurabak nu'lek menggi kwak, mondok nu'lek aret logogin~o.
55002020	O nggwok wurik inikime ti, mbuti emas paga inom, mbuti perak paga inom, togolowak ti mendek mban ogobakkigirik menggerak lek~o. Ata, ando eyo paga inom, ando nggween paga inom, ogobakkigirik menggerak. Togolowak abe kigirikwe kenok ti, iya mendek ambi eeriyak nduk, leenak menggerak. Ndi, maluk negen kenok perak, we ugun eekak yuurak nduk menggerak.
55002021	Togop aret menggerak me, aap ambit-ambi togolowak koorak mondok obeelom wonage kokwak, at omaluk mbo pege kenok, at ogoba nen yi mendek ndi mendek obeelom iya lombok eeke logowak nduk, ogoba ake mondok leenak aret menggerak.
55002022	Wologwe tawe iniki nengge nogo kokwak, kat togop eekkake kero, mbo punuk mbagangge logot~o. Abe kenok mban eekwi inom, iniki abet mbakwi inom, aakumi iniki kunik aganakwi inom, iniki ambit lambunik wonogwe inom, it aakumi iniki abe paga, "Ninogoba Ala aret~o," yinuk, yogwe nogo, kinom a'nuk it eekwi ti mendek mban mugurok nage logot~o.
55002023	Aap wi negen wone yugu pelaarit nugwi paga ndugwi pugwi nogo, kat keenu me, mbo pege logot~o.
55002024	Kat ninowe ayeloman aret kenok, ndugwi pegak eeriyak ti mage~o. Ata, yi aakumi ndi aakumi abok aret koone yanggorogon yorage, wone mamunirage, maluk eeppagagwi kwe, onggo yoraga'lek puk wonage, eeke logot~o.
55002025	It kinom ogoorak logonet, wone alik agan nugwi nogo, mbo punuk, abe wone ineenu aruwak nduk, Ala nen eeppiyoorak kagak eerukwak, koone yanggorogon mamunirage logot~o.
55002026	Ala nen togop eeppiige kenok, Ibilit mbake menggerak eeko logowak nduk, keele maarogo piyareegerak kagak, iniki warak a'nuk, keele nogo piinggo'nok wundi wogo logogun~o.
55003001	Naput wae. Peebi o age yobok paga aaninggin abu alik negen ninoba ari woraagin nogo, keenu a'nok nduk, yokkigi~o.
55003002	Ti eyom paga eeriyak nogo ti, aakumi nen, "An mban," mbako logonet, iniki nggilimi wonogwe, wu mban uugwe mbarit nugwi, iniki tiyappatit nugwi, "Wi!" iraawak nduk wogoppatit nugwi, inoreewi miyuk-meya eerogo piinet nugwi, inagalo-inogoba inoone liirogon konengga'lek nugwi, lambek-nggoonak nugwi, Ala wone taganogo pit nugwi, eeko logogun aret~o.
55003003	Ti eerit nugu logonet, inowe-inawot inabuwa mbakwi, inom lambuniyak mbakwi, eeka'lek aret logogun~o. Aakumi inabok mbanit nugwi, eeriyak aganake kenok tebenogo pugwi lek mondok eerit nugwi, inanini wulo lombok logonet, aakumi mondok inoorit nugwi, obeelom eeriyak mondok ineebi mbarit nugwi,
55003004	aakumi inambokan laganggwi, iniki koongga'lek ugun eerit nugwi, "An mban iya," mbarit nugwi, Ala inikilom mbaka'lek iniki nengge kenok mugurok noorak mban inikilom mbakwi, ti mendek mban eerit nogo logogun~o.
55003005	Ndi, ti eerit nugu logonet, Ala wone abet mba'nuk mugurok nogwe inetenggen negen eekkolamenggaarak kwe, iniki perak, "Ala nen obeelom eeppinaniyak nineebi," mba'nuk, eerit nogo logogun~o. It aap ti eekwi iinok, inogole nen mbagangge logonu~o.
55003006	It aap ti nen oome ungguwok nduk, inoone waanggo-waanggo yoraanuk unggwogo nagaatik, kumi iniki nengge kenok mugurok nogo logonet, maluk eeko nogogwaarak paga iniki aaninggin wonogwe nogo, it aap ti nen inoone yanggorogon yorogo nagaatik, it kumi nogo iniki nomoninako menggaarak.
55003007	It kumi ti nen kulinik-kalinik, "Ala ari menggerak wone ti, ambi yo'niraa-nip~o," yinuk, yorogo menggaarak kwe, Ala ari menggerak wone nogo wagangga'lek aret menggaarak.
55003008	It aap Yanet Yamberet imbirak en Muta wone, "Nineebi~o," yinuk, yogogwaarak nogo pogom, it aap ti, Ala ari menggerak wone, "Nineebi~o," yinuk, yogo menggaarak. It iniki mondok maluk mban koonggwi me, nit wone abet mba'nuk eekwi paga inabut mbambunuk, eekwi lek iinok, mbo piyareegurak.
55003009	It aap Yanet Yamberet imbirak nen eerit nogogwaarak kin agagerak nogo pogom, it aap ti, iniki ugun kobak logonet, agan nugwi nogo aakumi abok inenggaanom paga pagak ari kenok, ambinom eeko logogun lek~o.
55003010	Kat perak, an wone mamunirage, eerit nage, eeriyak niniki koongge, niniki at oba panggombunuk abet mbake, maluk eeppanugwi iigak, niniki yanggonak wonage, aakumi niniki kunik aganake, maluk eeppanugwi kwe, nogogumbuk logonet wagangge, eerit nage neyareegindak nogo~o.
55003011	Ndi, an o Andiyokiya inom, o Ikoniyum inom, o Litera inom, wonage me, piyak-payak ee'-nakwi iigak, nogogumbuk logonet wagangge nagagirak kwak, yogondak ee'nakwi iinok, wagangge minggirak abok aret kat keenu aret~o. An o time wonage me eeppanugwi iigak, nogogumbuk logonet wagangge neegak, nowe nen nagap ndareegerak me, iya!
55003012	Yi aakumi ndi aakumi Keritut Yetut inom kunik logonet, Ala wone liippunuk eeruwok mbakwi iinok, piyak-payak agago piinet nugu logogun aret~o.
55003013	Togop aret kwe, it aakumi maluk eeka inom, pilit pugungga inom, maluk ambinom nggwok eerit nugu logonet, it mban-mban inambokan laganggologo logogun kwe,
55003014	kat perak, yi wone ndi wone, "Yi abet aret~o," yinuk, mamunggolagagindak nogo, nggirik-nggerok porogo logot~o. Taamini nen mamunggireegwaarak nogo keenu aret.
55003015	Ala yereegerak wone liiru mbanak paga Keritut Yetut abet mbakwi niinok, ninagap ndariyak nineenu ee'ninaburak wone wulaga mbuuluk paga kat keenu agagindak nogo, abeke logonet, nggirik-nggerok porogo logot~o.
55003016	Ala yereegerak wone liiru mbanak abok aret Aberiniki aakumi inikime lik ari nagagerik, yorage kagak, liiru mbaneegwaarak me, wone mbanak yi nogo paga nen aakumi mamunirogwe, inoone alik agan nugwi nogo kooninakwi, maluk eekwi iinok inaruk wakwi, ndi, obeelom mban eeko logorak lengganogo yorogwe, eeko logowak nduk, mbanak aret menggerak~o.
55003017	At Ala yereegerak liiru mbanak wo'niragagerak nogo ti, nit Ala apuri logonet, yi obeelom ndi obeelom eeko logowok nduk, ninake li'luk agago pereegerak wonage agaarik~o.
55004001	Aakumi at abu'me piyoorak nduk, ninowe kin ari wage logonet, it ineenik wonogwe inom, kambeegwaarak inom, inowak loonogo inawone amburu mbani woroorak Keritut Yetut inom, Ala inom, imbirak inenggaanom paga an noone omaawi paga wone yi yokkiri~o.
55004002	Ala wone yoranet nege logot~o. Anggon kagak, anggon lek kagak, yiyom-ndiyom ugun yorage logonok nduk, pipuk aago logot~o. "E~o," yuwak nduk yorage, maluk eekwi iinok mberirage, koone yanggorogon inaruk wake, eeke logonet, kaanaga-nggenggwi lek kiniki kwippunuk liirogon mamunirage logot~o.
55004003	It aap wone kole wone mamunik nogo koneniyak, "Nineebi~o," yuurak eyom panggoni woraagin. Panggoni wage kenok, it aap ti nen, "Wone ngge yogwe iyaamun?" yinuk, inaruk nggoonit nogo logonet, wone it inikilom mbako menggaarak mban yogwe iinok, inabu'me unggwogo logogun~o.
55004004	It aakumi ti nen Ala ari menggerak abe wone kenok, nomonogo mbo punuk, woneelom kenok mban mbininit nogo logogun~o.
55004005	Togop kwe, kat perak, kiniki tum wakkolage logot~o. Maluk eeppagagwi iigak, kogogumbuk logonet wagangge, aap obeelom wone yoranet nugu mengga kwak, kat ndak-ndak yoranet nege, eeke logonok nduk, mippagareegwaarak nogo ndak-ndak aret eeke, eeke logot~o.
55004006	Ala ake amburu kilirogo pugwi kwak, an nooriyak nduk, abu punogo panegaarak wonage me, an lagi noorak panggoni waga~o.
55004007	Nit abet mba'nuk mugurok nogwe nogo kolaawok nduk, wakkagak eeko monggoorak nogo ti, an mondok wakkagak eeke nagagirak~o. "Kuli ndi paga mbe agan mi'nari nak~o," yorogwe iinok, mbe agan mi'nari nogo mengga kwak, an abu irip paga kuli mi'nari wagi~o. Nit wone abet mba'nuk mugurok nogwe nogo ti, an mondok aret porogo wonagagirak.
55004008	Ndi, yogondak at wone a'me nggelok owak loongga ninowe nen it aakumi obeelom eekwi iinok, onggo nggare-nggare mendaarak yippiige menggerak me, o age yobok paga an ambi yippanikit nduk, nake paneegerak wonage~o. An nalik yippanigin lek~o. Ata, yi aakumi ndi aakumi nen, "At kin ari woraawak lak, a~o," yinuk, tokkogwe nogo abok aret yippiyaagin~o.
55004009	Mbet-mbet neya woraanok nduk, koongge logot~o.
55004010	At Ndemat nogo, nggween paga mendek mban inikilom agagerak me, mbo paninuk o Tetalonika nagagerak~o. Ndi, at Kereket o Nggalatiya nage, at Titut o Ndalamatiya nage, eekwi iigak,
55004011	at Lukat alik perak, nimbirak agarik~o. At Marakut nogo nimbirak eeriyak op me, kat wage logonet, waganggak woraamunggun~o.
55004012	At Tikikut nogo, o Epetut nappigirak~o.
55004013	Kat wage logonet kenok, togwi yum o Terowat aap Karuput ame kagak wagagirak nogo inom, nambuku pirik-perek aago nogo inom, ndi, eyo agabolo paga liiru mbanak ti iya me, ti inom, abok aret wo'nombanok woraamunggun~o.
55004014	-
55004015	Aap mbuti paga yi mendek ndi mendek ogobakkigika Alekandet nogo nen nit wone yorogo monggoorak at mondok eebi lombok mbake logonet, maluk iya tit eeppaneegerak me, kat kunduk maluk eeppagukwak, tum wake logot~o. At eeppaneegerak nogo ti, nogoba nen onggo ndak-ndak wogorigin~o.
55004016	-
55004017	Aa'nduk, nawone mbaniyak nduk, eekwi me, noreewi ambi abu neya woroolik abok aret mbo paneegwaarak kwe, nowe Yetut nen perak, nimbirak logonet, niniki eyak wappaneegerak. An obeelom wone yorage logokit nduk, mippaneegerak nogo, ambi wuppulik tigitogon it aakumi endekem mendek abok aret konenuwak nduk, "An yoraakit~o," yinuk, mi'nage neegak, nowe nen mban nomaawi eeppanege, niniki eyak wappanege, eereegerak~o. Togop me, maluk eeppaniyak mbakaarak nogo singa ambeme nen ndinggwi kwak, ndinnabeegerak. Ndi, noreewi mbo paneegwaarak nogo maluk inoba piige kero, Ala yoge minggirak.
55004018	Maluk eeppaniyak mbakaarak nogo abok aret eeppanugwi iyo, nogoba nen nagap ndarogo at abu'me piige menggim mbogut paga time kuurik me aret pani nagin~o. At togop eeppaningin me, endage mondok-mondok tiyanak aret logowak~o. Amin.
55004019	Kwe Piritikila aap Akwila imbirak inom, ndi, aap Onetiporut aaganapuri inom, keyage wappiyaanok nduk yokkigi~o.
55004020	Aap Eratut o Korindut time puk agagerak. Aap Toropimut andi eereegerak me, o Miletut time kagak wagagirak.
55004021	O mayu kumulinggen wambi woroorak eyom awo panggoni waga'lek kagak, kat mbet-mbet neya woroorak koongge logot~o. Aap Ebulut kunduk, Puret kunduk, Linut kunduk, Kalawuriya kunduk, ndi, noreewi Ala apuri kunduk, nen abok aret keyage wakkaka~o.
55004022	Ninowe Yetut iniki kunik en eeppagage logonet, karum aret logogin~o. Wa!
56001001	-
56001004	Naput Titut wae. Nit abok wone abet mbakwi nogo paga naput abe kat aret me, it aakumi Ala nen miirinabeegerak iniki abet mbakwi wone nogo wigangge, ndi, Ala ari menggerak wone nogo liippunuk, Ala apuri nen eeko mengga kwak eekwi, eeruwak nduk, an Pawulut Ala ayeloman Yetut Keritut ayonggo nappiigak mendek agago paneegerak nogo nen aret yokkiri~o. At pilit ariilik abet mban ari menggerak Ala nogo nen, "Mondok-mondok ineenik logogun~o," yinuk, o yi wakkaga'lek kagak, koonogo pereegerak nogo, ee'ninabuwak nduk, niniki lunik wonogwe nogo ti, nit abet mbakwi, Ala ari menggerak nineenu ogwe, eekwi nogo paga panggonak wonage agaarik~o. Niniki lunik wone ti, maan togon koonogo pereegerak kwe, "Ndiyom paga kin arigin," mbareegerak nogo ninagap ndaka Ala nen, "At yorage logowak~o," yinuk, an yogondak abe wone yorage logokit nduk, unde eeppaneegerak nogo aret yorage neegak, nineenik ee'ninaburak wone ti inom yorage paga kenom aga~o. Ninogoba Ala ninagap ndaka Keritut Yetut imbirak iniki kunik nen wokkugwi, kiniki ugun tayenak ale'nggen logonok nduk, eeppagagwi, eeko logogun~o.
56001005	An eeka'lek kagak wagagirak nogo eeke, ndi, o kota lombok Ala apuri unde logowak nduk, "Aap ti mendek mippiyoorak," yokkereegirak nogo mippiige, eeke logonok nduk, kat o Kereta time keegak, an wagagirak nogo~o.
56001006	Ala apuri unde logowak nduk mippiyoorak nogo ti, aakumi inoone inoba piigulik kenok, inakuwi ambit wogo kenok, "Inapurilogwe nen ugun-ugun eerit nugu logonet, inagalomini-inogobamini inoone taganogo piigwi kwe, inaruk waka'lek kiraap!" yogolik Ala wone abet mba'nuk eeko menggaarak inogobamini kenok, it ti mendek mban mippiyoorak op~o.
56001007	It aap aakumi inarum logorak nogo ti, Ala eyabu eeka me, maluk eeke kenok aakumi inoone inoba piyookwak, obeelom mban eerit nugu logowak~o. It koonggwi mban eeriyak mbakwi, inanini mbet-mbet wungge, amburu kumili aganake mendek ndonggorogon nunggwi, ndugwi pugwi, aakumi inawu kolaawok nduk, wi-wi aganakwi, eeko menggaarak kenok, aap ti mendek mippiyoorak lek~o.
56001008	Ata, aap inanoniya laka kenok, obeelom eeriyak inikilom mbaka kenok, iniki warak kenok, a'me nggelok eeka kenok, Ala wone liippunuk eeka kenok, eeriyak eeke kagak kwe, iniki yungguppunuk, puk aga kenok, aap ti mendek mban mippiyoorak op~o.
56001009	Wone kole wone ti, it konenggo menggaarak nen abet mbaruwak nduk, lengganogo yorogwe, abe wone woorak ineebi mbakwi nogo waawak nduk, wone kenaarogo yorogwe, eeko logowak nduk, abe wone nogo paga niniki panggombunuk, waganeegurak wone nogo, it ndak-ndak iniki panggombunuk, nggirik-nggerok porogo wonogwe iinok mban mippiyoorak op aret~o.
56001010	Wone, "E~o," yinuk, konengga'lek logonet, inoone amburu puk-puk agan nugwi, aakumi inambokan laganggwi, eeko menggaarak ti, it ineebe apit aret kwe, it inagabolo mbanak abet mbareegwaarak nogo perak, abe iyagalo it nen aret agan nugu menggaarak.
56001011	It aap ti, inenggali ariyak kagak, yi mendek ndi mendek kolaawok nduk, wone mamuniyak lek mendek mamunirogo logonet, aap ambi aaganapuri apit inom iniki abut lagak-mbagak aganabit nogo menggaarak me, inoone mondok lek eerogo piige logot~o.
56001012	It aap wone ti mendek yorogo menggaarak ambi nen ari logonet, "It aap o Kereta mendek ti, mondok pilit pugungga aret menggaarak~o. Nggwiya nen yiwi-yawi ari logonet nibingge menggerak pogom it togop aret logonet, Ineenggi lebenak inalom mban koleewak menggaarak~o," yinuk,
56001013	-
56001014	yereegerak nogo ti, abet aret yereegerak~o. Togop me, it aap ti, wone abet mbareegwaarak nogo mondok nu'lek porogo logowak nduk, aakumi Yakuri inawoneelom mbininggo menggaarak wone inom, it aap Ala ari menggerak wone mbo punuk, iniki ugun koombunuk, "Yogop ee'nu, ndogop ee'nu," agan nugu menggaarak wone nogo inom, "Liippuurak mage~o," yinuk, koone omaawi paga mondok inaruk wake logot~o.
56001015	It aakumi iniki obeelom menggaarak kenok, it inigen me yi mendek ndi mendek obeelom mban aret kogo menggaarak. Ndi, it aakumi abet mbaka'lek maluk mban eeko menggaarak kenok ti, eeriyak inikime abe'nage inom, koonggwi inom, ti maluk mban aret me, it inigen me yi mendek ndi mendek maluk mban aret kogo menggaarak.
56001016	It aap ti nen yogo logonet, "Ala nineenu~o," yogo menggaarak kwe, it eerit nugwi paga nen perak, "Ala nineebi," mbako logonet, yogwe yelok iigo monggoorak. Ala wone konengga'lek taganogo pit nogo logonet, obeelom ambi eekulik maluk mban eekwi me, inogole warak aret iigo monggoorak~o.
56002001	Kat perak, wone mamunirage menggendak nogo wone kole wone kenok mban mamunirage logot~o.
56002002	It aap inanggok ti, iniki tum waka kenok, inayuk warak kenok, iniki warak kenok, it iniki abet mbakwi nu'lek menggaarak kenok, aap togop mendek logowak nduk, yorage logot~o. Aakumi abok abet aret iniki kunik aganakwi, ndi, aaninggin inoba age kenok inogogumbuk logonet, waganggwi, eeko logowak nduk, yorage logot~o.
56002003	It kumi inanggok ti, it eeko menggaarak liippunuk, Ala ayuk wuko logonet, eeko logowak nduk, aap inanggok yoroorak yokkigirak nogo ndak-ndak aret yorage logot~o. Inambe irip paga wonok nugwi, amburu kumili aganake mendek ndonggorogon nunggwi, ti eeko logorak lek~o. Ata, wone abe wone kenok mban mamunirogo logowak nduk, yorage logot~o.
56002004	-
56002005	Ala wone miyuk-meya eerogo pukwak, it kumi ndugum nogo nen inogonggelomini inom, inaagalogwe inom, iniki kunik aganakwi, iniki warak ogwe, inoreewi inabuwa nen inigen tebenak nugwi, iname liirogon wonogwe, kumi iniki obeelom logonet, inogonggelomini inabu'me tebe yinuk, inoone konenggwi, eeko logowak nduk, it kumi inanggok nogo nen kumi ndugum mamunirogo logowak~o.
56002006	Ndi, it wologwe tawe ti, togoti aret iniki warak logowak nduk, inaruk wake logot~o.
56002007	Aakumi kat paga in wakkagak eeko logowak nduk, kat yi eekak ndi eekak eeke logonet, obeelom mban eerit nage logot~o. Eerit nage logonet, wone mamunirage menggendak nogo, kat koone inom nabenogo ugun-ugun mamunirage, kayuk lek we i'ndok-i'ndok yorage, eeke logogun~o.
56002008	Ata, kayuk warak logonet, yorage kenok, it aap koone woorak, "Nineebi," mbakwi nogo nen wone maluk ambi yoramenggendak paga yilunogo punuk, nit tebembinaniyak lek me, it inenggali aruwak nduk, wone koleewak wone kenggali wappagarak lek nogo mendek mban yorage logot~o.
56002009	It aakumi inayeloman nogo ti, inogobamini lombok nen yorogwe nogo, inoone konembunuk, wone onggo yoraga'lek iinok, inogobamini inikilom logowak nduk, yorage logot~o.
56002010	It aakumi inayeloman nogo ti, inogobamini inamendek yogoot kumaako logorak lek~o. It nogo ti, yi eekak ndi eekak eeko logonet obeelom eerit nugwi paga aakumi ugun nogo nen, "Ninagap ndaka Ala wone waawok," mbaruwak nduk, "Kinogobamini inamendek wagangga'lek liirogon arum logonip~o," yinuk, yorage logot~o.
56002011	Ala iniki kunik nen wo'niragagerak wone nogo, it aakumi abok inagap ndaruwak nduk, kin agagerak.
56002012	-
56002013	Ninogoba nggwok Ala ninagap ndaka Yetut Keritut, "Wi!" ugwi iigak, kin ari woroorak nogo, nit niniki lunik logonet, ninale'nggen paga tokkogwe me, Ala iniki kunik nen yo'nirage logonet, "Kit o nggween paga yime Ala kinagabiti mbaka'lek maluk eekwi inom, nggween paga eeriyak kiniki nengge inom, mbo punuk, kiniki warak a'nuk, maluk eeka'lek obeelom mban logonet, Ala wone liippunuk, mugurok nogo logonip~o," yinuk, yo'nirage menggerak.
56002014	Nit yi maluk ndi maluk eeko monggoorak nogo eeko logokwak ninonggo mbanogo piinogo pinanege, ndi, "An napuri nake leenak logonet, obeelom eeriyak iniki aganggen paga eerit nugu logowak," mba'nuk, ninomaluk koorogo pinanege, eerikit nduk, nit ninake niya wagagerak.
56002015	Wone yi yorage, "Yogop eeriyak ndogop eeriyak," wone lengganinake, koone omaawi paga inaruk wake, eeke logot~o. Ndi, aap ambi nen kat meek eerogo pagarak lek~o.
56003001	Aakumi nen it o arum waka pemerintah inom, it aap inayuk warak menggaarak inom, inabu'me logonet, inoone konenggwi, ndi, eeriyak obeelom ambi kin age kenok, "Eeko logowok~o," yinuk, mbako logowak nduk yorage, eeke logot~o.
56003002	Aap ambi miyuk-meya eerogo pugwi, ndugwi pugwi, eeko logorak ti mage~o. Ata, iniki yanggonak logonet, yi aap ndi aap abok aret inabuwa mbako logowak nduk, yorage logot~o.
56003003	Nit kunduk, maan togop aret nineenggo'lek wi negen wonogwe, wone yo'niragaatak konengga'lek wonogwe, tu alik me nomo agan nogwe, aap ambi ayeloman yoge kenok, "E~o," yinuk, eeke menggi kwak, nit niniki nengge kenok eeriyak ninikilom mbakwi nogo mban eekwi, eeko nogogurak. Yi mendek ndi mendek eerit nogo logonet, maluk mban eekwi, neebi-keebi yogwe, nanini-kanini yogwe, ti mendek mban eeko nogogurak kwe,
56003004	ninagap ndaka Ala nen yi aakumi ndi aakumi inabuwa mba'nuk, obeelom eeppiyoorak nogo, kin ari wage nagagerik,
56003005	ninagap nda'ninabeegerak. Nit obeelom eeko nogogurak paga ninagap nda'ninabulik~o. Ata, at alik iniki nen ninabuwa mba'nuk, obeelom eeppinanege logonet, niniki maluk koorogo punuk, obaane'me ngget ndarogo pinanege, Aberiniki nen niniki ngget ogobakkigi'ninake, eereegerak ti paga ninagap nda'ninabeegerak.
56003006	At ninagap ndaka Yetut Keritut eereegerak paga Ala nen Aberiniki ndonggok togon wo'niragagerak.
56003007	At Ala iniki kunik nen eeppinaneegerak paga, "Aap yi, oba lek~o," yinuk, abu obeelom aret eerogo pinanege nagagerik, aap ambi ogoba eyate kolage menggi kwak, nit nineenik mondok-mondok logorak niniki lunik nogo kolaawok nduk, Aberiniki ndonggok togon wo'niragagerak.
56003008	An wone yokkigi ti, abet aret~o. It aakumi iniki Ala oba panggombunuk, abet mbakwi nogo iniki liippunuk, obeelom mban eeko logowak nduk, an yokkigirak ti, kulinik-kalinik koone omaawi paga yorage logot~o. "Wone yi, obeelom aret~o," yinuk, waganggwi paga obeelom ambi eekkoloorak aret me, yorage logot~o.
56003009	Wone irip me op eekkoloorak lek mendek inom, ndarak alom mbininggwi inom, Muta wone mbanak paga, "Yogop-ndogop," yogo logonet ndugwi pugwi inom, ti eerit nogo logonet, irip me time ambi eekkoloorak lek kagak we aanom warogo yogwe me, mbo puurak aret~o.
56003010	-
56003011	Aap aakumi iniki nomoninaka nogo nen abe wone mbo punuk, maluk mban eerit nage paga maluk onggo oba kwippatiyak kagak, eerit nage keenu me, ne mbere paga aruk wappunuk, mbo puurak aret~o.
56003012	An nen aap Aretemat ilik, aap Tikikut a, nappi wage logominggirik, o mayu kumulinggen wambi woroorak eyom paga o Nikopolit time logorak mbakirak me, time wonage me, kat mbet-mbet neya woraanok nduk, koongge logot~o.
56003013	Wone amburu mbangga aap Tenat nogo inom, aap Apolot nogo inom, mbet-mbet nappiya wage logonet, inamendek lek kenok, wogoranu~o.
56003014	It ninapuri ti, eyo anggen yegeelik pogom logokwak, it aakumi aaninggin inoba age kenok yeenggwaarogo logowak nduk, yabu liirogon eeriyak mamunggologo logowak~o.
56003015	It aap ninom minggirak abok aret an ninom nen keyage wakkako~o. Ndi, it Ala wone abet mba'nuk, iniki kunik ee'ninakwi kinom wonogwe time abok aret, "At Pawulut nen keyage wappinagagi~o," yinuk, yoret~o. Ala iniki kunik en eeppagage logonet, karum aret logogin~o. Naput wa!
57001001	Keritut Yetut wone yoranet nage minggirak paga keele maa'nabeegwaarak an Pawulut ninawot Timotiyut nimbirak nen, kat ninore Pilemon ninom niniki kunik logonet, eeko monggoorak inom,
57001002	nit niniriluk kwe Apipiya inom, aap Ala wone ninom piyanggo monggoorak ninore Arikiput nogo inom, Ala apuri kat kame kuwak eeko menggaarak inom, abok aret wone ambi yokkiraawi~o.
57001003	Ninogoba Ala ninowe Yetut Keritut imbirak iniki kunik nen wokkirogwe, kiniki ugun tayenak ale'nggen logobagip nduk, eeppinagagwi, eeko logogun~o.
57001004	-
57001005	Nore Pilemon wae. Kat kiniki ninowe Yetut oba panggombunuk abet mbake menggendak inom, it Ala apuri alik leenak abok aret kiniki kunik aganake menggendak inom, kabok an konengge me, tamban eeke logonet, kat koba niniki aberak wonage me, kulinik-kalinik, nogoba Ala, "Wa," yoge minggirak.
57001006	Kit abet mbakwi paga Ala apuri kinom monggotak nogo kinom kiniki ambit eeppunuk logonet, "Ndogop ee'ninakerak~o," yinuk, pagan-pagan yogwe paga Keritut ninom kunik logonet obeelom mendek eeppinaniyak mbake menggerak nogo, ambinom kineenu arubagip nduk, kinake tamban eeke minggirak.
57001007	It Ala apuri alik leenak kiniki kunik aganake logonet, iniki eyak wappiinet nage paga niniki kwippaneegindak me, niniki ale'nggen nggwok mbake logonet, "Wa," yokkigi~o, noreeluk.
57001008	Togop me, an koweeluk Keritut nimbirak kunik logonet, kat ambi eeriyak agaarak kagarak nogo, eeke logonok nduk, noone omaawi togon yokkiriyak op kwe,
57001009	kat an niniki kunik lombok wonage me, noone we yanggorogon yokkiriyak ee'nake~o. An Pawulut nogo aap abu nanggok agagirak~o. Ndi, Keritut Yetut oone wonok yonggo nege nagagirak paga keele maa'nabeegwaarak yogondak yime logonet,
57001010	an naput Onetimut awone nogo yokkiri~o. An keele maarogo mambiigo menggam yime logonet, an naput negen agagerak me,
57001011	aa'nduk, at kimbirak eerit noorak meek wonogogutak kwe, yogondak perak, kat kunduk, an kunduk, ninom eeriyak op lombok agaarak kagarak me nduk, yokkigi~o.
57001012	Yogondak keya woraawak nduk, kowagam nappi wagi ti~o. Ndi, at eebe wage logonet, an niniki inom nikkenok wage agaarik~o.
57001013	Obeelom wone yoranet nege nagagirak nogo paga an keele maarogo paneegwaarak yime wonage me, at kat kobaane'me an narum yime nimbirak logorak op aret mbakirak kwe,
57001014	kat unde nen, "E~o," yo'nega'lek me, obeelom eeppaniyak mbakendak kero, kiniki mba'nuk nen, "An eeppanuwam," noone omaawi paga yokkirigin lek~o.
57001015	-
57001016	Yogondak at keya wage nogo ti, aap inayeloman pogom keya wage ti lek~o. At aa'nduk mbaganeegerak nogo ti, we ne ambiriluk mbo paganuk mbaganeegerak kero. Ndi, yogondak perak, kat kore kimbirak iniki kunik lombok logomunggup nduk wage me, mondok-mondok wamen~o. At nimbirak ti, niniki mondok kunik kwe, kat kayeloman aret me, ndi, at kunduk, Keritut ninom niniki kunik logonet, keya woraagin me, mbo puurak mage~o, noreeluk.
57001017	Ti kenok, kat nimbirak ndak-ndak abet mbareegurak me, "Nore Pawulut aret~o," yinuk, an wo'naburak mbake nogo kokwak, at aret wamen~o.
57001018	Aa'nduk kimbirak logonet, maluk ambi eeppagage, kamendek ambi wagangge, eereegerak kenok, at yoriyak lek~o. Ata, an nobaalombok me, an aret yo'nirumunggun~o.
57001019	"At Pawulut nen yoga'lek kagak liiru mbanggerak~o," nombake keyo, "An Pawulut nen aret onggo wokkirigin~o," yinuk, wone ambiriluk ti, an neenggi lombok paga aret liiru mbanggigi~o. An wone yokkereegirak paga kiniki abet mbareegindak nogo ti, nanomat mbanak pogom koba wonage me, ambi yi inom koba pagakit lak kwe, mbo pigi~o.
57001020	Ai, noreeluk. Yokkigirak ti, abet aret eeke keenok, "Yi Ala nen iniki koonggerak paga eeke," komba'nuk, niniki ale'nggen ee'nabuwak nduk, at eebe wamen~o. Nimbirak Keritut apuri mban aret me, niniki ale'nggen eerogo panenok nduk, yokkigi~o.
57001021	An liiru mbanggege yi nogo mban kat eeke logonok nduk, yokkege ti lek~o. Ata, ando kat kiniki nen koombunuk ambinom nggwok togon eeke logomunggun abet aret kombake logonet mbanggigi~o.
57001022	Wone yokkigirak ti, eeke logonet, kat nake tamban eeke Ala aruk konembunuk, an keya woroorak koonnabigin abet aret mbake me, woraanuk nogo yuurak o ambi ogobakkigirogo panege logot~o.
57001023	Aap Epaparat Keritut Yetut wone yorage nagagerak nogo paga keele maarogo pereegwaarak yime nimbirak logonet, keyage wakkako~o.
57001024	Ndi, it nawurilogwe ninom eekwi nogo, Marakut kunduk, Aritarukut kunduk, Ndemat kunduk, Lukat kunduk, nit abok aret nen keyage wakkako~o.
57001025	At ninowe Yetut Keritut iniki kunik en eeppagage logonet, karum aret logogin~o. An Pawulut Timotiyut nimbirak nen abu aret yokkogo~o. Wa!
58001001	Maan aa'nduk Ala mbake menggerak nogo ninombomini ineenu aruwak nduk, Ala nen yorage kagak yoraga nogo, kulinik-kalinik inabi paga yorage, eerubok mendek inenggela'me eeriyak yorage, anebunu alitak lombok abok aret eeriyak yorage, eeke kenok, it nogo nen ninombomini yorogo nogogwaarak kwe,
58001002	o yogondak irip paga perak, ninenggela'me logonet, ogoba oone yo'nirage logowak nduk, aput lombok nappi wagagerak~o. "Naput mban yi mendek ndi mendek unde logowak~o," yinuk, mippege nagagerik, ogoba nen, "Yogop ee'nu, ndogop ee'nu," yoge kagak, aput nogo nen mbogut-nggween yi mendek ndi mendek abok aret wakkagagerak.
58001003	Ogoba mondok tiyanak eebe eya ndelenak-welenak aago kenok, "Wi!" ugwi nogo kokwak, aput ndak-ndak aret menggerak. Aput nogo ti, ogoba iniki ndak-ndak aret. Yi mendek ndi mendek wakkagagerak nogo abok aret, at oone omaawi paga pipporogo menggerak. Ninomaluk abok aret lek eerogo mbo nappege nagagerik, at agi mbogut paga mondok tiyanak menggerak nogo, eenggi abe'nggan paga tiyarogon kwi'nari laganeegerak wonage~o.
58001004	Togop aret me, at Ala nen, "Naput~o," yoge nagagerak nogo ti, malayikat ambi yoroolik me, it malayikat mendek tebenak negen iigak, at aput mondok tiyanak aret~o.
58001005	At Ala nen malayikat mendek ambi yoge logonet, "Yogondak kat an naput age, ndi an kat kogoba age, eekoorak~o," yinuk, ti yorulik. Ndi, ambi ari logonet, "An ti, at ogoba age, ndi, at ti, an naput age, eerugun~o," yinuk, ti yorulik mban.
58001006	Ata, Ala nen at aput ambolom ndarak nogo, o nggween paga yime wuppi woraakit nduk, eeke logonet, "Kit an nayonggo nugu monggotak malayikat abok aret at mban alut eeko logonip~o," yinuk, yorage,
58001007	ndi, ti'nuk, it malayikat eeko menggaarak nogo mbiningge logonet, "It an nayonggo nugu menggaarak malayikat nogo, o wiya pogom agago piige, Ndi, it an nayeloman mini nogo, kani omoonuk kwak eerogo piige, Eeke minggirak~o," yinuk, mbiningge, eereegerak kwe,
58001008	at aput eeke logorak awone ari logonet perak, "Nogoba Ala wae. Koone lengganogo yorage menggenom ti, mondok-mondok aret logogin~o. It kabu'me menggaarak inawone mondok koonak mban mbangge menggendak ti, Mbim obate mbanak ti kwak aret me, kat in wakkagak agan nogo logogun~o.
58001009	It obeelom eekwi iinok ti, kinikilom mbake, Ndi, maluk eekwi iinok ti, keebi lombok mbake, Eeke menggendak me, At Ala ti, kat kogoba Ala aret me, iniki ale'nggen kombake logonet, Amburu kilirogo pagareegerak paga koreewi tebenak iigak, inirimbaga tiyappagareegerak~o," yinuk, yoge nagagerik,
58001010	wone alik ambi ari logonet, "Nogoba~o. O maan aa'nduk nggween yi, alom kwippege, Kat keenggi paga nen mbogut ogobakkigirogo pege, Eereegindak~o.
58001011	Mbogut inom, nggween inom, ti lek arigin kwe, kat perak, kitok mondok aret menggendak~o. Yum maan yugu me, nibik ari kenok, mbo pogo mengga kwak, mbogut-nggween yi togop aret lek eerigin~o.
58001012	Yum etenggen maluk agaatak kenok, yuwi-mbuwi eerogo mbo punuk, Obaane'me alik ngget mendek yikkologo mengga kwak, mbogut-nggween yi, togop eerigin kwe, Kat perak, alik ageelik, kitok aret wonage, Nda'nagagindak eyom lek ageelik mondok aret wonage, Eeke menggendak~o," yinuk, aput yoreegerak kwe,
58001013	"It kinom wim mbanak mendek nogo, aan lebenogo kabu'me piiga'lek neegak, An neenggi abe'nggan kwi'nari mok~o," yinuk, yoreegerak nogo ti, it malayikat nen eeruwak nduk yoroolik~o. Ata, aput nen eeruwak nduk, yoreegerak ti paga, nonggop mbakop? Lek~o. At Ala nen, "Naput~o," yoge nagagerak nogo ti, it malayikat mendek ambi togop yoroolik me, it malayikat mendek tebenak negen iigak, at aput mondok tiyanak aret kogo~o.
58001014	Ndi, it malayikat ti nonggop negen menggaarak mbakop? Lek~o. It nogo aakumi inogoma ninigen iiga'lek nogo pogom logonet, Ala ake eeko menggaarak me, Ala nen aakumi inagap ndaruwak nduk, leenogo piyareegerak nogo, yeenggwaaraawak nduk, yonggo nappiige menggerak it aret~o.
58002001	Togop me, nit Ala wone ninaruk konembunuk waganeegurak nogo, mbo punuk nomo agan nogwe niyo, ambinom nggirik-nggerok agago porogo logowok~o.
58002002	Ala nen, "Yogop ee'nu, ndogop ee'nu," yereegerak wone nogo, it malayikat nen ninombomini we inaruk konembunuk, mbo puwak nduk, yoroolik. Ata, mondok eeko logowak nduk, lengganogo yorogwe iigak, taganogo punuk, maluk eeko mbareegwa, Ala nen onggo mondok ndak-ndak eeppiyareegerak me,
58002003	nit ninagap ndariyak wone mondok iya kooneegerak nogo, kobak eerogo punuk wonogwe niinok, nit teppinanigin mbakop? Mondok lek~o. Wone ti, aa'nduk ninowe nen aret paganogo yorage mbareegi, it koneneegwaarak nogo nen iniki yungguppegak yo'niroolik inoone mondok abet aret yo'nirogwe iigak,
58002004	"Wone yi abet aret~o," yinuk, waawok nduk, Ala nen ninagabiti warak mendek eeke, tam warak negen eeke, eerubok mendek eeke, eerit nage logonet, ninalitak lombok eeko logowok nduk, at Ala iniki mbareegerak nogo ndak-ndak Aberiniki nen tumbu'niragagerak kwe, mbo pugwi niinok, teppinanigin mbakop? Mondok lek aret~o.
58002005	"Mbogut-nggween yi lek age logonet, obaane'me ngget mendek ambi ari woraagin~o," yogo monggoorak nogo ti, at Ala nen, "Malayikat unde logowak," mba'nuk, yuulik.
58002006	Ata, aap ambi Ala wone liiru mbanak paga nen ari logonet, "Nit aakumi yi, taani me nduk, abe'ninake, Ndi, aap inapuri nit yi, taani me nduk, liippinanege, Eeke menggendak~o?
58002007	-
58002008	We yogondak luululuk, it malayikat tiyanak wonogwe iigak, nit aakumi tebenak logowok nduk, ogobakkigirogo pinanege, Ninendagembogut abu tiyanak ninayuk warak logowok nduk, koonogo pinanege, Eeke nagagindik, Yi mendek ndi mendek abok aret nit mban ninabu'me logowak nduk pereegindak~o," yinuk, yereegerak nogo ti, yi mendek ndi mendek nit aakumi ninabu'me pege logonet, ambiriluk ambi ninabu'me logorak lek ti mbarulik. Ata, abok aret ninabu'me logowak nduk kooneegerak nogo, liiru mbaneegerak kwe, yogondak yi paga ninabu'me wonage kaga'lek ogoorik~o.
58002009	At Yetut perak, tiyanak mondok ayuk warak wonage kogo ogoorik~o. At Ala iniki kunik en eeppinanege menggerak me, malayikat tiyanak iigak, aput ninalitak lombok ninake kambuwak nduk, ne ambit luulu at tebeppege mbareegi, nggween paga wambi wage nagagerik, ninake kangge logonet, andi-pandi kagak waganeegerak ti paga, aap ambi amindik-amendek li'luk eeppogo mengga kwak, Ala nen at aput togop aret ayuk wurogo tiyappereegerak wonage agaarik~o.
58002010	At yi mendek ndi mendek abok aret wakkage nagagerik, unde menggerak Ala nogo nen, "Napuri apit ninom ndak-ndak tiyanak logowok~o," yinuk, ninagap ndaruwak nduk, ninowe nen wo'niren noorak nogo, abut mbangga'lek kagak wo'niren noorak meek me, at kunduk iniki kole aruwak nduk, "Aa'nduk abut mbanikit~o," yinuk, andi-pandi eerogo at oba puurak kooneegerak nogo ti, op aret kooneegerak~o.
58002011	At Yetut nen ninomaluk lek eerogo punuk Ala ake leenogo pinanege menggerak nit inom, at leenogo pinanega inom, ninogoba Ala ambit aret me, ninowe Yetut nen, "Nawuri~o," yinuk, yo'niroorak agabiti mbaka'lek logonet,
58002012	"Kendage wiganogo noreewi wonogwe me yoranet nage, Kapuri kuwak aago inenggela'me kendage tiyappege, Eerigin~o," yinuk, yoge,
58002013	ndi, ambi ari logonet, "An niniki at paga panggonak wonage agarik~o," yinuk, yoge, ndi, ambi ari logonet, "Ala nen wo'nereegerak napuri ninom yime aret ogoorik~o," yinuk, yoge, eeke menggerak~o.
58002014	-
58002015	At Yetut ti, aap a'nuk kambemenggerak paga, at kanggwi alom unde menggerak Tile nogo omaawi lek eerogo punuk, it kambuurak inagabiti nen, "Nabelan-kabelan aruwok lak piriguru agan wagagerak yi, ao," yinuk, iniki mondok aaninggin ndugu agan koonit nugu logonet, iniki wakko'net nugwi nogo, teeluk eerogo piyaakit nduk, nit at apuri nineebe nggween paga kanggo monggoorak mendek ndak-ndak aret eekkolagagerak.
58002016	At eereegerak nogo ti, it malayikat mendek yeenggwaaraakit nduk eerulik~o. Ata, at Abarakam ombowologwe yeenggwaaraakit nduk, eereegerak me,
58002017	nit aakumi maluk eekwi niinok, Ala anini ninombake nogo, iniki yanggo yuwak nduk, Ala unde inowe nggwok logonet, ninabuwa nen puk aga'lek ko'lu-kii'me ninake eeke logowak nen, nit ee'ninake menggerak nogo, abok aret at ndak-ndak eeriyak age mbareegi, aa'nduk at awuri nit pogom aret eekkolagagerak.
58002018	At iniki nggagangge kagak, iniki lek agagerak kwe kagak, ogogumbuk nu'lek logorak mamunggolagagerak me, yogondak nit niniki nggagani wage kenok, ninake eeke logonet, yeenggwa nirage wonage agaarik~o.
58003001	Togop me noreewi~o. At mbogut paga menggerak nogo nen kinayonggo pege nagagerik, at apuri leenogo pinagareegerak me, nit wone abet mba'nuk, mugurok nogwe niigak, Ala unde ninowe nggwok logonet ninake eeke logowak nduk, nappi wagagerak Yetut nogo, liippogo logowok~o.
58003002	At Muta nogo, Ala awi wurik me logonet, eeriyak nogo puk aga'lek ko'lu-kii'me eeke nagagerak kwak, ninake eeke logowak nduk, Ala nen at Yetut mippereegerak nogo ndak-ndak eerit nage menggerak.
58003003	O wurik tebenak kagak, aap o wuketak nogo tiyappogo mengga kwak, Muta tebenak kagak, Ala nen Yetut mondok tiyanak logorak mbareegerak~o.
58003004	Yi o ndi o ti, aakumi nen aret wuko menggaarak kwe, yi mendek ndi mendek abok aret ti, Ala nen aret ogobakkigireegerak.
58003005	At Muta nen, "An Ala ayeloman aret me," yinuk, ake eerit nage logonet, peebi eeriyak wone aakumi ineenu aruwak nduk, Ala awi wurik me puk aga'lek ko'lu-kii'me at ake eeke nagagerak kwe,
58003006	Keritut perak, ogoba Ala awi wurik unde aput at aret me, togop aret ko'lu-kii'me eeke menggerak. Ndi, nit perak, nit niniki lunik ale'nggen mbakwi nogo, "Abet aret ee'ninabi woraagin~o," yinuk, at woroorak tokkogo logonet, mbo pega'lek mondok nu'lek porogo wonogwe niinok, Ala awi wurik ti, nit nineebe aret mbaruwok~o.
58003007	-
58003008	Togop me, Aberiniki nen ari logonet, "Kinombomini karume wogo logonet, inogogumbuk a'nuk, Ala wone, Nineebi~o, yinuk, Ala anini wunduwak nduk liirit-laarit yorit wogo nogogwaarak nogo kokwak, yogondak Ala nen wone kit yokkirage kenok, Nineebi~o, yinuk, kinogogumbuk arugup~o.
58003009	Karume time tahun 40 paga kinombomini inenggela'me eerit wage nogo, inigen kogo logonet kwe, Anini wungge kaamun ilik, lek a? yinuk, liirit-laarit yogak mban eeko nogogwaarak me,
58003010	anini nen mondok mberiragagirak. Mberirage logonet, An yokkirage eeka'lek logonet, kiniki mondok worokot-liinik monggotak yi, neebi a, yinuk,
58003011	An yonggonggolage minggim, kit ninom yonggonggola ungguurak abu lek~o, yinuk, Nanini nen nowak mbanogo wone ti abu aret yoragagirak~o," yinuk, yereegerak.
58003012	Togop aret yereegerak me, noreewi~o. Kit togon Ala mondok eenik menggerak kagak, nomonogo mbo punuk, abet mbaka'lek kiniki maluk koonit nugwi kiyo, tum wakkologo logonip~o.
58003013	"Ala nen ninooka'lek kagak," mba'nuk, maluk eerit nogo logonet, kiniki omaawi eekkinake kero, wone, "Yogondak~o," yereegerak nogo ti, lek aga'lek awo aret wonage me, Ala nen yokkirage nogo, konenggo logonet, kiniki eyak wat-wat yogo logonip~o.
58003014	Nit aa'nduk wone konembunuk, "Yi abet aret~o," yinuk, waganeegurak nogo, nggirik-nggerok agago porogo wonogwe niigak, o age yobok ari nage kenok, Keritut ninom kunik me, eeppinaniyak mbareegerak nogo, eeppinanege logogin aret~o.
58003015	"Inogogumbuk a'nuk, Ala wone, Nineebi~o, yinuk, Ala anini wunduwak nduk liirit-laarit yogo nogogwaarak nogo kokwak, Yogondak Ala nen wone yokkirage kenok, Nineebi~o, yinuk, kinogogumbuk arugup~o," yinuk, yereegerak liiru mbanak nogo ti,
58003016	taani nen Ala wone konembunuk, "Woorak nineebi~o," yinuk, at anini wunduwak nduk yogo nogogwaarak mbakop? Lek~o. At Muta nen it aakumi Iterali abok aret o Metit nen wogoren wundi wagagerak nogo nen aret liirit-laarit yogo nogogwaarak nogo lek a?
58003017	Ndi, Ala nen anini inoba piige kagak, tahun 40 eereegerak nogo, taani~o? Lek~o. It maluk eerit nogo mbareegwa, inooreegerak karume kambit nogogwaarak, inowak nggininit nagagerak nogo lek a?
58003018	Ndi, "An yonggonggolage mi-nggim kit ninom yonggonggola ungguurak mondok lek~o," yinuk, at owak mbanogo wone yoragagerak nogo ti, taani yoragagerak mbakop? Lek~o. It at oone taganogo punuk alik eerit nogo nogogwaarak nogo lek a?
58003019	It kinombomini nen aret iniki at oba panggombunuk, oone abet mba'nuk, mugurok nogo logolik me, it unggwi noorak meek aret agagerak iigo~o.
58004001	Togop me, at ninom yonggonggola ungguurak nduk, "Woraanip~o," yinuk, abok yo'niragagerak nogo, lek aga'lek awo aret wonage me, nit ambi eerumonggoorak paga ninom yonggonggola ungguurak meek age kero, liippunuk, eeko logowok~o.
58004002	Ninombomini wone obeelom wone yorogogwaarak koneneegwaarak kwe, iniki abet mba'nuk woolik me, wone ti paga ambi obeelom eekkoloolik we aanom warogo koneneegwaarak nogo kokwak, nit togon ndak-ndak, obeelom wone yo'nirogogwaarak nogo, abet mba'nuk wagangga'lek kenok, unggwi noorak meek age kero, liippogo logowok~o.
58004003	At Ala nen, "An yonggonggolage minggim, kit ninom yonggonggola ungguurak abu lek~o, yinuk, Nanini nen nowak mbanogo abu aret yoragagirak~o," yinuk, yereegerak liiru mbanak nogo ti, mbogut-nggween wakkage logonet, at eeriyak mbareegerak nogo, worok togon eeppunuk, muk tat yonggonggolage logonet yereegerak me, ti ngge nduk yereegerak mbakop? Lek~o. Ti, nit abet mbakwi ninom peebi yonggonggola ungguurak nogo aret nduk, yereegerak~o.
58004004	Ti'nuk, nogo 6 yippunuk, ko'lu 7 paga eeriyak Ala yereegerak liiru mbanak nogo, aap ambi nen mbiningge logonet, "At Ala nen, An yi mendek ndi mendek abu aret wakkagarak me, yinuk, nogo 6 yippunuk, ko'lu 7 paga tat yonggonggolage puk wonagagerak~o," yinuk, yereegerak nogo mbiningge,
58004005	ti'nuk, ambi ari logonet, "An yonggonggolage minggim, it ninom yonggonggola ungguurak abu lek~o," yinuk, yereegerak mbiningge, eereegerak liiru mbanak wonage ti paga
58004006	it aa'nduk obeelom wone yorogogwaarak nogo, taganogo mbo pereegwaarak paga Ala yonggonggolage menggim unggwi noolik me, inobaane'me aakumi alik mendek inom yonggonggola ungguwak nduk yereegerak kogo~o.
58004007	Togop me, wone, "Yogondak kit Ala nen yokkirage kenok, Nineebi~o, yinuk, kinogogumbuk arugup~o," yereegerak wone aginggwe aa'nduk mbininogo yokkiragarak nogo aret yi tahun ndi tahun eeppunuk, o peebi aap Ndawut nogo togop aret yoreegerak liiru mbaneegerak me, wone, "Yogondak~o," yinuk, Ndawut yoreegerak nogo ti, Ala nen ne alik ambi eyom paga aakumi alik mendek inom yonggonggola ungguwak nduk, iniki koombunuk, yoreegerak kogo~o.
58004008	Aap Yotuwa nen yonggonggologo menggam ninombomini piya woraanetak en, Ala nen ne alik ambi eyom paga yonggonggoloorak yereegerak wone nogo ti, yenetak lek kwe,
58004009	yereegerak aret me, Ala nen nogo 6 yippunuk, ko'lu 7 paga tat yonggonggolage wonagagerak nogo kokwak, yogondak nit Ala apuri kunduk yonggonggologo logowok nduk, o ne ambi punogo pereegerak wonage~o.
58004010	Ala yonggonggolage menggim ninom yonggonggola ungguurak mbakwi kenok, Ala nen yi mendek ndi mendek abu wakkage nagagerik, tat yonggonggolagagerak nogo kokwak, nit ndak-ndak tat yonggonggologo logogun~o.
58004011	Togop me, it Iterali mendek aa'nduk Ala wone taganogo mbo pogo mbareegwa, "Kit yonggonggola ungguurak lek~o," yinuk, yoragagerak nogo kokwak, nit ndak-ndak yo'nirage kero, unggwi nawok nduk, wakkenet unggwogo logowok~o.
58004012	At Ala mondok eenik logonet, alik en eerit nage menggi kwak, at oone ti ndak-ndak mondok omaawi alik en ninikime nggaganogo yo'nirage menggerak. Mbuti nggawi ngget peenok-peenok maarak ti, ngget mbuuluk negen me, ninendobanggun yunggu'me mondok pene'na unggwage logonet, ninowak kagak ninowak ako kin eeppi unggwage menggerak kwe, Ala wone yi perak, ngget mondok alik negen aret me, ninikime mondok nggoguk yi unggwage logonet, eeriyak niniki koonggo monggoorak nogo, abok aret leenogo kin eeppege menggerak.
58004013	Nit aakumi inom, yi mendek ndi mendek ogobakkigirik inom, abok aret at Ala enegen kage menggerak me, ambit-ambi at enegen neega'lek me nduk, kumaa'nariyak abu meek~o. At enggaanom paga yi mendek ndi mendek abok aret kin paga wonage me, at abok aret enegen kage menggerak~o. Togop aret me, nit eeko monggoorak nogo ambi kumaappugun lek abok aret mbininogo at yorugun~o.
58004014	Nit Ala unde ninowe nggwok Ala aput Yetut nogo, mbogut ta'mban-mban aago kagak irimbaga agi lombok tiyarogon kwi'nari lagangge nagagerik, yogondak ninake eeke wonage me, nit wone abet mba'nuk waganeegurak yogo monggoorak nogo, mondok nggirik-nggerok agago porogo logowok~o.
58004015	Ala unde ninowe nggwok nogo nen nit aap nggween paga mendek me, ninobaabut ninggin-nanggin eekwi niinok, "Eebi," ninomba'nuk ninake ugun-ugun eekeelik~o. Ata, "An kagagirak nogo aret eeginake~o," yinuk, ninake liirogon eeke menggerak~o. Nit ninabut mbaniyak nduk, aaninggin-paaninggin ninoba age menggerak nogo, at togop aret oba age kagak maluk eeka'lek ogogumbuk logonet, waganeegerak eenu me,
58004016	yogondak aaninggin ambi ninoba age kenok, ninabuwa mbake logonet, iniki kunik en eeppinanege kaawok nduk, ninagabiti mbaka'lek at Ala iniki kunik en eeppinanege menggim nogome panggo yi ungguwok~o.
58005001	At aap Ala unde inowe nggwok nogo ti, aakumi nen Ala alut eeko logonet, yi mendek ndi mendek ake pi wagaatak nogo, Ala wogoge, ndi, maluk eekaatak nogo, it inake warogo kani kumbege, eeke logowak nduk, Ala nen aakumi inenggela'me nen ambi leenogo mippegak eeke menggerak.
58005002	At aap ti, aap nggween paga mendek maluk eeke menggerak aret me, aakumi Ala wone liippega'lek nomo agan nogo logonet, maluk eekwi iinok, inabuwa mba'nuk, inake yanggorogon eeke menggerak.
58005003	Aakumi maluk eekwi nogo, inake warogo Ala wogoge logonet, at togon aap nggween paga mendek maluk eeke menggerak aret me, omaluk lek eerogo puwak nduk, ake warogo Ala wogoge menggerak.
58005004	Ndi, it iniki mba'nuk, "An Ala unde inowe nggwok logokit~o," yinuk, miikkologo logolik. Ata, Ala nen aap Karun leenogo mippereegerak nogo kokwak, leenogo mippiige menggerak.
58005005	Togop ndak-ndak at Keritut nogo nen, "An Ala unde inowe nggwok logokit~o," yinuk, tiyappatulik~o. Ata, Ala nen at yoge logonet, "Yogondak kat an naput age, ndi, an kat kogoba age, eekoorak~o," yinuk, yoge,
58005006	ndi, aap ambi nen Ala yereegerak wone liiru mbanak mbiningge logonet, "Aap Meliketerek eeke nagagerak nogo kokwak, kat an neebe unde logonet, mondok-mondok nake eeke logomunggun~o," yinuk, yereegerak mbiningge, eereegwaarak ti paga Ala nen aret leenogo mippereegerak kogo~o.
58005007	Maan at Yetut aakumi kwak nggween paga yime nege logonet, kambuurak agabiti nen leenggu maake logonet, oone nggwok paga tamban eeke, "Nagap ndaru~o," yinuk, Ala nggino yoge, eereegerak nogo, ogoba nen yoge kenok aruk konok mban eeke nagagerak me, aput nen tamban eereegerak nogo Ala aruk koneneegerak kwe,
58005008	"Naput aret kwe, andi-pandi oba pemenggaarak paga an yoge nogo, E~o, yinuk, yanggonak eeke logorak mamunggolaawak~o," yinuk, teppereegerak.
58005009	Teppege mbareegi, nit ee'ninake menggerak nogo, at abu li'luk eerogo mamunggolage nagagerik, nit at oone woppunuk, eerit nogwe nogo, abok aret nineenik mondok-mondok logowok nduk, ninagap ndake logorak alom at aret agagerak me,
58005010	Ala nen, "Aap Meliketerek eeke nagagerak nogo kokwak Ala unde inowe nggwok kat aret~o," yinuk, mippereegerak.
58005011	Wone yi mendek yokkiroorak ambik wonage kwe, ambinom koneniyak anggon eekkinake kagarak me, liirogon mbininogo yokkiroorak meek ee'naki~o, noreewi.
58005012	Kit o maan togon Ala wone konenggo nogogutak me, muk mamuniragak mendek logorak kwe, omaawi mendek noorak meek kenok, yilak amburu negen mban nonggo logorak kinobaabut kiigirak me, alom wone aa'nduk konenggo nogogutak nogo mendek mban ambinom mamunggiroorak ogotak kiigo~o.
58005013	It yilak amburu nunggwi nogo ti, elege-aabologwe pogom me, maluk eeriyak obeelom eeriyak eraambe yelok kaga'lek aret menggaarak kwe,
58005014	omaawi mendek nunggwi iinok perak, aap kole iniki warak pogom, Ala wone mondok liippunuk eekwi me, maluk eeriyak obeelom eeriyak eraambe yelok aret kogo menggaarak.
58006001	-
58006002	Togop me, nit abet mbaruwok nduk, Keritut eeke nagagerak wone aa'nduk mamunik nogo mendek mban mugurok nogo logorak lek~o. Ata, nit niniki kole ee'ninaburak wone nogo mendek inom woppunuk, mugurok nogo logowok~o. "Nit obeelom eekkolaawok," mba'nuk, eeko logonet kwe, kagak kanggo nogogurak wone nogo, mbo punuk, Ala abet mbakwi wone inom, niyome wanggwi wone inom, inanobak nineenggi tebembiinok, tamban eekwi wone inom, aakumi kanggaatak ineenik agago mippiyoorak wone inom, o age yobok paga inowak loonogo aaninggin inoba kwippiyamenggerak mondok-mondok yagan wako logorak wone inom, wone ti mendek abok aret ti, ogowa pugu pogom wonage op aret kwe, uum pega'lek ogowa mban pit nogwe ti mage~o.
58006003	Ata, nit niniki kole ee'ninaburak wone nogo woppunuk, mugurok nogo logowok~o. Ndi, Ala nen, "Eeriyak~o," ari kenok, ninom aret eerit nogo logowok~o.
58006004	It aakumi inomaluk mbo punuk, Ala wone konenggwi iigak, inikime eya aganake, mbogut paga nen onggo lek we wo'nirage nogo ombat kogwe, Aberiniki inikime waganggwi,
58006005	Ala wone ninikime obeelom eeppinanege nogo muk liippugwi, ndi, o age yobok paga Ala nen nineebe mondok alik negen eeppinaniyak wone nogo ineenu ogwe, eeko nagaatik,
58006006	mbo punuk, nomoninuk alik eerit nogwe iinok ti, Keritut eyo karo-karo paga ambinom nabenogo punuk, nggwok paga enggali wappugwi me, peebi inomaluk mbo punuk, Ala oba nabennari noorak abu meek aret kaagun~o.
58006007	O mayu wangge logonet, nggween yawenogo pegetak me, aakumi awi yakkolagaatak nogo nen anggen obeelom mbanggologwe Ala nen iige nagaatik, "Nggween yi, obeelom aret~o," yinuk, ale'nggen mbake menggerak kwe,
58006008	wola inom, alok inom, mban lagangge kenok perak, Ala nen, "Nggween yi, abu maluk me, pulunogo punuk, kani kumbikit~o," yinuk, mbake menggerak.
58006009	Noreewi~o. Kit nit niniki kunik me, wone ti eeriyak yokkirogoorak kwe, Ala nen togop eekkinaburak nit mbaka'lek ogoorik~o. Kit muk kinagap ndareegerak me, Ala nen aakumi inagap ndake logonet, obeelom eeppiige logorak mbareegerak nogo aret obeelom mban eekkinake logogin mbako ogoorik~o.
58006010	Kit kinogoba Ala a'me nggelok eeke menggerak me, at eyabu eerit nogo logonet, at endage tiyappuwak nduk, "Ao," mba'nuk, kinoreewi Ala apuri yeenggwaarogo nogogutak inom, yogondak awo yeenggwaarogwe wonogwe inom, at mari eerogo pigin lek~o.
58006011	O age yobok paga eeriyak niniki lunik wonogwe nogo, "Abet aret wo'niraagin~o," yinuk, wone ti paga kiniki panggonak logonet, kiniki mondok aganggen kerek togon kinalitak lombok mugurok nogo logorak, "Ao," lombok kinombako logonet, yokkirogo ogoorik~o.
58006012	Ala wone mugurok noorak kineebi eekkinake ti mage~o. Ata, Ala nen it aakumi, "Togop eeppinagagin~o," yinuk, wone yoragagerak nogo, abet mba'nuk, iniki inaanaganggenggwi lek mondok kwi'ndak wonogo mbareegwa, ndak-ndak eeppiyareegerak nogo pogom, kit togop ndak-ndak logorak kinombako ogoorik~o.
58006013	-
58006014	At Ala nen Abarakam abok yoge logonet, "An nen abet aret nale'nggen nggwok togon koba pagage logonet, kombowologwe apit wokkirigin~o," yinuk, yoreegerak nogo ti, at endage tiyanak kokwak, ambi wonage lek me, at endage aret kunogo yoreegerak.
58006015	Yoge mbareegi, Abarakam nen, "Abet aret eeppanigin~o," yinuk, iniki mondok kwippunuk, tokkage nagagerak me, abok yoreegerak nogo aret waganeegerak.
58006016	Aap ambi at oone mondok abet mbaruwak nduk, aap ayuk warak ambi endage kunogo yorage ti paga it wone onggo-onggo yogwe nogo, inoone lek aret age menggerak.
58006017	Nogo ndak-ndak at Ala nen, "Togop eekkabigin~o," yinuk, iniki koombunuk, abok yoreegerak nogo, "Peebi Abarakam ombowologwe nen Ala alik eeriyak iniki koombunuk, yo'niraagin lek, yo'nirage nogo abu ndak-ndak eerigin," nombaruwak nduk, wone eeppiyoorak Abarakam abok yoreegerak nogo yoge logonet, at endage inom kumbatinuk yoreegerak~o.
58006018	At Ala nen wone ambi iniki koombunuk Abarakam abok yoge, ndi, ti'nuk ambi, pilit mbarukwak at endage inom kunogo yoge, eereegerak nogo ti, at pilit puguniyak abu meek me, wone yugu alom mbere, lek eerogo puurak lek mendek aret yoreegerak. Ti yoreegerak paga at Ala nen, "An alik eeriyak niniki koombunuk, yokkiraagin lek~o," yinuk, nit ninagap ndarak mendek, "Wo'niraagin," yo'niragagerak niniki lunik mugurok nogo monggoorak nogo nen abet mba'nuk, mugurok nogo logowok nduk, abok yoreegerak me, nit mondok mugurok nogo logowok~o.
58006019	Yiiro niyo wonok nage kero, eyo nggwok paga mbarembogo mengga kwak, nit niniki ti, niniki lunik nogo paga aret mbarenak wonage~o. Yiiro eyo nu'lek paga mbarembogo mengga kwak, niniki lunik nogo ti, Ala awi wurik me yum oolo ogoorak kagak akem time mbarenak wonage me, lek arigin lek mondok nu'lek mbarenak aret logogin~o.
58006020	Ndi, at Yetut nogo ti, aap Meliketerek eeke nagagerak nogo pogom, Ala unde ninowe nggwok mondok-mondok logowak nduk, mippereegerak me, nit peebi unggwi nawok nduk, at aa'nduk ninake tu yarit unggwi nagagerak wonage~o.
58007001	Aap Meliketerek nogo ti, aakumi o Talem mendek inowe endagembogut inarum logonet, at tiyanak lombok menggerak Ala nogo, inom unde wonagagerak. Ne ambi paga aap inendagembogut ineebe ambik nen o Torom-Nggomora inawi oonda mbambunuk, inamendek kugun wonok nogwe me, Abarakam awuri inom muguren nage nagagerik, tebenogo piinok, kugun waganeegwaarak nogo ndininuk, iyokan ame wage me, aap Meliketerek nogo ka wungge nagagerik, ale'nggen Abarakam oba pereegerak.
58007002	Ale'nggen oba pege mbareegi, Abarakam nen ndininuk wagagerak nogo, "Kinamendek 10 wonage kenok ambi yendenogo an nake panu~o," yinuk, Ala nen yereegerak nogo ndak-ndak yendenogo Ala ake aap Meliketerek nogo wogoreegerak. Aap Meliketerek endage toonak nogo ti, alom mbere wonage. Ambi ti, "Iniki Abe Koonak Logonet Eeka Endagembogut~o," yinuk, yogwe, ndi, ambi, at o Talem endagembogut wonagagerak me, endage ambi, "Aakumi Iniki Ugun Inale'nggen Mbakwi Inogoba Endagembogut~o," yinuk, yogwe, eeko nogogwaarak.
58007003	At aap Meliketerek nogo ti, agalo-ogoba inom, ndarak alom inom, ne nda'nagagerak inom, ne kambeegerak inom, mbininogo liiru mbanak lek ti paga at Ala aput kwak Ala unde mondok-mondok itok menggerak kogo~o.
58007004	At Abarakam ti, nit apit ninombo aap nggwok aret wonagagerak kwe, at awim tebenogo piinok, wage nagagerik, kugun wogo ndininuk wagagerak nogo obeelom kenok, yendenogo Ala ake aap Meliketerek wogoreegerak ti paga, at Meliketerek nogo ti, aap mondok nggwok aret kogo~o.
58007005	Ala nen wone, "Yogop ee'nu, ndogop ee'nu," yinuk, aakumi Iterali mendek yorage logonet, "Kinamindik-kinamendek 10 wonage kenok, ambi yendenogo an nake panugwi kiinok, it an neebe unde Lewi mendek nen mban waganggo logowak~o," yinuk, yoragagerak liiru mbanak nogo ti, it Abarakam ombowologwe nen Ala ake pugwi nogo, inoreewi it mendek nen pugwi kwe kagak aret it Lewi ombowologwe nogo nen waganggo logowak nduk, yoragagerak kwe,
58007006	aap Meliketerek perak, Lewi mendek ndarak lek kwe, Abarakam nen Ala ake pugu yendenogo wogoge mbareegi, "Ala nen abok yoreegerak nogo porogo menggerak nogoba aap nggwok yi aret me, nagabiti~o," yinuk, yuurak kwe kagak, wagangge nagagerik, ale'nggen oba pereegerak.
58007007	It aap inoweewi inendage warak nogo nen, inawuri inendage lek tebenak mendek inale'nggen inoba piigo menggaarak nogo lek a? Togop eeko menggaarak me,
58007008	it aap Lewi ombowologwe Ala ake pugu waganggo menggaarak nogo ti, it aap ambi kangge kagak, obaane'me ambi mippegak eeko menggaarak mendek nen, Ala ake pugu waganggo menggaarak kwe, at ambi eereegerak nogo ti perak, "Ndi eyom paga kambeegerak," liiru mbanak lek me, at mondok-mondok eenik logonet, wagangge menggerak nogo mendek negen aret kogo ogoorik~o.
58007009	-
58007010	Ndi, aap Meliketerek nogo nen Abarakam ka wungge mbareegi, Abarakam nogo nen at ombooluk Lewi nogo nda'naga'lek awo inikime kagak Ala ake pugu wogoreegerak me, it Lewi mendek Ala ake pugu waganggo menggaarak nogo nen Ala ake pugu aap Meliketerek wogoreegwaarak yuurak ti, op aret~o.
58007011	It aap Lewi ombowologwe nogo, Ala unde logonet eeko logowak nduk, Ala nen mippiige mbareegi, it nen aakumi inake eeko logonet obeelom eeppiyaawak nduk, "Yogop ee'nu, ndogop ee'nu," wone yugu inom yoragagerak nogo, eeko logonet kwe, it eekwi paga aakumi obeelom aganaburak op logonetak en, peebi it aap Ala unde Karun ombowologwe mendek nogo mbo piinok, aap alik Meliketerek mendek ambi mippiyoorak koonenetak lek~o.
58007012	Ndi, it Ala unde logonet eeko menggaarak nogo, lek eerogo punuk obaane'me alik ngget mendek ambi eeko logowak nduk, mippiige kenok, it eeko logorak wone ngget mendek inom yorage menggerak.
58007013	At Meliketerek mendek mippuurak an yokkiragarak nogo ti, at ninowe Yetut nen eeke logorak me nduk, yokkiragi~o. At anebunu Lewi mendek lek anebunu alik mendek me, at anebunu mendek ambi nen aakumi inake warogo kani kunggo menggam nogome Ala unde logonet, eeko menggaarak nogo, eeka'lek aret agaarik~o.
58007014	At ninowe ti, anebunu Yekura mendek nit abok nineenu~o. Ndi, Muta nen, "Peebi aap Yekura mendek ambi Ala unde logogin~o," yinuk, ti yuulik kwe,
58007015	aap anebunu alik ambi Meliketerek kokwak, Ala unde logowak nduk kin agagerak ti paga, Ala nen inanebunu Lewi mendek nogo mbo piinok, aap anebunu alik mendek mippuurak kooneegerak kogo ogoorik~o.
58007016	Aap alik Meliketerek kokwak Ala unde logowak nduk, mippereegerak alom nogo ti, aakumi nen, "Aap ti mendek ndarak kenok ambi Ala unde logorak~o," yinuk, wone lengganak nogo paga mippulik~o. Ata, at lek eerogo puurak lek mondok itok eenik menggerak ti paga Ala nen aret mippereegerak.
58007017	Ala nen at mippege kenok eeke logorak wone yoge logonet, "Aap Meliketerek eeke nagagerak nogo kokwak, kat an neebe unde logonet, mondok-mondok nake eeke logomunggun~o," yinuk, yoreegerak liiru mbanak nogo ndak-ndak aret mippereegerak.
58007018	-
58007019	Ti eereegerak paga Muta wone lengganogo yoreegerak nogo, mugurok nogo logonet, obeelom eekkolaawok nduk, eekwi iigak kwe, obeelom eerogo piiga'lek we aanom warogo eeko nogogwaarak me, "Yogop ee'nu, ndogop ee'nu," wone aa'nduk lengganak nogo, lek eerogo punuk, wone alik ngget mendek kin eeppereegerak me, "Wone yi, mugurok nogwe paga obeelom eeppinaniyak abet aret kogo," yinuk, niniki lunik logonet, Ala owagam nagak eeko ogoorik~o.
58007020	It aa'nduk Ala unde logonet, eeko logowak nduk, mippiigo logonet, pilit mbakwi iyo, Ala endage kunogo mippiigo logolik kwe,
58007021	Ala nen at Yetut mippege logonet perak, "Kat an neebe unde logonet, mondok-mondok nake eeke logomunggun~o, yinuk, At endage kunogo kumbuk mbaneegerak me, Oone alik arigin abu lek~o," yinuk, yoreegerak nogo ti, at endage inom kunogo mippereegerak ti paga at Yetut ninake eeke logowak nduk koonogo mippereegerak nogo,
58007022	eeke logonet, aa'nduk eekwi yobok ari nagagi kwak, yobok yigin lek~o. Ata, yogondak mondok lik togon aret eerigin mbako logowok~o.
58007023	Ndi, ambi, it aa'nduk Ala unde logonet eeko nogogwaarak nogo, mondok-mondok eeko logolik. Ata, ambi kangge kagak obaane'me ambi mippegak eeko nogogwaarak me, ineebe ambik nen aret eeko nogogwaarak kwe,
58007024	Yetut perak, mondok itok menggerak me, ambi obaane'me mi'na'nuk eeke logogin abu lek~o. At alik nen mondok-mondok eeke logogin~o.
58007025	Togop me, nit aakumi niniki at oba panggombunuk, Ala owagam nogwe niinok, at ninake Ala yoriyak nduk mondok eenik mi'ndak menggerak me, ninagap ndarogo mondok obeelom agago pinaniyak op aret~o.
58007026	Ala unde ninowe nggwok ninake eeke logonet, obeelom eerogo pinanuwak nduk mippuurak agagerak nogo ti, Keritut aret~o. It aakumi maluk eekwi inenggela'me nege nagagerak kwe, at maluk ambi eeke, ndi, aakumi inoone at oba pugwi, eeka'lek mbareegi, mbogut ta'mban-mban aago kagak, irimbaga tiyarogon kwippi laganeegerak. Kwippi lagangge mbareegi, at maluk eeka'lek mondok obeelom ake leenak aret me, nit aakumi ninabuwa nen ninake eeke wonage~o.
58007027	Ninake eeke logonet, it aap Lewi mendek Ala unde inoweewi nggwok nogo nen ko'lu-kii'me aakumi inake warogo Ala wogogo logonet, aa'nduk it maluk eekaatak nogo lek aruwak nduk, Ala wogogwi, ti'nuk, peebi aakumi ugun maluk eekaatak nogo lek aruwak nduk inake wogogwi, eeko mengga kwak, at togop eekeelik~o. At Keritut perak, "It maluk eekwi nogo, lek eerogo piyaakit nduk inake kambikit~o," yinuk, Ala ake warogo wogogo nogogwa kwak, nit ninomaluk lek eerogo pinanikit nduk, at ne ambit mondok nggaruk togon ninake kambeegerak.
58007028	Wone Muta yoreegerak ndak-ndak eeko logonet, it aap nggween paga mendek kagak Ala unde inowe nggwok logowak nduk, mippiigo menggaarak kwe, Ala nen at aput mippege logonet, endage kunogo yoreegerak nogo ti, wone Muta yoreegerak nogo aa'nduk kagak peebi yoreegerak me, at aput iniki mondok koleewak Ala unde ninowe nggwok ninake eeke logowak nduk, mippereegerak.
58008001	Nit wone yogwe yi nogo, alom liirogon yi aret yokkira~o. Ala unde ninowe nggwok ti, togop aret wonage~o. At ninogoba mondok tiyanak menggerak mbogut paga wone lengganogo yorage menggim eenggi abe'nggan paga kwi'nari laganeegerak logonet,
58008002	it aakumi nen ooliya negen wureegwam nogome eeke lek~o. At ooliya abe Ala nen wureegim Mage Lombok Menggim time aret ninake eeke agaarik~o.
58008003	At Ala unde inowe nggwok nogo ti, yi mendek ndi mendek Ala ake pege, at ake warogo wogoge, eeke logowak nduk, leenogo mippogo menggaarak nogo ndak-ndak, Ala unde nit ninowe nggwok yi nogo kunduk, ninake eeke logonet, at we eeke logorak meek~o. At togon amendek ambi Ala ake puurak aret~o.
58008004	Ala unde ninowe nggwok yi nogo ti, nggween paga yime ninom logonetak en, at Muta nen, "Ala ndogop wogogo logonip~o," yinuk, lengganogo yoragagerak nogo ndak-ndak, wogogo logowak nduk, Ala unde ineebe muk mippiyareegerak wonogwe me, Ala unde ninowe nggwok logonetak lek~o.
58008005	At Muta nen it aap Ala unde logonet, eeko logowam ooliya negen wuriyak nduk eeke me, Ala nen, "Puut irimbaga nen wakkagak, Yogop aret ogobakkigirumunggup~o, yinuk, yokkigi yi, ndak-ndak aret eeko logowak, yegerak, yoret~o," yinuk, yoreegerak me, o eebe mbogut paga wurik wonage kagak, it Ala unde inoweewi nogo ti, we ogut wakkagak ooliya wurik paga eeko menggaarak kogo ogoorik~o.
58008006	Ndi, yogondak eerogo pinaniyak kooneegerak wone nogo ti, mondok iya lombok me, wone maan yugu eeko logonet, eerogo pinaniyak meek kenok, Yetut nen Ala ninom lambunninabuwak nduk, wone maan yugu ti, eerulik. Ata, wone alik ngget mendek koonogo pinanege nagagerik, yogondak ninowe nggwok logonet, mondok alik negen ninake eeke agaarik~o.
58008007	Wone aa'nduk Ala nen koonogo yo'niragagerak nogo, obeelom eeppiigo logonetak en, peebi eerogo piyoorak wone ti, koonogo yoraanetak lek kwe,
58008008	Ala nen wone yugu kagak at apuri alik eekwi iige nagagerik, inaruk wake logonet, "It Iterali paga wiganak inom, it Yekura paga wiganak inom, It ninom wone ngget mendek koonogo puurak eyom panggoni woraagin~o.
58008009	It inombomini o Metit nen wogoren wundi woraakit nduk, neenggi pigiren wundi wage logonet, Wone ninom koonogo yoragagirak nogo, it liippunuk, eerit naga'lek mbareegwa, An inogoba Ala nen aret mbo piyareegirak me, Wone ti mendek an ambinom ninom koonogo pigin lek~o. Ata, wone alik ngget mendek ninom koonogo pigin~o, yinuk, an Ala nen aret yagi~o.
58008010	Ti eyom abu aret age kenok, it Iterali paga wiganak wone ngget mendek ninom koonogo puurak nogo yi aret. Eeko logorak wone yoragagirak nogo, inikime nabenogo piige, It inikime liiru negen mbanogo piige, Eerigin me, An it inogoba age, ndi, it an napuri ogwe, eerugun~o.
58008011	It inendage abu tiyanak inom, inendage abu tebenak inom, abok aret neebe ineenu arugun me, Aap ambi at imbirak menggerak nen, Ala ndogop~o, yinuk, mamunege, Aap ambi oreeluk yoge logonet, Ala eebe keenu aru~o, yinuk, yoge, Eerugun lek aret~o.
58008012	It inobaabut maluk lombok logonet eekwi nogo, an lek eerogo pege, Ndi, it maluk eekwi nogo, an nen aberak logogin lek, nami eerogo pege, Eerigin~o, Yinuk, an Ala nen aret yagi~o," yereegerak nogo ti,
58008013	"Wone alik ngget mendek koonogo pigin~o," yereegerak ti paga wone aa'nduk yugu nogo meek negen agagerak me, yi mendek ndi mendek maan mendek etenggen maluk agaatak kenok, mbo pogo menggaarak nogo kokwak aret mbo pereegerak~o.
58009001	Wone aa'nduk koonogo yoragagerak nogo eeko logonet, Ala alut eeko logorak kenok, "Togop aret eeko logonip~o," yinuk, yoragagerak wone yugu inom, eeko menggam aakumi nen wureegwam nogo inom, wonagagerak.
58009002	Ala unde nen eeko logowam ooliya negen wuko logonet, ko mbere ogooreegwaarak. Ko endekenggwe ogoorak ti, "Mage Menggim," yogo nogogwaarak me, ndi wuninogo pegak ogobakkigirik inom, roti Ala ake pogo nogogwaarak eyo ndoonak inom, time aret wonagagerak.
58009003	Ndi, yum endekem tugunik kagak ko oolo akenggwe ogoorak me tugunik nogo ti, "Mage Lombok Menggim~o," yogo nogogwaarak me,
58009004	obari abe kaga kunggo menggam mbuti emas paga ogobakkigirik nogo, time aret wonagagerak. Ndi, togolowak mbuti emas paga ogobakkigirik me, mbi mana ando yonggolak inom, aap Karun owaanggun paga agarip wundeegerak nogo inom, ndi, Ala nen wone yugum paga liiru mbanogo Muta wogoreegerak nogo inom, abok aret Ala aloobut mbanak enaagan-ambokan mbuti emas mban nabenak wonagagerak nogome yonggolak o akenggwe Mage Lombok Menggim time aret wonagagerak.
58009005	Ndi, malayikat negen aakumi, "Wi," irogwe kerub mbere inogut nogo, aakumi inomaluk lek eerogo punuk, Ala inom lambungge menggim aloobut mbanak irimbaga ina'naabit wiganogo punuk, nobapporogo wonogogwaarak. Wone ti mendek ando apit mbininogo yokkiroorak kwe, meek me, ando kagak nggaruk togon ti aret yokkiragi~o.
58009006	Ooliya wurik ko ogoorak nogome togop aret ndigik-ndegek aago wonagagerak me, it Ala unde nogo, Ala ayuk wuko logonet eeko menggaarak nogo nen, eeko logowok nduk, ko endekenggwe nogome ko'lu-kii'me unggwi nogo nogogwaarak kwe,
58009007	ko ore akenggwe ogoorak nogome perak, at Ala unde inowe nggwok nogo mban tahun ambi eeke kenok, ne ambit paga mban unggwagak eeke nagagerak. Ndi, unggwagak eeke logonet, we unggwage logolik~o. Ata, at omaluk lek eerogo pege, ndi, oreewi nen, "Nit maluk eerulik," mbakwi iigak, Ala nen maluk eekaarak inombake kero, lek eeppiige, eeruwak nduk, inake amiya kilirik wonok mban unggwagak eeke nagagerak.
58009008	Ti eeke nagagerak paga Aberiniki nen paganogo yo'nirage logonet, ko endekenggwe eeko nogogwaarak nogo lek aga'lek awo eekwi wonogwe me, ko akenggwe Mage Lombok Menggim nogome tu paarogo pinanega'lek awo narak wonage nineenu aruwak nduk, yo'nirage nagagerak~o.
58009009	Ooliya wurik me eeko nogogwaarak nogo ti, eebe yogondak kin agaarak eekwi yi, ogut wakkagak aret eeko nogogwaarak me, yi mendek ndi mendek Ala ake pugwi, Ala ake warogo wogogwi, eeko nogogwaarak kwe, it wogori wogwe ti paga, "Nomaluk abu lek eerogo punuk, obeelom agago panegi~o," yinuk, iniki ale'nggen logolik. Ata, inomaluk aberak aret wonogogwaarak me, we ogut wakkagak aret eeko nogogwaarak kogo~o.
58009010	It yi mendek ndi mendek Ala wogori wogo nogogwaarak nogo ti, ineebe op logowok nduk, "Mbi inom, niyo inom, ndogop eerogo punuk nunggwi, kinabin ndogop eerogo kookwi, eeko logonip~o," yinuk, wone yugu kagak alik eeko nagaatik, onggo pi wagak eeko nogogwaarak me, peebi wone ngget mendek kin ari wage kenok, lek eerogo puwak nduk, eeko nogogwaarak kwe,
58009011	Keritut perak, Ala unde ninowe nggwok logonet, Ala nen mondok alik negen obeelom eerogo pinaniyak kooneegerak nogo, eeppinanikit nduk wage nagagerik, Ala nen yi mendek ndi mendek ogobakkigirogo pereegerak nggween paga wonage nogo mendek aakumi nen kuwak eeppunuk wureegwam nogome eekeelik~o. Ata, at o alik nggwok mondok abe lombok wurik nogome unggwi nage nagagerik, ninake eeke agaarik~o.
58009012	Ndi, at yum oolo ogoorak kagak Mage Lombok Menggim unggwi nage logonet, tapi inom, ndomba inom, amiya wonok unggulik~o. Ata, at amiya lombok wonok ne ambit aret pi unggwage nagagerik, nit mondok-mondok ninagap ndarak logowok nduk, ninonggo mbanogo pereegerak~o.
58009013	It aakumi eeriyak mage yugu kagak, ugun eeppunuk tapi inom, ndomba inom, amiya wonok wogwe, ndi, it aap lu pigaganggaatak inoba kooka'lek iinok, Ala nen inooke kero, inoba koo'naruwak nduk, tapi warogo kani kumbunuk, wun waganogo inagabolo paga yumbunogo piigwi, eekwi iinok, ineebe obeelom ogo nogogwaarak nogo kokwak,
58009014	Keritut amiya ti perak, iya lombok me, ninomaluk koo'ninaburak meek mbakop? Lek~o. At mondok itok menggerak Aberiniki nen eeppege kagak, ndomba awinde-obande aago lek obeelom nogo pogom iniki nen at eebe aret nit ninake Ala wogoreegerak me, yogondak nit Ala mondok eenik itok menggerak nogo, ake eeko logowok nduk, wone aa'nduk aanom warogo mugurok nogwe niigak, ninomaluk lek aga'lek abe'nagak mban eeke kagak kambit nogo nogogurak nogo, at amiya paga lek eerogo punuk, mondok obeelom eerogo pinaniyak op aret mbako logowok~o.
58009015	At togop eereegerak me, Ala nen wone aa'nduk koonogo yoragagerak nogo, eerit nogo logonet, ndak-ndak eeka'lek taganogo punuk, maluk eeko mbareegwa, keele maarak negen wonogwe nogo, inonggo mbanogo punuk, wondet aago nugu logowak nduk, inake aap ambi muk kambeegerak me, Ala nen, "Mondok logorak mendek wokkiraagin~o," yinuk, yonggo piyareegerak nogo nen wone alik woppunuk, eerit nogwe paga wone alik ngget mendek koonogo yo'niragagerak nogo waawok nduk, Keritut ninake eeke menggerak.
58009016	Aap ambi nen, "An kangge neenok neyate it ndogop-ndogop mban kolaawak~o," yinuk, liiru mbanogo pegetak kwe, "Abet aret kanggerak~o," yinuk, liiru mbanak lek kenok, eyate tumburirogolik~o.
58009017	At liiru mbanogo pegetak nogo awo eenik wonage kagak, "Togop koloorak~o," yinuk, liiru mbanak nogo ti, tumburirogolik~o. Eebe kangge kenok perak, tumburirogo menggaarak me,
58009018	wone aa'nduk Ala nen koonogo yoragagerak nogo, eeko logowak nduk, amiya werenogo puulik ta lek~o.
58009019	Ata, at Ala nen, "Yogop ee'nu, ndogop ee'nu," yinuk, wone nogo abu yoge mbareegi, it Yakuri nen eebe aret eeko logowak nduk, Muta nen wone nogo abok aret mbininogo yorage nagagerik, tapi-ndomba amiya niyo inom tooppunuk, ndomba eeruwak maa'ngga warak yigirok paga kunogo tamombunuk, mbuku pirik-perek aago liiru mbanak paga inom, aakumi ineebe paga inom, abok aret werenogo nagabit nagagerak.
58009020	Nagabit nage logonet, "Kit, E~o, yinuk, eeko logobagip nduk, Ala nen wone koonogo yokkiragaarak yi, Abet aret eerigin, mbako logobagip nduk, amiya yi, kinoba werenogo pinagagi~o," yinuk, yoragagerak nogo~o.
58009021	Ti eeppege nagagerik, ooliya wurik inom, Ala alut eeko logonet, eeko menggaarak yi mendek ndi mendek inom, abok togop aret amiya werenogo pereegerak.
58009022	Wone Muta yoreegerak nogo ndak-ndak eeko logonet, yi mendek ndi mendek abok aret amiya paga mban obeelom aruwak nduk, amiya werenogo puurak wone yugu me, amiya kilika'lek kenok ti, ninomaluk lek eerogo puurak lek aret kogo ogoorik~o.
58009023	Togop me, mbogut paga eeko logorak ogut wakkagak eeko nogogwaarak yi nogo ti, obeelom aruwak nduk amiya paga togop aret kooppunuk eeko nogogwaarak kwe, mbogut paga nen eeko logorak yi mendek ndi mendek ti perak, iya me, obeelom aruwak nduk, tapi-ndomba amiya paga kooriyak meek~o. Ata, amiya omaawi alik mendek paga kooriyak perak op~o.
58009024	Togop me, Keritut nogo ti, o abe wurik kagak ogut wakkagak Mage Menggim aakumi nen wureegwam nogome unggulik~o. Ata, at mbogut paga lombok unggwi nage nagagerik, Ala enggaanom paga ko'lu-kii'me ninake eeke agaarik~o.
58009025	Ndi, Ala unde inowe nggwok nogo nen Mage Lombok Menggim nogome unggwi nage logonet, at amiya wonok unggwi nage logolik~o. Ata, at nen tapi-ndomba amiya nogo mban wonok tahun ambi eeke kenok, ne ambit paga unggwagak eeke nagagerak kwe, Keritut perak, "Inake kambikit~o," yinuk, mbogut paga time kulinik unggwi nagak eeke logolik~o.
58009026	At Ala unde inowe nggwok nogo nen tapi-ndomba amiya wonok tahun ambi eeke kenok, unggwagak eeke nagagi kwak, Keritut nen at amiya paga togop eeke logonetak en, at o wakkagagerak kuli nen nok, yogondak kuli yagan wakak mban eeke logonetak kwe, at amiya lombok paga yi maluk ndi maluk abok aret lek eerogo pikit nduk, o age yobok yogondak panggoni wage yi paga, "Inake kambikit~o," yinuk, wambi wage nagagerik, ne ambit paga ninake yagan warogo kambeegerak.
58009027	Nit ne mbere paga kambugun lek~o. Ne ambit mban kambuurak koonak me, ne ambit kanggwi niinok, Ala nen ninowak loonigin nogo ndak-ndak
58009028	Keritut kunduk, nit yi aakumi ndi aakumi abok ninomaluk lek eerogo pikit nduk, wage nagagerik, ne ambit paga ninake kambeegerak me, peebi wage logomenggerik perak, ninomaluk lek eerogo pinanikit nduk, woraagin lek~o. Ata, nit abok at woraawak nduk, tokkogwe nogo ninagap ndarogo wo'niren naakit nduk woraagin~o.
58010001	Wone Muta yoreegerak eerit nogo nogogwaarak nogo ti, eebe lek aret kwe, eebe peebi obeelom ee'ninaburak wone yugu nogo, we ogut wakkagak aret eeko nogogwaarak me, yi tahun ndi tahun tapi-ndomba nogo mendek mban warogo Ala wogogak eekaatak kwe, ti paga it wogori wogo nogogwaarak nogo obeelom ogo logolik.
58010002	It wogori wogo nogogwaarak nogo ti paga obeelom ogo logonetak en, inomaluk inikime aberak wonage nogo, lek a'netak me, peebi ambinom warogo wogori wagak eeko logonetak lek~o.
58010003	-
58010004	Tapi-ndomba amiya ti paga ninomaluk lek eerogo puurak meek~o. Aberak mban wonage kenok, yi tahun ndi tahun tapi-ndomba wonok Ala wogori wagak mban eeko nogogwaarak.
58010005	Togop me, Keritut nggween paga wambi woraakit nduk, at ogoba Ala yoge logonet, "Kat kake warogo wokkugwi inom, yi mendek ndi mendek kat kake pugwi inom, Kat keebi mbake logonet, an neebe aakumi ineebe kwak agago panenok nduk, punogo paneegindak~o.
58010006	Kake warogo kani kunggwi inom, Inomaluk lek aruwak nduk, kake warogo wokkugwi inom, Kat kiniki ale'nggen mbaka'lek keege nagagirik,
58010007	Ai, nogoba Ala~o. An eeriyak nombareegindak mbuku pirik-perek paga liiru mbanak wonage nogo, an neebe nen aret eerikit nduk, agarik~o," yinuk, yoreegerak.
58010008	Keritut nen Ala yoge logonet, "Yi mendek ndi mendek kat kake pugwi, kake warogo wokkugwi, tapi-ndomba warogo enaani kani kumbugwi, aakumi inomaluk lek eerogo piyaanok nduk, warogo wokkiri wogwe, eekwi ti mendek abok aret ti, kat kiniki ale'nggen lek keebi mbake keegak eekwi~o," yinuk, yoreegerak nogo ti, wone Muta yoreegerak aret eekwi kwe kagak, yoge nagagerik, ti'nuk,
58010009	"An eeriyak nombareegindak nogo, an neebe aret eerikit nduk, agarik~o," yinuk, yoreegerak ti paga, it aa'nduk eeko nogogwaarak nogo, lek eerogo punuk, obaane'me peebi alik ambi eeko logowak nduk, tiyappereegerak kogo~o.
58010010	Yetut Keritut nogo nen at Ala eeriyak iniki mbareegerak nogo ndak-ndak aret eeke logonet, ninake kambikit nduk, at eebe ne ambit aret Ala wogoreegerak ti paga, ninomaluk mondok lek eerogo punuk, obeelom agago pinanege nagagerik, nineebe Ala ake leenogo pinaneegerak.
58010011	It aap Ala unde abok aret ko'lu-kii'me kulinik-kalinik aakumi inake eeko logonet, tapi-ndomba nogo mendek mban warogo Ala wogogo nogogwaarak kwe, inomaluk lek aga'lek itok aret wonagagerak.
58010012	At Ala unde Keritut perak, nit abok ninomaluk mondok lek eerogo pikit nduk, "Inake kambikit~o," yinuk, at eebe ne ambit nggaruk togon Ala wogoge nagagerik, Ala eenggi abe'nggan paga kwi'nari laganeegerak logonet,
58010013	Ala nen at inom wim mbanak mendek aan lebenogo abu'me tebenogo piyaawak nduk, tokkage agaarik~o.
58010014	Ala nen at apuri at ake leenogo patiyak mbareegerak nogo, inomaluk abu lek eerogo punuk, mondok obeelom aago logowak nduk, ninake kangge logonet, at eebe ne ambit nggaruk togon Ala wogoreegerak.
58010015	-
58010017	At Aberiniki nen nit yo'nirage logonet, "Ti eyom abu aret age kenok, it Iterali paga wiganak wone ngget mendek ninom koonogo puurak nogo yi aret~o. Eeko logorak yoragagirak nogo inikime nabenogo piige, It inikime liiru negen mbanogo piige, Eerigin~o," yinuk, ari nagagerik, ti'nuk, ambi ari logonet, "It Ala wone taganogo pugwi, Maluk eerit nugwi, eekwi iinok, An aberak logogin lek~o," yereegerak Aberiniki nen yo'niragagerak ti paga, Aberiniki kunduk nit mbakwi ndak-ndak aret mbake menggerak kogo ogoorik~o.
58010018	Togop me, Ala wone taganogo punuk, maluk eeko nogogurak nogo, muk lek eerogo pereegerak me, ambinom lek eerogo puwak nduk, nit nen ambi wogoriyak lek aret kogo~o.
58010019	-
58010020	Togop me noreewi~o.
