Yum oolo tugunik nogo ti, at eebe pogom aret me, ninake kambeegerak ti paga tu ngget mendek yarogo pinanit Mage Lombok Menggim unggwi nage nagagerik, time mondok-mondok eenik logonet, ninake eeke wonage me, at amiya wundeegerak ti paga, nit togon Mage Lombok Menggim nogome ninagabiti lek ungguurak op aret kogo ogoorik~o.
58010021	Nit Ala apuri ninake eekak yuwak nduk, Ala unde ninowe nggwok Ala awi wurik negen mbogut paga wonage me,
58010022	niyo abe mili-mili paga ninabin koorogo pinanege, ndi, maluk eeko nogogurak ninikime aberak logokwak, lek eerogo pinanikit nduk, at amiya paga werenogo pinanege, eereegerak me, "Abet aret panggo yi ungguurak, yegerak," mba'nuk, niniki mondok abe paga at owagam panggo yi ungguwok~o.
58010023	At nen, "Ndogop eeppinagagin~o," yinuk, abok yo'niragagerak nogo, alik ambi koonggak eekeelik, yegetak nogo a'me aret eeke menggerak me, nit eerogo pinaniyak wone abet mba'nuk, waganeegurak niniki lunik wonogwe nogo, mondok nggirik-nggerok agago porogo logowok~o.
58010024	Ndi, niniki-kiniki kunik eekwi, at ambi nen at ambi obeelom eeppegak eekwi, eeko logonet, at ambi nen at ambi kini wuppegak eeko logowok nduk, liippogo logowok~o.
58010025	It aakumi nit Ala wone yogome ninom kuwak eekulik nogo kokwak kit togop eerugup~o. Ata, niniki eyak wat-wat yogwe ti, "Yetut woroorak abu panggo yi wage kagi," mba'nuk, niniki aganggen kerek togon ambinom eeko logowok~o.
58010026	"Ala ndogop menggerak~o," yinuk, wone waganeegurak nineenu logonet kwe, kagak, maluk eeriyak niniki koombunuk eerit mban nogwe niinok, ninomaluk lek eerogo pinanuwak nduk, alik ambi warogo Ala wogoriyak lek me,
58010027	"Ala nen ninowak loonogo punuk, anini ninoba pinanege logonet, kani eyak mondok alik paga at inom ogoorak wonogwe nogo, ineebe pup eerogo piyoorak nogo ti, nit ninom lek eerogo pinanigin kagi," yinuk, ninagabiti mbako logowok~o.
58010028	Aap ambi wone Muta yoreegerak nogo tagangge kenok, aap mbere ilik, kenagan a, nen, "Abet aret ndogop eekerak~o," yogwe iinok, kambuwak nduk, abuwa mbaka'lek mondok warogo pogo menggaarak nogo lek a?
58010029	Togop aret eeko menggaarak me, nit Ala wone koonogo yo'niragagerak nogo, abet mbako logonet, at apuri inomaluk lek eerogo punuk, ake leenak logowak nduk, amiya wundeegerak nogo, aap ambi nen, "Wone ti, abe lek~o," yinuk, Ala aput iyok kenden aambele eerogo negen pege, ndi, at iniki kunik en obeelom eeppinanege menggerak Aberiniki nogo inom miyuk-meya eerogo pege, eeke kenok, at teppigin mbakop? Mondok lek~o. Ala nen maluk onggo mondok alik negen at oba kwippege kaamunggup~o.
58010030	"Aap inane'me wakwi inom, maluk onggo eeppiigwi inom, an nen mban aret eeppiige logogin~o," yinuk, ari, ndi, ambi, "Ala nen at apuri inowak loonogo maluk onggo inoba piyaagin~o," yinuk, ari, yereegerak eebe nogo nineenu aret~o.
58010031	At eenik menggerak Ala nogo nen nit maluk eekwi onggo abera'lek me ninoba kwippinanege nogo ti, mondok iya ninamineeri ne agan nage kagak eeppinanege kaagun~o.
58010032	Kit aa'nduk obeelom wone waganggo mbareegup, kinikime eya eekkinabeegerak me, aaninggin-paaninggin alik negen kinoba pinagagwi iigak, kinogogumbuk logonet, waganggo nogogutak nogo, abeko logonip~o.
58010033	Mondok alik negen eeppinagago logonet, kit ando nggwok paga kinendage miyuk-meya eerogo maluk eeppinagagwi, ndi, it ando inookwi iinok, kinagabiti mbaka'lek, inili yogwe me, kinom aret kinookwi, eeko nogogwaarak nogo~o.
58010034	Kinoreewi ando keele maarak wonogwe nogo, inabuwa mbako logonet, yeenggwaarogwe, ndi, kinamendek ndinggola unggwogwe iigak, "Namendek abe mondok logorak mendek alik ambime wonage aret me, op aret kolaga~o," yinuk, kiniki ale'nggen mbakwi, eeko nogogutak me,
58010035	yogondak kit kinookwi iigak, kinogogumbuk logonet wone abet mba'nuk waganeegutak nogo, mugurok nogwe kiinok, onggo nggwok wokkiraagin me, mbo puurak mage~o.
58010036	-
58010038	At Ala nen ari logonet, "At woroorak nogo ti, elaambirik logonuk woraagin lek~o. At mbet-mbet aret woraagin me, it an napuri iniki abe koonak nogo nen iniki noba panggombunuk abet mbakwi iinok perak, mondok-mondok ineenik aret logogun~o. Ndi, it abet nombakwi nogo mbo pugwi iinok ti, an inabuwa inombarigin lek~o," yinuk, yereegerak me, Ala nen kit eeko logorak kinombareegerak nogo, abu eekwi kiinok, wokkiroorak yereegerak nogo wokkiraawak nduk, maluk eeppinagagwi iigak kwe, kinogogumbuk logonet, waganggo logonip~o.
58010039	It aap wone abet mba'nuk waganeegwaarak nogo, mbo pugwi iinok, Ala nen ineebe lek eerogo piyaagin nogo mendek nit lek~o. Ata, it abet mbakwi iinok, mondok-mondok ineenik logorak nogo mendek nit aret ogoorik~o.
58011001	Nit niniki abet mbakwi eebe ngge~o? Nit niniki abet mbakwi eebe nogo ti, yi mendek ndi mendek nit niniki lunik wonogwe nogo, "Abet aret waagun," mbakwi, ndi, ninigen kaga'lek kwe, "Abet aret wonage," mbakwi, eekwi ti aret~o.
58011002	It ninombomini aa'nduk ndarak nogo ti, Ala yoragagerak wone nogo, "Abet aret kogo~o," yinuk, abet mbakwi iinok, Ala nen, "Aap yi, obeelom aret~o," yinuk, inombake nagagerak.
58011003	At Ala oone paga nen mbogut-nggween wakkagagerak nogo ninigen kogo logonet, "Yi Ala nen aret wakkagagerak~o," yinuk, abet mbakwi paga nineenu ogwe me, yi mendek ndi mendek ninigen kogwe yi, ninigen kaga'lek nogo paga nen wakkagagerak kogo~o.
58011004	At Kayin nogo nen amendek maluk negen Ala ake pi wagagerak kwe, Kaben perak, Ala yoreegerak nogo, "Abet aret yo'nigi," mba'nuk, amendek obeelom mendek warogo Ala ake pi wage mbareegi, ake pi wage nogo Ala enegen kage nagagerik, "Aap yi, iniki abe koonak aret kagi," yinuk, yereegerak. Ndi, at Kaben nogo ti, muk kambeegerak kwe, at abet mba'nuk eereegerak wone nogo nit awo mbininggwi me, ninom wone yogwe negen aret ogoorik~o.
58011005	Aap Enok kunduk, iniki abet mbareegerak paga kambulik Ala nen eenik wonok laganeegerak kagak, oreewi nen kwaareegwaarak mendek lek aret kogogwaarak. Wonok lagangga'lek kagak, "At Ala imbirak iniki kunik wonagagerak~o," yinuk, Ala wone liiru mbanak paga kogo monggoorak nogo~o?
58011006	"Ala abet aret menggerak me, niniki abe paga at owagam nogwe niinok, onggo wo'niraagin," abet aret mbako logonet, at owagam nagak eekwi niinok, inikilom ninombake menggerak kwe, aap ambit-ambi abet mbaka'lek kagak, at owagam nage kenok perak, Ala inikilom ombarigin abu lek~o.
58011007	Aap Nu kunduk, peebi eeriyak awo kin kaga'lek kagak, Ala nen kurumbi yoge mbareegi, "Yi abet aret eeriyak yo'nege kagi," yinuk, ayuk wuke logonet, akwe-apuri inom inagap ndaruwak nduk, o yiiro wureegerak. Ala nen at yoreegerak nogo abet mba'nuk, yiiro wureegerak ti paga, "Kit aakumi maluk eekwi onggo niyo paga kinoorigin~o," yinuk, ineenu eeppiyareegerak me, nit abet mbakwi paga at Ala nen, "Aap yi, iniki abe koonak aret~o," yinuk, yo'nirage nogo ndak-ndak, at Nu iniki abet mbareegerak paga, "Aap yi, iniki abe koonak~o," yinuk, yereegerak.
58011008	Ndi, at Abarakam kunduk, Ala nen, "Eyate kwak nggween ambi kat unde logonok nduk, wokkirigin me, nak~o," yoge mbareegi, o ti, eenggo'lek kwe kagak, "Abet aret wo'nirigin," mba'nuk, nagagerak.
58011009	-
58011010	"O wokkirigin~o," yoreegim nogome aret nagagerak logonet kwe, "O yi ti lek~o. Ala nen o kota alik ambi mondok logorak mendek ogobakkigirikit koombunuk, ogobakkigiremenggerak nogome, an aret unde eeppanigin~o," yinuk, abet mba'nuk, tokkage logonet, Itak Yakup imbirak inom ineyate kwak kolaawak nduk, yoragagerak me, it inom aap nggiru kwak ooliya wuppunuk, ya nogo yegak nda nogo yegak eerit nugu nogogwaarak.
58011011	At kwe Tara kunduk, abu kweegelo aagaluk ndariyak meek aret kwe, at Abarakam nen, "Ala yegetak ndak-ndak eeke menggerak me, yo'niragaarak nogo abet aret eeppinanigin kagi," mbareegerak paga Ala nen akwe nogo agabolo ki eeppege mbareegi, Abarakam apuluk aret ndareegerak.
58011012	Ndi, aap Abarakam nogo apuluk ndaka'lek me, kambeegerak negen wonagagerak kwe, iniki abet mbareegerak paga ombowologwe laaluguragan mbogut paga wonage kwak, mbini kale'ngga yi aa'nggi paga wonage ineenggi lingginiyak meek kwak, nogo ndak-ndak aap ambit Abarakam paga ombowologwe aret wigannogogwaarak.
58011013	It aap ti abok aret, "Wokkiraagin~o," yoragagerak wone nogo, agalu'mok negen o nda taati wage inigen nakkogo nogogwaarik, "Nogo yi aret ee'ninabi wage kogo~o," yinuk, iniki ale'nggen mbako logonet, "Nit aap o nggween paga yime ninaworak wonogwe lek~o. Aap nggiru negen aret ogoorik~o," yinuk, wone yugu eebe liirogon woolik kwe, "Abet aret wo'niraagin~o," yinuk, iniki abet mbareegwaarak ti paga, eebe waganeegwaarak negen aret logonet, kambit nogo nogogwaarak.
58011014	It aakumi togop yogwe paga inanggween alik ngget mendek it logowam kwaakkologo logonet, yogo menggaarak iigo~o.
58011015	It aap ti, inawi alom paga mbo pereegwaarak nogo, iniki aberak logonetak en, yungguninuk inawi alom paga nanetak op kwe, togop mbarulik~o.
58011016	It iniki nen, "Nit ninawi abe mbogut paga kola nawok lak ao," yinuk, miippunuk, kambit nogo mbareegwa, Ala nen it iniki mbareegwaarak nogo ndak-ndak inawi abe kota negen pipuk eerogo piyareegerak wonage me, "Ninogoba Ala~o, yinuk, yo'nogo logorak op aret," mbake menggerak.
58011017	-
58011019	Ala nen Abarakam abut mbanikit nduk yoge logonet, "Kaput warogo an nake kani kumbu~o," yoge mbareegi, Abarakam nen, "Kaput Itak paga nen kombowologwe apit wigannarugun~o, yinuk, yo'nege mbaki, abet aret mbakirak kwe, Waru~o, yo'nege me, nonggop togon wari?" ti mbarulik. Ata, "Ala nen kanggaatak ineenik eerogo mippiige menggerak neenu me, togop aret eenik eerogo mippigin kagi," yinuk, abet mbake logonet, "Naput ambolom ndarak yi kagak aret warikit," mbareegerak. Ndi, Ala nen kanggaatak ineenik agago mippiige menggerak abet mbareegerak nogo ndak-ndak, iniki nen abu warikit mbareegerak ti paga abet aret wakerak mba'nuk, Ala nen eenik agago mippereegerak negen aret mbaruwok~o.
58011020	Aap Itak nen, "O peebi Ala nen togop eeppinagage kaamunggup~o," yinuk, Ala yoreegerak nogo abet mbake logonet, ale'nggen Yakup Etawu imbirak inoba piyareegerak.
58011021	Ndi, Yakup kunduk, kambikit nduk eeke logonet, "Ala nen eeriyak yo'niragagerak nogo eerigin aret~o," yinuk, abet mba'nuk, Yutup apuri inalitak lombok ale'nggen inoba piige nagagerik, owaanggun paga anep kumbunuk Ala alut eereegerak.
58011022	Ndi, Yutup kunduk, kambuurak eeke mbareegi, Ala nen wone at yoreegerak nogo abet mbake nagagerik, yorage logonet, "Kit Iterali mendek o Metit yime logomunggup lek~o. Wundi namunggup aret me, wundi nogo logonet, an nowak nenenak inom wonok namunggup~o," yinuk, eenik logonet, wone abet mbareegerak paga awoneninu kiliriragagerak.
58011023	Muta agalo-ogoba kunduk, Ala nen eeriyak wone yugu nogo abet mba'nuk, elege Muta nda'nagagerak mondok abe amuni mbanak kogo nogogwaarik, aap endagembogut wone lengganeegerak nogo inagabiti mbaka'lek logonet, kumaappi nogogwaarak kagak, tut kenagan peneneegerak nogo~o.
58011024	Ti'nuk, peebi Muta nogo tawe age nagagerik, wone yoragagerak nogo mban abet mbake nagagerik, "Pirawun apuluk nogo aagaluk yo'niriyak ti neebi," mba'nuk,
58011025	-
58011026	"Peebi Ala nen onggo wo'nirigin~o," yinuk, iniki aberak logonet, "O Metit yime yi mendek ndi mendek abe mban wonage yi, iya lek~o. Ata, Keritut nen peebi eeppinaniyak tokkogwe ti, meek ninombakwi kwe, peebi eeppinaniyak ambi wonage me, iya~o," mba'nuk, maluk eerit nogo logonet, ne ambiriluk inikilom mbako menggaarak mendek nogo mbo punuk, Ala apuri aaninggin-paaninggin inoba piige nogo, "An ninom aret eeppanugo logowak~o," yinuk, miippunuk, Iterali wonogwe me, nagagerak.
58011027	Ala nen yoreegerak nogo, abet aret mbake nagagerik, "Aap endagembogut anini nen nooke kenok ti, nooruwak aret~o," yinuk, o Metit mbo punuk, agabiti lek aret wundi nagagerak. Ninigen kaga'lek mendek nogo, at enegen kage negen aret eereegerak me, mondok ogogumbuk a'nuk, mugurok nage nagagerak.
58011028	At malayikat aakumi inooke menggerak nogo nen, it aakumi o Metit mendek inapuri manggu ndarak inoorit nage logonet, Iterali mendek inom inooke kero, Ala yoreegerak nogo, at Muta abet mba'nuk, laago Obaga Mbo Noorak lako logonet, tu nggambe paga amiya labunogo pit nagagerak nogo~o.
58011029	Ala nen yoragagerak nogo abet mbako logonet, nggween woloonak paga nugu mengga kwak, Iterali mendek nogo niyo Merah yenggenak paga wunda wogo mbareegwa, it Metit mendek nen togop aret wunda woraawok nduk, eekwi me, niyo ndonggoninabeegerak~o.
58011030	Ala nen yoragagerak nogo abet mbako logonet, o Yeriko yengget-wangget eekwi iigak, nogo 6 yippunuk, ko'lu 7 paga yugum pak wurik nogo langgu-langgu wambit nagagerak.
58011031	Kwe yawukak Arakap kunduk, Ala nen it Iterali mendek eeppiige nogo, aruk konembunuk, iniki abet aret mbake nagagerik, aap o pekkaawok nduk wogogwaarak nogo, iniki obeelom paga kumaappiyareegerak me, peebi it aap Ala wone taganeegwaarak nogo inooko logonet, at kwe nogo teppereegwaarak.
58011032	Ndi, ambi ngge inom yokkira~o. Lek~o. It aap Nggireyon kunduk, Mbarak kunduk, Timeton kunduk, Yepeta kunduk, Ndawut kunduk, Temuwen kunduk, Ala nen yorage kagak yoraga kunduk, it abok aret togop mban Ala nen it yoragagerak wone abet mbareegwaarak paga, iya negen eeko nogogwaarak nogo mbininogo yokkiroorak op aret kwe, oonegen lek age me mbo~o.
58011033	It aap ti, Ala nen yoragagerak abet mbareegwaarak paga, it aap inendagembogut inabu'me piigo menggam tebenogo piigwi, obeelom eerit nogo logonet, a'me nggelok eeko logowak nduk, koonogo piigwi, Ala nen yoragagerak nogo ndak-ndak aret waganggwi, aakumi inooka singa nogo inambe keele maarogo piigwi,
58011034	kani omoonuk eyak ambik kwe, naganak-paganak eerogo pugwi, tege wooluwak paga inooriyak nduk eekaatak kwe, melak togon woppatinuk nggarek yogwe, ndeyak aganaketak kwe inomaawi eekkologwe, ndi, waka'ngget a'nuk wim nambuko logonet aap inanebunu alik mendek inawuri yigin unde nogo mondok mugogo wumbiinet nugwi, eerit nogo nogogwaarak.
58011035	It kumi ando inaagalogwe kanggaatak ineenik agago wogorogwe, ndi, it ando perak, "Peebi nineenik mondok logorak mippinanigin me, ninili eerogo teppinaniyak mage~o. Mondok-mondok ninooko logonip~o," yogwe iinok, iniki mondok alik negen taganak-mbaganak eerogo inookwi iinok kanggwi,
58011036	it ando miyuk-meya eerogo piinok yawi inookwi, ando mbutigeele paga ineenggi-iniyok maarogo mambiigo menggam mambiigwi,
58011037	it ando yugum paga iniki togu eerogo inookwi, ando nggege paga inobate mbanogo piigwi, ando tege wooluwak paga inookwi, ando inayum abu lek kenok, ndomba-kambin inagabolo mbelanogo inayum yirippunuk, mbi abu nugwi iigak, "Aap maluk me," nduk, inogole yogo logonet, maluk eerogo piigwi, eeko nogogwaarak.
58011038	Aap ti abu obeelom aret me, o maluk nggween paga yime nugu logorak meek kwe, kagak, karume inom, eyonggaame inom, mbaganit nugu logonet, "O nggeeme nogo yi na~o," yinuk, mbuun ambena inom, ndoome inom, ugun nogo yit nugu nogogwaarak.
58011039	-
58011040	It aap ti abok aret Ala yoragagerak nogo abet mbako logonet, eerit nogo nogogwaarak paga Ala nen, "Aap yi obeelom aret," inombake nagagerak kwe, at Ala nen nit awo niigak it inaa'nduk obeelom eeppiyoorak mbarulik~o. Ata, nit ninom ambugwi obeelom eeppinaniyak op mbareegerak me, wone yoragagerak nogo, eeppiiga'lek kagak, kambit nogo nogogwaarak.
58012001	It aap abet mba'nuk, eeko nogogwaarak yogoorak nogo nen, "Nit eeko nogogurak nogo ndak-ndak eekwi iyaamun ilik, lek a?" yinuk, ineebe apit aago wanggerak inigen wo'ninakwi negen wonogwe me, tu mbe agan nogo logonet, ninogowa lek age kero, yi mendek ndi mendek ninoba luurik wonage nogo inom, maluk mendek kagak, nit eeriyak ninikilom mbako logonet, yilinogo pinanege menggerak nogo mendek inom, abok aret nggonenogo mbo punuk, "Mbe agan ti kuli aret mi'nari nanip~o," yinuk, yo'niragagerak nogo, mondok ninogogumbuk a'nuk, mbe agan mi'nari nogo logowok~o.
58012002	Ndi, aa'nduk nit abet mba'nuk Ala wone waawok nduk niniki pipuk eerogo pinanege, ti'nuk, abet mbakwi niinok, niniki mondok kole eerogo pinanege, eeke menggerak ti, Yetut aret me, at mban ninigen loorit mugurok nogo logowok~o. It aap eyo karo-karo paga nabenogo piigwi iinok, "Aap mondok maluk mendek aret~o," yogo menggaarak nogo, at Yetut nen, "An togop nombariyak me, neebi~o," ti mbarulik. Ata, "Peebi nale'nggen nggwok kaagin me, yogondak we luulu togop ee'naburak op aret~o," yinuk, ogogumbuk a'nuk, eyo karo-karo paga kangge nagagerik, eenik a'nuk, Ala wone lengganogo yorage menggim Ala eenggi abe'nggan paga kwi'nari laganeegerak wonage~o.
58012003	It aap maluk eeko menggaarak nogo nen Yetut mondok ineebi mbako logonet, maluk eeppugwi iigak, at ogogumbuk logonet, wagangge nagagerak me, kit ta'liila eekkinake logonet, kineebi eekkinake kero, at eereegi kwak eeko logobagip nduk, liippogo logonip~o.
58012004	It aap maluk eeko menggaarak nen at Yetut nogo ti, maluk eeppugwi iigak, onggo yoraga'lek iniki yanggonak paga wagangge kagak, amiya wunogo wako mbareegwa, mondok kambeegerak kwe, kit perak, togop aret kinookwi kwe, kangga'lek aret ogotik~o.
58012005	-
58012006	At Ala nen, "Yi an napuri aret~o," yinuk, kiniki eyak wappinagakit nduk, yokkirage logonet, "Napuri wae. Kinogoba Ala nen it aap at iniki kunik nogo iniki koonnaruwak nduk, eeppiige, Ndi, Yi an napuri aret~o, yinuk, yorage nogo alik eekwi iinok, yawi inooke, Eeke menggerak me, Kiniki koonnaruwak nduk, eeppinagage kenok, Eeppinanege yi, iya lek~o, yinuk, meek mbakwi, Ndi, kinaruk wake kenok, kiniki maluk ogwe, eerugup~o," yinuk, yereegerak nogo kit kobak ogotak kiigi~o.
58012007	Wologwe iniki koonnaruwak nduk, inogobamini nen inaruk waka'lek ambi wonogolik~o. Tigitogon inapuri inaruk wako menggaarak me, Ala nen kiniki koongginabikit nduk, eeke kenok, "An at aput abet aret wonage neenok, nabuwa nen eeppanege kagi~o," yinuk, kiniki kwi'ndak logonet, waganggo logonip~o.
58012008	Nit Ala apuri kenok abok aret niniki koonnaruwak nduk, ninaruk wake menggerak me, kit ambi kinaruk waka'lek kenok perak, "Nit at apuri lek we terak ndarak aret wonogwe," mbarumunggup~o.
58012009	Ndi ambi, nit ninogobamini abe nda'ninabeegwaarak nogo nen niniki koonnaruwak nduk, ninaruk wakwi iinok, inoone liirogon konembunuk, eeko monggo kwak, at niniki lombok unde menggerak ninogoba Ala oone yo'nirage nogo, liirogon konembunuk ndak-ndak eekwi niinok, mondok-mondok nineenik logogun lek mbakop? Lek~o. Nineenik logogun aret~o.
58012010	Ninogobamini abe nda'ninabeegwaarak nogo nen, "Abe eeko logowak nduk eeppiyoorak yi aret kogo," yinuk, iniki koombunuk, luulu ninaruk wako menggaarak kwe, ninogoba Ala perak, at maluk eekeelik mondok alik leenak obeelom menggi kwak, nit togop ndak-ndak aret logowok nduk, liippunuk, niniki koonninake menggerak.
58012011	Nit niniki koonninaburak nduk ee'ninake nogo ti, ee'ninake kagak, niniki ale'nggen ee'ninaka'lek we ti eyom paga niniki puru ari mban kogo monggoorak kwe, "Yi op aret ee'ninake~o," yinuk, liippunuk, waganggwi niinok perak, eyoonggen abe yi'nage menggi kwak, nit togon obeelom eerit noorak mamunggolamonggoorak paga niniki ugun tayenak ale'nggen aret logogun~o.
58012012	Togop me, kinaganak nuk-nuk kirage logonet, kineenggi-kiniyok ndeyak eekkinake nogo kinomaawi eekkologo logomonggotik,
58012013	kiniyok andi nogo abunuk andi eekkinake kero, obeelom aruwak nduk, tu abe mot-mot yarak paga nogo logonip~o.
58012014	Maluk ninikime wonage kagak, ninowe ninigen koorak mondok meek me, yi aap ndi aap abok kinom lambunik kiniki ale'nggen logonet, maluk eeka'lek Ala ake leenak obeelom mban logobagip nduk, wakkagak eeko logonip~o.
58012015	Ala iniki kunik en obeelom eeppinaneegerak nogo mbo pugwi kiyo, liippogo logonip~o. Iri'ngga ale warak mendek ambi mbiingga larak paga pegaatak me, mbiingga apit ale age menggi kwak, aap ambi kinenggela'me oone togop agan nege kenok, kit aakumi apit at oone konembunuk, maluk eeriyak koonggwi kiyo, liippogo logonip~o.
58012016	Kit ambi kumi ugun-ugun eeginabit nugwi, ndi, aap Etawu nogo nen Ala wone taganogo punuk, maluk eereegi kwak eerit nugwi, eekwi kiyo, liippogo logonip~o. At Etawu nogo nen manggu ndarak kenok ineebe obeelom logowak nduk, awoneninu kiligirogo me-nggaarak nogo, "Nawuluk kat kilikkiruwak nduk, onggo mbi larak ti, an wo'niru~o," yoge mbareegi, wogoreegerak nogo ne ambit aret nengge nagagerik,
58012017	ti'nuk peebi, "Nogoba awone kili'niriyak neebi yagarak nogo, wo'niruwak lak ao," yinuk, le ari logonet, eereegerak nogo mbo punuk, alik ambi kolaakit nduk, wakkagak mban eereegerak kwe, "Woorak neebi," mbareegerak me, Ala nen at eebe mbo aret pereegerak.
58012018	-
58012021	Aakumi Iterali mendek puut Tinayi abu'me wogo mbareegwa, kani omoonuk wunuk ari, kaluk kwiragan lagangge, o apit age, o wiya nen nombok-kombok eeke, oone nggwok eeka trompet nogo oonebu eeke, eeke kagak, Ala oone nggwok paga yorage logonet, "Wam a, aakumi a, puut yi abu'me woraanuk, mbaanggogwe iinok, yugum paga mondok wariyak~o," yinuk, yorage mbareegi, inagabiti nen, "Wone ambinom yo'niroorak mage ubi," yinuk, yereegwaarak. Ndi, aakumi inagabiti mbaruwak nduk, Ala nen iya tit eeke nogo, Muta kage nagagerik, "An kunduk nagabiti nen naganak wake agarik~o," yinuk, yereegerak. It aakumi inom, Muta inom, inagabiti mbaruwak nduk, eereegerak nogo kokwak, kit yogondak Ala owagam nogwe kiinok, togop eerigin lek~o.
58012022	Kit yogondak puut alik Tiyon abu'me at eenik menggerak Ala nogo agota Yerutalem mbogut paga nogome aret ka nogogutak negen aret wonogwe~o. It yi malayikat ndi malayikat nineenggi lingginiyak meek mondok iya lombok kuwak eerak logonet, inale'nggen paga eekwi ineebe inom,
58012023	it aa'nduk abet mbareegwaarak Ala apuri kuwak eeko nogogwaarak inendage mbogut paga liiru mbanak ineebe inom, nit aakumi abok ninawone amburu mbanogo ninowak loongga Ala nogo inom, it aakumi iniki abe koonak logonet, kambeegwaarak obeelom eerogo piyareegerak inogoma inom,
58012024	ndi, Ala ninom lambuniyak nduk, wone ngget mendek koonogo ninake eeka Yetut nogo inom, time aret kuwak eerak wonogwe me, iya nogogutak negen aret wonogwe~o. Kit Kaben amiya wambeegim ambi eeppinaniyak meek nogome nogogutak lek~o. Ata, kit obeelom eekkinaburak Yetut amiya abe kilireegim nogome aret nogogutak me,
58012025	at nen wone yokkirage nogo konembunuk, mbo pugup~o. Liirogon aret porogo logonip~o. At nggween paga logonet, Ala nen eeriyak mbareegerak nogo yorage mbareegi, "Nineebi~o," yinuk, mbo pogo mbareegwa, Ala nen teppiyoolik mondok inooreegerak me, yogondak at mbogut paga wonage nogo nen wone yo'nirage nogo mbo pugwi niinok, nit teppinanigin mbakop? Lek~o. Mondok ninoorigin aret~o.
58012026	Ti eyom paga yorage logonet, o nggween yi nogo, na'ndo-wa'ndo eereegerak kwe, yogondak perak, peebi ambi eeriyak ari logonet, "An ne ambi paga nggween yi mban na'ndo-wa'ndo eerigin lek~o. Ata, mbogut inom togop aret eeke neyaamunggup~o," yinuk, yo'niragagerak.
58012027	"Ne ambi paga eeriyak~o," yinuk, wone yo'niragagerak nogo ti, yi mendek ndi mendek nu'lek wonage kenok, mondok nu'lek logowak nduk, teppege logonet, nuk-nuk ari kenok mbo pikit nduk, ne ambi paga yi mendek ndi mendek wakkagagerak abok aret na'ndo-wa'ndo eerikit nduk, yereegerak kogo~o.
58012028	-
58012029	Togop me, Ala abu'me piige menggim nit unde logorak mbareegerak nogo ti, nuk-nuk ariilik me, "Ala wa," yinuk, keyage wako logowok~o. Ninogoba Ala ti, kani omoonuk nen iri'ngga mondok pup eerogo nenet nage menggi kwak aret me, ninagabiti nen ayuk wuko logonet, at eeriyak inikilom mbake nogo mban aret eerit nogo logowok~o.
58013001	Kit Ala apuri aret wonogwe me, niniki-kiniki kunik eekwi nogo, lek age kero, liirogon aret eeko logonip~o.
58013002	It aakumi nen malayikat mendek kagak, "Yi aakumi aret~o," yinuk, kobak logonet inabugo lako nogogwaarak me, it aakumi nggiru kiya wogwe iinok, keyage warogo kiniki ale'nggen paga wogonako logonip~o.
58013003	It aakumi keele maarak wonogwe nogo, "An ninom keele maarak negen wonage kagi," yinuk, yeenggwaarogwe, ndi, aakumi nen yawi paga inookwi iinok, andi kogwe nogo, "An kunduk, togop aret noo'netak en, andi kaanetak~o," yinuk, iniki eyak wappiigwi, eeko logonip~o.
58013004	It aap kumi kundugume wurinabit nugwi, komologwe tawe ugun wurinabit nugwi, eekwi iinok, Ala nen inowak loonogo maluk onggo wogoraagin me, aap ambi akwe koloorak nduk, lambumbiigwi nogo ti, abu obeelom aret me, tiyappuurak aret~o. Ndi, kolage logomenggerik, imbirak nogo yuurak ti kunduk, abu obeelom mban aret me, nogo yugu menggam maluk age kero, arum liirogon logowak~o.
58013005	-
58013006	At Ala nen ari logonet, "An teppinagage, eraanggi mbo pinagage, eerigin lek~o," yinuk, yereegerak me, wu mban uugwe-uugwe mbarit nugwi paga wu ti, ayeloman eekkinabukwak, liippogo logonip~o. Kinamendek nano mendek ambi wonage kenok, "Yi abu aret wonage~o," yinuk, kiniki tayenak logonet, ale'nggen paga nugu logomunggup~o. Ala nen, "An mbo pinagagin lek~o," yinuk, yereegerak wone ti paga niniki panggombunuk, "Ninogoba nen yeenggwaanirage menggerak me, aakumi nen an eeppanugwi nogo, an nagabiti mbarigin lek~o," yinuk, yogo logorak ti op aret~o.
58013007	It aa'nduk togon Ala wone yokkirogo nogogwaarak kinogobamini nogo, inoba abeko logonet, it abet mba'nuk obeelom eerit nugu nogogwaarik, kambit nogogwaarak nogo, liippunuk, kit togop ndak-ndak abet mba'nuk eerit nogo logonip~o.
58013008	Maan inom, yogondak inom, peebi inom, at Yetut Keritut alik ageelik mondok itok aret menggerak~o.
58013009	Yi wone ndi wone alik agan wogwe nogo konembunuk, kiniki nomonggiren nogwe iyo, liippogo logonip~o. It ando nen, "Yi mendek ndi mendek nonggo logonet, Yogop ee'nu, ndogop ee'nu," yinuk, wone lengganak nogo eekwi paga iniki kole eekkolaga'lek we aanom warogo eerit nogwe me, kit nen yogo logonet, "Wone ti paga niniki kole ee'ninaburak lek~o. Ata, Ala iniki kunik en eeppinanege kagak niniki kole ariyak ti, op aret~o," yinuk, mbako logonip.
58013010	It ooliya wuppunuk, Ala unde logonet, aakumi inake eeko menggaarak nogo nen nit Ala ake warogo wogogo monggom ndomba ninake warak yi, it na woroorak mondok lek~o.
58013011	At Ala unde inowe nggwok nogo nen aakumi inomaluk lek aruwak nduk, Ala ake ndomba wappunuk, amiya wonok Mage Lombok Menggim pi unggwage kagak, eebe yagat endekem kani kunggo nogogwaarak nogo ndak-ndak,
58013012	Yetut kunduk, at amiya paga nit aakumi ninomaluk lek eerogo punuk, Ala ake leenogo pinanikit nduk, yagan warogo o kota endekem aret kambeegerak.
58013013	Togop me, at o kota endekem ninake kambikit nduk nage kagak miyuk-meya eerogo pogo nogogwaarak nogo kokwak, nit kunduk ti ndak-ndak miyuk-meya eerogo pinanugwi iigak, at mugurok o kota endekem aret wundi nawok~o.
58013014	Nit niname kota mondok-mondok logorak nogo nggween paga yime wonage lek~o. Ata, niname kota alik ambime nawok nduk, we luulu tokkogo ogoorik~o.
58013015	Togop me, eyoonggen abe yi'nage menggi kwak, "Yetut ninowe aret~o," yinuk, Keritut ninake eereegerak paga Ala ake warogo wogogwi negen, nit kulinik-kalinik ninoone paga Ala alut eeko logonet, endage tiyappegak mban eeko logowok~o.
58013016	Ndi, ti eeko logonet, Ala ake warogo wogogo nogogwa kwak, at ake aakumi obeelom eeppiigwi, yeenggwaarogwe, eekwi niinok, Ala inikilom ninombake menggerak me, mari eerogo puurak ti mage~o. Ata, eeppiinet nogo logonip~o.
58013017	It kinogobamini nogo ti, "Aakumi nonggop inarum wonogotak~o, yinuk, Ala nen yo'niraagin," mba'nuk, liirogon aret kiniki arum wonogwe me, inabu'me logonet, wone yokkirogwe nogo, liirogon aret konenggo logonip~o. It inoone konengga'lek wonogwe kiinok, inale'nggen lek logonet, kinarum liirogon wonogwe lek paga maluk aret eekwi kiyoorak me, iniki ale'nggen paga kinarum logowak nduk, inoone liirogon aret konenggo logonet, obeelom eeppiigo logonip~o.
58013018	Ninake tamban mban eeko logonip~o. Nit obeelom eerit nogo logorak mban, "Ao," mbako monggoorak me, yi eekak ndi eekak eeko logonet, maluk eekoorak ambi ninikime abe'naga'lek kenok, "Obeelom aret eerit nogo monggoorak kogo," yinuk, mbako ogoorik~o.
58013019	Ala nen an mbet-mbet kinowagam nappani woraawak nduk, "Nake tamban mban eeko logorak ao," mbake logonet yokkiragi~o, noreewi.
58013020	Ndi, yogondak abu aret~o, noreewi. Nit niniki ugun tayenak ale'nggen logowok nduk eeppinanege menggerak Ala nogo nen wone koonogo yo'niragagerak nogo, "Mondok-mondok eerigin~o," yinuk, abet mbako logowok nduk, ndomba mondok liirogon ndegenninake menggerak ninowe Yetut nogo, ninake amiya kili'nage mbareegi, kambunuk nogo menggam nen eenik agago mippereegerak me,
58013021	at Ala eeriyak mbake menggerak nogo, kit mondok ndak-ndak eeko logobagip nduk, yi mendek ndi mendek abe mendek kenok mban li'luk eerogo wokkirage, ndi, Yetut Keritut eereegerak paga kit eeppinagarak inikilom mbake menggerak nogo eeppinagage, eeke logogin me, at endage mondok-mondok tiyappogo logowok~o. Amin!
58013022	Noreewi~o. Kit eeko logorak an wone mbuuluk liiru mbanggiragi yi, kiniki abe paga waganggo logobagip nduk, yokkiragi~o.
58013023	Ninore Timotiyut keele maarak wonagagerak nogo, muk piinogo pereegwaarak kineenu arubagip nduk, yokkiragi~o. At mbet-mbet an neya wage kenok, nimbirak aret kiya woraagun~o.
58013024	It kinarum menggaarak inom, it abet mbakwi Ala apuri inom, abok aret, "At nen, Wa! yokkiragi, yegerak," yoraanip~o. Ndi, it aap o Italiya mendek ninom wonogwe nogo, abok ninom nen keyage wakkinako~o.
58013025	Ala iniki kunik en eeppinagage logonet, kinarum logogin~o. Abu aret yokkiragi~o. Wa!
59001001	Kit Yakuri kinanebunu 12 mendek yi o ndi o mbaganit nogogutak nogo, an Yakobut nen ninogoba Ala ninowe Yetut Keritut imbirak inayeloman logonet, keyage wappinagagi~o.
59001002	Nowe-nawot~o. Aaninggin-paaninggin kinoba age kenok, kiniki ale'nggen mban mbako logonip~o.
59001003	Kit abet mbakwi kiinok, kinabut mbangge me, aaninggin-paaninggin kinoba age kagak, kiniki kwi'na'nuk waganggo logonet, "Niniki nu'lek eerogo pinanit unggwage logowak nduk eeke kagi," yinuk, kinale'nggen mban mbako logonip~o.
59001004	Kit kiniki mondok kole eekkinake, ndi, abu obeelom eekkinake, eeke nogo ambi yobok yigin lek abok ndak-ndak eekkinabuwak nduk aaninggin-paaninggin kinoba age me, kiniki kwi'ndak logonet, waganggo logonip~o.
59001005	Kit nen eeriyak ambi kineenggo'lek kenok, "Ala yo'nip~o." Yogwi kiinok, at eebi mbakeelik yanggonak paga yi aakumi ndi aakumi abok aret kalo logonogo wogorage menggerak nogo nen ambi eerumunggup nduk, kineenu eeppinagage logogin~o.
59001006	Kit Ala yogo logonet, kiniki yungguppegak eeka'lek mondok abet mbako logonet, yogo logonip~o. Aap ambi iniki yungguppegak eeke logonet, Ala yoge kenok ti, o wiya wage logonet, niyo kilaarak-mogonik eeke menggerak nogo pogom aap ti, iniki togop aret menggerak~o.
59001007	-
59001008	Aap ti, iniki mbere logonet, yi eeriyak ndi eeriyak koonit nage me, iniki tayenak logogin lek iniki mbere logonet, Ala yoge me, "Wo'nirigin lek kagi," yinuk, mbake logowak~o.
59001009	-
59001011	Oonegen wundi wage logonet, mo andi nen iri'ngga-kale'ngga teebat age nagaatik, mono-mono wangge logonet, etenggen maluk negen age menggi kwak, it aap ineenggi warak eekkolaawok nduk, eerit nugwi iinok, ineebe togop aret lek arugun me, kit noreewi Ala apuri ando kineenggi lek me kinendage tebenak wonogwe nogo, kineenggi warak age logonet, kinendage tiyak ari kenok, "Ala nen aret eeppanege~o," yinuk, kiniki tebenak logonet, ale'nggen mbakwi, ndi, kit ando kineenggi warak me, kinendage tiyanak wonogwe nogo, kinamendek lek age logonet, kinendage tebek ari kenok, "Iri'ngga-kale'ngga lek age menggi kwak, ninendage togop aret lek age me, op aret~o," yinuk, kiniki obeelom logonet, ale'nggen mbakwi, eeko logonip~o.
59001012	It aakumi inabut mbangge kagak nu'lek wonogwe kenok, inale'nggen aret mbako logowak~o. It aakumi inabut mbangge kagak nu'lek wonogwe nogo, op eekwi iinok, nggare-nggare mendaarak yippiigo mengga kwak, "Kineenik mondok logorak mendek wokkiraagin~o," yinuk, abok yoragagerak ti, it aakumi Ala iniki kunik eekwi nogo, aret wogoraagin~o.
59001013	At Ala nen, "An maluk ambi eerikit," mbake, ndi, aakumi maluk eeruwak nduk, iniki nggaganogo piige, eekeelik me, aap ambit-ambi iniki nggagangge kenok, "Yi Ala nen niniki nggagangge~o," yinuk, yuurak ti mondok mage~o.
59001014	Nit niniki nggagangge nogo ti, aap ambi maluk eeruwak nduk, oone amburu puk-puk niikkenok nage menggi kwak, nit niniki nen eeriyak uugwe mba'nuk aret eeko monggoorak~o.
59001015	Ndi, kwe ambi elege inikime logombunuk, ndaketak nogo, ti'nuk, eebe kole a'nuk, kangge menggi kwak, nit niniki nen aret maluk eeriyak uugwe mba'nuk, eebe eeko nogootik, ti'nuk, nineebe aret kanggo monggoorak.
59001016	Nowe-nawot~o. Kit an niniki kunik me, kiniki nomongginakwi iyo, liippogo logonip~o.
59001017	Ninabuwa nen obeelom eeppinanege inom, wo'niroorak mbake nogo mondok ndak-ndak wo'nirage inom, abok aret agi nen mban wuppinani wage menggerak. Yi o ndi o abok aret eya eeke menggerak alom at ninogoba Ala nen aret wuppinani wage menggerak. At ambi agak eeke logonet, ne ambi paga o yumaak negen age, ne ambi paga o eya negen age, eekeelik mondok itok eya mban aret menggerak.
59001018	At nen yi mendek ndi mendek wakkaakit mbareegerak nogo tebenak kagak, it aakumi mban tiyanak logowak nduk, "Aap aa'nduk obeelom eerogo piyaakit~o," yinuk, oone yereegerak nogo paga iniki mbareegerak ndak-ndak eeke logonet, aa'nduk nit aakumi aret obeelom eerogo pinaneegerak.
59001019	-
59001020	Nowe-nawot~o. Kit an niniki kunik me, wone yi, liirogon waganggo logonip~o. Nit abe koonak mban eerit nogo logorak Ala nen ninombareegerak nogo ti, ninanini paga eerit nogo logorak lek me, kit abok aret wone mbet-mbet konenggo logorak op aret kwe, yuurak kenok perak, liippunuk yogwe, kinanini mbet-mbet wungga'lek logonet eekwi, eeko logonip~o.
59001021	Eeriyak lek mendek peyak wurik pogom kagak ugun eekwi, ndi, yi maluk ndi maluk eekwi, eeko monggotak nogo abok aret mbo punuk, kiniki yanggonak logonet, wone ninagap ndariyak wone Ala nen ninikime awi yappinanege menggerak wone nogo mban liirogon waganggo logonip~o.
59001022	Ala wone kinaruk mban konenggwi kenok, kit aret kinambokan laganggologwe me, kinaruk mban konenggak eeko logorak ti mage~o. Ata, konembunuk, eebe aret eeko logonip~o.
59001023	Ala wone liippunuk, eeka'lek we kinaruk mban konenggwi kenok ti, aap ambi pugagi paga etenggen pekkolage nogo pogom kit aret~o.
59001024	Aap ti nogo, etenggen pekkolage nagaatik, nage logonet, "Netenggen togop kagarak~o," yinuk, abe'naga'lek mbet-mbet kobak age menggerak kwe,
59001025	Ala wone li'luk eerogo yo'niragagerak paga wondet agago pinanege menggerak wone nogo, li'lak pekkolage logomenggerik, kobak aga'lek liirogon woppunuk eeke logomenggerak kenok, Ala nen ale'nggen ambik aap ti, oba pege logogin~o.
59001026	Kit ambi nen, "An Ala wone liippunuk eeke agarik~o," yinuk, yogo monggotak kwe, kinambe liirogon arum wonaga'lek kinamili irip paga ugun agan nugwi kiinok, kit aret kinambokan laganggologwe, ndi, "An Ala wone liippunuk eeke agarik~o," yogo monggotak nogo ti, aanom warogo aret yogwe, eeko monggotak kiigi~o.
59001027	It aap Ala oone liippunuk mondok abe eekwi iinok, ninogoba Ala nen ale'nggen mbake menggerak nogo ti, it wologwe-komologwe wenebela inom, kumi togwe inom, iniki aaninggin wonogwe iinok, inabuwa nen yeenggwaaranet nugwi, it aakumi iniki maluk nen maluk eeruwak nduk iniki nggagani wogwe iyo, tum wakkologwe, eeko menggaarak nogo it aret~o.
59002001	Nowe-nawot~o. At abu tiyanak menggerak ninowe Yetut Keritut nogo, kiniki oba panggombunuk abet mba'nuk eerit nogo logonet, aakumi inetenggen liippiinok, eeppiigo logogup~o.
59002002	Aap ambi nen mberaarenggen mbuti emas paga yarak inom, yum abu kigirikwe inom, yippunuk, kit tamban eeko monggo'nom unggwi wage, ndi, aap ambi eenggi lek yum maluk yirik unggwi wage, eekwi iinok,
59002003	aap yum abe kigirikwe yirik nogo ayuk wuppunuk, yogo logonet, "Nogoba~o. Kwi'nogo menggam abe paga yayi kwi'nari mok~o," yogwi, ndi, aap eenggi lek nogo ayuk wuka'lek logonet, "We taati mi'ndak logorak a, ilin me nggween paga time kwi'nagan a," yinuk, yogwi, eekwi kiinok,
59002004	kit kiniki nen aap ambi maluk, ambi abe, mba'nuk, yorogo logomunggup nogo lek a? Ndi, inetenggen liippiinok, yorogwe me, aap wone owak loongga nen eeko mengga kwak eeko logonet, maluk aret koombunuk, yorogo logomunggup nogo lek a?
59002005	Nowe-nawot~o. Kit an niniki kunik me, wone yi, liirogon konenggo logonip~o. It aakumi nen, "Aap ti, ineenggi lek," inombakwi iigak, Ala nen miirinabeegerak nogo ti, ineenggi warak kwak, "Iniki mondok abet mbaruwak," mbake, ndi, "Aap abok aret, Nogoba ao, yinuk, iniki kunik ee'nakwi iinok, nabu'me piyaagin~o," yinuk, abok yoragagerak nogo, Ala abu'me piige menggim ineyate kokwak unde eeppiige, eeruwak nduk, miirinabeegerak nogo lek a?
59002006	It aap ineenggi lek nogo, Ala nen aret miirinabeegerak kagak, kit nen meek eerogo piigwi kiigi~o. Piyak-payak eekkinako logonet, niikkiren wone owak loonggo menggam pinagi nogwe nogo ti, it aap ineenggi warak nen eerogo pinagagwi nogo lek a?
59002007	Ndi, kit at anebunu mendek ogogutak endage tiyanak menggerak nogo miyuk-meya eerogo pugwi ti, it aap ineenggi warak nen eeppugwi nogo lek a?
59002008	Ala wone mbanak ndak-ndak eeko logonet, "It ineebe iniki kunik eekkologo mengga ti kwak, aakumi inom menggaarak ti, togop aret iniki kunik aganako logowak~o," yinuk, nit ninogoba endagembogut wone lengganogo yo'niragagerak nogo eekwi kiinok ti, op aret eekwi kwe,
59002009	aakumi inetenggen liippiinok eeppiigwi kenok perak, maluk eekwi aret~o. Ti eekwi paga wone yugu nogo taganogo pugwi me, Ala nen, "Kit maluk aret eekwi~o," yinuk, yokkiraagin~o.
59002010	Ala nen wone lengganogo yo'niragagerak nogo abok aret kit eeko logonet kwe, ambiriluk ambi eeka'lek kiinok perak, wone ti abok aret eeka'lek me, maluk aret eekwi~o.
59002011	At Ala nen, "Kwe kundugume wuriyak mage~o," ari logonet, "Aap wariyak mage~o," inom yereegerak me, kit ambi kwe wuka'lek logonet kwe, aap wakwi kiinok ti, Ala wone yugu taganogo pugwi me, maluk eekwi aret~o.
59002012	It aakumi nen yogo logonet, "Ala nen wone lengganogo yo'niragagerak paga wondet agago pinanege menggerak wone ti paga ninowak loonigin~o," yinuk, abeko logonet, inoone yogwe, eerit nugwi, eeko mengga kwak, eeko logonip~o.
59002013	Kit kinoreewi inabuwa nen obeelom eeppiiga'lek kiinok, Ala nen kinowak loongge logonet, kinabuwa nen obeelom eeppinagagin lek~o. Ndi, kinoreewi inabuwa nen obeelom eeppiigwi kiinok perak, kinowak looniyak nogo kinagabiti lek aret logomunggup~o.
59002014	Nowe-nawot~o. Kit ambi nen, "Niniki abet mbake~o," yogwe kwe, eebe eeka'lek kiinok, kit abet mbakwi nogo kin age mbakop? Ala wone yugu eebe eeka'lek logonet, we abet mbakwi paga mban Ala nen kinagap ndarigin mbakop?
59002015	Kiniriluk ambi ilik, kinoreeluk ambi a, ayum inom, ko'lu-kii'me noorak mendek inom, wonage lek kagak,
59002016	kit ambi nen at eebe op logowak nduk wogoga'lek logonet, "Kambi ndonggorogon nengge, karogwiyum yikkolage, ee'nuk, kiniki ale'nggen paga nage logot~o," yinuk, yogwi kiinok, ti yogwi paga kit abet mbakwi nogo kin age mbakop?
59002017	Nit niniki abet mbakwi nogo ndak-ndak eebe inom eeka'lek logonet, abet mban mbakwi kenok ti, we aanom warogo abet mbakwi kogo~o.
59002018	Togop aret kwe, kit ambi nen, "Kat abet mban mbake kwe, an perak, eebe inom aret eeke~o," yinuk, yogwe kiigirak me, wologo wae. Kit abet mbakwi nogo, eebe inom eeka'lek kiinok, "Yi aap abet mbaka'lek aret," kinombarugun kwe, an perak, abet mba'nuk eebe inom aret eeke me, "Yi aap abet mbake aret," nombarugun yi kogo ogotik?
59002019	Kit nen, "Ala ti, alik aret menggerak abet mbako ogoorik~o," yinuk, mbakwi ti op aret kwe, it kugi kunduk wone ti togop aret abet mba'nuk, inagabiti nen inaganak nuguranet nugu menggaarak kwe, kit perak, abet mba'nuk puk mban wonogwe kiigi~o.
59002020	Nowe-nawot~o. Kit wi negen agan nugwi kiigi~o. Eebe eeka'lek kagak abet mban mba'nuk, puk wonogwe kiinok ti, "Yi aanom warogo aret abet mbakwi~o," yinuk, mbaka'lek ogotik ya?
59002021	Nit ninogoba Abarakam nogo nen Ala ake warogo kani kunggo menggam ogobakkigirogo punuk, at aput Itak Ala ake pereegerak nogo paga Ala nen, "Yi aap abe~o," yinuk, obeelom agago pereegerak nogo lek a?
59002022	Ala abet mbake logonet, eebe inom eeke mbareegi, "Aap yi, abe~o," yinuk, obeelom agago pereegerak yi kogo ogotik? Ndi, eebe aret eereegerak paga at iniki abet mbareegerak nogo yobok yuulik, mondok endak aret agagerak~o.
59002023	Ti eereegerak paga, "Aap Abarakam nen Ala abet mba'nuk iniki at oba panggombereegerak paga, Ala nen, Aap yi abe~o, yinuk, obeelom agago pereegerak~o," yinuk, Ala wone liiru mbanak nogo a'me lik ari mbareegi, at Ala nen, "Aap Abarakam nogo ti, an nore aret~o," yinuk, yereegerak.
59002024	Ti kenok, niniki abet mba'nuk eekwi kwe, eebe inom eeka'lek kagak, Ala nen, "Aap yi, abe~o," yinuk, obeelom agago pinanigin lek~o. Ata, abet mba'nuk, eebe inom eekwi paga eeppinanege menggerak yi kogo ogotik?
59002025	Ti eereegerak ndak-ndak, kwe terak wuka Arakap nogo nen it aap Iterali mendek o pekkoorak nduk wogogwaarak nogo, inookwi iyo, kumaappiinok, tu alik paga nomonogo nappiyareegerak nogo paga, Ala nen, "Kwe yi, abe~o," yinuk, obeelom agago pereegerak nogo lek a?
59002026	Ninagabolo wonage kagak, niniki nggigik togon nage kenok, "Aap ti kanggerak~o," yinuk, yogo monggoorak nogo ndak-ndak, niniki abet mbakwi kwe, wone ti eebe inom eeka'lek kenok ti, aanom warogo abet mbareegurak aret mbaruwok~o.
59003001	Nowe-nawot~o. Ala nen ninowak loongge logonet, nit aakumi mamuninako monggoorak nogo eeko logomonggoorak abu liippinaninuk, aaninggin nggwok ninoba pinanigin nineenu me, kit abok aret, "An mamuniraga mendek logokit," mbarugup~o.
59003002	Nit abok aret niniyogobit lik togon yigeebu wanggo monggoorak~o. Nit ninoone yogootak paga irip paga maluk age lek kenok, nit mondok obeelom logonet, nineenggi-niniyok paga maluk eeriyak ee'ninake nogo, abok aret tebenogo pogo logorak op aret~o.
59003003	Kuda wonok nogo logonet, nit, "Ndime noorak," mbako'nom nogo-me wo'niren nawak nduk, keele mbuuluk ambe paga mbarembunuk, eebe abok aret ena koonggo monggoorak.
59003004	Ndi, yiiro kunduk nggwok lombok me, o wiya omaawi wake logonet, wonok nage menggerak kwe, yiiro wonok nega nogo nen, "Ndime noorak," mba'nuk ogobak koonggak yuwak nduk, eyo abu mbuuluk akom paga pugunik menggerak nogo paga nomonogo nappege menggerak.
59003005	Ti pogom ninamili aret~o. Nineenggi-niniyok nggwok kagak, ninamili mbuuluk nogo nen yogootak paga ndugwi nggwok wigak ari menggerak. Kani anggen mbuuluk nen tekkani nggwok nengge menggerak nogo abe'nip~o.
59003006	Ninamili ti, kani pogom aret~o. Yi maluk ndi maluk anebunu abok aret alom ti, ninamili aret~o. Ninamili ti, nineebe ando aret me nineebe apit aret maluk eerogo pinanege menggerak. Kani omoonu'me nen kani anggen wonok ninamili paga wuninogo pi wagaatak paga, nit aakumi nggween paga mendek eeko monggoorak abok aret eerit nogo logonet, maluk mban eerit nogo logowok nduk, ninoba wuninogo pinanit nage menggerak alom ti, ninamili aret~o.
59003007	Towe-pagi inom, ndiimbu-nggwiya inom, woret-waalo inom, yi kole yenggenak laut inikime menggaarak yibut-yikwe inom, yi mendek ndi mendek ogobakkigirik nogo abok aret pigogo owaanggo eeginako menggaarak me, owaanggo eeginaburak op aret kwe,
59003008	ninamili perak, yanggonogo owaanggo eeriyak meek~o. Ninamili ti abu maluk, aakumi inooriyak nduk iri'ngga magagirak nogo pogom mondok yagabit aago wonage me, tebenogo puurak meek aret~o.
59003009	Ninambe peenok paga ninogoba Ala alut eekwi, ndi, peenok paga aakumi Ala etenggen ndak-ndak ogobakkigirogo piyareegerak kagak, kugi pulunogo piigwi, eeko monggoorak.
59003010	Ninambe ambit me nen wundi wage logonet, Ala alut eekwi, ti'nuk, aakumi kugi pulunogo piigwi, eeko monggoorak me, togop eeriyak abu mage~o, noreewi togon, ai.
59003011	Niyo eneeri ambit me nen ambi mili wundi wage, ndi, ambi nggut wundi wage, eeke kogo monggotak?
59003012	Woromo nen tawi yege, tawi nen woromo yege, eeriyak op mbakop? Ndi, niyo nggut nen niyo mili wundiyak op mbakop? Togop mondok eekeelik~o, noreewi.
59003013	Kit aap ambi kinenggela'me iniki warak logonet, yi mendek ndi mendek mbet-mbet yelok kage menggerak kenok, aap ti, iniki tebenak logonet, iniki warak nen obeelom eerit nage kinigen kogo logobagip nduk, eerit nage logowak~o.
59003014	"Niniki warak aret," mbakwi kwe, kinoreeluk ambi anini eeppogo logonet, worokot liinik agan nugwi, "An koongge mban eeriyak," mba'nuk, agan nugwi, eeko logonet kwe, "Niniki warak~o," yinuk, wogoppatiyak ti, mage~o. Togop agan nugwi paga Ala ndogop menggerak wone yugu kagak, abut laganggwi me, kit pilit pugunit nugwi aret kiigi~o.
59003015	-
59003016	Kit kinoreeluk ambi anini eeppogo logonet, worokot liinik agan nugwi, "An koongge mban eeriyak," mbako logonet, eerit nugwi, eekwi kiinok, abu naalop-kaalop age logonet, yi maluk ndi maluk abok aret age kogo monggoorak nogo ti, at iniki warak agi menggerak Ala nen koonogo pinagage kagak eekwi lek~o. Ata, at Tile nen it aakumi nggween paga mendek iniki koonogo piige kagak, iniki nengge kenok, eeko menggaarak nogo mendek aret eekwi kiigi~o.
59003017	At agi iniki warak menggerak nogo nen koonogo pinanege nogo ti, nit kikak naka'lek obeelom mban wonogwe, ugun logowak nduk, "Mage," yorogwe, niniki yanggonak paga yorogwe, yo'nirogwe iinok, "E~o," yinuk, eekwi, aakumi inabuwa nen obeelom eeppiigwi, eyoonggen abe yi'nage menggi kwak, nit togop aret obeelom eerit nugwi, aap ambi obeelom eeppugwi, ambi maluk eeppugwi, eeka'lek ndak-ndak eeppiigwi, niniki laakot logonet yoraga'lek abe paga mban yorogwe, eeko logowak nduk, ee'ninake menggerak aret~o.
59003018	It aakumi iniki lambumbiinet nega nogo nen awi anggen yako mengga kwak, aakumi iniki lambunik logowak nduk eeppiinet nugu nagaatik, ti'nuk, anggen kole age kenok, mbanggologo mengga kwak, aakumi obeelom mban eerit nugwi paga iniki ugun tayenak ale'nggen paga wonogwe iigo menggaarak~o.
59004001	Kit ndugwi pugwi, wone wakwi, eeko monggotak alom ti, ngge paga~o? Kiniki nengge alom abok aret ti, "An nduk eeriyak, kat nduk eeriyak," yinuk, kinikime nen nili-kili yogo logonet, eeko monggotak nogo lek a?
59004002	"An ndi mendek kolaakit lak, ao," yinuk, kiniki nengge kwe, woorak meek age kenok, aap wariyak koonggwi, "An aret kolaakit lak, at mban kolage ti, neebi a," yinuk, kinoreeluk aret kwe, kineebi mbakwi, eeko logonet, ndi mendek uugwe mbakwi nogo wagangga'lek kenok, wone wakwi, ndugwi pugwi, eeko monggotak. Kit uugwe mbakwi nogo, Ala nggino yoga'lek me, wagangga'lek aret ogotik~o.
59004003	Ndi, kit ando Ala nen wokkiraawak nduk nggino yogo monggotak kwe, kiniki nengge nogo mugurok nogo logonet, lek eerogo patuwok nduk, kiniki abu alik koombunuk yogwi me, wokkiraagin mondok lek~o.
59004004	Kwe ambi nen aap ambi waganggak eeke menggi kwak eeko monggotak kit yi, it aakumi nggween paga eeko menggaarak mendek kinom kunggologwe kiinok, Ala kinom ogookkologwe nogo kineenggo'lek me eeko ogotik? Togop me, aap ambit-ambi, "It aap nggween paga eeko menggaarak mendek ninom kunggola," mba'nuk, eeke kenok, Ala imbirak ogookkolage menggerak aret~o.
59004005	"Ala nen Aberiniki ninikime mambinaneegerak wonage kagak, niniki nengge nogo mugurok nogwe niinok, Aberiniki nogo nen, Ao, yinuk, iniki wakkolage menggerak~o," yinuk, Ala wone liiru mbaneegerak nogo ti, we mbaneegerak mbakop?
59004006	Aberiniki iniki togop aret wakkolage kagak kwe, maluk mbo puwak nduk, Ala iniki kunik nen eeppinanegak mban eeke menggerak. Ti kenok, Ala nen ari logonet, "It aakumi iniki wogoppako menggaarak nogo, an nen tebenogo piige minggirak kwe, Iniki tebenak menggaarak nogo perak, niniki kunik nen eeppiige minggirak~o," yinuk, yereegerak Ala wone liiru mbanak wonage~o.
59004007	Togop me, Ala abu'me tebe yinip~o. Ala abu'me tebe yinuk, wonogwe me, Tile nen maluk eekkinabi wage kenok, kole mbaganuwak nduk, kinom wim perenggologo logonip~o.
59004008	Kit Ala owagam nogwe kiinok, at kunduk, kit kinowagam ari wage logogin~o. Kit maluk eeko monggotak yi, kineenggi kookwi, ndi, kiniki mbere yi, ambit eeppunuk kinomaluk mbo pugwi, eeko logonip~o.
59004009	Kiniki puru yogo logonet, le yogwe, leenggup maakwi, eeko logonip~o. Kit i'ndok kanggwi, kinale'nggen yogwe, eekwi ti mbo punuk, kiniki puru yogo logonet, leenggu maako logonip~o.
59004010	Ala abu'me kiniki tebe yinip~o. Tebe yogwe kiinok, at nen kit aret tiyappinagagin~o.
59004011	Nowe-nawot~o. Nabok-kabok yuurak mage~o. Kit nen kinowe-kinawot inabok mbanggwi, inowak loonggwi, eekwi ti, "Ala nen wone lengganogo yo'niragagerak ti maluk yereegerak," mba'nuk, yogo logonet, Ala owak loonggwi negen eekwi me, kit wone lengganak eeka mendek lek~o. Kit Ala owak loonggo monggotak mendek aret kinombakwi me, togop eerugup~o.
59004012	Wone lengganogo yo'niragagerak owak loongge menggerak ti, at Ala alik aret~o. At alik nen ninagap ndake, lek eerogo pinanege, eeriyak op aret kwe, kit Ala kokwak eekko'nok kinowe-kinawot inowak looniyak nduk eeko ogotik ya? Mage~o, noreewi.
59004013	Wologo wae! Kit wone yogo logonet, "Yogondak a, ko'lu a, o kota time nogo logomonggoorik, wu kuwak eekkolaawok nduk, yi mendek ndi mendek kunit nugwi niigak, tahun ambit aruwak~o," yinuk, yogo monggotak nogo, kinaruk logonip~o.
59004014	Kit ko'lu eekkinaburak nogo, kineenggo'lek logonet yogwe kiigi~o. Nineenik wonogwe nogo ti, laago aagi pogom aret~o. Laago aagi nogo ti, ne ambit lagangge ninigen kogootak kwe, lek age menggerak kokwak ti, nineebe togop aret ee'ninake menggerak~o.
59004015	Kit nen yogo logonet, "Ninogoba nen koonogo yo'nirage kenok nineebe op logonet, Yogop eeruwok, ndogop eeruwok," yogo logorak perak op~o.
59004016	Ko'lu eeriyak kineenggo'lek kagak, kineenu negen eekko'nok wogoppakwi ti, maluk aret eekwi kiigi~o.
59004017	Ndi, kit obeelom eeko logorak kineenu logonet kwe, eeka'lek kiinok, tirogon maluk aret~o.
59005001	Kit aap kineenggi warak yi, kinaruk logonip~o. Kit andi yagan wako logorak eyom panggoni wage me, kinale yikkologwe, kinaleenggu maakkologwe, eeko logonip~o.
59005002	Kinamendek ambik wonage nogo ti, maluk age, kinayum abe nogo ti, kutabak nen nibinogo pege,
59005003	kinawu mbuti emas inom, perak inom, ogobakkigirik nogo ti, muk yi'mbaani kunit nage, eerogo pegerak agaarik~o. Kinawu yi'mbaani kunogo pegerak ti paga kit nggilimi negen kumaappatogo wonogogutak nogo kin arigin~o. Ndi, yi'mbaani kunogo pit nage menggi kwak, kit kinagabolo togop aret kani nen nenet nagin~o. O age yobok paga eeppinani woroorak nogo abu panggoni wage kagak kwe, yi mendek ndi mendek kiniki kundugu kuwak eerogo pako nogogutak me, kinenggali nen leenggu maakkologo logomunggup~o.
59005004	It kineyabu eeppinagagaarak nogo, onggo ndak-ndak wogoroorak kagak eeko nogogutak me, it inoone mumun kokop yokkirogwe yi, iyaanip~o. It ando anggen yugu wonok kira wogwe nogo kunduk, inoone yogwe at Omaawi Lombok Menggerak ninogoba nogo, muk aruk konengge agaarik~o.
59005005	Kit nggween paga mondok obeelom mban logonet, kinikilom kenok mban eerit nogo nogogutak nogo~o. Wam amok warak age kenok wariyak nduk, mbi abuk nggininogo wogorogo mengga kwak, kit, "Yi mendek ndi mendek amburu warak mban na," mbarit nogwe paga kinamok warak eekkologwe me, kinoorigin aret mbako logonip~o.
59005006	It aakumi maluk eekeelik nogo nen wone onggo yokkiraga'lek iigak, kit nen mban pilit wone inoba piinok, inooko nogogutak nogo~o.
59005007	Togop me, nowe-nawot~o. Ti eeppinagagwi nogo koonikit nduk, ninowe woraagin me, kiniki kwippunuk logonip~o. Aap ambi nen mbi awi yaketak nogo mayu kage, kibi kage, eeke kagak, kole aruwak nduk iniki kwippunuk, tokkage menggerak nogo liippinip~o.
59005008	Ti kokwak, kit kunduk kiniki kwippunuk logonip~o. Ninowe woroorak eyom abu panggoni wagaarak wonage me, kiniki nu'lek eeppatinuk logonip~o.
59005009	Nowe-nawot~o. Ala nen maluk onggo eeppinagi wage kero, kiniki laakit-laakot mbako logonet, at ambi abok mbanggak eeko logogup~o. Ninowak loongga nogo ti, muk tu ngga'nggi paga panggoni wagaarak wonage yi kaanip~o.
59005010	Nowe-nawot~o. It aap Ala nen yorage kagak yorogo nogogwaarak nogo piyak-payak eeppiigwi iigak, iniki kwippunuk inogogumbuk logonet waganggo nogogwaarak nogo kwak, kit ndak-ndak aret in wakkagak eeko logonip~o.
59005011	It aaninggin inoba age kagak inogogumbuk logonet waganggwi iinok, Ala ale'nggen inoba piige nagagerak nogo nineenu aret~o. Aap Ayup kunduk aaninggin oba age kagak wagangge nagagerak nogo ti, muk koneneegutak~o. Aakumi abok Ala inabuwa nen obeelom eeppiige menggerak me, aap Ayup aaninggin oba age kagak iniki kwippunuk abu wagangge mbareegi, ti'nuk, irip paga Ala nen eeppereegerak nogo ti, kineenu aret~o.
59005012	Togop me, nowe-nawot~o. Ala endage we lek me ugun yuurak mage~o. Mbogut endage inom, nggween endage inom, yi mendek ndi mendek endage abok aret kumbunuk, "Yokkiragi~o," yinuk, yoroorak mage~o. Kit maluk yogwe paga Ala nen aaninggin kinoba pinagage kero, "E~o," mbakwi kiinok, "E~o," aret yuurak. Ndi, "Lek~o," mbakwi kiinok, "Lek aret~o," yuurak. Wone iya lombok nogo ti aret yokkiragi~o.
59005013	Aap ambi kinenggela'me nen aaninggin-paaninggin oba age kenok, at tamban eekkolage logowak~o. Ndi, ambi iniki ale'nggen mbake kenok, ndawi wake logonet, Ala endage tiyappege logowak~o.
59005014	Ndi, ambi kugi andi eeke kenok, it aap Ala apuri unde nogo woraawak nduk, wiiramenggerak wogo logomenggaarik, amburu oba mbenambunuk, Ala endage kunogo ake tamban eeko logowak~o.
59005015	Ndi, iniki Ala oba panggombunuk, tamban eekwi iinok, ninogoba nen aap andi nogo omaawi aret nege logowak nduk, obeelom eeppigin~o. Ndi, at maluk eereegerak kenok, omaluk ti inom aret lek eerogo pigin~o.
59005016	Togop kenok, kit maluk eeko monggotak nogo, at ambi enggaanom paga paganggwi, at ambi nen at ambi ake tamban eekwi, eeko logomonggotak paga kugi andi eekkinake kenok, obeelom eekkinake logogin~o. Aap ambi maluk inikime lek logonet iniki abe koonak paga oone mondok nabek togon tamban eeke kenok, Ala nen mbo pigin lek~o. Aruk konenigin aret~o.
59005017	At aap Eliya ti, nit pogom aret kwe, "Mayu woraagun~o," yinuk, oone nabek togon tamban eereegerak me, mayu nggween paga wambi waga'lek kagak tahun kenagan eeppunuk, tut 6 peneneegerak.
59005018	Ti'nuk, peebi tamban eeke mbareegi, mayu nogo mondok lubu-lubu wambeegerak me, iri'ngga awi yarak nogo mbilangge nagagerik, anggen yi'nagagerak.
59005019	Nowe-nawot~o. Aap ambi Ala ndogop menggerak wone nogo koneniyak, "Neebi~o," yinuk, nomo agan nage me, kit ambi nen aap nogo iniki yanggombunuk wonok wogwe kiinok,
59005020	Ala nen yokkirage logonet, "Aap ti, maluk eeke menggerak nogo mbo punuk, an noone woorak nduk, iniki yanggombunuk wonok wogotak paga, aap ti, kambunuk nogo menggam nage me, omaluk lek eerogo agap ndaruwak nduk, eekotak me, op aret eekotak~o," yinuk, yokkiraagin~o.
60001001	Kit Ala iniki mba'nuk miikkinabeegerak o Pondut inom, Nggalatiya inom, Kaparokiya inom, Atiya inom, Mbitiniya inom, o time yi awi ndi awi mbaganit nogogutak aap nggiru negen wonogwe nogo, at Yetut Keritut ayonggo nappiigak mendek eerogo paneegerak an Peterut nogo nen wone ambi yokkira~o.
60001002	At Yetut Keritut yereegerak wone nogo woppunuk ndak-ndak eekwi kiinok, at amiya paga kookkinake logowak nduk, at ninogoba Ala nen peebi eeko logorak abok aret koonogo pege menggerak me, maan kooneegerak nogo ndak-ndak, Aberiniki nen eeppinagage kagak kit at apuri kikak naka'lek ake leenak logobagip nduk, miikkinabeegerak me, at Ala iniki kunik nen wokkirage, kiniki ugun tayenak ale'nggen logobagip nduk eeppinagage, eeke nogo, ambinom eeppinagagak mban eeke logowak~o.
60001003	-
60001004	At ninowe Yetut Keritut ogoba Ala nen ninabuwa nggwok lombok mbake nagagerik, obeelom eeppinanege logonet, at Yetut Keritut kambunuk nogo menggam nen eenik agago mippereegerak nogo paga ninake punik nineyate kokwak pili age, yi'mbaani kungge, lek age, eekeelik mondok mbogut paga pinanogo wonage niniki lunik wonogwe nogo, kola nawok nduk, niniki ngget nda'ninabeegerak me, "Ninogoba Ala wa," yinuk, endage tiyappogo ogoorik~o.
60001005	Ninake pinanogo wonage kola noorak nit nogo ti, abet mbakwi niinok, Ala nen o age yobok paga ninagap ndariyak kooneegerak nogo, peebi togop ndak-ndak eeppinanikit nduk, yogondak Ala omaawi paga nggelorogon pinanogo wonage nogo, ninake aret pipuk eerogo pinaneegerak mbogut paga wonage~o.
60001006	Togop me, nowe-nawot~o. Aaninggin-paaninggin kinoba wonage nogo paga kiniki ale'nggen lek aaninggin ndugu aago wonogwe kwe, "Peebi ninake pipuk eerogo pinaneegerak nogo kola nagun me, yi ti, we luulu eeppinanege me op aret~o," yinuk, kiniki ale'nggen nggwok aret mbako logonip~o.
60001007	Mbuti emas nogo ti, we luulu lek ariyak mendek kagak, "At mendek ilik, alik mendek a?" yinuk, kani paga abut mbanggo menggaarak nogo ndak-ndak, kit abet mbakwi nogo ti, mbuti emas ndak-ndak lek~o. Kit abet mbakwi nogo ti, mondok iya lombok me, at Ala nen, "Nu'lek wonogwe iyaamun ilik, lek a?" yinuk, kinabut mbangge logonet, aaninggin-paaninggin kinoba pinagage me, kiniki ale'nggen mbakwi kiinok, peebi Yetut Keritut eebe tena'me ari wage logonet, "Op eekotak~o," yinuk, ale'nggen kinoba pinagage, kinendage tiyappinagage, wogoppinagage, eeri woraagin~o.
60001008	-
60001009	Kit Yetut kinigen kaga'lek kwe, kagak, kiniki kunik eekwi, ndi, yogondak at eebe kinigen kaga'lek kwe, kiniki at oba panggombunuk, abet mbakwi, eeko logonet, "Nit niniki abet mbakwi nogo, anggen yugu paga nineebe ninagap ndarigin," mba'nuk, kiniki ale'nggen mbakwi nogo ti, mondok nggwok alik negen agaarak me, nonggop togon mbininogo yuubok aga~o.
60001010	-
60001011	Kit kinagap ndappunuk, obeelom eerogo pinagarak wone nogo ti, it aap Ala nen yorage kagak yoraga nogo nen, "Ala iniki kunik en obeelom eeppiyoorak nogo mandenom eeppiyaagin, ao," yinuk, mbakwi wonogwe me, at Keritut Aberiniki nogo it inikime logonet, "Keritut nogo peebi andi-pandi eerogo pemenggaarak ti paga Ala nen tiyappigin~o," yinuk, yorage mbareegi, it nen yogo logonet, "Ta nen ninagap ndari woraagin? Ndi, mandenom kin arigin?" yinuk, Ala wone pekkogwe, liippit unggwogwe, eeko nogogwaarak.
60001012	Mbogut paga nen Aberiniki nappi wagagerak it aap ti, inikime unggwage nagagerik, yorage kagak, obeelom wone yokkirogogwaarak konenggo nogogutak wone nogo, maan it aap Ala nen yorage kagak yoraga nogo nen, wone ti yorogwe iigak, at Ala nen, "Wone yi ti, kit kinake nduk yokkirage lek~o. Wone ti, it peebi nda'naremenggaarak inake nduk aret yokkiragi~o," yinuk, kin paga yoragagerak me, it malayikat kunduk wone ti, koneniyak uugwe mbakwi kwe, nit ninake nduk aret yorogo nogogwaarak kogo~o.
60001013	Togop me, nowe-nawot~o. "Peebi at Yetut Keritut wage eyom paga Ala iniki kunik en obeelom eeppinani woraagin~o," yinuk, wone ti paga kiniki mondok lunik logonet, li'luk agago punuk, kinagaket paga logonip~o.
60001014	Kit aa'nduk Ala kineenggo'lek logonet, kiniki nen nengge kenok ugun-ugun eerit nogo nogogutak nogo, mbo punuk, ogoba ari kenok, aput konembunuk ndak-ndak eeke menggi kwak, kinogoba Ala nen ari kenok mban eerit nogo logonip~o.
60001015	-
60001016	At Ala nen ari logonet, "An maluk eekeelik alik leenak minggirak ndak-ndak, kit togon maluk eeka'lek alik leenak togop aret logonip~o," yinuk, yereegerak wone liiru mbanak wonage me, at Ala maluk eekeelik alik leenak menggerak nogo nen kinayonggo pereegerak me, kit togon maluk eeka'lek alik leenak logonet, eerit nogo logonip~o.
60001017	"Ninogoba Ala~o," yinuk, tamban eeko monggotak me, at Ala nen nit yi aap ndi aap ninalitak lombok eeko logomonggoorak nogo abok ninawone ndak-ndak mbanigin me, yogondak mbogut paga unggwi naga'lek nggween paga yime luulu logonet, Ala mban kinagabiti eeppunuk, eerit nogo logonip~o.
60001018	-
60001019	Kit kinombomini maan mbogut paga unggwi noorak lek kagak we aanom warogo eerit nogo nogogwaarak nogo ndak-ndak, kit togop eekwi kiyo, wu mbuti perak inom, emas inom, yi mendek ndi mendek lek ariyak mendek ti paga kinonggo mbanulik~o. Ata, ndomba aagaluk awinde-obande aago lek mondok abe kwak Keritut amiya mondok iya lombok nogo paga kinonggo mbaneegerak nogo kineenu aret~o.
60001020	-
60001021	O maan mbogut-nggween wakkaga'lek kagak, at Ala nen, "An ogobakkigirogo piyaminggirak peebi maluk eerugun neenu aret me, inake Keritut aret leenogo pikit~o," yinuk, leenogo pereegerak kote kumaarak wonagagerak kwe, yogondak irip paga yi aret, at Keritut eereegerak paga nit niniki Ala oba panggombunuk abet mbakwi nogo, ninake aret kin eeppereegerak me, niniki at oba panggombunuk, abet mbakwi, niniki lunik wonogwe, eekwi ti, at Keritut kambunuk nogo menggam nen eenik agago mippege nagagerik, tiyappereegerak Ala eebe nogo aret~o.
60001022	-
60001025	"Iri'ngga-kale'ngga ero kwit agan lagangge nagaatik, ti'nuk, mbuk age, Ndi, iri'ngga anggen laambu yege kenok, aakumi nen, Wi! egaatak kwe, ne ambit liingge mono-mono wangge, Eeke menggerak nogo ti, Nit aakumi nineebe ti kwak aret kwe, Ala wone ti perak, mondok itok aret menggerak~o," yinuk, yereegerak liiru mbanak ndak-ndak, Ala wone lek ageelik mondok itok menggerak nogo aakumi waganggwi iinok, ineenik eeginake menggerak obeelom wone nogo aret yokkirogogwaarak waganggo mbareegup, mondok kineenik logobagip nduk, kiniki ngget ndakkinabeegerak nogo ti, aakumi inapuri ndaganakaatak kambit nogwe nogo pogom lek~o. Ata, at mondok eenik menggerak Ala nen aret ndakkinabeegerak me, kit Ala ari menggerak wone konembunuk, "Ndak-ndak eeko logowok~o," yinuk, eerit nogo logonet, maluk kinikime wonage nogo mbo pereegutak me, yogondak kiniki laakot paga kinoreewi Ala apuri kinom kunik aganako logogup~o. Ata, kiniki abe paga aret kinoreewi kinom niniki-kiniki kunik eeko logonip~o.
60002001	Ti kenok, kit pilit wone yogo monggotak inom, kinikime alik eeriyak mbako logonet, agan nugu monggotak inom, "An eerikit lak at mban eeke yi, neebi a," yinuk, yogo monggotak inom, nabok-kabok yogo monggotak inom, yi maluk ndi maluk ti mendek abok aret mbo pogo logonip~o.
60002002	-
60002003	Ala nen obeelom eeppinanege nogo, kit eekkinake muk liippogotak kenok, elege awo ngget ndarak yilak abu nen le yogonok yilak mili lenggenak lek abe wogoragaatak nonggo logonet, tawe ogo mengga kwak, at Ala nen muk kinagap ndakkinabeegerak me, kiniki kole eekkinake logowak nduk, abe wone ti mban, "Ao," yinuk, waganggo logonip~o.
60002004	Yugum ambi eenik menggerak pogom, at Yetut ti, eenik menggerak me, yugum nogo obeelom aret kagak aakumi nen meek kenok, mbo nappereegwaarak kwe, Ala nen perak, "Obeelom aret kagak mbo pugwi~o," yinuk, leenogo pereegerak me, at ninowe abu'me mban kuwak eeri wogo logonip~o.
60002005	-
60002006	Ala nen ari logonet, "An nen yugum onggo nggwok omaawi yangguk yuurak lek mendek o Tiyon paga ndoonogo piminggirak me, Aap ambi yugum ti paga iniki oba panggombege kenok, enggali arigin lek~o," yinuk, yereegerak liiru mbanak wonage me, it aap Ala unde nen Ala awi wurik me Ala ake warogo pogo mengga kwak, kit togop aret Ala unde at ake leenak logonet, Yetut Keritut eereegerak paga Ala inikilom mbake menggerak mendek aakumi inake eeko logobagip nduk, yugum obaga lu'luk eerogo o wuko mengga kwak, Ala nen kit kineebe paga at awi wukkolage agaarik~o.
60002007	-
60002008	Togop me, "It yugum paga o wuka nen o wuko logonet, Yugum ambi mbo pereegwaarak nogo, yugum ogowa ndoonnaga~o," yinuk, yereegerak liiru mbanak wo-nage me, it abet mbakwi nogo nen, "Yugum ti, nit ninake aret mippereegerak me, ia~o," mbako menggaarak. Ndi, wone ambi, "Yugum iniyogobit linggolaga kwak, Lik togon yigeebu wangga kwak, Ti, an neebe aret~o," yinuk, yereegerak liiru mbanak nogo ti, it aakumi iniki abet mbaka'lek mendek nogo nen, Ala wone woppunuk eerit naga'lek iinok, iniyogobit lik togon ngginnogwe nogo aret nduk yereegerak kogo~o. It togop eeko logowak nduk, Ala nen aret kooneegerak kwe,
60002009	kit perak, o apit me wonogwe nogo mbo punuk, o eya iya lombok kenok, aakumi nen, "Wi!" ugo menggam nogome logobagip nduk, Ala nen kinayonggo pereegerak nogo at eeke menggerak mendek paganogo yorogo logobagip nduk, "Kit an mendek aret~o," yinuk, miirogo pinagage, "Kinendagembogut logonet, an neebe unde logorak kit aret~o," yinuk, mippinagage, "Kit an napuri maluk eeka'lek nake leenak logomunggup~o," yinuk, leenogo pinagage, ndi, "Kit an napuri lombok aret~o," yinuk, eekkinake, eereegerak~o.
60002010	Kit maan aa'nduk nen Ala apuri lek aret wonogogutak kwe, yogondak perak, at apuri eekkinabeegerak wonogwe, ndi, kit aa'nduk Ala nen kinabuwa mbake nagagerak nogo kineenggo'lek wonogogutak kwe, yogondak perak, at Ala kinabuwa nen obeelom eeppinagage nogo liippugwi, eeko ogotik~o.
60002011	Nowe-nawot~o. Kit aap nggiru negen nggween paga yi awi ndi awi mbaganit nogogutak nogo, kit an niniki kunik me wone ambi yokkira~o. Kit kiniki nen nengge mugurok noorak kineebi mbakwi kiigak, nikkiren nage nogo, mugurok noorak ti mage~o.
60002012	It aap endekem iniki abet mbaka'lek mendek nogo nen, "It maluk eerit nugwi~o," yinuk, kinabok mbaniyak nduk eeremenggaarak kwe, obeelom mban eerit nogwe liippinagago logomenggaarik, Yetut wage eyom paga Ala wogoppuwak nduk, inenggela'me logonet, kiniki mondok liippunuk eeko logonip~o.
60002013	-
60002014	"Ninogoba meek eerogo pukwak me," yinuk, aap endagembogut kinarum menggerak Kayitat nogo inom, ndi, it aakumi obeelom eekwi nogo wogoppiigwi, maluk eekwi nogo aaninggin inoba piigwi, eeko logowak nduk, it o unde logorak mippiigwi ineebe nogo inom, it wone unde menggaarak nogo nen abok aret wone lengganogo yokkirogwe iinok, "E~o," yinuk, eeko logonip~o.
60002015	It wone lengganogo yokkirogwe nogo ndak-ndak eerit namonggotak paga, aakumi iniki lek we ugun agan nogo menggaarak nogo, at Ala nen, "Inoone taganogo piigo logowak," kinombareegerak me, kinogobamini nogo nen wone lengganogo yokkirogwe iinok, "E~o," yinuk, konenggo logonip~o.
60002016	Kit aakumi inayeloman kwak lek~o. Kit it aakumi we ugun wondet aago nugu menggaarak nogo mendek aret wonogwe me, "An wondet eerogo paneegerak me," yinuk, kiniki teeluk logonet, ugun maluk eerit nogo logorak mage~o. Ata, "An Ala ayeloman aret~o," yinuk, at yokkirage kenok mban eerit nogo logonip~o.
60002017	It abet mbakwi kenok kiniki kunik aganakwi, it weelek mendek abok aret inabuwa mbakwi, kinoweewi inendagembogut inayuk wukwi, ndi, Ala kinagabiti mbakwi, eeko logonip~o.
60002018	Kit aakumi inayeloman yi, it kinogobamini inoone yanggorogon yokkirogo logonet, obeelom eeppinagagwi iinok inoone konenggwi, ndi, inanini nen mbekkirogwe iinok kineebi inombakwi, eeriyak ti mage~o. Ata, mbekkirogwe, obeelom eeppinagagwi, eekwi iigak kwe, kagak, inoone konembunuk eeko logonip~o.
60002019	Kit maluk eeka'lek kiigak, andi-pandi kinoba pinagagwi iinok, "Ala nen togop eeppinaniyak mbakerak me, op aret eeppinanugwi iigo~o," mba'nuk, waganggwi kiinok, Ala ale'nggen kinoba pinagage kaamunggup~o.
60002020	Kit maluk eerumonggotak paga kinookwi iigak, kinoone lek puk wonogwe kiinok, aakumi nen kinaana'le mbaniyak op mbakop? Lek~o. Maluk eekotak paga kinookwi me, "Op aret inooka," kinombarugun kwe, kit obeelom eerit nogwe paga kinookwi iigak, kinoone lek logonet waganggwi kiinok perak, Ala kinabuwa mba'nuk, ale'nggen kinoba pinagage kaamunggup~o.
60002021	-
60002023	Keritut andi-pandi eerogo pereegwaarak nogo ti, "At andi-pandi oba pugwi iigak, at maluk eeke, An togop eerulik~o, yinuk, aana'le mbanggolage, Ti eerulik~o." It nen miyuk-meya eerogo pugwi iigak, at nen onggo miyuk-meya eerogo piige, wakwi iigak, at nen wone onggo yorage, ti eerulik mban. Ata, at iniki ogoba Ala oba panggombunuk, "Nogoba wone a'me nggelok mban inowak loongge menggerak nogo nen nawone mbanigin~o," yinuk, iniki kwi'ndak logonet, waganeegerak nogo ti, nit ninake aret waganeegerak me, at eereegerak nogo kokwak, nit togop ndak-ndak eeko logowok nduk, Ala nen ninayonggo pereegerak~o.
60002024	It aakumi kanggaatak yabu eekulik nogo kwak, nit aa'nduk maluk eeko nogogurak nogo, yogondak ambinom eeka'lek obeelom mban eerit nogo logowok nduk, at eyo karo-karo paga kangge logonet, nit ninomaluk abok aret waganeegerak me, at agabolo nibik-nobak eerogo wareegwaarak nogo paga nit obeelom ee'ninabeegerak~o.
60002025	Kit aa'nduk ndomba kobak aago kwak ugun nugu nogogutak kwe, yogondak nen at kinarum wake, ndegengginake, eeka nogo abu'me logobagip nduk, ka wogogutak~o.
60003001	-
60003002	"Kit aakumi inayeloman nen kinogobamini inoone liirogon konenggo logonip~o," yinuk, yokkiragarak nogo ndak-ndak, kit kumi kunduk kinogonggelomini inabu'me logonet, inoone liirogon konenggo logonip~o. Kit Ala kinagabiti eeppunuk, kinobaabut obeelom logonet, kinogonggelomini inabuwa nen kinigen tebenak nugwi kiigo logomenggaarik, it kinogonggelomini ando iniki awo abet mbaka'lek nogo nen, "An ninom Yetut mugurok naakit," mbaruwak nduk, inoone yokkirogwe iinok, kit nen wone onggo ambi yoraga'lek, we, "E~o," yinuk, liirogon eeko logonip~o.
60003003	It aakumi nen, "Kwe yi, kigirikwe togon~o," yuwak nduk, kinagabolo paga mban ogobakkigikkologo logonet, kineeruwak abe mbininggologwe, kinarenggen-kinagiinggen laambu yikkologwe, kinagali-kinayum abe kigirikwe yirikkologwe, ti mban eeko logogup~o.
60003004	Ata, kumi inobaabut abu yanggonak iniki kwi'ndak nogo, alik ogolik mondok porogo wonogwe iinok, at Ala nen, "Kwe yi, ia~o!" yinuk, iniki kundugu eeginake menggerak me, kit kinobaabut togop aret logonip~o.
60003005	It kumi aa'nduk iniki Ala oba panggombunuk at oone liirogon mugurok nogo nogogwaarak nogo ti, aakumi nen, "Kumi yi kigirikwe togon~o," yuwak nduk, inagabolo mban ogobakkigikkologo logolik~o. Ata, it togon togop aret inogonggelomini inabu'me logonet, inoone liirogon aret konenggo nogogwaarak me,
60003006	at kwe Tara nogo nen Abarakam oone ari kenok, "E~o, nogoba," yinuk, yanggonak mban eeke nagagerak nogo ndak-ndak, kit kumi o yogondak wonogwe yi, kinagabiti lek obeelom mban eerit nogwe kiinok, at Tara owowologwe kit aret logomunggup~o.
60003007	Togop me, yogondak kit aap kinakuwi warak nen eeko logorak ambi yokkira~o. It kumi ineebe ndeyak inomaawi lek wonogwe me, kinakuwi kinom logonet, inabuwa mba'nuk yeenggwaarogwe, ndi, kiniki ogoorak logonet, kinom tamban eeriyak meek eekkinake kero, "Ala ninabuwa nen nineenik mondok logorak mendek ninakuwi ninom ndak-ndak unde eeppinanigin~o," yinuk, obeelom eeppiigwi, eeko logonip~o.
60003008	-
60003012	At Ala nen ari logonet, "Kit kineenik logorak kinikilom mbakwi, Nit obeelom aret wonogwe me, li a'nuk, kambuurak op aret, mbakwi, Eekwi ti, Taamini nen togop mbako ogotik? Togop aret mbakwi kiinok, Kinoone maluk mendek kinambe paga wunabi wogwe, Wone pilit kinamili irip paga wonok nugwi, Eekwi kiyo, Tum liirogon wakkologwe, Maluk mendek mbo punuk, obeelom mendek kenok mban eerit nugwi, Nonggop agago niniki ambit lambunik logorak koonggwi, Abu koombunuk, ti aret kinomaawirogon mugurok nogwe, Eeko logonip~o. Aap iniki koonak menggaarak nogo, Ala enegen wogoren nege, Tamban eekwi iinok, at aruk liirogon konengge, Eeke menggerak kwe, Aap maluk eeko menggaarak perak, Ala enggaawak omaawi paga lek eerogo piige menggerak~o," yinuk, yereegerak liiru mbanak ndak-ndak, kit togon Ala ale'nggen kinoba pinagakit nduk, kinayonggo pinagareegerak me, kit nen maluk onggo-onggo eekwi, ambi nen ambi meek eeppegak eekwi, eeko logogup~o. Ata, it maluk eeppinagagwi nogo obeelom eeppiigo logonet, kinom kiniki ambit eeppunuk wone mbanggwi, kiniki eyak wat-wat eekkologwe, nore-kore yogwe, nabuwa-kabuwa mbakwi, kiniki tebenak nugwi, eeko logonip~o, yinuk, eeko logorak irip paga ambi yokkiraakit mbakirak nogo ti aret yokkiragi~o.
60003013	Kit kiniki aganggen kerek togon obeelom eerit nugwi kiinok, ta nen maluk eeppinagarak mbakop?
60003014	Togop eekulik kwe, kit obeelom wone yoranet nugwi kiigak andi-pandi eerogo pinagagwi iinok, "Nonggop nduk eeppinanugwi?" yinuk, kinagabiti nen kiniki piirik eerugup~o. Ata, "Ala ale'nggen ninoba pinanigin~o," yinuk, kiniki ale'nggen paga waganggo logonip~o.
60003015	"Keritut ti, nit ninowe aret logowak~o," yinuk, alik leenogo punuk, at mban oone konenggo logonip~o. Ndi, kit kiniki lunik wonogwe nogo, it aakumi nen, "Yo'niraanip~o," yinuk, kin wokkiigwi iinok, kiniki abe paga kinoone yanggorogon onggo yoroorak nduk, wone koonogo punuk logonip~o.
60003016	Kit Keritut kinom kunik logonet, obeelom eerit nogwe kiigak, it miyuk-meya eerogo pinagagwi nogo nen, kit obeelom mban eerit nogwe paga, "Ia!" yinuk, inagabiti mbarugun me, kiniki maluk ambi abe'naga'lek kiniki obeelom paga kinoone yanggorogon yorogo logonip~o.
60003017	Kit maluk eerit nogwe paga andi-pandi kinoba pinagagwi iinok ti, alom kit kinobaalombok eerumonggotak paga eeppinagagun me, ti iya lek~o. Ata, Ala iniki mbareegerak paga eerit nogwe kiigak, andi-pandi kinoba pinagagwi iinok ti perak, iya aret~o.
60003018	Nit maluk eekwi nogo abok aret lek eerogo pikit nduk, at Keritut ne ambit paga aret kambeegerak. At maluk eekeelik obeelom mban eeke menggerak nogo nen, nit obeelom eekwi lek maluk mban eekwi nogo, Ala abu'me pinanikit nduk at eebe aap aret age mbareegi, warogo pereegwaarak nit ninake aret kambeegerak kwe, Aberiniki nen eenik agago mippereegerak.
60003019	At mippereegerak Aberiniki nogo nen aret maan it aakumi kambeegwaarak inogoma keele maarak negen o apit me wonogwe me, wone obeelom wone yora nagagerak.
60003020	Obeelom wone yora nagagerak nogo ti, aap Nu nen maan aa'nduk it aakumi Ala wone yorage kagak, taganogo mbo pogo mbareegwa, Ala nen, "Mbet-mbet inoorikit," mbareegerak kwe, aap Nu nogo o awo wuke kenok, iniki yanggo yinuk, tokkage kagak, o nogo wuke mbareegi, aap Nu apuri inom ineebe 8 mban unggwogogwaarak nogo, niyo nen wogoren laganeegerak paga inagap ndake logonet, it ando apit niyo ndonggoninabeegerak inogoma keele maarak o apit me wonogwe me, wone obeelom wone yora nagagerak nogo it aret~o.
60003021	Ndi, it ineebe 8 niyo ndonggoninake kero, niyo nen wogoren laganeegerak paga inagap ndareegerak nogo ndak-ndak, nit yogondak niyo-me wuppinanugwi paga ninagap ndake ti, we ninagabolo mili kenok, koo'ninabuwak nduk, eekwi lek~o. Ata, nit nen Ala yogo logonet, "An pilit lek, abet aret yiluk-maluk mbo pigirak me, kat kabu'me logokit~o," yinuk, Ala enggaanom paganggwi niinok, niyome aret wuppinanugwi, ndi, at Yetut Keritut eenik eerogo mippereegerak paga ninagap ndake menggerak ndak-ndak, niyome nen pilanogo mippinanugwi, eeko menggaarak~o.
60003022	At Yetut Keritut nogo ogoba Ala nen eenik eerogo mippege mbareegi, it malayikat inom, it o oolo ya'i menggaarak Tile inom, yi kugi ndi kugi inom, abok aret at abu'me logowak nduk, tebenogo piige nagagerik, yogondak mbogut paga ogoba Ala eenggi abe'nggan paga kwi'nari laganeegerak wonage agaarik~o.
60004001	Aap ambi eebe andi yagan wake logonet, "An maluk ambinom eerigin lek," mbake menggerak me, at Keritut eebe andi-pandi eerogo pugwi iigak, iniki kwi'ndak logonet wagangge nagagerak nogo kwak, kit ndak-ndak kiniki kwi'ndak logonet, waganggo logobagip nduk, it aap wim eeka nen li'luk eeppunuk, mengga kwak, kit togop aret eerogo patinuk logonip~o.
60004002	Kit togop aret eerogo patinuk wonogwe kiinok, o yogondak kuli nen nggween paga yayi wonogo logonet, kiniki nen nengge nogo mban mugurok nogo logorak lek~o. Ata, Ala iniki mbake nogo mban ndak-ndak eerit nogo logonip~o.
60004003	Kit aa'nduk kinobaabut it aakumi Ala wone konengga'lek nen eeriyak inikilom mba'nuk, eerit nogo mengga kwak, eerit nogo logonet, we ugun uugwe-uugwe mba'nuk eekwi, kiniki nen nengge kenok mugurok nugwi, amburu kumili aganake menggerak mendek ndonggorogon nenet nugwi, ndem unggwogo logonet kwaanggen wakwi, amburu ndonggok togon nenok kumili-kumili agan nogo logonet maluk eekwi, ogole warak kagak kugi eekwi, eeko nogogutak nogo, yogondak ambinom eeka'lek kiinok,
60004004	it aakumi Ala wone ineenggo'lek mendek nogo iniki mondok lek me, "Nit yi maluk ndi maluk eekwi yi, abu aret eeko," mbaka'lek eerit mban nogo logonet, "It ninom eerit nogwe lek yi, nano nduk puk wonogwe mbakop? Wi!" yinuk, kinomba'nuk, meek eerogo pinagagwi kwe,
60004005	it aakumi kambeegwaarak inom, nineenik wonogwe inom, Ala nen nit abok ninawone amburu mbanogo ninowak looniyak nduk li'luk aago wonage me, it togon eeko logomenggaarak nogo Ala nen, "Paganogo yo'ninip~o," yinuk, yoraagin me, paganogo yorugun~o.
60004006	Togop me, it kambeegwaarak nogo ti, "Aap maluk aret~o," yinuk, ineebe andi-pandi eerogo piigwi iigak, kambeegwaarak kwe, at Ala eenik menggi kwak, it ndak-ndak inogoma mondok-mondok ineenik logowak nduk, obeelom wone yoragagerak nogo~o.
60004007	O age yobok paga eeriyak abu koorok panggo yi wagaarak me, tamban eeko logobagip nduk, kiniki kwi'ndak nu'lek logonet, kinagaket paga logonip~o.
60004008	Aap ambi ore imbirak iniki kunik logomenggerak nogo nen ore maluk ambik eerogo pit nage logomenggerak kwe, imbirak iniki kunik me, "Op aret~o," ari menggi kwak, kit togop aret, "Niniki-kiniki kunik eeko logonip~o," yinuk, wone ambit ti aret yokkiragi~o.
60004009	Kinoreewi ambi kiya wogwe iinok, kineebi mbaka'lek kiniki ale'nggen paga kinambi magarogo logonip~o.
60004010	At Ala nen eeko logorak ninalitak lombok unde eeppinaneegerak nogo, "Ala iniki kunik nen unde eeppaneegerak me, niniki kwippunuk aakumi inake eerit nage logokit~o," yinuk, kit mban-mban at ambi nen at ambi obeelom eeppegak eeko logonip~o.
60004011	Yi eekak ndi eekak eeko logonet, ninowe Yetut Keritut eereegerak paga at Ala endage tiyak yuwak nduk, kit ambi nen Ala wone yoroorak mbakwi kenok, Ala ari menggerak wone nogo aret yorogwe, ndi, ambi nen aakumi yeenggwaarogo logorak mbakwi kenok ti, Ala omaawi eeppinagage kagak yeenggwaaranet nogwe, eeko logonip~o. At Ala ti, abu tiyanak mondok-mondok ayuk warak logowak~o. Amin!
60004012	Nowe-nawot~o. Kit an niniki kunik me, wone ambi yokkira~o. Kit kinabut mbaniyak nduk, aaninggin-paaninggin mondok alik negen kinoba pinagagwi ti, it aap nen eeppiigo menggaarak nogo mendek aret eeppinagagwi me, "Yi nonggop eeppinanugwi? Ia!" yinuk, yugup~o.
60004013	Kit andi-pandi eerogo pinagagwi nogo ti, peebi, at Keritut mondok tiyanak wage kinigen kogo logomonggotik, "Nit togop aret tiyappinanigin~o," yinuk, kiniki ale'nggen mondok alik negen eekkinabigin me, "Yogondak at Keritut eeppogo nogogwaarak ando nogo aret eeppinanugwi me, op aret~o," yinuk, kiniki ale'nggen mbako logonip~o.
60004014	It aakumi nen, "Kit Keritut oone wagangga mendek~o," yinuk, miyuk-meya eerogo pinagagwi iinok, "Ala Aberiniki mondok tiyanak menggerak nogo nit ninoba wuppi wagaarak ninom wonage kenok, yo'nirogwe iigo~o," yinuk, kiniki ale'nggen logonip~o.
60004015	Kit nen aap wakwi, yogoot kiraakwi, maluk eekwi, aap ambi inawone kagak unde a'nuk mbanggwi, eekwi nogo paga andi-pandi eerogo pinagagwi iinok, kiniki ale'nggen mbarugup~o.
60004016	Ata, "Kit Ala apuri mendek aret~o," yinuk, aaninggin kinoba pinagagwi iinok perak, kinagabiti lek logonet, "Keritut endage paga eeppinanugwi me, op aret," mba'nuk, Ala, "Wa," yinuk, alut eeko logonip~o.
60004017	-
60004018	At Ala nen ari logonet, "It aakumi iniki abe koonak nogo aaninggin eeppiinet unggwogwe iigak inagap ndarigin me, It an noone konengga'lek maluk mban eerit nogwe nogo perak, nonggop togon eeppiyaagin mbakop?" yinuk, yereegerak ndak-ndak, at Ala nen nit yi aap ndi aap abok aret ninawone mbanogo ninowak loonninaburak eyom abu panggo yi wagaarak me, nit Ala apuri aa'nduk ninawone mbambunuk, at oone yugu ndak-ndak eeka'lek logomonggoorak kenok, onggo eeppinanigin me, it Ala wone obeelom wone nogo mondok wagangga'lek iinok ti, inawone mbangga'lek teppiyaagin mbakop? Lek~o. Inawone abu mbanogo punuk, mondok alik negen eeppiyaagin~o.
60004019	Togop me, kit andi-pandi eerogo pinagagwi nogo ti, Ala iniki mbake ndak-ndak eeppinagagwi me, kit obeelom mban eerit nogo logonet, at kineebe ogobakkigikkinabeegerak nogo nen, "Eeriyak," yegetak nogo, a'me liirogon aret eeke menggerak me, kiniki inom, kineebe inom, apit aret at unde logowak nduk, wogo'nuk logonip~o.
60005001	Nowe-nawot~o. Kit Ala apuri inenggela'me logonet inarum monggotak kwak, an togon Ala apuri inarum minggirak nen wone ambi yokkira~o. At Keritut aaninggin-paaninggin oba pogo nogogwaarak nogo, an nenegen kagagirak me, peebi at pi wakwi iigak, woroorak eyom paga, "An togon tiyappani woraagin," mbake logonet, "Wone eebe yokkiraakit," mbakirak nogo liirogon konenggo logobagip nduk, yokkira~o.
60005002	Kit Ala apuri inarum logobagip nduk, mippinagareegerak nogo, "Kineebi," mbako logonet, inarum logorak ti mage~o. Ata, Ala iniki mbake ndak-ndak, "Inarum logokit," mbako logonet, ndomba ndegeninako mengga kwak, Ala apuri ti, togop aret ndegeninako logonip~o.
