Ndi, onggo koloorak paga mban kiniki lunik logonet, ndegeninako logorak ti mage mban. Ata, we kiniki ale'nggen paga aret ndegeninako logonip~o.
60005003	Inarum logobagip nduk, unde eeppinagareegerak nogo inarum logonet, "An noone mban konenggo logonip~o," yinuk, kinoone omaawi paga yorogwe ti mage~o. Ata, it Ala andomba nogo nen kit kinobaabut obeelom mban eerit nogwe nogo liippinaganuk, "At eeke ti, an ndak-ndak eeke logokit," mbaruwak nduk eeko logonip.
60005004	Togop eekwi kiinok, nit ndomba ndegenninaka ninowe nogo, peebi wage logonet, "Kit abu obeelom eeko nogotak~o," yinuk, kinenggare-nggare mendaarak kiik ariyak lek mondok laambu logorak mendek yirippinagi woraagin~o.
60005005	Togop me, kit aap tawe nen eeko logorak wone ambi yokkira~o. Kinogobamini nen inoone yokkirogwe iinok, kinaruk liirogon konembunuk eeko logonip~o. "It aakumi iniki wogoppako menggaarak kenok, Ala nen tebenogo piige menggerak kwe, Iniki tebenak wonogwe iinok perak, inabuwa nen obeelom eeppiige menggerak~o," yinuk, yereegerak Ala wone liiru mbanak wonage me, kit abok aret kiniki tebenak logonet, yeenggwa-yeenggwa eeko logonip~o.
60005006	At Ala nen, "Ne ti eyom paga tiyappiyaakit~o," yinuk, kooneegerak nogo a'me lik yi wage kenok, tiyappinagawak nduk, at omaawi ambik menggerak Ala nogo abu'me tebe yinuk, logonip~o.
60005007	At Ala nen kinabuwa mbake menggerak me, kiniki piirik-paarik eekwi nogo abok aret paganogo at oba mban pogo logonip~o.
60005008	Kit kinom ogoorak monggotak Tile nogo nen maluk eekkinabikit nduk, nggeewo anini warak pogom nibingginaburak eyak nde agan kwaakkinabit nege me, kit mondok kiniki warak a'nuk, kinagaket paga logonet, tum wakkologo logonip~o.
60005009	Ndi, it kinoreewi yi awi ndi awi menggaarak kinom kiniki abet mbakwi nogo, andi-pandi kit eerogo pinagagwi ndak-ndak, it togon togop aret eeppiigwi nogo kineenu me, kit kiniki abet mba'nuk, kinogogumbuk mondok nu'lek logonet, Tile nen kiniki nggagani wage kero, mugogo nappogo logonip~o.
60005010	At iniki kunik nen wo'nirage menggerak alom unde ninogoba Ala nogo nen Keritut ninom kunik wonogwe paga at tiyanak menggim nogome ninom ndak-ndak mondok-mondok tiyanak logowok nduk ninayonggo pereegerak me, ne ambiriluk ambi andi-pandi eerogo pinagagwi iinok, ninogoba Ala nen kinobaabut koonogo pinagage, kiniki nu'lek eerogo pinagage, kinomaawi agago pinagage, kinogogumbuk nu'lek logobagip nduk eerogo pinagage, eeke logogin me, kiniki kwi'ndak logonet, waganggo logonip~o.
60005011	At Ala ti, mondok-mondok ayuk warak logowak~o, yinuk, abet aret yokkiragi~o. Amin!
60005012	Wone yokkirage ti abok aret at iniki kunik nen obeelom eeppinanege menggerak Ala nogo nen an ndak-ndak eeppanege kagak paganogo yokkirage me, "Yi abet aret eeppinanege menggerak~o," yinuk, kiniki eyak wappinagawak nduk, at li'lak mban eerit nage kage minggirak ninore Tilat nogo nen yeenggwaanege kagak, liiru yi, we nggaruk togon mbanggirage kwe, wone yi ti, mondok iya me, porogo logonip~o.
60005013	It kinoreewi Ala apuri o Mbaben mendek kunduk, Ala nen leenogo piyareegerak me, it nogo nen keyage wappinagagwi, ndi, an naput Marakut nogo nen kunduk keyage wappinagage, eeka~o.
60005014	Kit-kit aret kiniki kunik paga keyage wat-wat yogo logonet, li-nggik-kambuk yogo logonip~o. Ndi, kit Keritut kinom kunik wo-nogwe nogo abok aret kiniki ugun tayenak ale'nggen logobagip nduk, eeppinagage logogin~o. Wa!
61001001	At ninagap ndaka Yetut Keritut ninogoba Ala nogo nen nit obeelom eerogo pinanikit nduk, eereegerak paga wone abet mba'nuk, waganeegurak niniki kunik porogo wonogwe nogo, kit ninom ndak-ndak waganeegurak me, an Timon Peterut Yetut Keritut ayeloman ayonggo nappiigak mendek agago paneegerak nogo nen, kit abok aret wone ambi yokkira~o.
61001002	At ninogoba Ala ninowe Yetut imbirak iniki kunik nen wo'nirogwe, niniki ugun tayenak ale'nggen logowok nduk eeppinanugwi, eeko menggaarak nogo mondok liippunuk waganggwi kiigak, nggwok togon eeppinagit wundi wogo logowak~o.
61001003	At abu obeelom mondok tiyanak menggerak nogo, ninom ndak-ndak logowok nduk, ninayonggo pinaneegerak nit nogo nen at eeke menggerak liippunuk waganggwi paga, nit nggween paga yime logonet, Ala ari menggerak nogo liippunuk, eerit nogo logowok nduk, at omaawi eeppinaneegerak.
61001004	At Ala abu obeelom mondok tiyanak menggerak me, at nen, "An ndogop eeppinagagin~o," yinuk, yo'nirage menggerak mondok iya iniki kunik nogo mendek, "Onggo lek we aret eeppinagagin~o," yinuk, yo'niragagerak wone nogo ti, mugurok nogwe paga at Ala iniki menggi kwak nit niniki ndak-ndak ee'ninake, ndi, it nggween paga mendek iniki nen nengge nogo mugurok nogo logonet, ineebe maluk eerogo patit nogo mengga kwak, nit togop ee'ninake kero, ninagap ndarogo pege, eeke nogo nit kaawok nduk, wone ti yo'niragagerak.
61001005	Togop me, kit kiniki Ala oba panggombunuk abet mbakwi nogo paga obeelom eerit nogo logorak liippunuk mamunggologwe, ndi, obeelom eerit nogwe paga yi eeriyak ndi eeriyak kineenu eekkologwe,
61001006	ndi, kineenu ogwe nogo paga nen kiniki warak eekkologwe, ndi, kiniki warak eekkologwe nogo paga maluk eeppinagagwi iigak, kiniki kwi'ndak nu'lek logorak mamunggologwe, ndi, kiniki kwi'ndak nu'lek wonogwe nogo paga Ala ari menggerak ndak-ndak eerit nogo logorak mamunggologwe,
61001007	Ala ari menggerak ndak-ndak eerit nogwe paga kinoreewi inabuwa mbako logorak mamunggologwe, ndi, inabuwa mbakwi nogo paga irip paga aakumi abok aret kinom kiniki kunik eekkologo logorak mamunggologwe, eerit nogo logonip~o.
61001008	Ti eeko logorak nogo mendek abok aret nggwok togon eerit nogwe mban kiinok, aakumi nen, "Inowe Yetut Keritut ineenu kwe, anggen alik mendek yi'nage kiraap!" yinuk, yogo logogun lek~o. Ata, "Inowe Yetut Keritut abet aret ineenu me, anggen obeelom mendek nggwok togon yi'nage agaarik~o," yinuk, yogo logogun~o.
61001009	Ndi, kit ti eeko logorak yokkiragarak nogo eeka'lek kiinok perak, "Ala nen ninomaluk lek eerogo pinaneegerak," mbaka'lek mari eerogo punuk wonogwe me, aap inigen mbuk nen yi mendek ndi mendek nda nakkoorak meek nogo kokwak wonogwe kinombarugun~o.
61001010	Ti kenok, nowe-nawot~o. At Ala nen miirogo pinagage nagagerik, kinayonggo pereegerak me, "Abet aret mii'ninabeegerak kogo," mba'nuk, kiniki mondok nu'lek logonet, nggwiirit-nggwaarit eeko logonip. Togop eeko logomonggotak kenok, kit kiniyogobit lik togon yigeebu wambumunggup lek~o.
61001011	Ti eeko logomonggotak kenok, nit ninagap ndaka ninowe Yetut Keritut abu'me piige menggim mondok-mondok menggim nogome, at Ala nen, "Kit aret unde eekkola woraanip~o," yinuk, yokkiraagin~o.
61001012	Togop me, Ala ndogop menggerak wone nogo kinaruk konembunuk waganggo nogogutik, mondok nu'lek monggotak kwe, kagak, ambinom liippunuk eerit nogo logobagip nduk, an nen kulinik-kalinik yokkiragak mban eeke logogin aret~o.
61001013	-
61001014	At ninowe Yetut Keritut nen an nagabolo ooliya wurik kwak yi, mbet-mbet nggonenogo punuk, noorak paganogo yo'negerak nogo ndak-ndak, nagabolo nggonenogo puurak eyom abu panggo yegerak neenu me, awo nagabolo nggonengga'lek neenik wonage logonet, yi wone ndi wone yokkirage minggirak nogo kit aberak logobagip nduk, an yokkirage logorak ti, op aret mbake agarik~o.
61001015	An kambiminggirak neegak, kit nen, "At ninogoba nogo nen wone ndogop yo'niragagerak nogo~o," yinuk, kiniki abeko logobagip nduk, an awo kangga'lek logonet, yi wone ndi wone yokkirage minggirak nogo, mondok nggwiirit-nggwaarit aret yokkirage logogin~o.
61001016	Nit ninowe Yetut Keritut, "Wi," yinuk, pi wakwi iigak woroorak wone yokkirogogurak nogo ti, it aakumi nen timbayok wone mbininggo logonet, inoone amburu ndik-ndik yogo menggaarak nogo paga niniki panggombunuk yokkirogo logolik~o. Ata, at Yetut Keritut mondok tiyanak lombok menggerak ninigen abe nen kogogurak nogo aret yokkirogogurak~o.
61001017	-
61001018	Keritut ninom puut ayuk warak menggim nogome niigak, at mondok tiyanak, "Wi!" ugwi ninogoba Ala nogo nen ninowe Yetut Keritut ayuk wurogo tiyappege logonet, "An naput niniki kunik nale'nggen ee'nake nogo yi aret~o," yinuk, mbogut paga nen oone ari nit aret ninaruk konembunuk, yokkirogogurak nogo~o.
61001019	Ti yereegerak kenok, o maan it aap Ala nen wone yorage kagak yorogo nogogwaarak nogo a'me lik yi wagak eeke kogo nogogurik, nit niniki abet mbakwi nogo, mondok nu'lek eerogo pinanegak eeke kogogurak~o. O weerikit nduk, kilim nagake kagak, ndowan ambiret abinak ndelenak-welenak ari kogo monggoorak nogo, wundi waga'lek kagak, o apit me ndi wuninogo pogootak eya kenok, niniki ale'nggen age menggi kwak, kinikime awo eya eekkinabi waga'lek kagak, wone yo'nirogo nogogwaarak nogo kiniki kunik eekkologo logonet, liippogo logorak ti, op lombok aret~o.
61001020	Wone yi ti, mondok iya me, liippinip~o. Aap ambi Aberiniki nen koonogo yoga'lek kagak, "Ala wone liiru mbanak nogo, niniki koombunuk, ambi yokkira~o," yinuk, yuurak ti, abu meek me,
61001021	it aap aa'nduk Ala wone yorogo nogogwaarak nogo nen iniki koombunuk yorogo logolik~o. Ata, Aberiniki inikime lik yi unggwage mbareegi, Ala nen yorage kagak yorogo nogogwaarak nogo kineenu arubagip nduk yokkiragi~o.
61002001	Maan aa'nduk it aap wone pilit pugunogo yorogo menggaarak mendek nogo nen aakumi Iterali inenggela'me unggwi wogo nogogwaarik, pilit pugunogo yorogo nogogwaarak nogo ndak-ndak, peebi it aap ti mendek nogo nen, kit maluk eerogo pinagawok nduk kinenggela'me unggwi woraagun~o. Ndi, unggwi wogo logomenggaarik, aakumi ambik iniki nomoninabuwok nduk, yi wone ndi wone abe mendek lek kagak, pilit pugunogo kinikime manabit wogo logonet, "At amiya paga ninonggo mbaneegerak Aliku ninowe Yetut aret~o, yinuk, yogwe nogo ti, nit nineenggo'lek~o," yinuk, agan wogo logomenggaarak paga abera'lek me, Ala nen it inenggaawak lek eerogo piyaagin~o.
61002002	Aakumi ambik nen it aap ti nogo, iniki nengge mugurok nugwi iigo logomenggaarik, "Nit togon ninom aret eerit nogo logowok~o," yinuk, inom eerit nogo logonet, Ala ndogop menggerak wone nogo woppunuk eerit nogwe nogo, "Yi nano wone agan nugu agaarik~o?" yinuk, miyuk-meya eerogo pogo logogun~o.
61002003	It aap mamuniraga ti nen ambi kolaawok nduk, kinambokan laganggo logonet, inoone ugun pilit pugunogo yokkirogo logogun~o. Togop yokkirogo logomenggaarak kwe, it eekwi paga at inowak loombunuk maluk inoba piyoorak maan koonogo pereegerak Ala nogo ti, we ugun maanggo yugu logonet nogo lumok ari wonage lek~o. Ata, ineebe lek eerogo piyoorak nduk abu li'luk eerak aret wonage agaarik~o.
61002004	It malayikat nogo mendek nen maluk eeko mbareegwa, Ala inabuwa nen teppiyareegerak mbakop? Lek~o. "Peebi kinowak loonogo pinagagin~o," yinuk, kani omoonu'me mbuun ambena kiiniki paga logowak nduk mbutigeele maarogo wuppiyareegerak wonogwe nogo lek a?
61002005	Ndi, it aakumi maan aa'nduk o nggween paga yime logonet, maluk eeko mbareegwa, Ala inabuwa nen teppiyareegerak mbakop? Lek~o. Mayu wuppi wagagerak nogo paga niyo yenggenit lagangge logonet, it aakumi Ala ineebi mba'nuk, maluk eekwi nogo tigitogon inooke kagak, "Kit maluk eeriyak mage~o. Ata, obeelom mban eerit nogo logonip~o," yinuk, Ala wone yorage nagagerak aap Nu nogo, akwe-apuri inom ineebe 8 mban inagap ndareegerak nogo lek a?
61002006	Ndi, at Ala nen, "It aakumi o Torom-Nggomora mendek kunduk maluk mban eekwi yi, neebi~o," yinuk, kani wurabit wage logonet, pup eerogo piyareegerak nogo ti, it aap peebi Ala ineebi mba'nuk, maluk eekwi nogo nen, "Nit togop aret ninoorigin kagi," mbako logowak nduk, eereegerak nogo lek a?
61002007	-
61002008	Ndi, at aap Lot iniki obeelom aret wonagagerak kwe, it aakumi ti, inenggela'me logonet, Ala wone taganogo punuk, iniki nen nengge kenok ugun-ugun eerit nogwe nogo enegen iige, inoone ugun agan nogwe nogo aruk konengge, eeke logonet, at iniki mondok abe koonak me, "Yi eekwi yi, ao," yinuk, ko'lu-kii'me iniki mondok wakko'net unggwage Ala nen kage nagagerik, it aakumi ti, pup eerogo piige logonet, at aap obeelom aret me, agap ndareegerak nogo lek a?
61002009	Ala nen togop aret eeginabit wundi wagagerak me, nit at apuri at oone eerit nugwi nogo aaninggin mendek ninoba age kenok, ninagap ndake, ndi, it obeelom eekwi lek maluk eeko menggaarak nogo peebi age yobok paga inowak loonogo punuk, maluk inoba kwippiige, eeriyak nogo at eenu aret me, eerigin aret mbako logowok~o.
61002010	-
61002011	It togop eeppiyoorak nogo ti, mbuuluk negen eeppiyoorak kwe, it aakumi nen, "Nit maluk eeko logowok~o," yinuk, iniki nen nengge kenok, ugun eerit nogwe, Ala nen wone lengganogo yorage nogo taganogo punuk, at eebe miyuk-meya eerogo pugwi, eekwi nogo perak, aaninggin mondok ndonggok togon inoba piige kaagun. It malayikat nogo ti, inomaawi ambik inayuk warak me, Ala yogo logonet, "It aap kat ari menggendak kagak pilit pugunogo yorogo menggaarak nogo ti, mondok maluk eekwi me, kat ninogoba nen mondok inooke logot~o," yinuk, inoone omaawi paga Ala yoriyak op kwe, inagabiti warak me, we yanggorogon yogo menggaarak. Yanggorogon togop aret yogo menggaarak kwe, it aap pilit wone yaga ti nen perak, "Ninagabiti~o," yinuk, inaganak waka'lek iniki wogoppako logonet, kugi inom, malayikat inom, abok aret ugun miyuk-meya eerogo piinet nogo menggaarak.
61002012	-
61002013	Wam nggwiya nda'nogo nagaatik, iniki lek ugun eerit nugwi iigak, aakumi nen pippiinok, inoorogo lako mengga kwak, it aap ti, togop aret iniki lek me, we ugun ambi eeriyak aganake kenok mban eerit nogo logonet, wone ineenggo'lek kagak, miyuk-meya eerogo pugwi me, wam nggwiya inoorogo lako mengga kwak, it maluk eekwi onggo at Ala nen aaninggin inoba kwippiige logonet, ineebe togop aret inoorigin~o. It iniki nengge nogo mugurok nogo logonet, inagabiti nen kote eeriyak mbaka'lek tena'me aret eerit noorak inikilom mbako menggaarak me, kinambokan laganiyak inikilom mbako logonet, kinom lambunna'nuk, mbi nunggwi me, inagabolo mili inawin aaga'ne kunik nogo pogom, it aap ti, kinenggela'me togop aret menggaarak~o.
61002014	Ti eeko logonet, it inigen alik ambi paga pugwi lek~o. Ata, kumi we ugun ya wurinakak nogo mban inigen wogoren nogo logonet, ugun-ugun eeginabit nogo nagaatik, "A! Yi abu eekirak me, ndonggoppanigi," yinuk, yogolik, nabenak mban eerit nogo logonet, it aap iniki awo kole aga'lek nogo, inenggaanok nggerok yuwak nduk, nomoniren keele pugume piya nogo menggaarak. It yi mendek ndi mendek koloorak uugwe mbako menggaarak me, ti kolaawok nduk, "Wone ngge yoraawok~o," yinuk, iniki koombunuk agan nugwi nogo paga, Ala nen mondok pulunogo piyareegerak wonogo agaarik~o.
61002015	Aap Mbeyot aput Mbileyam nogo nen maluk eekwi onggo koloorak iniki lunik logonet, Ala nen yereegerak kagak, alik eerit nagagerak nogo ndak-ndak, it aap ti, togop aret tu koonak noorak kagak mbo punuk, tu alik paga nomoninuk, nogo agaarik~o.
61002016	At aap Mbileyam nogo maluk eerit nage logonet, obaabut kumili negen eeke mbareegi, at eerit nage nogo teppuwak nduk, keledai oone lek aruk logu aret kwe, aakumi inoone negen ari logonet, at Ala wone yoraga nogo mberereegerak.
61002017	-
61002019	Aap ambi nen ogoba abu'me logonet, aruk konok mban eeke menggi kwak, it aap pilit pugunggo menggaarak ti nen maluk eeriyak aganake kenok, tebenogo pugwi lek eerit noorak mban aganake me, it maluk eekwi ti, ayeloman negen aret kwe, kagak, wogoppako logonet, it aap ngget iluk maluk eeriyak, "Nineebi~o," yinuk, mbo pegaarak nogo iniki nggaganggo logonet, "We ugun eeko logorak mendek kagak, nano nduk mu-mage mban yogo ogotik?" yinuk, iniki nengge nogo mban mugurok nawak nduk, inikime manabit nogo menggaarak me, wone alom lek kagak, ugun yorogo menggaarak~o. It aap ti, niyo eneeri poronak kwak logonet, inoone o wiya nen ameraakot wonok nage menggi kwak yogo menggaarak me, at Ala nen o apit me logowak nduk, inake ogobakkigirogo pereegerak wonage agaarik~o.
61002020	"Ninagap ndaka ninowe Yetut Keritut nineenu me, nggween paga yime maluk eeriyak ee'ninake menggerak nogo nineebi~o," yinuk, inambo'me mbo pereegwaarak kwe, ti'nuk, aa'nduk eeko nogogwaarak nogo, inikime aberogo eerit nogwe iinok, inobaabut aa'nduk mbuuluk obeelom negen logonet, eeko nogogwaarak kwe, peebi irip paga nen abunuk, maluk nggwok aret eekkologo menggaarak me,
61002021	it aakumi maluk eeko menggaarak nogo nen Ala ari menggerak wone woppunuk, eerit noorak wone nogo, ineenggo'lek logonet, maluk eerit nogo logonetak en ti, op negen kwe, wone, "Yogop ee'nu, ndogop ee'nu," yugu alik leenak nogo, abu ineenu logonet, maluk eekwi ti perak, abu maluk lombok aret~o.
61002022	"Nggeewo nen peyak wurogo punuk, ti'nuk, melak togon nengge menggerak~o," yinuk, yogwe, ndi, ambi, "Wam ngguu'mo amuni mbanogo wappiigaatak kwe, ti'nuk, iniyok paga yungguninuk purok me wanggini wari unggwogo menggaarak~o," yinuk, yogwe, eeko monggoorak nogo ti, abet aret yogo monggoorak me, it nogo ti, ti ndak-ndak aret eerit nogo menggaarak~o.
61003001	Nowe-nawot~o. Kit an niniki kunik me, liiru ambi aa'nduk mbanggiragagirak nogo ndak-ndak, yogondak ambi yi inom aret mbanggiragi~o. Liiru mbanggirage yi nogo ti, kiniki abe mban koonggo logorak abeko logobagip nduk, mbanggiragagirak me, ambi yi inom aret mbanggiragi~o.
61003002	It maan aa'nduk Ala nen aap at oone yorogo logowak nduk, leenogo piyareegerak wone yorogo nogogwaarak nogo inom, ndi, ninagap ndaka ninowe nen, "Yogop eeko logowak~o," yinuk, it aap nappiigak mendek yorage kagak, yokkirogo nogogwaarak nogo inom, kit abeko logobagip nduk, liiru yi mbanggiragi~o.
61003003	Kit kineenu arubagip nduk, wone aa'nduk lombok yi aret yokkira~o. Peebi o age yobok paga it aakumi miyuk-meya eerogo piigwi, iniki nen nengge kenok mugurok nogwe, eeka nogo nen, wogo logomenggaarik,
61003004	yogo logonet, "O yi, maan Ala nen wakkagagerak kuli nen, nok, yogondak kuli alik aga'lek itok menggerak kagak, ninombomini nen, O yi, lek eeri woraagin~o, yogwe iigak, kambit nogogwaarak me, Woraagin, yereegerak nogo, eebe wage lek, ngge?" yinuk, miyuk-meya eerogo pinagagwi iyaamunggup~o.
61003005	-
61003006	Ti yogwe nogo ti, Ala oone paga nen mbogut wakkage, nggween wakkage, eeke logonet, niyo mban wonage mbareegi, Ala nen, "Nggween aruwak~o," ari kagak, niyo inikime nen nggween aret kin age, ti'nuk, ti eyom paga mban peebi mayu nappi wagagerak nogo paga niyo yenggenit lagangge logonet, o aa'nduk wakkagagerak nogo maluk eerogo pege, eereegerak nogo ineenu logonet kwe, taganogo mbo pogo menggaarak~o.
61003007	Ndi, yogondak mbogut-nggween ninigen kogo monggoorak yi nogo ti, peebi it aakumi Ala ineebi mba'nuk, maluk eeko menggaarak nogo inawone amburu mbanogo inowak loombunuk, ineebe lek eerogo piyoorak eyom nogo paga, o yi, kani pikit nduk, at oone paga porogo wonage wone nogo, it kobak logonet agan nugwi me, peebi age yobok paga eeke kaagun~o.
61003008	Ti agan nogo logomenggaarak kwe, nowe-nawot~o. Kit an niniki kunik me, wone ambiriluk yokkiraagin yi, kobak eerogo mbo pugup~o. Nit nen o ne ambit weege mbakwi nogo, at ninogoba Ala nen tahun seribu aret mbake, ndi, nit nen tahun seribu mbakwi nogo, at nen o ne ambit weege mbake, eeke menggerak~o.
61003009	Togop me, ninowe nen, "An peebi woraagin~o," yinuk, yereegerak nogo, it aakumi ando nen, "Mbet-mbet waga'lek yi, pilit yereegerak kwa?" yinuk, mbakwi nogo kwak, kit togop mbako logogup~o. Ata, "Ala nen, Aakumi maluk eeppiyoorak ti, neebi~o, mba'nuk, nit yi aakumi ndi aakumi abok aret niniki koonogo punuk, ninomaluk mbo puwok nduk, iniki yanggoppunuk, to'ninake wonage," mbako logonip~o.
61003010	At ninowe woroorak nogo ti, "Ne ti eyom woraagin," mbaka'lek kiigak, aap yogoot wagangga nogo pogom abera'lek me woraagin~o. Ndi, wage kenok, mbogut yi, telangge logonet lek age, tut-laaluguragan mbogut paga menggerak inom, nggween yi inom, nggween paga wonogwe inom, abok aret kani nenet nage, eeke kaamunggup~o.
61003011	-
61003012	Yi mendek ndi mendek abok togop aret lek arigin me, nit ninobaabut nonggop logonet eerit nogo logowok mbakop? Lek~o. Ninowe wage eyom paga mbogut kani nanet nage, ndi, tut-laaluguragan kani eyak mondok aganggen alik nen amburu tigi-tigi wungge logonet, lek eerogo pege, eerigin me, "Ninowe mbet-mbet woraawak~o," yinuk, tokkogo logonet, nineebe apit Ala ake leenogo punuk, maluk eeka'lek ninobaabut mondok obeelom logonet ninowe mugurok nogo logowok~o.
61003013	At Ala nen, "Mbogut-nggween ngget mendek ogobakkigirogo pu-nuk, aakumi obeelom eeko menggaarak kenok mban time logowak nduk, unde eeppiyaagin~o," yinuk, abok yo'niragagerak nogo unde eeppinanuwak nduk, tokkogo ogoorik~o.
61003014	Togop me, nowe-nawot~o. Kit an niniki kunik me, wone ambi yokkira~o. "Nit o ti unde eeppinanuwak~o," yinuk tokkogwe me, maluk kinoba lenggenggwi, aakumi inoone kinoba pugwi, eeka'lek kiniki abu obeelom Ala kinom kiniki ambit lambunik wonogwe me kiya woraawak nduk, kulinik-kalinik kiniki ndegenggologo logonip~o.
61003015	-
61003016	At ninore niniki kunik Pawulut nogo nen yi mbuku ndi mbuku abok aret liiru mbangge logonet, an wone yokkiragarak yi nogo ti, inom aret mbangge menggerak kwe, at liiru mbangge menggerak nogo ti, wone ando taberak negen mbangge menggerak me, it aakumi Ala wone awo liippega'lek mendek iniki kole aga'lek nogo nen, ineebe lek eerogo patuwok nduk, Ala wone yugu liiru mbanak ando abut laganogo yorogo logonet, Pawulut liiru taberak negen mbangge menggerak nogo togop aret abut laganogo yorogo menggaarak nineenu kwe, Ala nen at Pawulut iniki nggaganogo yoge kagak, iniki warak nen liiru mbanggiragagerak nogo ndak-ndak, an togon liiru mbanggirage logonet, "Ninowe mbet-mbet waga'lek kenok ti, nit abok ninagap ndaruwak nduk to'niige me, niniki ndegenggologo logorak nanonggwan aret~o," yinuk, mbako logobagip nduk, liiru yi, mbanggiragi~o.
61003017	Ti kenok, nowe-nawot~o. Kit an niniki kunik me, wone yokkiragarak nogo ti, abu kineenu aret~o. Kineenu aret me, it Ala wone taganogo punuk inoone ugun agan nugwi paga nomongginakwi iinok, kit wone abet mba'nuk waganeegutak mondok nu'lek obeelom porogo wonogwe nogo, mbo punuk, it agan nugwi nogo mugurok nogo logokwak, mondok kinagaket paga logonip~o.
61003018	Ninogoba Ala iniki kunik nen eeppinanege menggerak nogo kit kiniki kole aruwak nduk, ambinom eeppinagage, ndi, at ninagap ndaka ninowe Yetut Keritut eebe kineenu aret kwe, ambinom kineenu arubagip nduk, eerogo pinagage, eeke logogin~o. Yogondak nen, nok, mondok logorak kuli at eebe mondok tiyanak aret logowak~o, yinuk, an Peterut nen abu aret yokkiragi~o. Wa!
62001001	Mbogut-nggween yi, awo wakkaga'lek kagak aa'nduk togon wonagagerak aakumi ineenik eeginake menggerak at Wone nogo, abok paganogo yokkirogo ogoorik~o. At oone ninaruk konenggwi, eebe ninigen abe nen kogwe, eerit nage nogo liippugwi, eereegurak eebe lombok nogo aret nineenggi pigaganeegurak~o.
62001002	Ndi, eebe nineenggi pigaganeegurak nogo kin age mbareegi, ninigen kogogurak nogo aret paganogo yokkirogwe, ndi, nit mondok-mondok nineenik logowok nduk, ee'ninake menggerak ninogoba imbirak wonagagerak eebe nineenu aruwok nduk, kin agagerak nogo, "Yi aret~o," yinuk, yokkirogwe, eeko ogoorik~o.
62001003	Nit ninogoba Ala aput Yetut Keritut imbirak ninom kunik wonogwe me, kit kunduk, ninom niniki ambit kunik logowok nduk, ninigen kogwe, ninaruk konenggwi, eereegurak nogo aret yokkirogo ogoorik~o.
62001004	Ndi, paganogo yokkirogwe yi nogo abok aret, nit niniki ale'nggen mondok nggwok aruwak nduk, liiru yi, mbanggirogo ogoorik~o.
62001005	"At Ala ti, o eya kwak menggerak me, at inikime o apit aago kwak wonage abu lek~o," yinuk, at Wone nogo nen yo'niragagerak ninaruk konembunuk, yokkirogwe nogo ti aret.
62001006	Togop me, nit o apit paga nugu logonet, "An Ala nimbirak kunik wonage~o," yogwe kwe, Ala ari menggerak wone ndak-ndak eeka'lek logonet yogwe me, pilit aret pugunggo monggoorak.
62001007	Togop kwe, at Ala o eya paga wonage menggi kwak, nit o eya paga nogwe niinok perak, ninoreewi ninom kunik aret logogun me, at aput Yetut amiya paga ninomaluk abok aret lek eerogo pinanegak mban eeke logogin~o.
62001008	Nit maluk eeko logonet kwe, "Nit maluk eekulik~o," yogwe niinok, pilit aret ninambokan laganggologwe me, Ala ndogop menggerak wone nogo ninikime wonage abu lek aret~o.
62001009	Ndi, ninomaluk abet aret paganggwi niinok perak, at Ala yegetak mbeyok ariilik, a'me liirogon mban eeke menggerak me, nit obeelom eeka'lek maluk eerit nugwi nogo lek eerogo pege, ndi, maluk ninikime wonage nogo koo'ninake, eeke logogin~o.
62001010	"Nit maluk abu eekulik aret~o," yogwe niinok, at Ala pilit pugungga negen eerogo pugwi me, at ari menggerak wone nogo nit ninikime wonage abu lek aret mbako logowok~o.
62002001	Napuri~o. Kit an niniki kunik me, maluk eekwi kiyo, wone yi, liiru mbanggiragi~o. Togop kwe, nit ambi nen maluk eekwi niinok, at a'me nggelok eeke menggerak Yetut Keritut nogo nen nit ninake wone wonok ninogoba yori nagak eeke menggerak~o.
62002002	Ala iniki yanggo yuwak nduk, ninomaluk lek eerogo punuk, Ala ninom lambunogo pinaniyak ninake eeka ti, at Yetut aret~o. Nit mban ninomaluk lek eerogo punuk, Ala ninom lambunogo pinaniyak nduk, ninake eeke ti lek~o. Ata, nit yi aakumi ndi aakumi o nggween paga yime monggoorak abok aret ninomaluk lek eerogo punuk, Ala ninom lambunogo pinaniyak nduk, ninake eeke menggerak~o.
62002003	Ala nen, "Yogop ee'nu, ndogop ee'nu," wone yo'nirage nogo ndak-ndak eekwi paga, "Nit Ala apuri abet aret wonogwe kogo~o," yinuk, yogo monggoorak kwe,
62002004	aap ambi nen Ala wone yo'nirage nogo eeka'lek logonet, "An Ala aput aret~o," ari kenok perak, Ala ndogop menggerak wone nogo at inikime lek kagak ari me, aap ti pilit pugungga aret~o.
62002005	-
62002006	Ndi, aap ambi nen Ala wone yugu nogo ndak-ndak eeke kenok perak, aap ti mondok abet aret Ala iniki kunik lombok eeke menggerak. "Nit Ala ninom kunik wonogwe~o," yogo logonet, at Yetut eeke nagagerak ndak-ndak eekwi ti paga, Ala ninom abet aret kunik wonogwe nineenu ogo monggoorak.
62002007	Noreewi~o. Kit an niniki kunik me, an nen, "Yogop eeko logonip~o," yinuk, liiru mbanggirage yi ti, wone ngget mendek liiru mbanggirage lek~o. Wone yi, o maan togon kinaruk konenit wundi wogo monggotak nogo aret liiru mbanggirage kwe,
62002008	o apit lek age kagak o eya abe lombok unggwi wage logonet, wone maan yugu nogo aret Keritut nen eerit nage, ndi, kit nen niniki-kiniki kunik eekko'net nugwi, eekwi paga kin age me, wone ngget yugu negen aret kenok, liiru mbanggiragi~o.
62002009	Aap ambi nen, "An o eya paga nage agarik~o," ari logonet kwe, awot eebi mbake kenok, aap ti, iniki o apit pogom yogondak wonage aret~o.
62002010	Ndi, aap ambi nen at awot iniki kunik eeke kenok perak, at o eya paga nage me, nage logonet, aganak kolaagin lek kwe,
62002011	aap ambi nen at awot eebi mbake kenok perak, aap ti, iniki o apit pogom logonet, o apit paga wonage menggerak~o. O apit nen at enegen mbuk eerogo pereegerak me, "An o ndime aret nage agarik," mbaka'lek aret menggerak~o.
62002012	Napuri niniki kunik yi wae. At Keritut eereegerak nogo paga Ala nen kinomaluk lek eerogo pinagareegerak me, Kinake liiru yi, mbanggirage,
62002013	Nogobamini yi wae. At o aa'nduk nen nok-nok yogondak kuli itok mondok menggerak kit kineenu ogogutak me, Kinake liiru yi, mbanggirage, Nawuri yi, wae. At maluk ee'ninaka nogo tebenogo pogotak me, Kinake liiru yi mbanggirage, Eeke agarik~o. Kit an napuri niniki kunik yi, wae. Ninogoba Ala kineenu ogogutak me, Liiru yi, mbanggirage,
62002014	Kit an nogobamini yi wae. At o aa'nduk nen nok-nok, yogondak kuli itok mondok-mondok menggerak kineenu ogogutak me, Liiru yi, mbanggirage, Kit an nawuri yi wae. Kit Ala wone kinikime kologo nogogutik, kiniki kole ogogutak nogo nen at maluk ee'ninaka nogo tebenogo pereegutak me, Liiru yi, mbanggirage, Eeke agarik~o.
62002015	It aap nggween paga mendek nen iniki koombunuk eeko menggaarak inom, yi mendek ndi mendek nggween paga mendek inom, abok aret kiniki kunik eerugup~o. It aap nggween paga mendek nen iniki koombunuk eekwi nogo kinikilom mbakwi kiinok, ninogoba kiniki kunik eeko logomunggup lek aret~o.
62002016	It aap nggween paga mendek nen iniki nengge kenok mugurok nogwe nogo inom, inigen pekkenok, uugwe mbakwi nogo inom, "An koongge mban iya~o," yinuk, wogoppatit nugwi nogo inom, ti eeko menggaarak abok aret eerit nugu logowak nduk ninogoba nen koonggeelik~o. Ata, it aap nggween paga mendek nen aret iniki koombunuk, eeko menggaarak~o.
62002017	It aap nggween paga mendek nen iniki koombunuk eekwi inom, yi mendek ndi mendek iniki nengge kenok mugurok nogwe inom, abok aret lek arigin kwe, Ala iniki mbake menggerak nogo, kit ndak-ndak eekwi kiinok perak, mondok-mondok kineenik aret logomunggup~o.
62002018	Napuri niniki kunik yi wae. O age yobok paga eeriyak nogo muk panggo yegerak~o. Ndi, "Pilit Keritut woraagin," koneneegutak nogo, yogondak ti mendek ineebe ambik muk mi'nagaarak wonogwe ti paga, "Ie! O age yobok paga eeriyak nogo muk panggo yegerak kagi," yinuk, mbako ogoorik~o.
62002019	It aap ti, aa'nduk ninom kuwak eeko nogogurak kwe, "It ti, nit mendek lek~o," yinuk, mbo pinaninuk mbaganeegwaarak. "It aap ti, nit mendek aret," mba'netak en, ninom aret logonetak kwe, "It ti, nit mendek lek," kin aruwak nduk, mbo pinaninuk mbaganeegwaarak~o.
62002020	Kit perak, aap ambi eeke logowak nduk, leenogo punuk amburu kilippogo mengga kwak, at maluk eekeelik alik leenak menggerak nogo nen, kit leenogo pinaganuk, Aberiniki wokkiragagerak me, wone abe wone mamunggirage nogo, kit abok kineenu aret kiigi~o.
62002021	Ala ndogop menggerak wone nogo kit kineenggo'lek me nduk liiru yi mbanggirage lek~o. Kineenu aret me, it aap nen Ala ndogop menggerak wone yogo logonet, alik ambi inom nabenogo yogwe iinok, "Yi pilit aret yogwe~o," yinuk, yelok kaabagip nduk liiru yi, mbanggirage agarik~o.
62002022	Aap pilit pugungga ti, ta mbakop? Lek~o. Aap ambi nen, "Yetut ti, Keritut lek~o," ari kenok, pilit pugungga at aret~o. "Yetut ti, Keritut lek~o," yogwe ti paga Ala aput Yetut inom, ogoba Ala inom, "Nineebi~o," yinuk, mbo pugwi me, Pilit Keritut nogo it aret~o.
62002023	Aput Yetut mbo pugwi kenok, ogoba kunduk mbo pugwi, ndi, "Yetut ti, Ala aput Keritut aret~o," yinuk, waganggwi iinok perak, ogoba kunduk waganggwi, eeko menggaarak~o.
62002024	Kit perak, o maan aa'nduk togon wone konembunuk, waganeegutak nogo, kinikime mondok aberak logonet, porogo logonip~o. Mondok nu'lek porogo wonogwe kiinok, ninogoba Ala aput imbirak kinom kunik aret logomunggup~o.
62002025	Nit ee'ninaburak Ala nen koonogo pereegerak nogo ti, "Kit mondok-mondok kineenik logobagip nduk, eekkinabigin~o," yinuk, yo'niragagerak ti aret~o.
62002026	It nen kit kinambo'me laganggo logonet, nomonggiren nogwe iyo, liiru yi mbanggiragi~o.
62002027	Napuri~o. Aberiniki kinoba wuppinagi wagagerak kinikime wonage me, aap ambi nen kit mamunggiroorak lek aret~o. At nen yi wone ndi wone abok aret mamunggirage logonet, pilit mamunggirageelik abet mban mamunggirage menggerak me, at mamunggirage nogo ti, ndak-ndak eekwi kiinok, Keritut kinom kunik aret logomunggup~o.
62002028	Ndi, napuri niniki kunik yi wae. Peebi at woroorak nogo eyom paga nit ninenggali lek niniki teeluk logowok nduk, yogondak nen niniki ambit a'nuk Yetut ninom kunik aret logowok~o.
62002029	At Keritut ti, abe koonak mban eeke menggerak kineenu me, it aap obeelom eeko menggaarak nogo, "Yi at Ala nen aret ndaganabeegerak kagi~o," yinuk, abet aret mbarumunggup~o.
62003001	Nit at apuri abet aret wonogwe me, at Ala nen, "Kit an napuri aret~o," yo'nirage ti paga at ninogoba ninabuwa nggwok mondok alik negen mbake menggerak ti, kaanip~o. It aakumi nggween paga mendek mban mugurok nogwe nogo nen aa'nduk Ala yelok kaga'lek wonogogwaarak kwak, yogondak at apuri nit kunduk yelok niiga'lek aret agaarik~o.
62003002	Noreewi~o. Kit an niniki kunik me, wone ambi yokkira~o. Nit yogondak aret Ala apuri ogoorik~o. Ndi, peebi nonggop eeppinanege kenok wonogo logorak nogo, nit awo kin kaga'lek kwe, at wage kenok, "Etenggen yi kwak eeppinaniyak nduk, wonogoorak kagi," yinuk, mbakwi niigak, "At etenggen kokwak eeppinanigin, nineenu aret ogoorik~o."
62003003	Nit eeppinaniyak nogo niniki lunik wonogwe niinok, at Keritut iniki kikak naka'lek wonage nogo pogom, nit ndak-ndak niniki kikak naka'lek aret eekkologo logowok~o.
62003004	Maluk eekwi ti, Ala wone yugu aret taganggwi me, aap ambi maluk eeke kenok ti, Ala wone yugu nogo aret taganogo punuk eeke menggerak~o.
62003005	At Keritut maluk abu eekeelik aret me, nit ninomaluk lek eerogo pinanikit nduk, wambi wagagerak nogo kineenu aret mbako~o.
62003006	Aap ambi at Keritut imbirak kunik wonage kenok, at maluk eerit nageelik aret~o. Ndi, aap ambi maluk eerit nage menggerak kenok perak, Keritut enegen kage, eebe eenu age, eeka'lek aret wonage menggerak~o.
62003007	Napuri niniki kunik yi, wae. It aakumi ugun nen kit nomonggiren nogwe iyo, liippogo logonip~o. Aap ambi maluk eeka'lek obeelom mban eeke kenok, at Keritut maluk eekeelik mondok obeelom mban wonage nogo pogom aret menggerak~o.
62003008	At Tile o maan iyaalok nen maluk eerit wundi wage menggerak me, aap ambi maluk mban eeke menggerak kenok, at Tile aput aret menggerak. Ndi, at Ala aput wambi wagagerak nogo ti, at Tile nen yi eekak ndi eekak eeke menggerak nogo abok aret, mondok lek eerogo pikit nduk, wambi wagagerak.
62003009	Aap ambi Ala nen ndake kenok, at Ala obaabut aret wagangge me, at maluk eeke logogin lek~o. At Ala nen aret ndaremenggerak me, at maluk eeke logorak ti meek~o.
62003010	Ala apuri inom, Tile apuri inom, nano paga nineenu ariyak nogo yi aret. It aakumi obeelom eeka'lek maluk mban eekwi, inowe-inawot iniki kunik eekwi lek ineebi mbakwi, eekwi iinok ti, Ala apuri lek aret yelok iigo monggoorak.
62003011	O maan aa'nduk nen wone konenggo nogogutak nogo ti, "Niniki-kiniki kunik eeko logonip~o," yinuk, yo'niragagerak ti aret.
62003012	At Kayin nen eereegerak nogo pogom, kit togop eeriyak mage~o. Maluk eeriyak ee'ninake menggerak aput at aret me, awuluk mondok wareegerak. Nonggop nduk awuluk wareegerak mbakop? Lek~o. At Kayin maluk mban eeke menggerak me, awuluk obeelom mban eeke kage nagagerik, anini nen aret awuluk wareegerak.
62003013	Togop kenok, noreewi~o. It aakumi nggween paga mendek mban mugurok nogwe nogo nen ineebi kinombakwi iinok, "Ie," yinuk, kinagabiti mbarugup~o.
62003014	Nit ninoreewi ninom niniki kunik eeginakwi ti paga, kanggo menggam nen nineenik ee'ninake menggim muk pinani wagagerak wonogwe nineenu ogoorik~o. Aap ambi nen aakumi iniki kunik aganake lek kenok, at kanggo menggam time awo aret wonage agaarik~o.
62003015	Aap ambi at awot eebi lombok mbake kenok, at aakumi inooka aret~o. Ndi, aakumi inooka nogo ti, at mondok-mondok ineenik logorak mendek unde eekkolaga'lek ti, kineenu aret~o.
62003016	Nano eekwi paga ninoreewi niniki kunik eeginakwi nogo nineenu ariyak mbakop? Lek~o. At Yetut iniki nen, "An aakumi inake nooruwak aret~o," mba'nuk, ninake kambeegerak ti kokwak, nit togon, ninoreewi inabuwa nen inake kambuurak op aret mbakwi kenok, aakumi iniki kunik eeginakwi nogo ti aret.
62003017	Aap ambi eenggi warak nen ore aaninggin oba agaarak enegen kage kwe, abuwa mbaka'lek, "Obaalombok~o," yinuk, mbo pege kenok, Ala nen aakumi inabuwa mbake menggerak nogo mendek inikime wonage abu lek aret mbako logowok~o.
62003018	Napuri niniki kunik yi wae. Nit ninoone paga nen mban, "Aakumi ninom niniki kunik wonogwe~o," yinuk, yuurak mage~o. Ata, niniki paga nen aret inabuwa lombok mbako logonet, obeelom eeppiinet nogo logowok~o.
62003019	-
62003020	Nit eeko monggoorak nogo Ala enggaanom paga abe'nage logonet, maluk ambi eekoorak paga niniki nen ninenggali wappinanege kenok, ninagabiti mbariyak kwe, nit yi eekak ndi eekak eeko monggoorak nogo inom, ninikime ee'ninake menggerak nogo inom, abok aret at Ala eenu me, nit Ala enggaanom paga, "An aakumi inabuwa nen obeelom eeppiinet nage nagagirak nogo paga kat Ala ari menggendak nogo an ndak-ndak eeke nagagirak~o," mba'nuk, ninagabiti lek logonet, at yoriyak op aret~o.
62003021	Noreewi niniki kunik yi wae. Nit ambi eekoorak paga ninikime nen ninenggali wappinanega'lek kenok, Ala enggaanom paga ninagabiti mbariyak lek~o.
62003022	At Ala nen, "Yogop ee'nu, ndogop ee'nu," yinuk, yo'nirage menggerak wone inom, at eeriyak inikilom mbake menggerak nogo inom, ndak-ndak eekwi me, nit yi mendek ndi mendek wo'niraawak nduk, nggino yogwi nogo, at wo'nirage logogin aret~o.
62003023	"Kit kiniki an naput Yetut Keritut oba panggombunuk abet mbakwi, ndi, an nen yokkiragagirak nogo ndak-ndak kinoreewi kiniki kunik aganakwi, eeko logonip~o," yinuk, wone lengganogo yo'nirage nogo ti aret.
62003024	Wone, "Yogop ee'nu, ndogop ee'nu," yo'nirage menggerak wone nogo, kit ambi nen ndak-ndak eekwi kiinok, Ala kit kinom kunik wonage, ndi, kit at kinom kunik wonogwe, eeko logomunggup~o. Ndi, Aberiniki wo'niragagerak ninikime wonage ti paga at Ala abet aret nit ninom kunik wonage nogo nineenu ogo~o.
62004001	Noreewi niniki kunik yi wae. "Aberiniki nen yo'nirage kenok, yokkira wogo~o," yogwe iinok, inoone abet mba'nuk ugun woorak mage~o. It pilit wone yoraga nogo nen yi awi ndi awi abok aret yoranet nugwi me, "At Ala nen abet aret nappiya wagaarak agan wogwe ilik, it iniki koombunuk nen agan wogwe a?" yinuk, inabut mbambunuk inoone konenggo logomunggup~o.
62004002	"Ala Aberiniki inikime logonet, agan wogwe ilik," yinuk, yelok kogo logorak nogo yi aret. "Yetut Keritut abet aret nggween paga wambi wage nagagerik, aap aret nda'nagagerak~o," yinuk, paganggwi iinok, "Aap ti, Ala nen abet aret nappiya wagagerak Aberiniki inikime logonet, yogwe iigo~o," yinuk, inoone konenggo logorak op kwe,
62004003	it aap ti nen wone ti, paganggwi lek iinok perak, "Aap ti, Ala nen nappiya woroolik iniki mba'nuk aret wagaarak," mbarumunggup~o. "O age yobok togon Pilit Keritut wage logomenggerik, ndogop agan wage logogin~o," yinuk, yogwe koneneegutak nogo, "Muk wagaarak yi aret iigo~o," yinuk, mbarumunggup~o.
62004004	Napuri niniki kunik yi wae. Kit Ala apuri aret~o. Ndi, kit Ala apuri aret me, at omaawi ambik Aberiniki wokkiragagerak kinikime wonage nogo ti, omaawi ambik, ndi, it aap nggween paga mendek mban mugurok nugwi inikime wonage nogo ti, omaawi mbuuluk me, it Ala nen yorage kagak yoraga inetenggen kumbunuk agan wogwe ti, muk tebenogo piyareegutak~o.
62004005	It aap ti, nggween paga mendek mban mugurok nugwi nogo mendek aret me, it aap nggween paga mendek mban mugurok nugu menggaarak nen inoone yogwe iinok, it aap nggween paga mendek mban mugurok nugwi nogo nen inoone yogwe nogo inaruk konenggo menggaarak.
62004006	Ndi, nit perak, Ala apuri mbogut paga mendek aret me, nit ninoone yogwe nogo, it Ala inom kunik nogo nen mban inaruk konenggo menggaarak. Ndi, Ala apuri lek kenok perak, nit ninoone yogwe nogo konenggulik aret~o. Nit ninoone konengga'lek ti paga, "Aberiniki nen yorage kenok yogwe ilik, iniki koombunuk nen pilit yogwe a?" yinuk, nineenu ogo monggoorak.
62004007	Noreewi niniki kunik yi, wae. Aakumi niniki kunik aganako logowok nduk, Ala nen aret eeppinanege menggerak me, niniki-kiniki kunik eeko logowok~o. Ninoreewi niniki kunik aganakwi niinok, "It yi ti, Ala nen aret ndaganabeegerak me, inogoba Ala ineenu aret iigo~o," yinuk, yogo logogun~o.
62004008	Ndi, at Ala nen yi aap ndi aap abok aret inabuwa mbake logonet, iniki kunik lombok aganake kagak kwe, nit ninoreewi niniki kunik aganakwi lek niinok perak, "It aap yi, Ala ineenggo'lek aret iigo~o," yinuk, mbako logogun.
62004009	Nit nineenik logowok nduk, Ala nen at aput ambolom nggween paga nappi wagagerak ti paga, Ala abet aret ninabuwa mbake logonet, iniki kunik ee'ninake menggerak nogo ti, yelok kogo ogoorik~o.
62004010	Ninoreewi niniki kunik aganaburak nogo ti, ngge kokwak mbakop? Lek~o. Nit nen Ala niniki kunik eerulik~o. Ata, Ala ninabuwa nen iniki kunik ee'ninake nagagerik, ninomaluk lek eerogo pege logonet, ninom lambumbinanuwak nduk, at aput aret nappi wagagerak nogo kwak, nit togop aret ninoreewi niniki kunik aganako logowok~o.
62004011	Noreewi niniki kunik yi, wae! At Ala nen togop aret ninabuwa mbake logonet, iniki kunik ee'ninabeegerak me, nit togon ndak-ndak niniki-kiniki kunik eeko logowok~o.
62004012	Nit abok aret Ala eebe ninigen kaga'lek aret wonogwe kwe, niniki-kiniki kunik eekwi niinok perak, Ala ninom kunik logonet, aakumi ando eebi mbake, ando inikilom mbake, eekeelik abok aret inabuwa mbake menggi kwak, nit togop aret aakumi abok niniki kunik aganako logowok nduk, ee'ninake menggerak~o.
62004013	At Ala nen Aberiniki wo'niragagerak ti paga at nit ninom kunik wonage, ndi, nit at ninom kunik wonogwe, eekwi nogo nineenu aret~o.
62004014	Ndi, ninogoba nen yi aakumi ndi aakumi abok aret inagap ndaruwak nduk, at aput nappi wagagerak nogo ninigen kogo nogogurik, paganogo yokkirogo monggoorak.
62004015	Kit nen, "Yetut ti, Ala aput aret~o," yinuk, paganggwi kiinok, at Ala kit kinom kunik wonage, ndi, kit at kinom kunik wonogwe, eeko logomunggup~o.
62004016	At Ala ninabuwa mbake nagagerik, iniki kunik ee'ninabeegerak nogo, nineenu ogo nogoorik, "Abet aret," mba'nuk, niniki ti paga panggombunuk, ogoorik~o. At Ala nen nit yi aakumi ndi aakumi abok ninabuwa mbake logonet, iniki kunik ee'ninake menggerak me, kit kinoreewi kiniki kunik aganakwi kiinok, Ala kit kinom kunik wonage, ndi, kit Ala kinom kunik wonogwe, eeko logomunggup~o.
62004017	O peebi age yobok ninowak loonninaburak eyom paga, "At Yetut eeke nagagerak nogo kwak, nit o nggween paga yime logonet, ndak-ndak eeko nogogurak~o," mba'nuk, ninagabiti mbaka'lek niniki teeluk logowok nduk, Ala nen ambi eebi mbake, ndi, ambi abuwa mbake, eekeelik abok aret ninabuwa mbake menggerak nogo pogom, nit yogondak ti ndak-ndak aret eeko logowok~o.
62004018	Aap ambi nen oreewi inabuwa mba'nuk iniki kunik aganake kenok, oreewi nen at paga inagabiti ombarugun lek~o. At aap nogo nen abet aret inabuwa mbake me, inabuwa mbake ti paga inagabiti mbakwi nogo lek aret age menggerak kwe, ninagabiti mbakwi kenok ti perak, "Ninoreeluk maluk eeppogoorak me, onggo ninooke kaamun ilik," yinuk, ninagabiti mbakwi me, ninom niniki kunik lek aret mbako logowok~o.
62004019	Aa'nduk at Ala nen nit ninabuwa mba'nuk, iniki kunik ee'ninabeegerak me, yogondak nit togon togop aret aakumi inabuwa mba'nuk, niniki kunik aganako logowok~o.
62004020	Aap ambi at awot enegen kage logonet kwe, iniki kunik eekeelik kenok, at Ala enegen kaga'lek me nonggop togon iniki kunik eeriyak mbakop? Meek me, awot eebi ombake logonet, "An Ala niniki kunik eeke~o," ari kenok, aap ti pilit pugungga aret~o.
62004021	At Ala nen ari logonet, "Kit an kiniki kunik ee'nakwi kiinok, kinoreewi kunduk inabuwa mbako logonet, kiniki kunik aganako logonip~o," yinuk, wone lengganogo yo'niragagerak nogo ti aret.
62005001	Kit nen, "Yetut ti, Keritut aret~o," yinuk, abet mbakwi kiinok, Ala nen aret ndakkinabeegerak me, kit at apuri aret ogotik~o. Ndi, kinogoba Ala kiniki kunik eekwi kiinok ti, apuri ndarak nogo inom kiniki kunik eeginako logorak me,
62005002	nit nonggop eekwi paga Ala apuri niniki kunik aganakwi nineenu ariyak mbakop? Lek~o. Ala nen, "Yogop ee'nu, ndogop ee'nu," wone yo'nirage nogo eeko logonet, Ala niniki kunik eekwi ti paga at apuri niniki kunik aganakwi mbako monggoorak.
62005003	At Ala niniki kunik eekwi nogo ti, at nen, "Yogop ee'nu, ndogop ee'nu," yinuk, wone yo'nirage eekwi nogo ti aret. Ndi, at Ala nen wone, "Yogop ee'nu, ndogop ee'nu," yo'nirage nogo ti, aaninggin lek aret~o.
62005004	Nit Ala nda'ninabeegerak nogo nen it aakumi nggween paga mendek mban mugurok nogwe nogo tebenogo piigo monggoorak. It aakumi nggween paga mendek mban mugurok nogwe tebenogo piigwi nogo ti, nit abet mbakwi paga nen aret tebenogo piinok, nit tiyanak aret ogoorik.
62005005	Taani nen it aap nggween paga mendek mban mugurok nogwe nogo, tebenogo piigo menggaarak mbakop? Lek~o. Nit nen, "Yetut ti, Ala aput aret~o," yinuk, abet mbakwi nogo nen aret tebenogo piigo monggoorak kogo~o.
62005006	At niyome wuppege kogogurak nogo inom, ndi, kangge logonet, amiya wangge kogogurak nogo inom, ti, Yetut Keritut eebe aret~o. Niyome wuppege kogogurak nogo mban ti lek~o. Ata, at amiya wangge nogo inom kogo nogogurik, "Yi Yetut Keritut abet aret~o," yinuk, mbareegurak. Ndi, Aberiniki nogo ti, Ala ari menggerak ndak-ndak abet mban ari menggerak me, at nen kunduk, "Yi Yetut Keritut abet aret~o," yinuk, abok paganogo yo'nirage menggerak.
62005007	-
62005008	Togop me, Aberiniki nen yo'nirage inom, niyome wuppege kogogurak nogo inom, ndi, amiya wangge ninigen kogogurak nogo inom, wone kenagan ti aret eereegerak kwe, alom ambit, "Yetut ti, Keritut aret~o," yinuk, nineenu aruwok nduk, eereegerak.
62005009	Aakumi nen paganogo yo'nirogwe iinok ti, abet mba'nuk woorak op mbakwi kwe, nit abet mbaruwok nduk Ala nen alom kenagan paga, "Yetut ti, an naput aret~o," yinuk, eereegerak ti, mondok iya me, "Yi abet aret~o," yinuk, waganggo logowok~o.
62005010	Nit niniki Ala aput oba panggombunuk, abet mbakwi niinok, ninikime nen, "Yi Ala aput abet aret waganggoorak kogo~o," yinuk, mbako logogun~o. Ndi, it Ala abet mbaka'lek logonet, at aput iniki oba panggombunuk, abet mbaruwak nduk, paganogo yoragagerak nogo, abet mbaka'lek me, Ala pilit pugungga negen agago pogo logogun~o.
62005011	At Ala nen wone paganogo yo'niragagerak nogo yi aret~o. Nit nineenik mondok-mondok logowok nduk, Ala nen nabelan-kabelan wo'niragagerak me, at aput waganggwi niinok, nit mondok-mondok nineenik logogun ti aret.
62005012	Nit Ala aput waganggwi niinok, nineenik mondok-mondok logogun kwe, wagangga'lek niinok perak, nineenik logogun abu lek aret~o.
62005013	Kit kiniki Ala aput oba panggombunuk abet mbakwi nogo, Ala nen kineenik mondok-mondok logorak unde eeppinagareegerak kineenu arubagip nduk, liiru yi mbanggiragi~o.
62005014	At Ala iniki mbake nogo ndak-ndak wo'niraawak nduk, nggino yogwi niinok, at aruk konembunuk, wo'nirage menggerak nineenu me, ninagabiti mbaka'lek, "Wo'niraagin aret," mba'nuk, at nggino yogo logowok~o.
62005015	Nit nen at nggino yogwi nogo, at abet aret aruk konengge menggerak nineenu me, wo'niraawak nduk, nggino yogwi nogo ti, "Wo'niraagin aret," mbako logowok~o.
62005016	Aap ambi nen maluk eeriyak iniki miippatinuk eerit nage kinigen kogo logomonggotik, at kani omoonu'me noorak nduk, eekwi nogo mendek eerit nage me, ake Ala yorubagip nduk, yokkirage ti lek~o. Ata, kinore ambi Ala nen ninomaluk lek eerogo pinaniyak nogo mendek eeke kinigen kogwe kenok, Ala nen omaluk lek eerogo punuk, eenik mondok logorak mendek unde logowak nduk, "Ake Ala yogo logonip~o," yinuk, yokkiragi~o.
62005017	Yi maluk ndi maluk eekwi nogo ti, abok endage maluk aret kwe, ambi kani omoonu'me noorak nduk, miippunuk eekwi nogo mendek wonage kenok, yokkiragi~o, noreewi.
62005018	Aap ambi Ala nen ndareegerak kenok, at maluk eerit nageelik ti, nineenu aret~o. Ala aput Yetut nen aap ti, liirogon aret porogo menggerak me, at maluk eeka nogo nen aap ti, maluk eeppuurak mondok meek aret~o.
62005019	Yi aakumi ndi aakumi maluk eeko menggaarak nogo abok aret at maluk eeka Tile nogo abu'me wonogwe nineenu kwe, nit perak, Ala apuri aret ogoorik~o.
62005020	At Ala aput wambi wage nagagerik, Ala ambit alik lombok menggerak nogo nit liippuwok nduk nineenu eeppinaneegerak~o. Ndi, at alik lombok menggerak Ala aput Yetut Keritut imbirak ninom niniki ambit kunik aret ogoorik~o. At Yetut Keritut ti, at alik lombok menggerak Ala nogo aret me, nineenik mondok logorak unde eeppinanege menggerak alom at aret~o.
62005021	Napuri niniki kunik yi wa! At Ala alik lombok menggerak nogo mbo punuk, obaane'me alik ambi mippunuk, alut eekwi kiyo, liippogo logonip~o. Abu aret yokkiragi~o. Napuri wa!
63001001	Ala nen miikkabeegerak niriluk kat kaagalogwe kinom an Ala apuri inarum logokit nduk, mippaneegerak nogo nen, kit abet aret niniki kunik eekkinake minggirak me, wone ambi yokkira~o. An nen mban niniki kunik eekkinake ti lek~o. Ata, it aakumi nen Ala ndogop menggerak wone waganeegwaarak nogo abok ninom nen niniki kunik eekkinako~o.
63001002	Ala ndogop menggerak wone waganeegurak ninikime wonage nogo ti, mondok-mondok logogin aret me,
63001003	nit, "Ala ndogop menggerak," wone nogo woppunuk, mugurok nogo logonet, ninoreewi ninom niniki-kiniki kunik eerit nogwe niigak, ninogoba Ala at aput Yetut Keritut imbirak iniki kunik en wo'nirogwe, ninabuwa nen obeelom eeppinanugwi, niniki ugun tayenak ale'nggen logowok nduk, eeppinanugwi, eeko logowak~o.
63001004	At ninogoba Ala nen, "Yogop ee'nip~o," yo'niragagerak nogo kat kaagalogwe ando kinom ndak-ndak eerit nogwe konengge nagarik, an niniki abu ale'nggen mbakirak~o.
63001005	Ndi, niriluk~o. Yogondak ambi eeke logonok nduk, yokkiri. "Niniki-kiniki kunik eeko logonip~o," yinuk, yokkege yi nogo ti, wone ngget mendek lek~o. O maan aa'nduk togon konenggo nogogutak nogo aret yokkigi~o.
63001006	Niniki-kiniki kunik eeko logorak nogo ti, Ala wone yugu ndak-ndak eeko logorak ti aret. Niniki-kiniki kunik eerit nogo logorak wone ti, maan aa'nduk togon yo'niragagerak koneneegutak nogo aret yokkiragi~o.
63001007	It aap ando nen, "Yetut Keritut ti, aap kwak nggween paga yime nda'narulik~o," yinuk, aakumi inambo'me laganuwok nduk yoranet nogo menggaarak mendek yi o ndi o ineebe ambik aret wonogwe~o. It aap ti, Pilit Keritut negen logonet, pilit-pilit aret aakumi inambo'me laganggo menggaarak me,
63001008	nit nen yokkirogogurak waganeegutak nogo, kobak eerogo mbo pugwi kiinok, obeelom eekwi paga Ala nen onggo ndak-ndak wokkiroorak mbareegerak nogo, lek eerogo patukwak, kiniki liirogon tum wakkologo logonip~o.
63001009	Aap ambi Keritut wone mamunniragagerak nogo mban ari lek at iniki koombunuk, alik inom nabenogo yoranet nage kenok, at Ala imbirak kunik logonet ari lek~o. Ndi, Keritut wone mamunniragagerak nogo ndak-ndak eeke kenok perak, ninogoba Ala aput imbirak inom kunik aret logonet ari mbaruwok~o.
63001010	Aap ambi wone yi mendek lek alik mendek wonok yokkira wage kenok, keyage warogo kiname mambuurak mage~o.
63001011	Keyage warogo kiname mambugwi kiinok, at omaluk kit kinom ndak-ndak aret nabenggolaamunggup~o.
63001012	An wone ambik yokkiroorak nduk wonage kwe, liiru mbanggiroorak anggon ee'nake me, kiya wage logominggirik, ninom ninengga kunna'nuk, ninale'nggen paga wone li'lak aret mbaniyak uugwe mbake agarik~o.
63001013	Koweeluk Ala miireegerak aagalogwe nogo ninom nen keyage wakkinako~o. Wa!
64001001	Noreeluk Nggayut wae. "Ala ndogop menggerak~o," yinuk, wone nimbirak waganeegurak paga kat niniki kunik me, an Ala apuri inarum logokit nduk, mippaneegerak nogo nen wone ambi yokkiri~o.
64001002	Noreeluk~o. Kat an niniki kunik me, kat Ala wone liirogon mugurok nage logonet, kiniki abe koonogo patit nage menggendak nogo kwak, keebe andi lek obeelom aret logonet, yi mendek ndi mendek eeke menggendak nogo obeelom mban age kage logonok nduk, kake tamban eeke minggirak~o.
64001003	"Ala ndogop menggerak~o," yinuk, wone nogo woppunuk, eerit nage menggendak nogo, noreewi ando neya wogo nagaarik, "Nogo ndak-ndak aret eerit nage agaarik~o," yinuk, mbininogo yo'niri wogo mbaka, an niniki ale'nggen ambik aret mbakirak~o.
64001004	Yi mendek ndi mendek eerit nage nogo ti, nale'nggen mbuuluk mbake minggirak kwe, an napuri nogo nen, "Ala ndogop menggerak~o," yinuk, wone woppunuk, mondok ndak-ndak eerit nogwe naruk konengge kenok perak, niniki ale'nggen nggwok lombok mbake minggirak~o.
64001005	Noreeluk~o. Kat an niniki kunik me, wone ambi yokkiri~o. Kat kulinik-kalinik ninoreewi Ala apuri nogo obeelom eeppiige logonet, ninoreewi ando nggiru wogwe iigak kwe, abu iya tit eeppiige nogo paga, "Wa!" lombok yokkigi~o.
64001006	It nogo nen Ala apuri yime kuwak eeko menggaarak inenggaanom mbininggo logonet, "Aap Nggayut iniki kunik ee'ninake logonet, ndogop eeppinanege menggerak~o," yinuk, yo'niragaarak me, aap togoti mendek ambi keya wogwe iinok, Ala inikilom kombaruwak nduk, inamendek ambi lek kenok, wogorage logomenggendik, nappiyoorak ti op aret~o.
64001007	It aap ti, Keritut wone yoranet nawok nduk, nogo logonet, "It aap abet mbaka'lek inamendek woorak nineebi~o," yinuk yagaarak me, kat yeenggwaaragak yuurak ti, op aret nduk, yokkigi~o, noreeluk.
64001008	It aap Ala ndogop menggerak wone nogo nggwok wiganit nage logowak nduk, eerit nogwe nogo nen, "Ninom ndak-ndak yoranet nogwe~o," yinuk, ninombaruwak nduk, yeenggwaarogo logorak ti op aret~o.
64001009	Ala apuri time kuwak eeko menggaarak nogo, inake liiru mbuuluk ambi mbanogo nappi wagarak kwe, aap Ndiyoterepet nogo nen, "Inenggela'me an mban tiyanak logokit~o," yinuk, inikilom mbake menggerak me, noone woolik~o.
64001010	Togop me, nit eerulik kagak oone abu maluk ninoba pinaneegerak me, an wage logominggirik, at yereegerak nogo liirogon mbininogo yokkege neyaamunggun~o. Oone maluk ti mban ninoba punuk, puk age ti lek~o. Ata, ninoreewi wogwe iinok, ineebe wogonaka'lek logonet, it wogonaburak mbakwi nogo, "Wogonaburak lek~o," yinuk, inenggela'me nen wumbiige menggerak me, liirogon yokkege neyaamunggun~o.
64001011	Noreeluk niniki kunik yi wae! It maluk eeko menggaarak nogo kat ndak-ndak eeke logogun~o. Ata, it aap obeelom eeko menggaarak nogo ndak-ndak mban eerit nage logot~o. Aap ambi obeelom eeke menggerak kenok ti, Ala nen ndareegerak aret mbariyak kwe, at maluk mban eeke menggerak nogo nen perak, Ala mondok liippega'lek aret menggerak~o.
64001012	Aap Ndemeteriyut nogo, "Ala ndogop menggerak~o," yinuk, wone yugu nogo liippunuk, ndak-ndak eerit nage kenok, Ala inom, it aakumi abok aret inom, nen, "Aap ti, abu obeelom aret~o," yinuk, yogo menggaarak. Ndi, nit pilit lek, abet aret yogo monggoorak kat keenu me, nit kunduk, aap ti, iya tit eeke kogo monggoorak me, yokkogo~o.
64001013	An wone ambik yokkiriyak mbakirak kwe, liiru mbanggiriyak anggon ee'nake me,
64001014	an mbet-mbet keya wage logominggirik, nimbirak ninengga kunna'nuk, wone li'lak mbaniyak uugwe mbake agarik~o.
64001015	Ala karum wonage me, kiniki ugun tayenak ale'nggen aret logomunggun~o. Koreewi ninom wonogwe nogo nen keyage wappagaga~o. Ndi, an noreewi kinom wonogwe nogo ti, "Kinendage kunogombo mban keyage wappinagagi," yegerak, yoret~o. Abu aret yokkigi~o. Noreeluk wa!
65001001	Kit ninogoba Ala nen yonggo pinagareegerak kinom kunik Yetut Keritut kinarum wonage nogo, an Yakobut ore Yetut Keritut ayeloman Yurat nogo nen aret keyage wappinagi~o.
65001002	At Ala kinabuwa nen obeelom eeppinagage, kiniki ugun tayenak ale'nggen logobagip nduk, eeppinagage, iniki kunik eekkinake, eeke menggerak nogo ti, kulinik-kalinik eeppinagagak mban eeke logowak~o.
65001003	-
65001004	Noreewi~o. Kit an niniki kunik me, wone ambi yokkira~o. Kit ugun kineenggo'lek kiigak, it aap ando kinenggela'me unggwi wogo nagaarik, Ala iniki kunik en obeelom eeppinanege menggerak wone nogo, abut laganogo, "Ala iniki kunik ee'ninake menggerak me, nit maluk eekwi niinok, maluk ninoba pinanigin lek~o," yinuk, iniki liirak lek iniki nengge kenok ugun-ugun eerit nogo logonet, at Aliku ninowe Yetut Keritut nogo ti, "Nit ninowe lek~o," yinuk, yogo menggaarak. Togop me, Ala nen it maluk eekwi onggo muk inoba piyoorak nduk, punogo piyareegerak wonage kagak, we ugun kobak logonet, agan nugwi me, nit ninagap ndareegerak wone ndak-ndak waganeegurak nogo, amburu mbanogo liiru mbanggiraakit mbakirak kwe, it togop agan nugwi iinok, abet mbakwi wone ambit at Ala nen o maan nit at apuri ake leenak mondok-mondok unde eeppinaneegerak wone nogo, taganogo mbo pugwi kiyo, "Yi Ala wone aret me, taganiyak lek~o," yinuk, mondok kinogogumbuk logonet, pipporogo logobagip nduk, liiru yi, mbanggiragi~o.
65001005	Ninogoba Ala nen maan it at apuri Iterali mendek o Metit nen inagap ndarogo wumbiya wage nagagerik, ti'nuk, it ando abet mbaka'lek iinok, Ala nen inooke logonet, lek eerogo piyareegerak wone nogo ti, kit muk kinaruk koneneegutak kwe, aberak logobagip nduk, ambinom yokkiragi~o.
65001006	Ndi, at Ala nen it malayikat ando, "Yogop eeko logonip~o," yinuk, o unde eeppiyareegerak kagak, "O yi mban unde logorak nineebi~o," yinuk, mbo pogo mbareegwa, at Ala nen, "An mondok iya tit eeke neyoorak nogo eyom paga inawone amburu mbanogo maluk eekwi onggo inoba piyaakit~o," yinuk, ineebe mondok-mondok mbutigeele paga maarogo o apit me mambiyareegerak wonogwe nogo, kiniki abeko logonip~o.
65001007	Ndi, it malayikat eeppiyareegerak nogo pogom, it aakumi o Torom inom, o Nggomora inom, yi kota ndi kota enaagan-ambokan wonogwe nogo inom, nen nggeewo negen kumi ugun wurinabit nogwe, iniki aganggen eeginake kenok eekulik mendek kagak ugun-ugun eeginabit nogwe, eeko mbareegwa, "It aakumi maluk eekwi iinok, Ala nen kani omoonu'me mondok-mondok nappiyaagin kogo~o," yinuk, nineenu ogo logowok nduk, kani paga inooreegerak nogo~o.
65001008	It aap kinenggela'me ugun unggwi wagaarak nogo ti, aakumi o Torom inom, Nggomora inom, eeko nogogwaarak nogo ndak-ndak eerit nogo logonet, "Nabinggaanggo paga yogop eeriyak op aret kagarak~o," yinuk, iniki aganggen eeginake kenok, eekulik mendek kagak ugun-ugun eeginabit nogwe, Ala wone konenggo logorak, "Nineebi~o," yinuk, taganogo mbo pugwi, ndi, it inayuk warak mbogut paga menggaarak malayikat nogo kunduk, miyuk-meya eerogo piigwi, eerit nogo menggaarak.
65001009	Muta kangge mbareegi, at yonggo mbogut paga nugu menggaarak inowe Mikayen Tile imbirak, "Eebe an koloorak kat koloorak," nili-kili yogo logonet, at Mikayen nen, "Kat abu maluk lombok me, kambu~o," yinuk, Tile yoriyak op aret kwe, agabiti nen, "Nogoba nen mban mbekkirigin~o," yinuk, yoreegerak kwe,
65001010	it aap kinenggela'me unggwi wagaarak wonogwe ti perak, wone alom liirogon ineenggo'lek kagak miyuk-meya eerogo pogo logonet, nggeewo iniki lek ugun eerit nogo mengga kwak, it togop aret iniki aganggen eeginake kenok eerit nogwe nogo mban ineenu logonet eerit nogwe me, ineebe aret lek eerogo patit nogo agaarik~o.
65001011	It nogo nen at Kayin eereegerak nogo ndak-ndak eerit nogwe, aap Mbileyam maluk eereegerak nogo kokwak, it togon iniki lek negen wu koloorak mban iniki lunik logonet mugurok nogwe, ndi, aap Kora awuri inom Muta wone taganogo mbo pogo mbareegwa, Ala nen lek eerogo piyareegerak nogo pogom, it ndak-ndak ineebe lek eerogo piyaawak nduk, eekkologwe, eerit nogwe me, inabuwa~o.
65001012	Niniki-kiniki kunik paga mbi nawok nduk, kuwak eekwi me, it aap ti, inageerok abe mendek ko'nok wa'nuk, it ando abu iigak, inagabiti mbaka'lek inalik mban nonggo menggaarak me, yum abu laambu kwe, oololuk mili eerak menggi kwak logonet, eeko menggaarak~o. Mayu ndugwi paga luurik lek me, ndugwi o wiya nen wonok nage, eyoonggen abe yuwak nduk, awi yakaatak kwe, anggen abe yega'lek kanenep age kenok, kinogo pegaatak me, mondok mbuk age,
65001013	niyo kilaarak-mogonik eeke logonet, eyak-nggoyak eerogo nippit wage menggi kwak, it aap ti, eekulik mendek kagak togop aret ugun-ugun eerit nugwi, ndi, laaluguragan inobaane'me lombok wonogwe iigak, ambiret ambi nggigik togon, pinda agan lek ari nage menggi kwak, eerit nugwi, eeko menggaarak me, at Ala nen o apit aago me mondok-mondok logowak nduk, inake ogobakkigirogo piyareegerak wonage agaarik~o.
65001014	-
65001015	Aram ombowologwe ambo'me-ambo'me nda'narit wundi wogo logonet, 7 nda'nagagerak Enok nogo, Ala nen at yoge kagak aakumi yorage logonet, "It aakumi Ala wone woorak, Nineebi~o, yinuk, Ala miyuk-meya eerogo pugwi, oone taganogo punuk, iniki liirak lek maluk ugun eerit nugwi, eekwi nogo ninowe nen inowak loonogo maluk onggo inoba piyaakit nduk, at awuri ake leenak malayikat nogo ineebe ambik lombok aago at inom wogwe iigirak~o," yinuk, yoragagerak nogo ti, it aap kinenggela'me agan nugwi nogo, aret eeppiyoorak nduk, yoragagerak~o.
65001016	It aap ti nen ineebi-ineeba yogwe, inoreewi meek inombakwi, eeriyak iniki nengge kenok eerit nugwi, "An aap nggwok~o," yinuk, wogoppatit nugwi, inamendek kolaawok nduk, inoone amburu ndik-ndik agan nugwi, eeko menggaarak~o.
65001017	Togop kwe, noreewi~o. Kit an niniki kunik wonogwe me, wone ambi yokkira~o. At ninowe Yetut Keritut nen nappiigak mendek agago mippiyareegerak nogo nen wone aa'nduk yokkirogo nogogwaarak nogo abeko logonip~o.
65001018	It nogo nen kit yokkirogo logonet, "O age yobok paga it aakumi iniki liirak lek nogo nen iniki nengge kenok mban eerit nogo logonet, kit miyuk-meya eerogo pinagarak nogo kin ari woraagun~o," yinuk, yokkirogo nogogwaarak nogo, abeko logonip~o.
65001019	It aap ti, Aberiniki inikime lek me, nggween paga mendek mban iniki nengge kenok mugurok nogo logonet, Ala apuri ogoorogo piinet nogo menggaarak it aret.
65001020	-
65001021	Togop kwe, noreewi niniki kunik kit perak, kit kiniki kole aruwak nduk, wone abu alik leenak kit abet mbareegutak wone nogo mban eerit nogo logonip~o. Ninowe Yetut Keritut ninabuwa nen mondok-mondok nineenik eeppinaniyak nogo, eeppinanuwak nduk, tokkogo logonet, Ala iniki kunik eekkinake nogo eeppinagagak mban eeke kogo logomunggup nduk, Aberiniki yokkirage kagak tamban eeko logonip~o.
65001022	It ando iniki yungguppegak eeko menggaarak nogo inabuwa mbako logonet, yanggorogon yorogwe,
65001023	it ando nen kani omoonu'me nogwe me, kinagabiti mbaka'lek inagap ndarogo piya wogwe, ndi, it ando perak, iniki nengge mugurok nogo logonet, mbogoyum laambu abe me mili mondok nabek yi unggwage menggi kwak maluk eekwi ti, ogole warak me, ninom lambunggologwe niyo, "Ninagabiti~o," mbakwi kwe, kagak, inabuwa mbako logonet yorogwe, eeko logonip~o.
65001024	-
65001025	Ninowe Yetut Keritut eereegerak paga ninagap ndareegerak at Ala nogo nen nit abet mbareegurak nogo mbo punuk, alik eerit nogwe niyo, ninarum liirogon logomenggerik, "Kit wone ambi kinoba wonage lek abu obeelom aret me, nowagam mi'nari woraanip~o," yinuk, yo'nirage mbaremenggi, nit niniki ale'nggen mbakak at mondok tiyanak menggerak enggaanom mi'nari nawok nduk, wo'niren pinani nagin aret me, yi aakumi ndi aakumi aa'nduk nda'nogogwaarak inom, yogondak ndarak inom, peebi nda'nariyak inom, nit abok ninogoba ambit ninagap ndaka kat aret me, kat aap nggwok kendagembogut komaawi ambik yi aakumi ndi aakumi abok kabu'me logonet, kat koone mban konenggwi, kat kendage mban tiyappagagwi, eeko logowak~o. Amin.
66001001	At Ala nen yi eeriyak ndi eeriyak logonuk lek mbet-mbet eeriyak wone nogo, nit at ayeloman mini nineenu eeppinanuwak nduk, Yetut Keritut yoge mbareegi, at nen paganogo yo'niragagerak wone nogo yi aret~o. Ala nen Yetut Keritut yoge mbareegi, ti'nuk, Ala ayeloman an Yaya nogo neenu eeppanuwak nduk, Yetut Keritut nen at ayonggo malayikat ambi wuppi wagagerak.
66001002	Ndi, malayikat wuppi wagagerak nogo nen, an yo'nege mbareegi, ti'nuk, Ala nen wone yo'nege, ndi, Yetut Keritut nen paganogo yo'nege, eeke kagagirak nogo abok aret mbininogo liiru mbaneegirak yi aret me,
66001003	wone yi eeriyak nogo abu panggo yegerak me, it aakumi nen peebi eeriyak wone liiru mbanak yi, pekkagak mbininogo yorogwe, ndi, yorogwe iigak, inaruk konembunuk, liirogon waganggwi, eekwi iinok, Ala nen ale'nggen inoba piige logogin~o.
66001004	-
66001005	An Yaya nen kit Ala apuri o Atiya nggereya 7 paga kuwak eerit nogo monggotak nogo, keyage wappinagi~o. Aa'nduk wonagagerak, yogondak wonage, peebi logogin mondok itok menggerak Ala inom, ndi, Ala wone lengganogo yorage menggim abu'me menggaarak Aberiniki eeke menggerak alom 7 nogo inom, ndi, eeruwak nduk nappi wagagerak mondok liippunuk yubuk togon eeke nagagerik, kambunuk nogo menggam inenggela'me nen at aa'nduk mi'nage nagagerik, yogondak it aap nggween paga mendek inoweewi nagawan-nagawan abok inowe endagembogut agagerak at Yetut Keritut nogo inom, it abok aret iniki kunik en wokkirogwe, ndi, kiniki ugun tayenak ale'nggen logobagip nduk, eeppinagagwi, eeko logowak~o. At Yetut Keritut ninabuwa nen iniki kunik ee'ninake, amiya paga ninomaluk koorogo pinanege,
66001006	"An kinowe endagembogut aret~o," yinuk, abu'me pinanege, at ogoba Ala unde logonet ake eeko logowok nduk, leenogo mippinanege, eereegerak me, nit yi abok aret at endage mban tiyappugwi, abu'me tebe yinuk, at oone mban konengggwi, mondok-mondok eeko logowok~o, yinuk, amin!
66001007	At ndugwi paga wage kenok, it aakumi o nggween paga menggaarak inanebunu lombok at wareegwaarak nogo mendek inom abok aret inalitak lombok nen inigen kogo logomenggaarik, leenggu maako logogun me, liippogo logonip~o, yinuk, abet aret yokkiragi~o. Amin.
66001008	Aa'nduk wonagagerak, yogondak wonage, peebi logogin at omaawi lombok menggerak ninogoba Ala nen ari logonet, "O maan aa'nduk togon wonagagirak Alpa inom, ndi, peebi irip paga mondok logorak Omega inom, ti an aret~o," yinuk, ari menggerak~o.
66001009	Kit aaninggin-paaninggin kinoba pinagagwi iigak kwe, "Ala abu'me pinanigin me, op aret~o," yinuk, Yetut kinom kunik kiniki nu'lek logonet, waganggo monggotak nogo ti, an kinore Yaya togop ndak-ndak eeppanugwi iigak, wagangge minggirak nogo nen Ala wone yorage, ndi, Yetut wone ari nagagerak nogo paganogo yorage, eeke minggirak nogo paga, niyo yenggenak oolo kup mbanak o endage Pa'mot pani wogogwaarak yime agarik~o.
66001010	Yime wonage me, Ninowe mi'nagagerak eyom tamban eekwi nogo paga Aberiniki ninikime lik ari mbaki, nambokan nen oone nggwok eeka trompet nogo oone nggwok ari naruk konengge neegak,
66001011	yo'nege logonet, "Eeriyak titikkege neegak, mbuku pirik-perek aago paga liiru mbangge logomenggendik, it Ala apuri o Epetut inom, Timirina inom, Peragamut inom, Tiyatira inom, Taririt inom, Pilarelipiya inom, Laworikiya inom, nggereya 7 paga kuwak eekwi nogo abok aret pekkaawak nduk, nappunu~o," yinuk, yo'nege konenggirak~o.
66001012	Naruk konengge nagarik, "Ta nen yo'nege agaarik~o," yinuk, eebe nenegen kaakit nduk, nena logurogon pekkage nagarik, ndi wuninogo pegak 7 mbuti emas paga ogobakkigirik kwi'ndak wonage kagarak~o.
66001013	Ndi, ndi wuninogo pegak 7 ogobakkigirik nogo inenggela'me oolo taati aakumi inetenggen pogom ambi wonage kagarak. Aap ti nogo, ambogoyum nggorek, nok, iyok me linik yirik wonage, agabee'le mbuti emas mendek obate paga yirik wonage,
66001014	towe yanggwi eeruwak abinak lan ari nogo pogom at eeruwak togop aago wonage, enegen kani omoonuk wunuk ari pogom wonage,
66001015	ndi, mbuti tembaga kani kunik me mambugwi iinok, eyak kwindagala eerogo pegetak me, abinak pigan-pigan eeke menggi kwak, iyok togop aret abinak pigan-pigan eeke, niyoraakut oonebu wangge menggi pogom, at oone togop aret ari,
66001016	at eenggi abe'nggan paga laaluguragan 7 porogo wonage, mbuti togowa ngget peenok-peenok maarak ambeme titik aago wonage, ndi, oonegen ndelenak-welenak eeke nogo pogom, at etenggen togop aago wonage, eeke kagarak~o.
66001017	At eebe togop aago wonage nenegen kage nagarik, aakumi inambuluk yuppuk ngginnari nogo mengga kwak, an togop aret at abu'me ngginnari nage mbaki, at eenggi abe'nggan paga pi'nake logonet, "Aa'nduk togon wonagagirak inom, peebi irip paga lombok mondok logorak inom, ti an aret me, kagabiti mbarugun~o.
66001018	Neenik nitok minggirak an aret~o. Aa'nduk kambeegirak kwe, yogondak perak, neenik mondok-mondok wonage yi neyet~o. Kanggwi inom, kambunuk nogo menggam inom, imbirak an mban aret unde logonet, tu paaka kunci porogo minggirak~o.
66001019	Togop me, eerit wage kenegen kagandak inom, yogondak eeke kenegen kage inom, ndi, peebi eeriyak kenegen kaamunggun inom, abok aret liiru mbanogo pege logot~o.
66001020	Laaluguragan 7 neenggi abe'nggan paga kagandak nogo inom, ndi, ndi wuninogo pegak 7 mbuti emas paga ogobakkigirik kagandak nogo inom, ti wone nobarak negen wonage me, alom liirogon yokkiri~o. Laaluguragan 7 nogo ti, it Ala apuri nggereya 7 paga kuwak eekwi inarum menggaarak malayikat nogo aret iigen. Ndi, ndi wuninogo pegak 7 nogo ti, Ala apuri nggereya 7 paga kuwak eeko menggaarak nogo aret iigen~o," yinuk yo'nege kagarak~o.
66002001	Yo'nege kage nagarik, wonage me, "At malayikat Ala apuri o Epetut kuwak eekwi inarum menggerak nogo nen apuri yoraawak nduk, yoriyak, yokkiri~o. Neenggi abe'nggan paga laaluguragan 7 porogo logonet, ndi wuninogo pegak mbuti emas paga ogobakkigirik 7 inenggela'me nege minggirak an nogo nen
66002002	Ala apuri o Epetut eerit nogo menggaarak nogo an neenu aret~o. It ndeyak aganake kagak mbo pega'lek mondok nabenak mban eerit nogwe, It aap maluk mendek nit ninenggela'me yime logorak mondok lek~o, yinuk, ineebi mbakwi, it aap ando nappiigak mendek lek kwe, wogo nagaatik, Ala nen nappinani wagaarak~o, yinuk, yorogwe iinok, inabut mbambunuk, Yi pilit agan wagaarak~o, yinuk, mbo piigwi,
66002003	ndi, an nendage mban yi awi ndi awi wigak yuwak nduk, eerit nogwe paga aaninggin-paaninggin eeppiinet nogwe iigak, iniki kwippunuk waganggo logonet, ta'liila eeginake kagak mondok nabenak mban eekwi, eerit nogo menggaarak nogo ti, an neenu aret~o.
66002004	Neenu aret kwe, mbuuluk ambi eekwi iigirak nogo perak, apuri yoraawak nduk, yoriyak yokkiri~o. Aa'nduk it iniki kunik lombok ee'nako nogogwaarak kwe, yogondak perak, ninom kunik lek mbo panugwi iige nagarik, yagi~o.
66002005	It aa'nduk an ninom kunik logonet, iniki aganggen paga noone mugurok nogo nogogwaarak nogo mbo punuk, yogondak mondok alik eerit nogwe nogo, liippatinuk, inomaluk mbo pogo logomenggaarik, yungguninuk iniyok paga woraanuk, aa'nduk eeko nogogwaarak nogo ndak-ndak eerit nogo logowak~o. It iniki koombunuk inomaluk mbo pugwi lek iinok perak, an wage logominggirik, ndi wuninogo pegak inenggela'me wonage nogo nggiginogo mbo wumbi woraagin~o.
66002006	Ndi, ambi op negen eekwi iigirak nogo ti, it aap Nikolawut oone mugurok nogo logonet, eerit nogo menggaarak ti, an neebi lombok mbake minggirak nogo, it ndak-ndak ineebi mbakwi iigirak me op aret~o.
66002007	Aberiniki nen Ala apuri yi awi ndi awi kuwak eeko menggaarak yorage nogo ti, inaruk wonage kenok, liirogon aret konenggo logowak~o. Ndi, it Ala wone mbo pega'lek, iniki nu'lek porogo logonet, liirogon mugurok nogwe iinok, eyoonggen aakumi ineenik eeginake menggerak Ala eyabu me wonage nogo, It noorak op aret yoraagin~o, yinuk, wone yi yagarak nogo abok aret at malayikat Ala apuri o Epetut kuwak eekwi inarum menggerak nogo nen apuri yoraawak nduk, liiru mbanogo nappu~o."
66002008	"Ndi, at malayikat Ala apuri o Timirina kuwak eekwi inarum menggerak nogo nen apuri yoraawak nduk, yoriyak, yokkiri~o. An kangge nagagirik, neenik a'nuk mi'nagagirak aa'nduk togon wonagagirak me, peebi irip paga mondok logogin nogo nen
66002009	it Ala apuri o Timirina eerit nogo menggaarak nogo, an neenu aret~o. It aaninggin-paaninggin inoba age logonet, ineenggi lek age kwe, agi mendek paga ineenggi warak negen wonogwe nogo an neenu aret~o. Ndi, it Yakuri mendek lek Ibilit eeke menggerak ndak-ndak eeruwok nduk kuwak eeko menggaarak nogo mendek kagak, we piliret, Nit Yakuri mendek aret~o, yinuk, Ala apuri o Timirina mendek inoone miyuk-meya eerogo piigwi ti, neenu mban.
66002010	Togop eeppiigwi iigak kwe, it Ala apuri eeppiyoorak koonak wonage nogo ti, lek aga'lek awo aret wonage me, inagabiti mbakwi iyo, apuri yoraawak nduk, yoriyak, yokkigi~o. Tile nen ari logonet, An aaninggin-paaninggin inoba piige neenok, nonggop eekwi iyaamun? yinuk, inabut mbanikit nduk, aakumi iniki nggagangge mbaremenggi, it Ala apuri o Timirina ineebe keele maarogo o mbuuluk me mambiyamenggaarak wonogwe iigak, nogo aap ambit eenggi aret yugun~o. It nogo nen, Eeppinanugwi iigak, kambi noorak kuli ariyak op aret~o, yinuk, mondok inogogumbuk logonet, waganggwi iinok, mondok-mondok ineenik logorak mendek nggare-nggare mendaarak nogo yippiyaagin~o.
66002011	Aberiniki nen Ala apuri yi awi ndi awi kuwak eeko menggaarak yorage nogo ti, inaruk wonage kenok, liirogon aret konenggo logowak~o. Ndi, it aaninggin-paaninggin nogo mendek abok aret inoba age kwe, kagak, Ala wone mbo pega'lek mondok inogogumbuk logonet liirogon mugurok nogwe iinok, ne mbere paga kambugun lek~o, yinuk, wone yi yagarak nogo abok aret at malayikat Ala apuri o Timirina kuwak eekwi inarum menggerak nogo nen apuri yoraawak nduk liiru mbanogo nappu~o."
66002012	"Ndi ambi, at malayikat it Ala apuri o Peragamut kuwak eekwi inarum menggerak nogo nen apuri yoraawak nduk, yoriyak, yokkiri~o. An mbuti togowa ngget peenok-peenok maarak porogo minggirak nogo nen,
66002013	it an napuri o Peragamut time nggeeme wonogwe nogo an neenu~o. It Ibilit oone konenggo menggam inenggela'me inom time aret menggaarak kwe, naput ambi noone liirogon woppunuk ko'lu-kii'me yoranet nege nagagerak Andipat nogo, it inenggela'me Tile wonage menggim inagota time aret wako mbareegwa, it iniki abet mba'nuk, an noone waganeegwaarak nogo, Mugurok noorak nineebi~o, yinuk, yuurak kwe, kagak, Lek~o. Nit ninowe Keritut aret me, at oone waganggoorak nogo ti, mondok aret porogo logowok~o, yinuk, yogwe iigirak~o.
66002014	Togop aret yogwe iigirak kwe, mbuuluk ambi ninggin eekwi iigirak nogo perak, yoraawak nduk, yoriyak, yokkiri~o. It aakumi Iterali mendek nen Ala wone mbo punuk kugi aanggo warak nunggwi, ndi, kumi we ugun-ugun wurinabit nogwe, eeko logowak nduk, at Mbileyam nen aap Mbalak mamunege mbareegi, aap Mbalak nen Iterali mendek mamuniragagerak wone nogo, it Ala apuri o Peragamut wonogwe ando nen wone ti, mugurok nogwe,
66002015	ndi, ando nen at Nikolawut oone mugurok nogwe, eekwi iigirak me,
66002016	it maluk eekwi nogo ti, iniki koombunuk, mbo pogo logowak~o. Mbo pega'lek iinok perak, an mbet-mbet wage logominggirik, mbuti togowa an nambeme wonage yi nogo paga inoori wambi woraagin~o.
66002017	Aberiniki nen Ala apuri yi awi ndi awi kuwak eeko menggaarak yorage nogo ti, inaruk wonage kenok liirogon aret konenggo logowak~o. It Ala wone mbo pega'lek nu'lek porogo logonet liirogon mugurok nogwe iinok, mbi mbogut paga mendek kumaarak wonage nogo wogorage, ndi, it waamenggaarak nogo mban ineenu logowak nduk, inendage ngget toonogo yugum yanggwi negen lan ari nogo paga liiru mbanogo wogorage, eerigin~o, yinuk, wone yi yagarak nogo abok aret at malayikat Ala apuri o Peragamut kuwak eekwi inarum menggerak nogo nen apuri yoraawak nduk liiru mbanogo nappu~o."
66002018	"Ndi, ambi at malayikat Ala apuri o Tiyatira kuwak eekwi inarum menggerak nogo nen apuri yoraawak nduk, yoriyak, yokkiri~o. An nenegen kani omoonuk wunuk ari pogom logonet, mbuti tembaga kani kunik me mambugwi iinok, eyak kwindagala eerogo pegetak me, abinak pigan-pigan eeke menggi kwak, niyok togop ndak-ndak pigan-pigan eeke minggirak nogo nen,
66002019	it Ala apuri o Tiyatira eerit nogo menggaarak nogo an neenu aret~o. It aakumi iniki kunik aganakwi, abet mba'nuk iniki noba panggombanugwi, inoreewi yeenggwaaranet nugwi, aaninggin-paaninggin eeppiigwi iigak, inogogumbuk logonet waganggwi, eerit nogwe nogo abok neenu aret~o. Ndi, aa'nduk we mbuuluk eeko nogogwaarak kwe, yogondak nggwok togon eerit nogwe ti, neenu mban aret kwe,
66002020	mbuuluk ambi ninggin eekwi iigirak me, yoraawak nduk, yoriyak, yokkiri~o. Kwe Iteben nogo nen, An Ala wone yorage minggirak mendek aret~o, yinuk, an nayeloman mini ineebe ambik nomoniren nage logonet, kumi ugun-ugun wurinabit nogwe, ndi, kugi aanggo warak nunggwi, eerit nogo logowak nduk, mamunirage kagak kwe, mberega'lek, Op aret~o, yinuk teppugwi iigirak me, abu neebi lombok ee'nake kenok yagi~o.
66002021	At kwe ti, iniki koombunuk, omaluk mbo puwak nduk, tokkagarak kwe, An ee'nabuwak, mbarit nege nogo mbo puurak neebi~o, yinuk, eerit nage me,
66002022	andi yagan yobak-nggolak wake logowak nduk, aaninggin oba kwippege logonet, it ando kwe ti inom maluk eerit nogo menggaarak nogo kunduk, iniki koombunuk inomaluk mbo pugwi lek iinok, it togop aret aaninggin mondok luurik-maarak agago inoba kwippiige neyaagun~o.
66002023	Kwe ti, aagalogwe nogo abok aret inoorit nage neenok, it an napuri yi awi ndi awi kuwak eeko menggaarak nogo abok nen, Nit niniki mbakwi inom, niniki koombunuk eerit nogwe inom, abok aret liippinaninuk onggo ndak-ndak wo'nirage menggerak ti, at aret kogo~o, yinuk, an neebe ineenu arugun~o.
66002024	Ndi, it ando o Tiyatira wonogwe nogo, kwe ti, oone inom, Tile eeke menggerak kote kumaarak yogo menggaarak wone nogo inom, it mugurok naga'lek mbo pereegwaarak me, an nen aaninggin mendek ambi inoba piyoorak mbarulik kwe,
66002025	it abet mba'nuk waganeegwaarak nogo mondok nu'lek porogo wonogwe me, An aret woraagin, yegerak~o, yinuk, yoraawak nduk, yoriyak, yokkigi.
66002026	-
66002027	It Ala wone mbo pega'lek mondok nu'lek porogo logonet, an eeriyak mbake minggirak nogo eerit nogwe iigak, o age yobok ari wage kenok, an nogoba nen aakumi inanebunu lombok inarum logokit nduk, mippaneegerak nogo kokwak, it togop aret, yi aakumi ndi aakumi inabu'me piinok, wone lengganogo yorogo logowak nduk, mippiyaagin~o. Ala nen ari logonet, Mbim obate mbanak eenggime logonet, Oone omaawi paga wone lengganogo yorage, Ndi, yi mendek ndi mendek nggween nggabok paga ogobakkigirik nogo, Telenogo pogo mengga kwak, eerogo piige, Eerigin~o, yinuk, yereegerak nogo ndak-ndak eeko logogun~o.
66002028	Ndi, it Ala wone mondok nu'lek porogo wonogwe me, an wage logominggirik, o weerikit nduk eeke kagak laaluguragan abinak kere ari nogo aret wogora woraagin~o.
66002029	Aberiniki nen Ala apuri yi awi ndi awi kuwak eeko menggaarak yorage nogo ti, inaruk wonage kenok, liirogon aret konenggo logowak~o, yinuk, wone yagarak nogo abok aret at malayikat Ala apuri o Tiyatira kuwak eekwi inarum menggerak nogo nen apuri yoraawak nduk liiru mbanogo nappu~o."
66003001	"Ndi, ambi, at malayikat Ala apuri o Taririt kuwak eekwi inarum menggerak nogo nen apuri yoraawak nduk, yoriyak, yokkiri~o. Laaluguragan 7 neenggime porogo logonet, Ala Aberiniki eeke mengge-rak alom 7 unde minggirak nen, Ala apuri o Taririt eerit nogo menggaarak ti, an neenu aret~o. It abu ndeyak kambak negen aret wonogwe iigak kwe, aakumi nen, Lek~o. Aap eenik omaawi nege menggi kwak, it Ala apuri nggereya ti paga kuwak eekwi nogo mondok inomaawi aret wonogwe iigo~o, yinuk, yogwe nogo neenu aret kwe,
66003002	it eerit nogwe nogo an nogoba Ala nen, Op aret eekwi, inombaka'lek me, it abu ndeyak kambuurak negen aganake nogo mbet-mbet ineenik a'nuk, Ala wone mbuuluk mugurok nogwe iigirak nogo nggwok togon mugurok nogo logowak nduk, inomaawi eekkolaawak~o.
66003003	It wone mamunirogwe iigak, inaruk konembunuk waganeegwaarak nogo abeppunuk, inomaluk mbo pogo logomenggaarik, wone koneneegwaarak nogo aret liirogon porogo logorak yoraawak nduk yokkigi~o. Ndi, Nit nonggop eeko ogoorik~o, yinuk, inomaluk mbo pugwi lek iinok perak, aap yogoot woorak nduk wage menggi kwak, an o ndiyom paga woroorak ineenggo'lek iigak, togop aret abera'lek me perak togon inowagam woraagin~o.
66003004	Togop kwe, it Taririt mendek ando mbuuluk mban inayum mili eekkolaga'lek obeelom mban eerit nugwi me, Kit obeelom aret~o, yinuk, inayum laambu abe yirik ninom nugu logogun~o.
66003005	Ndi, it Ala wone mbo pega'lek mondok nu'lek porogo logonet, mugurok nogwe me, an wage logominggirik, aakumi mondok-mondok ineenik logorak inendage mbuku paga liiru mbanak wonage nogo, an kagaarigin lek~o. It togop aret inayum abu laambu yippiige logominggirik, an nogoba inom, at ayonggo malayikat inom, inenggaanom paga, It aap yi, an nawuri aret~o, yinuk, yoraagin~o.
66003006	Aberiniki nen Ala apuri yi awi ndi awi kuwak eeko menggaarak yorage nogo ti, inaruk wonage kenok, liirogon aret konenggo logowak~o, yinuk, wone yagarak nogo abok aret at malayikat Ala apuri o Taririt kuwak eekwi inarum menggerak nogo nen apuri yoraawak nduk liiru mbanogo nappu~o."
66003007	"Ndi, ambi at malayikat Ala apuri o Pilarelipiya kuwak eekwi inarum menggerak nogo nen apuri yoraawak nduk, yoriyak, yokkiri~o. An Ndawut agunci nogo porogo logonet, tu paake neenok aakumi nen nakwi, ndi, nake neenok paakwi, eekulik an mban unde logonet, pilit ariilik abet mban ari minggirak nalik leenak minggirak nogo nen,
66003008	it Ala apuri o Pilarelipiya eerit nogo menggaarak nogo an neenu aret~o. Neenu aret me, it an nendage mbo pega'lek porogo logonet, inomaawi mbuuluk wonage nogo paga an noone mugurok nogo menggaarak me, it ambi eeko logowak nduk, tu paarogo piyareegirak nogo, aakumi nen narogo piyoorak mondok meek aret~o.
66003009	It aap Tile eeke menggerak ndak-ndak eeko logowok nduk, kuwak eeko menggaarak nogo, it Yakuri mendek lek kagak we piliret, Nit Yakuri mendek aret~o, yinuk, yogo menggaarak nogo nen, Yi Ala apuri inom iniki abe kunik wonogwe iigo~o, yinuk, it Ala apuri o Pilarelipiya mendek inabu'me tebe yi wa'nuk inoone konenggo logowak nduk, eeppiige neyaagun~o.
66003010	Ndi, Kit kinogogumbuk kiniki kwi'ndak logonet eeko logonip~o, yinuk, yoragagirak nogo, konembunuk liirogon aret eekwi me, peebi yi aakumi ndi aakumi nggween paga menggaarak abok aret inabut mbanikit nduk, aaninggin-paaninggin inoba piya woroorak eyom nogo paga, it an napuri ti, inoba arukwak, an nen ndegeninake logogin~o.
