66003011	An logonuk lek mbet-mbet aret woraagin~o. Ndi, wage logominggirik, it abet mba'nuk waganeegwaarak nogo liirogon porogo wonogwe iinok, nggare-nggare mendaarak nogo mendek yippiya woraagin me, aakumi nen waganggwi iyo, liippunuk, tum wako logowak~o.
66003012	It Ala wone mbo pega'lek liirogon porogo wonogwe me, an wage logominggirik, o omaawi logowak nduk, tiru oolo yinggo mengga kwak, it aakumi ti, Ala awi wurik me togop aret mippiinok, an nogoba Ala endage inom, Ala awi wurik o kota Yerutalem ngget mendek nogoba Ala mbogut paga nen wuppi woraagin nogo endage inom, ndi, an nendage ngget toonak nogo inom, inalitak lombok inoba liiru mbanogo piyaminggirak wonogwe me, it peebi time nen wundi nagun abu lek~o.
66003013	Aberiniki nen Ala apuri yi awi ndi awi kuwak eeko menggaarak yorage nogo ti, inaruk wonage kenok, liirogon aret konenggo logowak~o, yinuk, wone yagarak nogo ti, abok aret at malayikat Ala apuri o Pilarelipiya kuwak eekwi inarum menggerak nogo nen apuri yoraawak nduk liiru mbanogo nappu~o."
66003014	"Ndi, ambi at malayikat Ala apuri o Laworikiya kuwak eekwi inarum menggerak nogo nen apuri yoraawak nduk, yoriyak, yokkiri~o. At Ala nen yi mendek ndi mendek wakkaakit mbake kagak, wakkagagirak alom an aret me, Ala nonggop menggerak mondok liirogon abet aret paganogo ari minggirak nendage Amin nogo nen,
66003015	it Ala apuri o Laworikiya eerit nogo menggaarak nogo an neenu aret~o. Iniki miin lek aganggen togon lek we niyo tarom ombat negen wonogwe iigirak me, iniki aganggen logorak mbakwi kenok, aganggen aret wonogwe, ndi, iniki miin logorak mbakwi kenok, miin aret wonogwe, eeko logorak op aret mbake kwe,
66003016	iniki aganggen lek, miin lek, we niyo tarom ombat negen wonogwe me, niyo kulubit ombat kenok inambeme nen kilirogo wumbogo mengga kwak, it ineebe togop aret kilirogo wumbiyoorak mbake agarik~o.
66003017	It nogo nen, Ninigen mbuk ninagap mbelanak nineenggi lek niniki ale'nggen mondok lek aaninggin ndugu aago nugu logonet, agan nugu monggoorak kogo~o, yinuk, mbaka'lek logonet, Nit ninamendek ambi lek ti lek, abok aret wonage me, nineenggi warak aret~o, yinuk, yogo menggaarak me, it eeko logorak yoraawak nduk, yoriyak wone ambi yokkiri~o.
66003018	It inagap mbelanak nugwi me aakumi nen inigen iigwi iinok, inenggali ogwe iyo, inayum laambu yanggwi negen yikkolaawak nduk kunggologwe, inigen mbuk nogo obeelom a'nuk yi mendek ndi me-ndek inigen kaawak nduk, amburu inigen me puurak kunggologwe, ndi, abe mendek paga ineenggi warak aruwak nduk, an nawu mbuti emas abe kani paga worarak nogo mendek inom onggo kunggologwe, eeko logorak yoraawak nduk, yoriyak, yokkigi~o.
66003019	It aakumi an niniki kunik eeginake minggirak nogo ti, inaruk wake, iniki koonnaruwak nduk yawi inooke, eeke minggirak me, iniki koombunuk, inomaluk nggaruk togon mbo puwak~o.
66003020	An tunggambe paga mi'ndak logonet, tu puk-puk eeke nogo liippanuwak~o. Aap ambi an tu puk-puk eeke nogo, aruk konembunuk, tu paa'neege kenok, an ka unggwage logominggirik, nimbirak niniki ambit lambunik nore-kore logonet, mbi nonggo logogun~o.
66003021	Ndi, it an noone mbo pega'lek mondok nu'lek porogo logonet mugurok nogwe iinok, an nogoba yo'nereegerak nogo abu worok togon eeppunuk, at wone lengganogo yorage menggim nimbirak kwi'ndak wonage nogo ndak-ndak, it kunduk an noone lengganogo yorage minggim ninom kwi'ndak logowok nduk, Neya woraanip~o, yinuk, yoraagin~o.
66003022	Aberiniki nen it Ala apuri yi awi ndi awi kuwak eeko menggaarak yorage nogo ti, inaruk wonage kenok, liirogon aret konenggo logowak~o, yinuk, wone yagarak nogo ti abok aret at malayikat Ala apuri o Laworikiya kuwak eekwi inarum menggerak nogo nen apuri yoraawak nduk, liiru mbanogo nappu~o," yinuk, yo'nege kagarak~o.
66004001	Ti yo'nege mbaki, nabinggaanggo ambi kage logonet, o mbogut paga time tungga ambi paarak kage neegak, nogome nen aap ambi nen oone nggwok eeka trompet oone nggwok ari pogom aa'nduk yo'nege konenggirak nogo ambinom yo'nege logonet, "Yogondak eeriyak kagandak nogo eeppunuk, peebi eeriyak nogo titikkirikit nduk lagi mok~o," yinuk,
66004002	awo aret yo'nege kagak, Aberiniki ninikime lik ari nagaarik, wo'neren pani laganggerak mban kagarak. Pani laganggerak wonage me, mbogut paga time wone lengganogo yorage menggim eyo ndoonak nogo paga, aap ambi kwi'ndak wonage kagarak.
66004003	Wu kirin abinak pindan-pindan eeke menggi kwak, aap kwi'ndak wonage nogo etenggen ti, yugum yatipit pogom, yugum taririt pogom, eerak wonage kagarak. Ndi, at kwi'ndak menggim irimbaga liware yugum tamurut etenggen kunik negen wanggerak wonage kagak,
66004004	it mbogut paga wonogwe inoweewi ineebe 24 nen inayum yanggwi negen yirikwi, mbuti emas paga nggare-nggare mendaarak inanobak paga yirikwi, eeppunuk, wone lengganogo yorage menggim oolo kagak, it wone lengganogo yorogo menggam eyo ndoonak 24 wanggerak wonage nogo paga inoweewi 24 nogo ti paga kwi'ndak wonogwe iigirak.
66004005	At wone lengganogo yorage menggim time nen o kimbik pindanggage kagak, oone ngguurubu agan wundi wage kagarak. Ndi, wone lengganogo yorage menggim enaame nggwe taati ndi 7 wuninik wonage kagarak. Ndi 7 nogo ti, Ala Aberiniki eeke menggerak alom 7 nogo aret~o.
66004006	Ndi, wone lengganogo yorage menggim eyo ndoonak abu'me taati pugagi abu abe tabak lombok yilaa'nggun kole yenggenak kibu-kibu pege nogo pogom wonage kagarak. Ndi, aakumi nen iigulik mendek ineebe 4 enaagan-ambokan inigen abok wonage me, wone lengganogo yorage menggim oolo taati wanggerak wonogwe iigirak.
66004007	Ineebe nogo ti, ambi nggeewo singa etenggen pogom, ambi tapi ngguunok etenggen pogom, ambi ti, aakumi inetenggen pogom, ndi, ambi ti, towe wu a'naabit wiganak nogo pogom, wonogwe iigirak~o.
66004008	Aakumi nen iigulik mendek ineebe 4 nogo ti, inalitak lombok ina'naabit 6 aret me, ineebe paga apit aret inigen warak mban wonogwe iigirak. It nogo puk aga'lek ko'lu-kii'me inoone yogo logonet, "Maan wonagagindak, yogondak wonage, peebi logomunggun, nogo ti, kat mondok itok komaawi lombok menggendak ninogoba Ala aret me, Kat mondok obeelom alik leenak aret~o. Kat mondok obeelom alik leenak aret~o. Kat mondok obeelom alik leenak aret~o," yinuk, yogak mban eeko logonet,
66004009	at mondok-mondok eenik menggerak wone lengganogo yorage menggim kwi'ndak wonage nogo, "Wa," yinuk, alut eekwi, endage tiyappugwi, eekwi iigak,
66004010	-
66004011	it inoweewi ineebe 24 nogo nen at mondok-mondok eenik itok menggerak wone lengganogo yorage menggim eyo ndoonak paga kwi'ndak wonage nogo, abu'me tebe yinuk, alut eeko logonet, "Ninogoba Ala wa. Kat kiniki koombunuk yi mendek ndi mendek abok aret wakkaakit~o, yinuk, wakkagagindak kat mban kalik nggwok aret me, Yi aakumi ndi aakumi abok kat kabu'me tebe yinuk, kendage tiyappagago logonet, kalut eeko logowak~o," yinuk, inenggare-nggare mendaarak yirik nogo, nggoorogo at abu'me pi wogwe iigirak~o.
66005001	Ti eekwi iige nagarik, ti'nuk, ambi kage logonet, mbuku pirik-perek aago ambi nggorek peenok-peenok liiru mbanak me, "Piiniyak lek~o," yinuk, ambi perengge keele maake, ambi perengge keele maake, eerit keele 7 paga maarak at wone lengganogo yorage menggim eyo ndoonak paga kwi'ndak wonage nogo eenggi abe'nggan porogo wonage kagarak.
66005002	Kage neegak, malayikat alilaakwi ambi nen oone nggwok ari logonet, "Mbuku mbanak pirik-perek eerak yi, aap ta nen keele piinogo pekkoorak op~o?"
66005003	Ari mbaki, mbogut paga inom, nggween paga inom, nggween abu'na inom, aakumi ambik aret wonogwe kwe, it ambi nen keele piinogo wondekka woroorak unde eeppiyoolik me, ambi pekka wage iyoolik~o.
66005004	Piinogo wondekka waga'lek aret mbaki, "Nit aap abok maluk eeko monggoorak me, nit piiniyak unde eeppinanulik aret kagi~o," yinuk, niniki mondok wakkolage logonet, le nggwok yagarak.
66005005	Awo le ari wonage me, mbogut paga wonogwe inoweewi nogo ambi nen an yo'nege logonet, "Le ari mage~o. Eyo ambi agarip lagangge menggi kwak, anebunu Yekura nen Ndawut ombooluk nggeewo singa pogom nda'nagagerak nogo, eegin tiyak yereegerak me, at nen mbuku pirik-perek eerogo keele 7 maarak nogo, piinogo wondekkoorak op me, wondekka wage kaamunggun~o."
66005006	Yo'nege mbaki, inoweewi 24 nogo inom, aakumi nen iigulik mendek ineebe 4 nogo inom, wone lengganogo yorage menggim taati wanggerak wonogwe iigak, Ndomba Aagaluk ambi eebe warak negen kwe, it inenggela'me mi'ndak wonage kagarak. Ndomba Aagaluk nogo ti, aruk alom me eyak 7, ndi, enegen 7, wonage kagarak. Aruk alom me eyak 7 inom, enegen 7 inom, nogo ti, Ala Aberiniki eeke menggerak alom 7 o nggween paga yi awi ndi awi nappiige menggerak nogo aret~o.
66005007	Ti'nuk, Ndomba Aagaluk nogo wage nagaarik, wone lengganogo yorage menggim eyo ndoonak paga kwi'ndak mbuku eenggi abe'nggan porogo wonage nogo wagangge kagarak.
66005008	Wagangge mbaki, it aakumi nen iigulik mendek ineebe 4 nogo inom, mbogut paga wonogwe inoweewi ineebe 24 nogo inom, Ndomba Aagaluk nogo abu'me tebe yinuk,
66005009	-
66005010	ndawi ngget mendek wako logonet, "It aakumi inanebunu alitak lombok inom, inoone alitak lombok inom, inagabolo alitak lombok inom, yi aakumi ndi aakumi abok aret wonogwe kwe, Inenggela'me nen ambitak nggiginogo Ala apuri aruwak nduk, kat kooko mbareegwa, kamiya paga inonggo mbaneegindak ti paga mbuku pirik-perek aago keele 7 maarak nogo, kat nen waganogo piiniyak op aret~o. It kat kamiya paga inonggo mbaneegindak nogo, ninogoba Ala abu'me piinok, Ala unde logonet, ake eeko logowak nduk leenogo mippiyareegindak me, Inendagembogut logonet, aakumi nggween paga ogu time wonogwe nogo wone lengganogo yorogo logogun~o," yinuk, at yogwi naruk konenggirak. Konengge nagarik, it inoweewi ineebe 24 nogo nen nggitat inom, togolowak mbuti emas paga ogobakkigirik obari abe kaga toolak nogo inom, inalitak lombok porogo logonet, ndawi paga yogwi iigirak~o. Obari abe kaga togolowak mbuti emas paga toolak nogo ti, it Ala apuri ake leenak tamban eeko nogogwaarak inoone toolak negen aret kagarak.
66005011	Ti eekwi iige neegak, wone lengganogo yorage menggim eyo ndoonak nogo inom, it aakumi nen iigulik mendek ineebe nogo inom, it mbogut paga wonogwe inoweewi nogo inom, oolo wonogwe iigak, it malayikat ineebe ambik ineenggi lingginiyak mondok meek lombok wanggerak wonogwe nogo nen inoone nggwok paga ndawi wako logonet,
66005012	"Ndomba Aagaluk wareegwaarak nogo, yi aakumi ndi aakumi abok at abu'me tebe yi unggwogwe, Yi mendek ndi mendek abok aret at wogogwi, Yi wone ndi wone abok kat mban keenu aret~o, yinuk, yogwi, Kat kalik mondok komaawi aret~o, yinuk, ayuk wukwi, endage tiyappugwi, Kat obeelom aret~o, yinuk, inale'nggen ombakwi, Eeko logorak op aret~o," yinuk, yogwe iigak,
66005013	it mbogut paga wonogwe inom, nggween paga wo-nogwe inom, nggween abu'na wonogwe inom, yi nggwok yenggenak laut inikime nugwi inom, Ala nen ogobakkigireegerak yi mendek ndi mendek yi aakumi ndi aakumi abok aret inoone nggwok paga ndawi wako logonet, "Nit abok aret, at wone lengganogo yo'nirage menggim kwi'ndak wonage nogo inom, Ndomba Aagaluk nogo inom, kimbirak obeelom aret~o, yinuk, Inabu'me tebe yinuk, inalut eekwi, inendage tiyappiigwi, eeko logonet, inoone mondok-mondok konenggo logogun~o," yinuk, yogwe iigak,
66005014	it aakumi nen iigulik mendek ineebe 4 nogo nen, "Abet aret yaga~o," yinuk, "Amin," mban yogwe, ndi, it inoweewi 24 nogo nen Ndomba Aagaluk nogo abu'me tebe yinuk, alut eekwi, eekwi iigirak~o.
66006001	Ti eekwi iige neegak, Ndomba Aagaluk nogo nen keele 7 maarak nogo aa'nduk maarak piingge kagak, aakumi iigulik mendek ineebe 4 nogo ambi nen oone o ngguurubu pogom ari logonet, "Omok~o," ari naruk konengge nagarik,
66006002	nenegen neegak, kuda eeruwak yanggwi lombok me, amborowak paga aap ambi kwi'ndak eegin eenggime wage mbaki, "Aakumi tebembiya nak~o," yinuk, nggare-nggare ambi yippunuk, nappege mbaki, tebenogo piinet nage kagarak.
66006003	Ti'nuk, Ndomba Aagaluk nogo nen keele aa'nduk maarak piingge nagaarik, ambi maarak nogo piingge kagak, ineebe 4 nogo inore ambi nen ari logonet, "Omok~o," ari naruk konengge nagarik, nenegen neegak,
66006004	kuda alik ambi eeruwak maa'ngga kunik me, amborowak paga aap ambi kwi'ndak wage mbaki, "It aakumi o nggween paga ogu time iniki ugun tayenak ale'nggen nugu logorak lek~o. Ata, it-it wat-wat yogo logowak~o," yinuk, unde logorak mippege logonet, mbuti wooluwak nggorek lombok wogoge kagarak~o.
66006005	Ndi, Ndomba Aagaluk nogo nen keele mbere maarak nogo piingge nagaarik, ambi maarak piingge kagak, ineebe 4 nogo inore ambi nen ari logonet, "Omok~o," ari naruk konengge nagarik, nenegen neegak kuda mili lombok me, amborowak paga aap ambi kwi'ndak aaninggin wakkagak nogo mendek eenggime wonok wage mbaki,
66006006	it aakumi iigulik mendek ineebe 4 nogo, inenggela'me nen oone ambi ari logonet, "Mbato yum mbuuluk ambi yonggolak nogo ti, wu ne ambit paga it yabu eekwi onggo wogorogwe ndak-ndak nogo paga kungge, ndi, gandum yum mbuulogwe kenagan yonggolak nogo ti, ndak-ndak wu ne ambit paga it yabu eekwi onggo wogorogwe nogo paga kungge, eeriyak kwe, eyo tayitun amburu inom, anggur amburu inom, ti perak, maluk eerogo puurak mage~o," yinuk, ari kagarak.
66006007	Ti'nuk, Ndomba Aagaluk nogo nen keele kenagan maarak piingge nagaarik, ambi maarak nogo piingge kagak, aakumi iigulik mendek ineebe 4 nogo inore ambi nen ari logonet, "Omok~o," ari naruk konengge nagarik,
66006008	nenegen neegak, aap kambuurak nduk eeke logonet, etenggen ndoongga kere agago pege menggi kwak, kuda togop aret aap ambi endage Kanggwi Unde nogo kuda amborowak paga kwi'ndak wage kagak, aap ambi endage Kambunuk Nogo Menggam ambokan nabek togon aago wage eekwi iigirak. Wogo mbaka, it nen aakumi o nggween paga ando mogonogo teppiigo logonet, ando mogonogo seperempat nogo wooluwak paga inoorit nogwe, mbi abu nen kambuwak nduk, noogelo eerogo piigwi, andi nen kambuwak nduk, kugilengga ndi wurogo piigwi, ndi, nggwiya eyonggaame mendek nen nibininabuwak nduk, inanini eerogo piigwi, eerit nogo logowak nduk, unde eeppiige kagarak.
66006009	Ti'nuk, Ndomba Aagaluk nogo nen keele 4 maarak piingge nagaarik, ambi maarak nogo piingge mbaki, it aakumi Keritut inake eereegerak wone abet mba'nuk, mbo pega'lek Ala wone mondok liippunuk mugurok nogwe iinok, inooko nogogwaarak nogo, inogoma Ala ake warogo kani kunggo menggam abu'me taati wonogwe iigirak.
66006010	It nogo nen inoone nggwok yogo logonet, "Ninogoba Kaliku Ala wae. Kat kalik mondok nggwok alik leenak menggendak me, it aakumi o nggween paga wonogwe nen ninooreegwaarak ninamiya wambit nagagerak nogo, inowak loonogo ninane'me inooka'lek keegak, ne mande arigin~o," yinuk, yogo mbaka,
66006011	"Lek~o. Kit kinowe-kinawot inom, it kinom Ala wone mondok liippunuk mugurok nogwe inom, kit kinooreegwaarak kokwak inookwi iinok perak, kinane'me ambugwi lambuk togon inoorigin aret me, we ne ambiriluk puk logomunggup~o," yinuk, mbogoyum nggorek yanggwi negen inalitak lombok yippiige kagarak~o.
66006012	Ti'nuk, Ndomba Aagaluk nogo nen keele 5 maarak piingge nagaarik, ambi maarak nogo piingge mbaki, o mi nggwok nuk ari, kibiyan kiik worako mengga kwak oonegen apit age, tut aakumi inamiya negen age,
66006013	o wiya nggwok omaawi wake logonet mbogom anggen ki kagak nggaru-nggaru nggween paga oone ndu wambit wage menggi kwak, laaluguragan mbogut paga nen nggween paga wambit wage,
66006014	mbuku pirik-perek eeko mengga kwak mbogut nggoguk ari logonet, pirik-perek arit nage, ndi, puut inom, niyo inikime nggween kup mbanak inom, abok aret wo'narok ambi me ari nagak eeke, eeke kagarak.
66006015	-
66006017	Ti eeke kage nagarik, it aakumi nggween paga mendek inendagembogut inom, nagawan-nagawan inom, it aap wim eeka waka'ngget inom, aap ineenggi warak inom, aap inoone omaawi inom, aakumi inayeloman mini inom, aakumi weelek mendek inom, abok nen yogo logonet, "Ala anini eeppinaniyak eyom muk panggo yegerak me, nit nineenik logorak meek aret kogo~o," yinuk, inagabiti nen, "Nggeeme nawi?" yinuk, ndoome inom, yugum ambe nggaganak me inom, kumaa'nari nogo nagaarik, "At wone lengganogo yorage menggim eyo paga kwi'ndak wonage Ndomba Aagaluk inom, imbirak inanini nen nit ninoorukwak, puut yi paga inom, yugum nggwok yi paga inom, aan lebenninabu~o," yinuk, puut inom, yugum inom, yogwi iigirak~o.
66007001	Ti eekwi iige nagarik, o yi irip 4 wonage me nen o wiya ndak-ndak 4 aret warit wundi wage menggerak me, o nggween paga inom, yi nggwok yenggenak laut inom, iri'ngga-kale'ngga inom, o wiya nen abolok eerit nage kero, malayikat ineebe 4 nen panggomborogo wonogwe iigirak.
66007002	Iige nagarik, wonage me, malayikat alik ambi oonegen wundi wage menggim nen wundi wage logonet, Ala eenik menggerak apuri leenogo piinok, ineraambe yelok iigo logowak nduk, amburu eeppiigak wonok wage nagaarik, nggween inom, niyo nggwok yenggenak laut inom, maluk eerogo puwak nduk, it malayikat ineebe 4 unde eeppiyareegerak nogo, oone nggwok paga yorage logonet,
66007003	"Nit ninogoba Ala ayeloman mini leenogo piinok, yelok logowak nduk, amburu inenggaawak paga labumbiiga'lek neegak, nggween inom, yi nggwok yenggenak laut inom, iri'ngga-kale'ngga inom, maluk eerogo puurak mage~o," yinuk, yorage mbaki,
66007004	"It Iterali paga wiganak inanebunu lombok abok ineebe lambuk togon seratus empat puluh empat ribu leenogo piya~o," yinuk, ari naruk konengge nagarik,
66007005	anebunu Yekura mendek dua belas ribu leenogo piige, anebunu Uruben mendek dua belas ribu leenogo piige, anebunu Nggat mendek dua belas ribu leenogo piige,
66007006	anebunu Atet mendek dua belas ribu leenogo piige, anebunu Natali mendek dua belas ribu leenogo piige, anebunu Manate mendek dua belas ribu leenogo piige,
66007007	anebunu Timeyon mendek dua belas ribu leenogo piige, anebunu Lewi mendek dua belas ribu leenogo piige, anebunu Itakat mendek dua belas ribu leenogo piige,
66007008	anebunu Tebulon mendek dua belas ribu leenogo piige, anebunu Yutup mendek dua belas ribu leenogo piige, anebunu Mbeniyamin mendek dua belas ribu leenogo piige, eeke logonet, Ala apuri yelok logowak nduk, amburu inenggaawak paga labunogo piinet nagaarak nogo ti, ineebe lambuk togon seratus empat puluh empat ribu aret iigirak~o.
66007009	Ti eeke kage nagarik, it aakumi inanebunu inalitak lombok inom, inoone alitak inom, inagabolo alitak inom, inenggela'me nen ambitak nggigik kuwak eereegwaarak nogo ti, ineebe ambik ineenggi lingginiyak abu meek iigirak. It aakumi ti, inambogoyum nggorek yanggwi negen yippunuk eyoongga kalenak wik-wik eeko logonet, at wone lengganogo yorage menggim eyo ndoonak paga kwi'ndak wonage nogo inom, Ndomba Aagaluk nogo inom, imbirak inabu'me mi'na'nuk,
66007010	inoone nggwok yogo logonet, "Wone lengganogo yorage menggenom kwi'ndak wonage kat ninogoba Ala nogo inom, Kat Ndomba Aagaluk inom, Kimbirak nen ninagap ndareegutak me, wa," yinuk, yorogwe iigak,
66007011	at wone lengganogo yorage menggim inom, it mbogut paga wonogwe inoweewi ineebe 24 nogo inom, it aakumi nen iigulik mendek ineebe 4 nogo inom, oolo wonogwe iigak, it malayikat yendok-wandok aago mi'ndak wonogwe nogo abok aret at wone lengganogo yorage menggim kwi'ndak wonage nogo, abu'me tebe yinuk, Ala alut eeko logonet,
66007012	"Amin~o! Kat ninogoba Ala aret me, Yi aakumi ndi aakumi abok kabu'me tebe yinuk, Inale'nggen kombakwi, kendage tiyappagagwi, Yi wone ndi wone abok kat keenu~o, yinuk, yokkugwi, Wa, yogo logonet kayuk wukwi, kalik komaawi ambik mondok kalilaakwi me, Wi, kugwi, eekwi nogo, Mondok-mondok togop aret eeko logowak~o, amin," yinuk, yogwi iigirak~o.
66007013	Yogo mbaka, it mbogut paga wonogwe inowe ambi nen an yo'nege logonet, "It aakumi inayum yanggwi negen yirik ti, taamini~o? Ndi, it nggeeme nen wagaarak mbaken~o?"
66007014	Yo'nege mbaki, "Nogoba~o. An neenggo'lek me, kat nen mban yu~o," yoge mbaki, at nen an yo'nege logonet, "Lek~o. It aakumi yi, aaninggin-paaninggin mondok alik negen eeppiigwi iigak, inenggela'me nen wundi wagaarak nogo ineebe yi aret~o. It nogo ti, inayum laambu yanggwi negen aruwak nduk, Ndomba Aagaluk amiya nogo paga inayum kookkologogwaarak me,
66007015	Wone lengganogo yorage menggim Ala enggaanom time logonet, Ko'lu-kii'me Ala awi wurik me ake eekwi iigak, At wone lengganogo yorage menggim eyo ndoonak paga kwi'ndak wonage ninogoba Ala nogo nen maluk inoba age kero, abu'me piirogo wonage agaarik~o.
66007016	-
66007017	Ndi, wone lengganogo yorage menggim oolo lombok menggerak Ndomba Aagaluk nogo nen ineebe liirogon aret ndegeninake, Ineenik mondok logowak nduk, niyo eneeri abe mili me piya nage, Eerigin me, Mbi abu aganake, niyo abu aganake, mo andi inooke, o aganggen nen ndeyak eerogo piige, Eerigin mondok lek~o. It le yogwe iinok, Ala nen aret inale amburu lek eerogo piyamenggerak logogun~o," yinuk, yo'nege kagarak.
66008001	Ti'nuk, Ndomba Aagaluk nogo nen keele age wobok maarak 7 nogo piingge mbaki, mbogut paga time inoone inom, inabolok inom, mondok lek puk wonogwe iigak, setengah jam negen age mbaki,
66008002	it malayikat ineebe 7 Ala abu'me mi'ndak menggaarak nogo oone nggwok eeka trompet 7 wogorage kagarak.
66008003	Kage neegak, malayikat alik ambi togolowak mbuti emas paga ogobakkigirik eenggime wonok, Ala ake warogo kani kunggo menggam mi'nari wage mbaki, it Ala apuri ake leenak tamban eekwi inoone yogwi nogo at yoge logonet, kani kunggo menggam mbuti emas paga ogobakkigirik Ala wone lengganogo yorage menggim abu'me wonage nogome, kani kuni ungguwak nduk, obari abe kaga apit toologo wogoge kagarak.
66008004	Ndi, at malayikat nen kani kungge kagak, ka'luk obari nogo Ala nen obeelom kage, ndi, it Ala apuri ake leenak tamban eekwi inoone Ala unde yogwi iinok, at nen Ala yoge nogo aruk konengge, eeke kagarak~o.
66008005	Nogo eeke kage neegak, obari abe kaga togolowa'na toolak wonagagerak nogo, kani kungge menggim nogome nen kani kunik anggen wagangge nagaarik, togolowa'na nogome mambunuk, mbo nggween paga wuppi wage mbaki, o ngguurubu oone ari, o kimbik pindanggage, eeke kagak, mi nggwok nuk-nuk eeke kagarak.
66008006	Ti eeke kage nagarik, it malayikat ineebe 7 inalitak lombok oone nggwok eeka trompet wogoragaarak porogo wonogwe nogo, oone eeruwok nduk, li'luk eekwi iigirak.
66008007	Oone nggwok eeka trompet porogo wonogwe nogo, ambi aa'-nduk arompet oone eeke mbaki, mayu kumulinggen inom, kani inom, amiya inom, nenggelak-kenggelak eerogo punuk, o nggween paga mbo wuppit wage mbaki, nggween inom, eyo inom, ando mogonogo teppunuk, ando mogonogo sepertiga nogo kani nengge logonet, iri'ngga-kale'ngga ki wonage nogo tigitogon nenet nage kagarak.
66008008	Malayikat ambi oone nggwok eeka arompet nogo, oone eeke mbaki, ti'nuk, inore ambi nen arompet eeke kagak, puut nggwok ambi kani wunuk agan yi nggwok yenggenak laut nogo paga kwi'nari wangge mbaki, yi nggwok yenggenak ando mogonogo teppege logonet, ando sepertiga nogo amiya eerogo pegerak me,
66008009	yi mendek ndi mendek niyo inikime nugu menggaarak nogo ando mogonogo teppege logonet, ando sepertiga nogo kambit nogwe, ndi, yiiro nggwok niyo ogombaga nugwi nogo ando mogonogo teppege logonet, ando sepertiga nogo kalenak-pugunik arit nage, eeke kagarak.
66008010	Malayikat mbere oone nggwok eeka inarompet nogo, oone eeko mbaka, ti'nuk, at ambi nen arompet oone eeke kagak, laaluguragan nggwok ambi ndi wunuk ari nogo pogom mbogut paga nen wunuk agan wambi wage nagaarik, niyo nage inom, eneeri wungge menggim inom, abok aret ando mogonogo teppege logonet, ando sepertiga nogo ale eerogo pit nage kagarak.
66008011	Laaluguragan nogo ti, endage Aleegwi aret me, niyo eneeri-eneeri ando mogonogo sepertiga nogo ale eerogo pit nagaarak me, aakumi nonggo nagaarik, kambit nogwe iigirak~o.
66008012	Malayikat kenagan oone nggwok eeka inarompet nogo, oone eeko mbaka, at ambi nen arompet oone eeke kagak, oonegen eya inom, tut eya inom, laaluguragan eya inom, abeenok mogonogo sepertiga nogo, abinak lek eerogo pege kenok, o liingge nogo eya mbuuluk age, ndi, oonikiya kenok, o abu apit age, eeke logowak nduk, oonegen eya inom, tut eya inom, laaluguragan eya inom, ando mogonogo teppege logonet, ando sepertiga nogo, abinak lek age kagarak.
66008013	Ti age kage neegak, towe wu negen mbogut paga wuga agan nage logonet, "Malayikat ineebe 4 oone nggwok eeka inarompet nogo, oone muk eekaarak kwe, ineebe 3 perak, eeruwok nduk, abu li'luk eekwi wonogwe me, it aakumi nggween paga mendek ti, inabuwa~o, inabuwa~o, inabuwa~o," yinuk, oone nggwok paga agan nage naruk konenggirak.
66009001	Konengge nagarik, wonage me, malayikat ineebe 4 oone nggwok eeka inarompet nogo oone eeko mbaka, ti'nuk, at ambi nen arompet eeke kagak, laaluguragan ambi mbogut paga nen nggween paga wambi wage kagarak. Wambi wagaarak nogo nen Kambunuk Nogo Menggam mbuun ambena ogu kiiniki paga lombok tu paaruwak nduk, kunci wogoge kagarak~o.
66009002	Wogogerak Kambunuk Nogo Menggam mbuun ambe nogo tu paake mbaki, yugum yugu ka'luk yonggo-ndonggo eeke menggi kwak, mbuun ambena nen ka'luk alik negen lagi wage logonet, oonegen inom, o oolo ogona ya'i inom, apit eerogo pege kagarak.
66009003	Kage neegak, ka'luk enggela'me nen wurin ambik lagi wogo nagaarik, nggitamuru eyak inooketak andi kogo mengga kwak, wurin nogo nen aakumi ineyak mbaninabit nogwe paga andi yagan wako logowak nduk, inomaawi eeppiige kagarak.
66009004	Inomaawi eeppiige nagaarik, yorage logonet, "Iri'ngga-kale'ngga inom, igale inom, yi mendek ndi mendek ki wonage nogo abok aret kineyak lelenogo nenet nogo logorak mage~o. Ata, it aakumi Ala nen amburu inenggaawak paga labumbiyoolik kenok mban kineyak mbaninabit nogo logonip~o.
66009005	Ndi, ineebe kambuwak nduk, nibininaburak ti mage~o. Ata, we andi yagan wakwi iigak, tut 5 penenuwak nduk, kineyak mbaninabit nogo logonip~o," yinuk, yorage mbaki, nggitamuru nogo nen ineyak mbaninakaatak andi yagan wako mengga kwak, ndak-ndak aret ineyak mbaninabit nogwe iigak, andi nen yagan yobak-nggolak warit nogwe iigirak.
66009006	Ti eyom paga it aakumi andi nen yagan wako logonet, "Nggarurogon kambuwok lak ao," yinuk, inowe-inawot nen mondok-mondok inooruwak nduk, yoramenggaarak kwe, kambuurak inoba ari woraagin lek me, kangga'lek we ineenik yagan yobak-nggolak mban wako logogun~o.
66009007	-
66009009	Ndi, wurin nogo ti, inetenggen aap kokwak kwe, ineeruwak ti, kumi ineeruwak laanak nogo pogom, ndi, ineyak ti, nggeewo singa eyak nogo pogom, wonogwe iigirak. Ndi, kuda amborowak paga kwi'na'nuk wim namburuwok nduk, li'luk eerogo piigo mengga kwak, it wurin ineebe nogo ti, togop aret li'luk eerogo piige logonet, nggare-nggare mbuti emas paga ogobakkigirik inom, tin mbuti omanggen paga yarak inom, yirippiinok, wim namburuwok nduk, kuda nggweendo paga mbarembunuk, niikkenok wim endok kuni unggwogo logonet, kuda ineebe apit me iniyogobit oonembogu nogwe konenggo mengga kwak, wurin nogo wuga agan nogo logonet, ina'naabit oone ti, togop aret agan nogwe iigirak~o.
66009010	Ineyak ti, nggitamuru ineyak nogo pogom me, ineyak aakumi mbaninakwi iinok, andi nen yagan wakwi iigak, tut 5 penengge kagarak.
66009011	Ndi, at malayikat Kambunuk Nogo Menggam mbuun ambeme unde menggerak nogo ti, it wurin inowe endagembogut inarum menggerak at aret~o. At endage ti, aakumi Iberani inoone paga, "Abaron," yogwe, ndi, Yunani inoone paga, "Apoliyon," yogwe, eeko menggaarak. (Ndi, nit ninoone paga ti, "Pup Eerogo Piiga~o," yinuk, yogo monggoorak.)
66009012	"Inabuwa~o, yinuk, ne kenagan paga ari konenggendak nogo ti, ambi wurin nen muk eeke kagandak nogo aret kwe, mbere ti awo eeka'lek me, kenegen logot~o," yinuk, yo'nege kagarak.
66009013	Yo'nege mbaki, nenegen wonage me, malayikat ineebe 5 oone nggwok eeka inarompet nogo oone eeko mbaka, ti'nuk, at ambi nen arompet oone eeke mbaki, obari abe kaga kani kunggo menggam mbuti emas paga ogobakkigirik irip-irip ndomba eyak negen 4 to ari Ala abu'me wonage nogome nen oone ambi ari logonet,
66009014	"Malayikat ineebe 4 niyo nggwok Eparat aa'nggi paga keele maarak wonogwe nogo, mbet piinogo nappiyet~o," yinuk, at malayikat trompet oone eekerak nogo yoge mbaki,
66009015	it malayikat ineebe 4 nogo nen tahun ti paga, tut ti paga, ne ti paga, oonegen ti paga, mondok ndak-ndak ari nage kenok, aakumi ando mogonogo teppiigo logonet, ando sepertiga nogo inoorit nogo logowak nduk, pipuk eerogo piyareegerak nogo aret inoorit nogo logowak nduk, piinogo teppiige kagarak.
66009016	Kage nagarik, "It aakumi yigin unde kuda inamborowak paga kwi'nogo nagaarik, wim namburi nagaarak nogo ti, ineebe duaratus juta aret~o," yinuk, ari naruk konenggirak.
66009017	Ndi, kuda inom, aap ineebe kuda inamborowak paga kwi'ndak wonogwe inom, nabinggaanggo kage logonet, iigirak nogo yi~o. Inarin nogo ti, kani kunik kere ari, mbogut mili kibu-kibu pege, ndi, yaliingga yi'nip nggwi ari, eeke nogo pogom, inarin etenggen togop aret kagarak. Ndi, kuda inanobak nogo ti, nggeewo singa anobak nogo pogom aret me, kugi lengga ndi wurogo pit nawak nduk, inambeme nen kwi yigirik etenggen yaliingga yi'nip nogo pogom inom, kani omoonuk inom, ka'luk inom, wundi wage kagarak.
66009018	Inambeme nen wundi wagaarak nogo paga nen, kugilengga ndi wurogo pit nagaarak me, aakumi ando mogonogo teppiige logonet, ando sepertiga nogo kugi andi nen mondok kambit nogwe iigirak.
66009019	It kuda inage ti, waalo muuru anobak nogo pogom nen aakumi inoorit nogo nagaarak me, inambe inom, inage inom, ti mondok omaawi ambik aret iigirak~o.
66009020	It ando andi nen kambulik teppiigerak ineenik wonogwe nogo nen, "Nit togop aret kambit nogwe niyo, ninagugiwak nogo ti, yi mendek ndi mendek inigen kogwe, ninoone inaruk konenggwi, tu nogwe, eekulik kagak we aanom warogo mbuti emas paga, mbuti perak nogo paga, mbuti tembaga etenggen kunik negen nogo paga, yugum paga, eyo paga, ogobakkigirogo punuk, alut eekwi, kugi inendage tiyappiigwi,
66009021	aakumi inookwi, magagirak inookwi, kumi ugun wurinakwi, yogoot waganggwi, eeko monggoorak abok aret mbo punuk, niniki koonuwi~o," yinuk, yuurak op aret kwe, mbo pega'lek iniki kundugu logonet, eerit nogwe iigirak.
66010001	Eekwi nogo iige nagarik, ti'nuk, malayikat alilaakwi ambi, ndugwi nogo ayum negen pirik-perek eerak mbogut paga nen wambi wage kagarak. Anobak paga liware negen nggare-nggare yirik logonet, etenggen ti, oonegen pogom, ndi, iyok ti, eyo yinik paga kani wunuk ari nogo pogom logonet,
66010002	mbuku mbuuluk pirik-perek eerak ambi eenggime mbigamborogo wonage kagarak. Iyok abe'nggan niyo nggwok yenggenak laut nogo ogombaga pege, ndi, iyok kwaare'nggan nggween paga pege, eeppunuk logonet,
66010003	nggeewo singa oone mondok ku ari menggi kwak, oone nggwok ari mbaki, o ngguurubu ne 7 paga ari naruk konenggirak.
66010004	O ngguurubu ne 7 paga ari naruk konembunuk, ari nogo liiru mbanikit nduk eeke me, mbogut paga nen oone ambi yo'nege logonet, "O ngguurubu ne 7 paga ari konenggendak nogo ti, liiru mbanugun~o. Ata, kinikime mban kumaapporogo logot~o," yinuk, yo'nege kagarak.
66010005	Yo'nege mbaki, nenegen neegak, malayikat iyok ambi niyo nggwok yenggenak laut ogombaga pege, ndi, ambi nggween paga pege, eeppunuk, mi'ndak wonage kagarak nogo nen, Abet aret ari, mbaruwak nduk eenggi abe'nggan mbogut paga nippunuk,
66010006	-
66010007	at mbogut inom, mbogut paga wonogwe inom, nggween inom, nggween paga wonogwe inom, niyo nggwok yenggenak inom, inikime wonogwe inom, abok aret wakkagagerak mondok-mondok itok eenik menggerak nogo endage kungge logonet, "At Ala nen, Kit nagote wone kumaarak nogo ando yokkiragagirak kwe, irip pagaluk ando kumaarak wonage nogo, peebi kineenu arumunggup~o, yinuk, at ayeloman mini yorage kagak, yoraga nen yoragagerak nogo, ambinom kumaapporogo logogin lek~o. It malayikat inee-be 6 nen oone nggwok eeka trompet nogo oone muk eekaarak kwe, ambiret 7 nogo ti, awo eeka'lek me, eeke kenok, wone nogo pagak yigin~o," yinuk, ari naruk konenggirak.
66010008	Naruk konengge nagarik, wonage me, mbogut paga oone ambi yo'nege kagarak nogo nen ambinom yo'nege logonet, "At malayikat iyok peenok nggween paga pege, ndi, peenok niyo nggwok yenggenak laut paga pege, eeppunuk, mi'ndak mbuku mbanak eenggime mbigamborogo wonage ti, kola nak~o,"
66010009	Yo'nege mbaki, malayikat nogo owagam nage nagarik, "Mbuku mbuuluk ti, wo'niru~o," yoge mbaki, at nen wo'nege logonet, "Waganogo namen~o. Nengge keegak, kambe paga nggiin amburu negen ombat abe kaamenggendak kwe, kaanagale paga perak, alembere agan nage kaamunggun~o," yinuk, yo'nege kagarak.
66010010	Yo'nege mbaki, mbuku malayikat eenggime wonage nogo waganogo nengge neegak, nambe paga nggiin amburu negen ombat abe kagarak kwe, naanagale paga perak, alembere agan nage kagarak~o.
66010011	Mbuku nogo nengge mbaki, mbogut paga oone yo'nege kagarak nogo nen ambinom yo'nege logonet, "Aakumi inanebunu alitak lombok inom, inagabolo alitak inom, inoone alitak inom, aap inendagembogut inom, yi aakumi ndi aakumi apit wone yi abok aret, Ndogop arigin, yorage logonu~o," yinuk, yo'nege kagarak.
66011001	Ti yo'nege kage nagarik, wonage me, wakkagak waanggun negen ogobakkigirik ambi wo'nege logonet, "Ala awi wurik inom, Ala ake warogo kani kunggo menggam inom, wakkage, ndi, aakumi Ala awi wurik me alut eeri unggwogo menggaarak nogo, ineebe keenggi linggininake, eeri nak~o.
66011002	Eerit nage logonet, Ala awi wurik me oore'nggam endekem nogo wakkaagun~o. It aakumi endekem mendek nen o kota abe alik leenak menggim nogome iniyok aambele eerogo pit nogo logonet, Ala awi wurik me oore'nggam endekem time inom aambele eerogo pit nogwe iigak, tut 42 peneniyak koonak me, wakkoorak mage~o.
66011003	Ndi, it aap ineebe mbere noone yorogo logowak nduk, nappiyaminggirak nogo nen aakumi iniki puru yogo logonet, inayum nibinik maluk mendek yiko mengga kwak yirik logonet, an noone yorogwe iigak, nogo seribu duaratus enam puluh yogo logogun~o," yinuk, yo'nege kagarak.
66011004	Eyo tayitun mbere inom, ndi, ndi wuninogo pegak mbere inom, at yi mendek ndi mendek alom unde ninogoba abu'me menggerak nogo pogom ti, it Ala wone yorogo menggaarak ineebe mbere nogo aret~o.
66011005	It aap mbere ti, inambeme nen kani wunuk agan wundi wage logonet, it inom ogoorak wonogwe nogo inooko menggaarak me, "Aap mbere ti, inooruwi~o," yinuk, inooriyak nduk eekwi iigak, it inambeme nen kani wunuk agan wundi wage logonet, it inooriyak eekwi ineebe nogo kani wunuk togon nunggwi iigirak~o.
66011006	It aap ineebe mbere nogo ti, iniki koombunuk, "O kibi paga wone yorogo logowam mayu woraagun~o," yinuk, yogwi iinok, mayu waga'lek puk wonage, "Niyo yi, amiya aru~o," yogwi iinok, amiya aret age, ndi, "O nggween paga yime kugi lengga ndi wu'naru~o," yogwi iinok, kugi lengga ndi wu'nage, togop aret eerit nogo logowak nduk, Ala nen unde eeppiige kagarak~o.
66011007	Kage mbaki, at wone yo'nege nogo nen ambinom yo'nege logonet, "Wone yorogo logowak nduk, nappiyamenggerak nogo age yobok togon yorogo mbaremengga, nggwiya nggwok lombok Kambunuk Nogo Menggam mbuun ambena nen lagi wage logomenggerik, aap ineebe mbere nogo nggugiraanet muguren nage logonet, nibininake kenok, kanggo mbaremengga,
66011008	ineebe o kota nggwok inowe eyo karo-karo paga warogo pereegwam tu nggwok yarak nogo paga, pili ogo logowak nduk, mbo piyaagun~o. O kota nggwok yogo monggoorak nogo, it ando wone eegu laarogo yogo logonet, O Torom~o, o Metit~o, yinuk, yogo menggaarak nogome aret ineebe mbo piinok,
66011009	it aakumi inanebunu alitak lombok inom, inoone alitak inom, inagabolo alitak inom, yi aakumi ndi aakumi apit nen, Wi! yinuk, pegiya wogwe iigak, nogo kenagan abu yippunuk, o ambi weeremenggerak liingge paga nggween taambiyoorak me, mbo piyaanip, yugun~o.
66011010	Ndi, it aakumi nggween paga wonogwe nogo abok nen, It aap Ala wone yaga mbere yi nen inoone yogo nagaarak paga nit andi-pandi mondok alik negen eeppinanit nugu nagaarak me, Kayik a! Op kangga~o, yinuk, inale'nggen mbako logonet laago lakwi, inamendek tumbut-tumbut eekkologwe, eerugun~o," yinuk, yo'nege kagarak.
66011011	-
66011012	Kage nagarik, nenegen nee-gak, nogo kenagan yippunuk, o ambi weegerak liingge paga Ala nen ambebubu aap mbere nogo inikime mambiige mbaki, it apit inigen iigak, ineenik a'nuk, mi'nogo mbaka, mbogut paga nen oone nggwok ari logonet, "Lagi wa'nip~o," yorage mbaki, inaruk konembunuk, "It op kangga~o," yinuk, inale'nggen mbakwi nogo inigen iigak, ndugwi enggela'me mbogut paga laganggwi iinok, aakumi nogo nen, "Ia!" yinuk, iniki ma'nogo logonet, inagabiti ambik ogwe iigirak.
66011013	Awo pi wogonakwi iigak, mi nggwok nuk-nuk eeke kagak, o kota time aakumi inawi ambik wurik nogo ando teppege, ando sepersepuluh langgu-langgu nage, eeke logonet, aakumi apit ineebe tujuh ribu aret aambeleninake mbaki, it ando teppiigerak nogo inagabiti nen at mbogut paga menggerak Ala nogo mondok tiyappugwi iigirak.
66011014	Iige nagarik, nenegen wonage me, at mbogut paga nen oone ari nogo ambinom yo'nege logonet, "Inabuwa~o, yinuk, ne kenagan paga ari konenggendak ti, mbere muk eeke kagandak kwe, ambiret nogo mbet-mbet eerikit nduk eeke me, kenegen logot~o," yinuk, yo'nege kagarak.
66011015	Yo'nege mbaki, nenegen wonage me, malayikat 6 inarompet oone eeko mbaka, ambi nogo nen arompet nogo oone eeke mbaki, it mbogut paga time nen inoone nggwok yogo logonet, "O nggween paga time aakumi inabu'me piinok menggam abok aret, at ninogoba inom, at leenogo mippereegerak Keritut inom, imbirak inoone konenggo logowok nduk, inabu'me ari waga~o. Ari wogwe iinok, Keritut nogo nen inowe endagembogut logonet, mondok-mondok wone lengganogo yorage logogin~o," yinuk, yogwe iigirak.
66011016	Yogo mbaka, nenegen neegak, it mbogut paga wonogwe inoweewi ineebe 24 wone lengganogo yorogo menggam eyo ndoonak paga Ala abu'me kwi'ndak menggaarak nogo nen inetenggen wanduk Ala abu'me ngginnari nogo nagaarik, alut eeko logonet,
66011017	"Kat komaawi lombok menggendak aa'nduk wonagagindak, yogondak wonage, ninogoba Ala nogo kat aret~o. It aakumi abok inowe kendagembogut logonet, wone lengganogo yorage logokit nduk, unde agagindak nogo, Yogondak yi eyom paga aret eeke logokit nduk, mi'nagandak me, Wa, wa, yokkogo~o.
66011018	Yi aakumi ndi aakumi abok inanini kombako logonet, At ninowe endagembogut logorak nineebi~o, yinuk, agan nogwe nogo, Kanini inoba piige, it kambit nogogwaarak nogo inawone amburu mbanogo inowak loonogo piige, It kayeloman mini yorage keegak yoraga inom, kapuri kake leenak nogo inom, it kayuk wuko menggaarak inom, inendage lek inendage warak abok aret obeelom eekwi iinok onggo wogorage, Ndi, it o nggween paga time maluk eerogo pugwi nogo pup eerogo piige, Eeriyak eyom abu panggo yi wagaarak me, wa," yinuk, yogwi iigirak.
66011019	Yogo mbaka, Ala awi wurik mbogut paga nogome tu paa'nage mbaki, Ala aloobut mbanak wone yoragagerak liiru mbanak yonggolak wonage nogo, kin ari wage kage neegak, o yabok eeke, ngguurubu ari, mi nuk ari, mayu kumulinggen mondok lubu-lubu wangge, eeke kagarak~o.
66012001	Eeke kage nagarik, mbogut paga time eerubok mendek mondok iya lombok ambi eeke kagarak. Kage logonet, kwe ambi tut eebe paga mi'ndak wonage me, ambogoyum negen ti, oonegen aret yirik, ndi, anobak paga nggare-nggare mendaarak enggela'me laaluguragan 12 nabenak wonage kagarak.
66012002	Kwe nogo, abila wonage me, aagaluk ndariyak nduk enegen paganak andi nen yagan wake logonet, kwa ari kagarak.
66012003	Kwa ari mbaki, mbogut paga time inagabiti warak mendek alik ambi eeke kagarak. Kage logonet, waalo nggwok tinambe pogom agabolo maa'ngga kunik me, eebe ambit aret kwe, anobak 7, ndi, anobak nogo paga eyak 10, ndi, anobak 7 nogo paga nggare-nggare mendaarak abok aret yirik kagarak.
66012004	At waalo nogo age paga laaluguragan mbogut paga wonage nogo ando iigak, ando sepertiga nogo pelenogo nggween paga mbo wuppit wage kagarak. Kage nagarik, waalo nggwok nogo nen, "Kwe nogo aagaluk ndake kenok, naakit~o," yinuk, kwe nogo owagam enaarak wonage kagak,
66012005	yi aakumi ndi aakumi endekem konenggulik mendek abok aret inarum logonet, mbim obate mbanak ineenggime logonet, inoone omaawi paga yorogo mengga kwak, oone omaawi paga wone lengganogo yorage logowak nduk, at kwe nogo nen aagaluk aap aret ndake mbaki, elege nogo ndininuk, wone lengganogo yorage menggim at Ala owagam pi lagangge kagarak.
66012006	Pi lagangge mbaki, agalo nogo, logowam Ala nen ogobakkigirogo pereegim karume aakumi lek me time kole nagaarak wonage me, Ala nen arum wonage kagak, nogo seribu duaratus enam puluh yit nage kagarak~o.
66012007	Ti eeke kage nagarik, at Mikayen awuri malayikat mendek inom nen at waalo nggwok tinambe pogom nogo, awuri inom mbogut paga time wim nambukwi iigirak.
66012008	Nambuko logonet, it nen waalo nggwok nogo awuri inom tebenogo piigo nagaarik, "O mbogut paga yime logorak lek~o," yinuk,
66012009	at waalo nggwok nogo awuri inom mbelenogo nggween paga mbo wuppiya wage kagarak. Wuppiya wage mbaki, waalo nggwok mbo wuppi wagaarak nogo ti, o maan nen yi aakumi ndi aakumi abok aret inambokan lagangge menggerak Ibilit nogo ti, Tile aret me, at awuri inom abok aret mbogut paga nen mbelenogo nggween paga wuppiya wogwe iigirak~o.
66012010	Mbelenogo wuppiya wogo mba-ka, oone nggwok ambi mbogut paga nen ari logonet, "At Ala enggaanom paga ninoreewi Ala apuri ko'lu-kii'me pilit wone inoba piige menggerak nogo, muk wuppi wagaarak me, At Ala omaawi paga Tile tebenogo punuk, apuri inagap ndake, Ninogoba Ala nen it yi aakumi ndi aakumi abok at abu'me piige, Ndi, Kinowe endagembogut yi aret~o, yinuk, leenogo pereegerak Keritut nogo, oone mban konenggwi, Eeke logorak eyom ari waga~o.
66012011	It ninoreewi nogo nen Ndomba Aagaluk amiya wundeegerak abet mba'nuk, iniki ti paga panggombunuk logonet, Ninooriyak op aret~o, yinuk, Inagabiti lek Ala wone wonok yoranet nugwi paga Tile tebenogo pugwi me,
66012012	Kat mbogut inom, kit mbogut paga monggotak inom, kiniki ale'nggen mbako logonip~o. It nggween paga wonogwe nogo inom, niyo nggwok yenggenak laut paga wonogwe nogo inom, nogo perak, Inenggela'me at Tile wuppi wagaarak nogo nen, An ne mbereeluk logonuk, nenggaawak lek arigin kagi, mba'nuk, Anini nen aakumi lale-pale eerogo piyaakit nduk, wambi nagaarak wonage me, inabuwa~o," yinuk, ari kagarak.
66012013	Ndi, at waalo nggwok nogo nen, "An nggween paga abu aret mbo wuppani wagaarak kagi," mbake nagaarik, kwe aagaluk wulaga ndakerak nogo, mugurok nage mbaki,
66012014	wake kero, o at logowam ogobakkigirogo pereegim karume nogome nawak nduk, Ala nen towe wu a'naabit kokwak, kwe nogo, a'naabit warak eeppege mbaki, wuga agan o nogome namenggerak wonage me, Ala nen arum wonage kagak, tahun kenagan eeppunuk, ambi oolo eeruwak nduk, nage kagarak.
66012015	Ndi, nage kagak, niyo nen kwe ti wonok nawak nduk, niyo nggwok wu'nuk nage menggi kwak, at waalo nggwok nogo ambeme nen niyo kilirogo aru nggaruk nappegerak kwe,
66012016	nggween nogo nen kwe nogo yeenggwaage logonet, ambe nggaganogo punuk, niyo kole nage kwak ambeme nen kilirogo nappegerak nogo, nggween ambe nggaganak me time wuppege kagarak.
66012017	Ti eeke mbaki, at waalo nggwok nogo nen anini agaket ari nagaarik, "Ala nen, Yogop ee'nu ndogop ee'nu, ari menggerak wone liirogon eerit nogwe inom, Yetut nen paganogo yoragagerak wone abet mba'nuk mugurok nogwe inom, kwe nogo aagalogwe ando it aret me, Ninom wim namburi naakit~o," yinuk,
66012018	niyo nggwok yenggenak laut aa'nggi paga enaa'nari nagaarak wonage kagarak.
66013001	Ti eeke kage nagarik, nggeewo negen ambi niyo nggwok yenggenak laut inikime nen wundi wage kagarak. At nggeewo negen nogo ti, aruk alom me eyak 10, ndi, anobak 7, wonage kagarak. Ndi, eyak 10 nogo paga nggare-nggare mendaarak abok yirik, ndi, anobak 7 nogo paga Ala endage miyuk-meya eerogo pugu liiru mbanak abok wonage kagarak.
66013002	Ndi, nggeewo pogom anini ambik niyome nen wundi wage kagarak eebe nogo ti, nggeewo harimau negen aret me, iyok ti, yo'nggok beruang iyok pogom, ndi, eyagarin nogo ti, nggeewo singa eyagarin nde eerak nogo pogom wonage kagarak. At waalo nggwok tinambe pogom nogo nen, "An nomaawi paga eerit nage, an wone lengganogo yorage minggim logonet, wone lengganogo yorage, eeke logonok nduk, abok aret kat unde eeppagagi~o," yinuk, yoge kagarak.
66013003	Kage nagarik, nggeewo anobak ando nogo kagak, anobak ambit nogo wako mbaka, mondok kambuurak nduk eeke kagarak kwe, lek age mbaki, it aakumi nggween paga mendek abok aret, "Wi!" ugo logonet, at mban amugurok nogwe iigirak.
66013004	Ndi, waalo nggwok nogo nen at nggeewo negen niyome nen wundi wagaarak nogo, awone kiliregerak me, waalo nggwok nogo tiyappunuk, alut eekwi, ndi, nggeewo nogo kunduk alut eeko logonet, "Nggeewo yi kokwak ambi wonogwe mondok lek me, taani nen at inom wim namburiyak mbakop? Mondok lek aret~o," yinuk, at tiyappugwi, eekwi iigirak.
66013005	At nggeewo anini warak niyome nen wundi wagaarak nogo tut 42 penengge kagak, wogoppake logonet, Ala miyuk-meya eerogo pege, ndi, wone lengganogo yorage, eeke logowak nduk, waalo nggwok nogo nen awone kilirege kagarak.
66013006	Awone kilirege mbaki, nggeewo nogo nen at Ala eebe inom, at endage inom, at menggim inom, ndi, it mbogut paga menggaarak inom, it abok aret at oone paga miyuk-meya eerogo piinet nage kagarak.
66013007	It aap inanebunu alitak lombok inom, inoone alitak inom, inagabolo alitak inom, yi aakumi ndi aakumi abok aret at abu'me tebenogo piinok, at mban mondok tiyanak logowak nduk, waalo nggwok nogo nen awone nggeewo nogo kiliregerak me, at nggeewo nogo nen it Ala apuri ake leenak nogo inom wim nambuke logonet, tebenogo piinet nage kagarak.
66013008	Ndomba Aagaluk wareegwaarak nogo nen o maan mbogut-nggween yi awo wakkaga'lek kagak, aakumi o nggween paga menggaarak abok aret it inendage mondok-mondok ineenik aganaburak mbuku paga liiru mbanak wonage lek kenok, at nggeewo nogo alut eekwi iigirak.
66013009	-
66013010	"It keele maarinaburak punik kenok keele maarinakwi, Kambuwak nduk mbuti tege paga inooriyak punik kenok, inookwi, Eeko logogun~o, yinuk, yereegerak nogo aret aganabit nagun me, aganabit nogwe iigak, it Ala apuri ake leenak nogo nen, Yi nonggop ee'ninakwi~o? yinuk, iniki lek-lek arugwaarik~o. Ata, Obeelom eeppinaniyak yereegerak nogo abet aret eeppinanigin~o, yinuk, iniki kwippunuk, inogogumbuk logonet, waganggo logowak~o. Inaruk wonage kenok, wone ti, liirogon aret konenggo logowak~o," yinuk, yo'nege kagarak.
66013011	Ti'nuk, peebi nen nggeewo alik ambi nggween enoona nen lagi wage kagarak. Nggeewo nogo ti, aruk alom me eyak mbere ndomba eyak pogom kwe, oone perak, waalo nggwok oone nogo pogom ari kagarak.
66013012	Nggeewo aa'nduk niyo yenggenak me nen lagi wagaarak awone kiliregerak nogo li'luk eerogo wagangge nagaarik, it aakumi nggween paga wonogwe abok aret yorage logonet, "Kit nen nggeewo aa'nduk lagi wagaarak anobak ambi wako mbaka, kambuurak nduk eekerak kwe, lek agaarak nogo mban alut eeko logonip~o," yinuk, oone omaawi paga nabek togon yorage kagarak.
66013013	Ndi, nggeewo peebi nggween enoona lagi wagaarak nogo nen eerubok mendek iya tit eerit nage logonet, aakumi abok inenggaanom paga kani kunik mbogut paga nen nggween paga wuppi wage kagarak.
66013014	At nggeewo aa'nduk lagi wagaarak oone kiliregerak paga, eerubok mendek iya tit eerit nage logonet, "Nggeewo negen ambi mbuti tege paga wakaarak kwe, eenik agaarak nogo, ogut wakkagak ambi ogobakkigirogo punuk, at mban alut eeko logonip~o," yinuk, it aakumi nggween paga wonogwe nogo inambokan lagangge logonet, yorage kagarak.
66013015	Yorage mbaki, nggeewo aa'nduk lagi wagaarak ogut wakkagak ogobakkigirik nogo oone yuwak nduk, ambebubu inikime pu eerogo mambuurak unde eeppegerak me, pu eerogo mambege mbaki, ogut wakkagak ogobakkigirik nogo oone warak age nagaarik, at alut eeka'lek nogo anini nen inoorit nage kagarak.
66013016	At nggeewo ti nen it aap inendage warak inom, inendage lek inom, ineenggi warak inom, ineenggi lek inom, weelek mendek inom, aakumi inayeloman inom, abok aret ineenu agak ambi ineenggi abe'nggan paga ilik, inenggaawak paga a, liiru mbanogo piige nagaarik, yorage logonet,
66013017	"It aakumi ti, an nendage ilik, an nanomor a, ineebe paga liiru mbanak wonogwe lek kenok, inamendek onggo mbanggologwe, ndi, yi mendek ndi mendek kunggwi, eeko logorak mondok mage~o," yinuk, wone lengganogo yorage kagarak.
66013018	Kage nagarik, at wone yo'nege nogo nen ambinom yo'nege kage logonet, "Wone lengganogo yorage kagandak nogo ti, it aap iniki warak nen mban kin kogo logogun~o. At nggeewo nogo nen liiru mbanggerak nogo ti, aakumi nen eekwi inanomor liiru mbanak 666 aret me, it aakumi iniki warak kenok, Yi aret kagi~o, yinuk, liippogo logowak~o," yinuk, yo'nege kagarak.
66014001	Yo'nege kage nagarik, wonage me, it aap ineebe apit seratus empat puluh empat ribu nogo Ndomba Aagaluk endage inom, at ogoba endage inom, inalitak lombok inenggaawak paga liiru mbanak Ndomba Aagaluk nogo inom puut Tiyon nogo paga mi'ndak wonogwe nenegen nagiigirak.
66014002	Nagiige nagarik, niyoraakut oonebu ari, o ngguurubu iya tit ari, eeke nogo pogom, mbogut paga nen nggitat nggwok oone eekwi nogo pogom, oone nggwok ambi ari naruk konenggirak.
66014003	Konengge nagarik, at wone lengganogo yorage menggim menggerak eebe nogo inom, it aakumi nen iigulik mendek ineebe 4 nogo inom, ndi, it mbogut paga wonogwe inoweewi inom, wonogwe iigak, it ineebe seratus empat puluh empat ribu nogo nen inabu'me wanggeko logonet, ndawi ngget mendek wakwi iigirak. Ndi, ndawi wakwi iigirak nogo ti, it aakumi ugun nen mamumbunuk tiyaniyak abu meek~o. Ata, at Ala nen, "It o nggween paga time logorak lek~o," yinuk, aap seratus empat puluh empat ribu inonggo mbaneegerak nogo nen mban tiyaniyak perak op me, tiyanggwi iigirak~o.
66014004	It aap ti, kumi wogonakulik me, kumi inom mondok lambunulik aret menggaarak. Yi mendek ndi mendek aa'nduk mendek Ala ake pogo mengga kwak, aakumi ando iigak, it nogo mban Ala inom, at Ndomba Aagaluk inom, inake leenak logowak nduk, inonggo mbanogo inagap ndareegerak me, Ndomba Aagaluk nogo mban inom nugu menggaarak.
66014005	It nogo pilit wone ambi abu yogolik me, maluk ambi inoba mondok lek aret iigirak~o.
66014006	Ti iige nagarik, wonage me, malayikat alik ambi mbogut oolo taati wuga agan nage logonet, "Kit aakumi kinanebunu alitak lombok inom, kinoone alitak inom, kinagabolo alitak inom, yi aakumi ndi aakumi nggween paga monggotak abok aret wone lek ageelik obeelom mondok menggerak wone yokkirage yi, konenggo logonip~o,"
66014007	ari nagaarik, "Mbogut inom, nggween inom, niyo nggwok yenggenak laut inom, niyo eneeri wundit nage menggim inom, at Ala nen mban wakkagagerak me, yogondak Ala nen kinowak loongginaburak eyom abu koorok panggo yegerak me, kinagabiti nen at Ala mban ayuk wuko logonet, at abu'me tebe yinuk, endage tiyappogo logonip~o," yinuk, oone nggwok paga agan nage kagarak.
66014008	Agan nage mbaki, ore ambi wage logonet, "O kota nggwok Mbaben ti, kwe mbabilu ya wukak pogom me, amburu kumili aganaka nenok, ugun-ugun eerit nogo mengga kwak, maluk ugun eerit nugwi, iniki nengge kenok maluk ugun eerit nugwi, eeko logonet, Nit eekwi yi, it yi aakumi ndi aakumi inanebunu lombok abok aret ndak-ndak eeko logowak~o, yinuk, mamuninako menggaarak me, inawi inom, ineebe inom, abu pup eerogo piigi~o. Pup eerogo piigi~o," yinuk, ari naruk konenggirak.
66014009	It malayikat mbere nogo wone ti, yorogo mbaka, alik ambi wage nagaarik, oone nggwok paga ari logonet, "It aakumi nen nggeewo nogo inom, at ogut wakkagak kugiwak ogobakkigirik nogo inom, inalut eeko logonet, it inapuri yelok logowak nduk, ineenggi paga ilik, inenggaawak paga a, nggeewo endage liiru mbanak wonage kenok,
66014010	anggur amburu niyo inom toolak lek, at mban toolak nonggo logonet ale ambik kogo mengga kwak, at Ala nen it aakumi ti, inabuwa mbaka'lek anini mondok alik negen inoba piige logonet, kani kunik yugum anggen inom kwippiige mbaremenggi, it Ala ake leenak menggaarak malayikat inom, at Ndomba Aagaluk inom, inigen iigak, Kani omoonuk eyak~o. Yugum yugu andi~o, yinuk, yagan yobak-nggolak wako logogun~o," yinuk, ari naruk konenggirak.
66014011	"It aakumi ineenggi paga ilik, inenggaawak paga a, nggeewo endage liiru mbanak logonet, nggeewo inom, at ogut wakkagak ogobakkigirik nogo inom, inalut eeko logomenggaarak nogo, kani kunik yugum anggen inom inoba kwippiyamenggerak ka'luk nogo nggaruk yaga'lek mondok-mondok inoba wungge kagak, liingge inom, oonikiya inom, tat yonggongga'lek mondok-mondok yagan wako logogun~o," yinuk, ari naruk konenggirak.
66014012	Ari naruk konengge mbaki, at oone yo'nege nogo nen, "It iniki Yetut oba panggombunuk, oone yugu li'lak eerit nogwe, ndi, Ala nen, Yogop ee'nu ndogop ee'nu, yereegerak wone liirogon mugurok nogwe, eeko menggaarak at apuri ake leenak nogo, andi-pandi inoba piigwi iigak kwe, inogogumbuk logonet, waganggo logowak~o," yinuk, yo'nege kagarak.
66014013	Ti yo'nege mbaki, ti'nuk, mbogut paga nen wone ambinom yo'nege kage logonet, "Yogondak nen it aap ninowe inom kunik logonet kanggwi nogo, iniki ale'nggen aret mbako logogun~o, yinuk, liiru mbanu~o," yo'nege mbaki, liiru mbangge me, Aberiniki nen, "Abet aret~o. It kanggwi iinok, ineenik logonet, ta'liila eeginake kagak yabu eerit nugu nagaarak nogo, Ala nen kobak eerogo pigin lek me, iniki ale'nggen mbako logonet, tat yonggonggologo logogun~o," yinuk, ari naruk konenggirak.
66014014	Wone ari nogo naruk konengge nagarik, wonage me, aakumi inetenggen pogom ambi nggare-nggare mendaarak mbuti emas mendek anobak paga yirik, ndi, paloowi ena yomonak ngget ambik eenggime porogo logonet, ndugwi abinak lan ari nogo paga kwi'ndak wonage nenegen kagarak.
66014015	Kage mbaki, ti'nuk, malayikat alik ambi Ala awi wurik me nen wundi wage nagaarik, oone nggwok paga at ndugwi paga kwi'ndak wonage nogo yoge logonet, "O nggween paga ogu time anggen yugu abu kole agaarak mbaniyak eyom agaarak me, kobaloowi woppunuk, mbet-mbet mbani wambu~o," yinuk,
66014016	yoge mbaki, at ndugwi paga kwi'ndak wonage nogo nen abaloowi yomonak nogo paga o nggween paga time anggen yugu abu kole agaarak nogo, abok aret mbani wangge kagarak.
66014017	Wangge mbaki, mbogut paga Ala awi wurik nogome nen malayikat alik ambi wundi wage nagaarik, at kunduk, paloowi yomonak ngget ambik eenggime wonage kagarak.
66014018	Ti'nuk, malayikat alik ambi Ala ake warogo kani kungge menggerak unde nogo kani kungge menggim nogome nen wundi wage nagaarik, at malayikat obaloowi yomonak ngget ambik aa'nduk eenggime wundi wagaarak nogo, yoge logonet, "O nggween paga ogu time anggur anggen yugu nogo, abu kole agaarak me, kobaloowi ngget ambik ti paga mbanogo yonggoli wambu~o," yinuk,
66014019	yoge mbaki, at malayikat nogo nen anggur anggen mbanikit nduk obaloowi yomonak nogo nggween paga wuppi wage nagaarik, anggur anggen nogo abok aret mbanogo punuk, kubulogo Ala anini nen aambiranuwak nduk, aambirangge menggim nogome mambege kagarak.
66014020	Mambege mbaki, anggur anggen amburu aambirangge menggim o kota yagat endekem nogome aambirangge kagak, aakumi inamiya niyo wurik negen yenggenit lagangge logonet, aloboguk ambik kuda anobak ndak-ndak age nagaarik, irip o nda tiga ratus kilometer ndak-ndak ari nage kagarak.
66015001	Ti'nuk, peebi mbogut paga time inagabiti warak mondok iya tam warak negen eeke kage logonet, malayikat ineebe 7 nen irip paga aakumi andi aganabuwak nduk, kugi alom 7 unde wonogwe iigirak. It malayikat 7 yi nen aakumi andi aganabuwak nduk, kugi 7 nogo inoba piya woramenggaarak andi aganabit nogwe iinok, Ala anini mbake nogo lek age logomenggerik, iniki yanggo yigin me, irip paga eeppiyoorak nogo unde wonogwe iigirak.
66015002	Iige nagarik, yilaa'nggun nggwok yenggenak negen kwe, etenggen pugagi pindan-pindan eeke enggela'me nen kani omoonuk wungge kagarak. Kage nagarik, wonage me, nggeewo aa'nduk lagi wagaarak nogo nen, "Kit an noone waganggwi, an nogut wakkagak ogobakkigirik nogo alut eekwi, ndi, an nendage kinenggaawak paga liiru mbanak nogo wonok nugwi, eeko logonip~o," yinuk, yoragaarak kwe, "Nit kat koone woorak mondok lek~o," yinuk, oone taganogo mbo pogo mbaka, Ala tiyappiigerak nogo nen yilaa'nggun nggwok yenggenak etenggen pugagi pogom nogo aa'nggi paga nggitat nggwok Ala nen wogoragaarak ineenggime porogo mi'ndak wonogwe iigirak. Iige nagarik, wonage me, nggitat nogo oone eekwi,
66015003	ndi, Ala ayeloman Muta endawi inom, Ndomba Aagaluk nogo endawi inom, wakwi, eeko logonet, "Komaawi lombok menggendak ninogoba Ala kat aret~o. Kat eeke menggendak nogo ti, eerubok mendek mondok iya lombok eeke menggendak~o. Yi aakumi ndi aakumi aa'nduk wonogogwaarak, yogondak wonogwe, peebi logogun abok inowe kendagembogut kat aret~o. Kat eeke menggendak nogo ti, mondok a'me nggelok abe mban eeke menggendak~o.
66015004	Ninogoba~o. It taani nen kayuk wukwi, kendage tiyappagagwi, eeka'lek logogun mbaken? Lek aret~o. Kat maluk eekeelik kalik leenak obeelom mban menggendak~o. Kat mondok a'me nggelok mban inowak loongge menggendak ineenu me, It aakumi inanebunu lombok abok aret kowagam tebe yi wogo logomenggaarik, kalut eeko logogun~o," yinuk, ndawi wakwi iigirak.
66015005	Ti wakwi iige nagarik, Ala ninom wonage mbaruwak nduk, Ala awooliya wurik mbogut paga wonage nogo, tu paarak kage nagarik,
66015006	nogome nen malayikat ineebe 7 nogo nen aakumi andi-pandi eeginaburak kugi alom 7 nogo, wonok wundi wogwe iigirak. It nogo inambogoyum yawenak abu laambu abinak kere'li-kere'lo aago yirik, ndi, inagabee'le tabak mbuti emas paga ogobakkigirik inobate paga nggerenak wonogwe iigirak.
66015007	Iige nagarik, nenegen neegak, it aakumi nen iigulik mendek ineebe 4 nogo ambi nen at Ala eenik mondok itok menggerak anini aakumi inoba piyaawak nduk, togolowak mbuti emas paga ogobakkigirik 7 nogome eno korok togon toolak it malayikat ineebe 7 nogo wogorage kagarak.
66015008	Wogorage mbaki, Ala mondok omaawi ambik me, eebe eya ndelenak-welenak eeke paga nen ka'luk wungge logonet, Ala awi wurik me mondok endak wa'nage mbaki, it malayikat ineebe 7 nogo nen andi aganaburak kugi alom 7 aakumi inoba nappiigwi nogo, worok togon nappiiga'lek iigak, aakumi nen Ala awi wurik me time ungguurak meek aret age kagarak.
66016001	Ti eeke kage nagarik, Ala awi wurik me nen oone nggwok ambi it malayikat ineebe 7 nogo yorage logonet, "Ala anini togolowak 7 paga toolak ti, wonok, aakumi nggween paga wonogwe ti, inoba kilirogo wuppiya nanip~o," yinuk, yorage konenggirak.
66016002	Yorage mbaki, at malayikat ambi nen Ala anini arologowa'na toolak nogo, wonok nggween paga kilirogo wuppege mbaki, it aakumi nggeewo endage inenggaawak paga liiru mbanak wonogwe nogo inom, at ogut wakkagak ogobakkigirik alut eekwi nogo inom, abok aret inawin maaluget inoba nik ari mbaki, aakumi nen ogole ambik yogwe iigirak.
66016003	Malayikat nen Ala anini arologowa'na toolak nogo kilirogo wuppege mbaki, ore ambi nen arologowa'na toolak nogo niyo nggwok yenggenak laut nogo paga kilirogo wuppege mbaki, niyo nogo aakumi inookaatak inamiya negen age logonet, niyo inikime nugu menggaarak nogo mendek abok aret kambit nogwe iigirak.
66016004	Malayikat mbere nogo nen Ala anini inarologowa'na toolak nogo, abu kilirogo wuppogo mbaka, ambi arologowa'na toolak nogo wonok niyo nage paga inom, eneeri wundit nage paga inom, kilirogo wuppege mbaki, niyo ti abok aret aakumi inamiya pogom age mbaki,
66016005	at malayikat niyo ti, unde menggerak nogo nen ari logonet, "Aa'nduk wonagagindak yogondak wonage kat nogoba Ala kalik leenak kitok obeelom logonet, a'me nggelok mban eeke menggendak me, It maluk eekaarak onggo kanini inoba piige yi ti, op aret eeke keegi~o.
66016006	It kapuri kake leenak inom, kat yorage keegak yoraga inom, inamiya wunogo inooreegwaarak nogo, Onggo aakumi inamiya yi, niyo negen nonggo logowak nduk, eeppiigendak me, op aret eeken~o," yinuk, yoge kagarak.
66016007	Yoge mbaki, Ala ake warogo kani kunggo menggam nogome nen oone ari logonet, "Wone ti, abet aret yigi~o. Komaawi lombok menggendak ninogoba Ala kat aret~o. Aakumi eekwi onggo mondok ndak-ndak a'me nggelok mban eeppiige menggendak me, abet aret yigi~o," yinuk, ari naruk konenggirak.
66016008	Malayikat ineebe 3 nogo nen Ala anini inarologowa'na toolak nogo kilirogo wuppogo mbaka, ambi nen arologowa'na toolak nogo oonegen paga kilirogo nappegerak. Nappege mbaki, oonegen nogo aganggen ambik age logonet, mo aganggen nen aakumi yaganinabit nage logowak nduk, omaawi eeppege kagarak.
66016009	Eeppege mbaki, aakumi yaganinabit nage kenok, it nen yogo logonet, "Andi-pandi yogobi eeppinanege me, ninomaluk mbo punuk, Ala endage tiyappogo logowok~o," yinuk, yuurak op aret kwe, kagak, inomaluk iniki kundugu patogo logonet, at andi-pandi eeppiiga unde menggerak Ala nogo endage miyuk-meya eerogo pit nogwe iigirak.
66016010	-
66016011	Ndi, it malayikat ineebe 4 nogo nen Ala anini inarologowa'na toolak nogo aakumi inoba kilirogo wuppogo mbaka, ambi nen arologowa'na nogo nggeewo negen wone lengganogo yorage menggim nogome kilirogo wuppege kagarak. Wuppege kage nagarik, nenegen neegak, nggeewo nogo wone lengganogo yorage menggim time o apit age mbaki, at abu'me logonet, oone waganggo menggaarak nogo, kugi andi aganake, inawin maaluget inoba nik ari, eeginakerak nogo, andi nen ineyak nggilik maako logonet, "Ninomaluk mbo puwi~o," yinuk, mbo puurak op aret kwe, kagak, inomaluk iniki kundugu patogo logonet, Ala endage miyuk-meya eerogo pugwi iigirak.
66016012	It malayikat ineebe 5 nogo nen Ala anini inarologowa'na togolowak inalitak lombok kilirogo wuppogo mbaka, ambi nen arologowa'na toolak nogo niyo nggwok endage Eparat paga kilirogo wuppege kagarak. Wuppege mbaki, niyo nogo porok yegerak. Niyo porok yegerak ti paga it aap inendagembogut oonegen wundi wage menggim nen woraawak nduk, inaru koonogo piige kagarak.
66016013	Kage nagarik, nenegen neegak, waalo nggwok tinambe pogom nogo ambeme inom, nggeewo anini warak niyome nen wundi wagaarak nogo ambeme inom, ndi, aap pilit wone pugunogo yorage menggerak nogo ambeme inom, time nen ogolem pogom kugi maluk lombok ineebe kenagan wundi wogwe iigirak.
66016014	It inambeme nen wundi wagaarak nogo ti, kugi Tile awuri aret me, At Omaawi Lombok Menggerak Ala mondok iya eeppiyoorak eyom nogo paga it yi aap ndi aap inendagembogut o nggween paga menggaarak abok aret at Ala nogo inom wim namburiyak kuwak eeri woraawak nduk, it ogolem pogom nogo nen yonggo nogo logonet, aakumi abet mbaruwak nduk, eerubok mendek eerit nogwe iigirak.
66016015	Ti'nuk, at oone yo'nege menggerak nogo nen, ambinom yo'nege logonet, "An aap yogoot wagangga pogom abera'lek me woraagin me, aakumi inenggaanom nggwok paga kinagap mbelanak nogwe kiinok, kinenggali ogwe kiyo, liippogo logonip~o. Kinayum abu ndigik-ndegek eerogo patinuk, kinagaket paga wonogwe me, an wage neenok, kiniki ale'nggen eekkinake kaamunggup~o," yinuk, yo'nege kagarak.
66016016	Ndi, it kugi ogolem pogom nogo nen aap nggween paga inendagembogut abok aret o endage Iberani inoone paga Aramageron nogome aret kuwak eeppiya wogwe iigirak.
66016017	Malayikat ineebe 6 nogo nen Ala anini inarologowa'na toolak nogo abu kilirogo wuppogo mbaka, ambi nen arologowa'na toolak nogo o oolo yayi kilirogo wuppege mbaki, Ala wone lengganogo yorage menggim Ala awi wurik me nen oone nggwok ambi ari logonet, "Abu age yobok togon aret eeki~o," yinuk, ari kagarak.
66016018	Ari mbaki, o yabok mondok kunik-kunik eeke, o ngguurubu ari, ndi, maan aakumi wakkagagerak kuli nen, nok, yogondak kuli paga togop eekeelik kwe, o mi mondok alik negen nuk eerit wage logonet, nggween mondok abut laganak-mbaganak eeke, eeke kagarak.
66016019	Ti eeke kage nagarik, wonage me, o kota nggwok nogo nggween mondok nggoguk ari logonet, kenaga'ndak mogonnage, ndi, yi awi ndi awi nggween paga kota-kota nogo abok aret yigirik-noonom arit nage, eeke kagak, at Ala nen, "O kota nggwok Mbaben nogo perak, at maluk eeke onggo anggur amburu toolak kwak an nanini lombok ombake minggirak toolak nogo, yogondak aret oba kilirogo wuppigi~o," yinuk, kilirogo wuppege kagarak.
66016020	Wuppege kagak, niyo nggwok yenggenak nggween oolo kup mbanak inom, puut-puut inom, abok aret eenggi-iyok lek, lek age kagak,
66016021	o mayu kumulinggen yo'nggok lombok aaninggin wakkage logonet, 40 kilo negen mbogut paga nen aakumi inoba wuppit wage mbaki, mondok iya tit kambit nogo logonet, "Ala anini nen mayu kumulinggen paga ninooke yi, nineebi a," yinuk, inanini agaket yogwi iigirak~o.
66017001	-
66017002	Ti yogwi iige nagarik, wonage me, it malayikat ineebe 7 Ala anini toolak 7 porogo wonagaarak nogo, ambi an nowagam wage nagaarik, yo'nege logonet, "O kota Mbaben niyo kunit wage menggim nogobak-kogobak paga o wurik nogo ti, kwe yawukak lombok pogom me, yi aap ndi aap inendagembogut nen maluk eeppi wogwe, ndi, yi aakumi ndi aakumi nggween paga menggaarak abok aret amburu nenok kumili-kumili negen agan nogo mengga kwak, kwe nogo pekka ungguwok nduk, nili-kili yogwe, eekwi me, at Ala nen kwe nogo maluk onggo oba kwippege kaanok nduk, omok~o," yinuk, yo'nege kagarak.
66017003	Kage nagarik, wonage me, Aberiniki ninikime lik ari mbaki, malayikat nen wo'neren karume aakumi lek me time pani nagaarak wonage me, nggeewo nggwok anini warak ambi eeruwak maa'ngga kunik, ndi, anobak 7, ndi, aruk alom me eyak 10 wonage nogo, amborowak paga kwe ambi kwi'ndak wonage kagarak. Ala miyuk-meya eerogo pogo logonet, yogo menggaarak abok aret nggeewo eebe nogo paga liiru mbanak kuurik lek aago wonage kagarak.
66017004	Ndi, kwe nogo ambogoyum maa'ngga kunik inom, maa'ngga amu kunik inom, mondok abe lombok yirik, ndi, mbuti emas inom, yugum etenggen abe inom, kundali inom, nogo paga ogobakkigirik abok aret oba li'luk eekko'nok, at maluk eerit nage menggerak inom, "Ee'nabuwak," mbarit nege menggerak inom, abok aret togolowak mbuti emas ogobakkigirik nogo paga niyo toolak kwak eenggime porogo wonage kagarak.
66017005	"O nggween paga eekulik mendek eerit nugwi, It kumi nen, "Ee'ninabi woraanip~o," yinuk, yogwe, Eeka nogo inagalo o kota nggwok Mbaben an aret~o," yinuk, enggaawak paga endage ti, liiru mbanak wonagaarak. Ndi, endage mbanak wonagaarak nogo ti, eegu laarogo negen mbanak me, aakumi liippuurak meek aret wonagaarak.
66017006	It Ala apuri ake leenak inom, Yetut eeke nagagerak wone mbo pega'lek mondok mugurok nogo menggaarak ineebe inom, kwe nogo nen inooppiinok, inamiya anggur amburu negen nenok, kumili kunggerak kage nagarik, "Wi!" mbakirak.
66017007	"Wi!" ari mbaki, at malayikat wo'neren nagaarak nogo nen, an yo'nege logonet, "Kat nonggop nduk, Wi! ari agandik? At kwe nogo inom, at nggeewo nggwok anini warak anobak 7, ndi, eyak 10 nogo amborowak paga kwe nogo kwi'na'nuk, wonok nage kagandak nogo inom, imbirak eeko menggaarak inawone kote kumaarak wonage nogo alom paganogo yokkiri~o.
66017008	Nggeewo nggwok anini warak kagandak nogo ti, aa'nduk wonagagerak kwe, lek age nagagerik, ti'nuk, Kambunuk Nogo Menggam mbuun ambena nen lagi wage kenok, Ala nen enggaawak lek eerogo pege kaamunggun~o. Ndi, mbogut-nggween wakkagagerak kuli nen it mondok-mondok ineenik aganaburak inendage mbuku paga liiru mbanulik o nggween paga awo kangga'lek ineenik wonogwe nogo nen, nggeewo nggwok aa'nduk wonagagerak kwe, lek agagerak mbareegwaarak mendek kin ari wage inigen kogo logomenggaarik, it kunduk, Wi! mbarugun~o.
66017009	Wone yokkirigin yi nogo ti, it aap iniki warak nen liippogo logowak~o, Anobak 7 nogo ti, puut 7 aret me, kwe ti paga kwi'ndak wonage kagandak. Ndi, puut 7 paga kwe kwi'ndak wonage kagandak nogo ti, aap inendagembogut ineebe 7 aret me,
66017010	ineebe 5 nogo ti, muk inendage lek ogogwaarak kwe, ambi nogo ti, awo mi'ndak wonage, ndi, ambi perak, peebi mi'narigin~o. Mi'nage logomenggerik, ne ambit logonuk, endage lek aret arigin~o.
66017011	Ndi, nggeewo nggwok anini warak aa'nduk wonagagerak kwe, lek agagerak nogo ti, it aap inendagembogut ineebe 7 nogo lek ogwe iinok, inobaane'me it nogo mendek at aret me, mi'nage mbaremenggi, Ala nen enggaawak mondok lek eerogo pigin~o.
66017012	Ndi, eyak 10 kagandak nogo ti, it aap inendagembogut ineebe 10 aret kwe, aakumi inarum logowak nduk, awo unde eeppiiga'lek me, at Tile nen aakumi inanebunu alitik-alitak nggeewo nogo inom we luulu inarum wonogwe iigak, 1 jam aruwak nduk, unde eeppiyaagin~o.
66017013	Unde eeppiige mbaremenggi, inendagembogut ineebe 10 nogo nen iniki ambit eeppunuk, nggeewo nogo yogo logonet, Kat kendage mban tiyak yuwak nduk, ninawuri ninom yeenggwaagiruwok~o, yinuk,
66017014	Ndomba Aagaluk nogo tebenogo puwok nduk, inom wim nggagambunuk namburit namenggaarak kwe, Ndomba Aagaluk nogo ti, aakumi inoweewi inowe inom, ndi, yi aap ndi aap inendagembogut inowe endagembogut inom, ti, at alik aret me, apuri miirinake nagagerik, yonggo piyareegerak inom liirogon eerit nogwe nogo, inom wunggo logonet, nggeewo awuri inom tebenogo piyaagin~o," yinuk, yo'nege kagarak.
66017015	Yo'nege nagaarik, ambinom yo'nege logonet, "Yi niyo ndi niyo kunit wage menggim nogobak-kogobak paga kwe yawukak kwi'ndak wonage kagandak nogo ti, yi aakumi ndi aakumi inanebunu lombok inom, aakumi ugun inom, inagabolo alitak inom, inoone alitak inom, ineebe ti aret iigendak~o.
66017016	-
66017017	At Ala nen yereegerak nogo a'me nggelok yuwak nduk, aap inendagembogut ineebe 10 nogo, iniki ambit eeppunuk, awuri inom nen nggeewo nogo yeenggwaago logonet, Ala kooneegerak nogo mban eerit nogo logowak nduk, inikime mambiyareegerak me, it aap inendagembogut ineebe 10 nogo nggeewo inom nen, Kwe yawukak yi, abu nineebi~o, yinuk, amindik-amendek li'luk eerak nogo nggoorogo mbo pogo logonet, we agap mbelanak kagak warogo punuk, enggaanggum ando nunggwi, ndi, ando kani kumbugwi, eeruwi~o, yinuk, yugun~o.
66017018	Ndi, kwe kagandak nogo ti, o kota nggwok nogo pogom aret me, yi aap ndi aap inendagembogut nggween paga menggaarak nogo abok aret at kwe yawukak nogo abu'me logonet, oone konenggo agaarik~o," yinuk, yo'nege kagarak.
66018001	Ti yo'nege mbaki, malayikat alik ambi oone mondok omaawi paga yorage logowak nduk unde eeppegerak nogo, at abinak ndelenak-welenak aago nggween paga eya eerit wambi wage kagarak.
66018002	-
66018003	Wambi wage nagaarik, oone mondok omaawi paga ari logonet, "O kota nggwok Mbaben nogo, mondok lek eerogo pigi~o. Lek eerogo pigi~o. It o kota Mbaben menggaarak nogo ti, kwe yawukak pogom me, Kwe nogo nen iniki nengge kenok, Ee'nabi woraanip~o, ari kenok, Yi aap ndi aap inanebunu lombok abok aret, anggur amburu nenok, kumili-kumili agan nugu mengga kwak, ugun-ugun kwe nogo eeppi wogwe, Yi aap ndi aap inoweewi inendagembogut o nggween paga menggaarak abok aret kwe nogo eeri unggwogwe, Ndi, kwe nogo nen aap iniki nengge kenok, eeppi unggwagak eekwi paga It aakumi yi awi ndi awi kunggo menggam unde menggaarak nogo, ineenggi warak eekkologwe, eekwi iinok, O Mbaben nogo pup eerogo pegerak me, Yogondak yi kugi ndi kugi inom, it kambeegwaarak inogoma inom, yi towe ndi towe nen aakumi kanggaatak nunggwi iinok inogole yogo menggaarak inom, Abok aret inawi eekkola unggwa-ga~o," yinuk, oone nggwok paga ari naruk konenggirak.
66018004	-
66018005	Konengge nagarik, wonage me, mbogut paga nen oone alik ambi ari logonet, "Kit an napuri yi wae. It o kota Mbaben maluk eekwi nogo obaga lu'luk arit mbogut ndak-ndak ari lagangge kenok, At Ala mondok aberak wonage me, kinom maluk eerit nogwe kiinok, It maluk onggo inoba piige logonet, kinom kinoba pinagage kero, o time mbo punuk, kole mbaganggo logonip~o.
66018006	O Mbaben nen kit aakumi eeppinagage nagagerak nogo, yogondak kit nen at onggo ndak-ndak eeppugwi, Ndi, o Mbaben nen kit maluk eerit nogo nogogutak onggo ne ambit paga maluk kinoba pinagareegerak kwe, Yogondak kit nen at maluk eeke onggo ne mbere paga at oba pugwi, Ndi, at kinom ogoorak wonage logonet, anini yi toolak kwak ne ambit kinoba kilirogo pinagareegerak kwe, Yogondak onggo kit kinanini at oba pogo logonet, ne mbere paga kilirogo pugwi, Eeko logonip~o.
66018007	At Mbaben nogo ti, kwe yawukak nogo pogom me, iniki mbake logonet, An kwe togwe wonage nen niniki wakkolage logonet, le yikit lak kwe, aap pe'neya wogo menggaarak ineebe ambik wonogwe me, An kwe nggwok aret kagi, mba'nuk, niniki ale'nggen ambik mbake agarik~o, yinuk, Iniki wogoppake logonet, endage tiyanak paalo aago mban wonage nogo obaane'me ale'nggen lek age logomenggerik, Iniki puru ari, andi yagan yobak-nggolak wake, eeke logowak nduk, aaninggin mondok oba kwippogo logonip~o.
66018008	At eerit nage menggerak awone amburu mbanogo owak loonigin ninogoba Ala nogo ti, omaawi ambik me, At wogoppatit nege onggo ne ambit liingge aaninggin oba age logonet, mbi abu age, andi nen aagalogwe kambit nogwe iinok, iniki wakkolage, eeke logonet, Le ari kagak, eebe waganogo kani kumbugun~o," yinuk, yo'nege kagarak.
66018009	-
66018010	Kage nagarik, wonage me, "It aap inendagembogut yi awi ndi awi o nggween paga menggaarak nen kwe nogo pekka wogo nagaatik, inom aberogon logonet, eeppegak mban eeko nogogwaarak nogo nen, kwe nogo kani andi nen kwa ari inaruk konembunuk, Nit togon togop ee'ninake kero, ninagabiti~o, yinuk, tayorogon taati mi'ndak logonet, Kat o kota nggwok abe menggendak Mbaben yi, kabuwa~o. Nomaawi ambik neenggi warak me, obeelom mban logokit, mbake keegak, ne ambiriluk 1 jam teppaganuk, wonagaarak kwe, maluk eeke nagandak onggo aaninggin mondok koba kwi'nagaarak me, kabuwa~o, yinuk, o kota kwe yawukak nogo pogom aret me, kani nengge ka'luk inigen nakkogo logomenggaarik, iniki wakkologo logonet, aleenggu maako logogun~o," yinuk, yo'nege kagarak.
66018011	Yo'nege nagaarik, ambi yo'nege logonet, "It aap yi awi ndi awi o nggween paga kunggo menggam unde menggaarak nogo kunduk, o kota Mbaben kwe yawukak pogom kani kumbugwi inigen kogo logomenggaarik, iniki wakkologo logonet,
66018012	Ninamendek mbuti emas inom, mbuti perak inom, yugum yeebibit inom, kundali inom, yum abe yawenak lombok inom, yum maa'ngga amu kunik inom, yum laambu maa'ngga anggup kunik inom, yum abe mili-mili lombok inom, eyo obari abe ogobakkigirik inom, meeli-kono inom, yi mendek ndi mendek eyo abe paga ogobakkigirik inom, mbuti tembaga etenggen yaliingga yi'nip kunik nogo paga ogobakkigirik inom, mbuti abe mbuti nogo paga ogobakkigirik inom, yugum moolingget paga ogobakkigirik inom,
66018013	liboongga inom, kiinde inom, obari abe kaga inom, inagabolo abe kaawak nduk, eyo mur amburu mbenanggwi inom, eyo yibinggami amburu nogo inom, anggur amburu inom, tayitun amburu inom, gandum anggen abe yigirik inom, gandum anggen mbanak inom, tapi-ndomba inom, kuda inom, kuda nikkenok nega nggweendo inom, aakumi ayeloman logowak nduk ineebe kunggologwe inom, aakumi inogut inom, yi mendek ndi mendek anebunu pereegerak abok aret, nit kunggo monggom wonage kwe, ninamendek yi, taani nen kunggola wogo logogun~o? yinuk, Ai-ao, yugun~o.
66018014	Yogo logonet, Kwe kat yi, yi mendek ndi mendek abe kigirikwe kenok mban, Name logowak lak ao, mbake nagandak kwe, yogondak kamendek lek agaarak me, peebi ambi kenegen kage logomunggun abu lek~o.
66018015	-
66018017	O kota nggwok abe menggendak kat Mbaben yi, kabuwa~o. Kambogoyum abe yawenak etenggen maa'ngga amu kunik inom, maa'ngga anggup kunik inom, yirik logonet, mbuti emas inom, yugum yeebibit inom, kundali inom, nogo paga kobaanggi-kobaangge li'luk eekko'nok keegi-wogi aago nege keenok, aakumi nen, O kota nggwok abe aret me, abok eenggi warak aret~o, yinuk, yogo menggaarak kwe, ne ambit 1 jam paga aret lek agaarak me, kabuwa~o," yinuk, it yi mendek ndi mendek kunggo menggaarak nogo kunggo logonet, ineenggi warak eekkologo nogogwaarak nogo, kwe andi nen kwa ari inaruk konembunuk, "Nit togon togop ee'ninake kero, ninagabiti~o," yinuk, tayorogon taati ale yogwe, aleenggu maakwi, eekwi iigirak~o. Ndi, it yiiro nggwok wonok nega inom, it abok yiiro inikime yonggolak nugu menggaarak inom, nogo logonet yiiro ndegenggo menggaarak inom, ndi, yiiro paga kunggo'net nugu menggaarak inom, abok aret tayorogon taati logonet,
66018018	kwe yawukak pogom o kota Mbaben nogo kani nengge ka'luk lagangge inigen nakkogo logomenggaarik, "Kota nggwok abe yogobi ambi wonage lek me, yi eekerak ao," yinuk,
66018019	wun inanobak paga yumbunogo wuppako logonet, "O kota nggwok abe menggendak yi, kabuwa~o. Aakumi inanebunu lombok abok aret inamindik-inamendek yi awi ndi awi nen yiiro paga wonok wogwe iinok, Kunggologo logonet, ineenggi warak eeppiige nagandak kwe, Ne ambit 1 jam paga aret lek agandak me, kabuwa~o," yinuk, ale yogwe, aleenggu maakwi, eekwi iigirak.
66018020	Eekwi iigak, at oone yo'nege nogo ambinom yo'nege logonet, "Kat mbogut yi, wae. Kale'nggen mbake, Kit Ala apuri ake leenak inom, obeelom wone yoranet nugu nogogutak nappiigak inom, Ala nen yokkirage kagak yoraga inom, Kit abok aret kwe yawukak nogo pogom o Mbaben yi nen eeppinagage nagagerak nogo onggo Ala nen aret eeppege me, kiniki ale'nggen mbakwi, Eeko logonip~o," yinuk, ari naruk konenggirak.
66018021	Konengge nagarik, nenegen neegak, malayikat alilaakwi ambi wage nagaarik, yugum nggwok gandum yigika nogo pogom waganogo niyo nggwok yenggenak me mbo wuppege logonet, "Nanini paga yugum mbo wuppigirak yi kwak, o Mbaben togop aret yigirik-noonom eerogo pege neenok, o ngga wurik wonagaarak negen kobak aret arigin~o.
66018022	-
66018024	Kit o Mbaben monggotak yi, It aakumi inanebunu lombok abok aret iya kinombaruwak nduk, tili paganit nogo logonet, nomoniren nogwe, Ndi it Ala apuri alik leenak inom, Ala nen yorage kagak yoraga inom, nogo inamiya nunggwi, Yi aakumi ndi aakumi nggween paga menggaarak abok aret inoorogo piinok, inamiya nunggwi, Eekwi nogo, Ala nen kiyareegerak me, Mbuti luu'ngget inom, nggawiiwak luu'ngget inom, nggitat inom, oone nggwok eeka trompet inom, O kota time nen oone eerit nogwe konenggo nogotak nogo ambinom konenggwi, Yi aap ndi aap nen yi mendek ndi mendek ineenggi paalo eerogo patit nugwi, Gandum yigiko logonet, inale'nggen paga inoone agan nugwi, Kwe amili lako logonet, inale'nggen nen noone-koone yogwe, Eerit nogo logonet, inoone konenggwi, Eekwi nogo abok aret ambinom eerit nogo logogun mondok lek~o. Ndi, o kota nggwok me, ndi ambik wunuk agan nage nagaarak nogo yogondak ambiriluk ambi wunuk agan nage kogo logogun mondok lek~o," yinuk, ari naruk konenggirak.
66019001	Ti konengge nagarik, wonage me, o mbogut paga time aakumi ambik abu alik negen komaarak inoone nggwok ambugwi yogo mengga kwak yogo logonet, "Kat kalik komaawi ambik ninagap ndaka kendage mondok tiyanak, ninogoba Ala wa.
66019002	Kwe yawukak mondok iya eerit nage nogo nen, Ee'nabi woraanip~o, ari kenok, Yi aap ndi aap abok aret eeppi unggwagak eekwi paga o nggween paga time maluk eerogo pege nagagerak nogo onggo kwe nogo oba kwippege, Ndi, kwe nogo nen kat kayeloman mini inooreegerak inane'me wake, Eekendak me, Kat kalik mondok obeelom irip-kunduk eerogo aakumi liirogon inowak loongge logonet, Kwe nogo owak loonogo maluk onggo eeppegendak me, Wa!" yinuk,
66019003	yogo nagaarik, ambi yogo logonet, "O kota nggwok kwe yawukak pogom nogo, Kani nengge logonet, ka'luk mondok-mondok yarugu-paru-gu lagangge logogin~o," yinuk, Ne ambi paga, "Wa," yinuk, yogo mbaka,
66019004	it mbogut paga wonogwe inoweewi ineebe 24 inom, aakumi nen iigulik mendek ineebe 4 nogo inom, at wone lengganogo yorage menggim Ala time kwi'ndak wonage kagak abu'me tebe yinuk, alut eeko logonet, "Ninogoba wa, wa," yinuk, "Amin," yogwi naruk konenggirak.
66019005	Yogwi naruk konengge nagarik, wonage me, wone lengganogo yorage menggim nen oone ambi ari logonet, "Kit Ala ayeloman mini nen at ayuk wuko monggotak kinendage warak inom, kinendage lek inom, abok aret ninogoba Ala mban alut eeko logonip~o," yinuk, ari mbaki,
66019006	niyoraakut nggwok oonebu ari, o ngguurubu alik negen ari, it yi aakumi ndi aakumi ambik kuwak eerak ambugwi inoone nggwok yogwe, eeko mengga kwak, yogo logonet, "At Omaawi Lombok Menggerak ninogoba Ala nogo, Yi aap ndi aap inowe endagembogut logokit nduk, mi'nagagerak wonage me, Ninogoba Wa, yinuk, alut eeruwok~o.
66019007	At Ndomba Aagaluk nogo akwe lambumbuurak eyom age mbaki, akwe nogo amindik-amendek li'luk eekko'nok wage me, Ninale'nggen nen ndawi lubuk wako logonet, endage tiyappogo logowok~o," yinuk,
66019008	inoone yogwe iigak, akwe nogo wage mbaki, ayum ambi abu yawenak kikak naka'lek abe laambu yanggwi negen lan aago yikkolawak nduk, wogoge kagarak. Ndi, ayum abe yawenak nogo ti, it Ala apuri ake leenak nen maluk eeka'lek obeelom mban eerit nugwi nogo kwak aret kagarak.
66019009	Kage mbaki, malayikat nogo nen an yo'nege logonet, "Ndomba Aagaluk akwe lambumbogo logonet, abugo larak inom nawak nduk, yonggo piyareegerak nogo, iniki ale'nggen mbako logowak~o," yinuk, yo'nege nagaarik, ambinom yo'nege logonet, "Wone ti, Ala nen abet aret yegerak me, liiru mbanu~o," yinuk, yo'negerak.
66019010	Yo'nege mbaki, abu'me tebe yinuk, alut eerikit nduk eeke me, at nen yo'nege logonet, "Togop eeriyak mage~o.
