At Yetut wage nagagerik, Ala ndogop menggerak~o, yinuk, paganogo yoragagerak wone koreewi waganggo nogogwaarik, porogo wonogwe nogo inom, kat inom, an kit pogom Ala ayeloman aret me, Ala abu'me tebe yinuk, at mban alut eeke logot~o. At Yetut nen paganogo yorage nagagerak wone nogo ti, nit abok Aberiniki nen yo'nirage kagak yorogo monggoorak me nduk, yokkigi~o," yinuk, yo'nege kagarak.
66019011	Yo'nege kage nagarik, mbogut paga tungga paarak wonage kagak, aap ambi endage Abet Mban Ari, Liirogon Eeke, Eeka nogo, kuda yanggwi negen amborowak paga kwi'ndak wage kagarak. Wage nagaarik, liirogon inowak loonogo a'me nggelok mban onggo wogorage, wim liirogon aret nambuke, eerit nage kagarak.
66019012	At enegen ti, kani omoonuk wunuk ari pogom. At anobak paga nggare-nggare mendaarak apit yirik, ndi, at endage toonak eebe paga liiru mbanak wonage nogo, aakumi nen maleniyak meek at mban eenu wonagaarak kwe,
66019013	"At endage ti, Ala Wone aret~o," yinuk, an yo'nege kagarak. At ambogoyum nggorek paga aakumi inamiya labunik yikko'nok nage kagak,
66019014	it yigin unde mbogut paga wonogwe nogo abok aret inayum abe yawenak kikak naka'lek abu laambu yanggwi negen yirik logonet, inalitik-inalitak kuda ineeruwak yanggwi negen inamborowak paga kwi'na'nuk, inom nogwe iigirak.
66019015	Inom nogo logonet, at yi aakumi ndi aakumi inanebunu lombok abok aret tebenogo piyoorak nduk, paloowi ngget ambik ambeme nggelenak wonok nage logonet, tebenogo piinok, mbim obate mbanak ineenggime logonet, inoone omaawi paga yorogo mengga kwak, at oone omaawi paga wone lengganogo yorage kagarak. At omaawi lombok menggerak Ala anini nen aakumi eeppiyoorak nogo ti, anggur amburu aambiranggo mengga kwak aret me, at nogo nen aakumi togop aret aambiranogo piinet nage kagarak.
66019016	Ndi, at endage nogo ti, Aap Inendagembogut Inowe Endagembogut inom, Aakumi Inoweewi Inowe inom, nogo ti aret me, ambogoyum paga inom, ambulok paga inom, at endage ti, liiru mbanak wonage kagarak.
66019017	-
66019018	Kage nagarik, at malayikat ambi oonegen paga mi'ndak logonet, yi towe ndi towe o oolo yime wuga agan nugu menggaarak nogo yorage logonet, "It aap inendagembogut inom, aap wim eeka inoweewi inom, aap waka'ngget inom, kuda inom, it kuda amborowak paga kwi'na'nuk wim namburi nogo menggaarak inom, aap inendage warak inendage lek inom, aakumi inayeloman mini inom, aakumi weelek mendek inom, yi aakumi ndi aakumi abok aret Ala nen inoorogo punuk, kinake pipuk eerogo pegerak me, Inenggaanggum namunggup nduk, kuwak eeri wogo logonip~o," yinuk, yorage kagarak~o.
66019019	Yorage mbaki, nggeewo anini warak nogo inom, aakumi inoweewi inendagembogut inom, inawuri yigin unde inom, nen at kuda amborowak paga kwi'ndak wonage nogo awuri inom wim namburuwok nduk, kuwak eeppunuk, inom perenggolaawok nduk eekwi iigirak.
66019020	Ti eekwi iigak kwe, at nggeewo anini warak aa'nduk lagi wagaarak eebe nogo inom, ndi, it aakumi inenggaawak paga nggeewo aa'nduk lagi wagaarak endage liiru mbanak wonok nugwi, at ogut eerak nogo alut eekwi, eeruwak nduk, awone kilirik paga inagabiti warak mendek eerit nage logonet, inambokan lagangge menggerak nggeewo peebi lagi wagaarak eebe nogo inom, imbirak ineenik ngge-ngge pigogo kani omoonuk wunuk mban ari menggim nogome nappiige kagarak.
66019021	Nappiige kage nagarik, at kuda amborowak paga kwi'ndak paloowi ambeme nggelenak nogo paga inawuri ando nogo inoorogo piinet nage mbaki, yi towe ndi towe abok wogo nagaarik, aakumi inoorak nogo inenggaanggum inaanoma'le nggaruk yogorak nonggo nagaarik, kumunuk ndan agan nogwe iigirak.
66020001	Ti'nuk, malayikat ambi Kambunuk Nogo Menggam mbuun ambena tu paariyak nduk, kunci inom, mbutigeele nggwok inom, eenggime wonok, mbogut paga nen wambi wage kagarak.
66020002	Wambi wage nagaarik, at waalo nggwok tinambe negen o maan togon aakumi inambokan lagangge menggerak Tile ti, Ibilit aret me, at pigogo mbutigeele nogo paga maappunuk, tahun seribu logowak nduk,
66020003	mbuun ambena wuppege logonet, "O peebi ne ambiriluk piinogo teppagarak kwe, yogondak aakumi inambokan lagangga'lek tahun seribu paga keele maarak yime aret logot~o," yinuk, mbo wuppunuk, tu kunci narogo pege kagarak.
66020004	Pege mbaki, wone lengganogo yorogo menggam eyo ndoonogo pit nagaarak nogo kage nagarik, it ti paga kwi'ndak wonogwe nogo aakumi inowak loonggo logowak nduk, unde eeppiige kagarak. Ti kage nagarik, it Ala wone mugurok nogo logonet, Yetut wone paganogo yoragagerak nogo abet mba'nuk, yoranet nogwe iigak, inenggaanok mbanogo piyareegwaarak inogoma nogo iigirak. It ti nen, "At nggeewo aa'nduk lagi wagaarak eebe inom, ogut ogobakkigirik nogo inom, nit alut eerugun lek~o. Ndi, nggeewo endage nogo ti, nit ninenggaawak paga inom, nineenggi paga inom, ti kunduk, liiru mbanogo puurak lek mban~o," yinuk, yogwi iinok, inenggaanok mbanogo piyareegwaarak inogoma nogo ineenik a'nuk Keritut inom tiyanak logonet, wone lengganogo yorogwe iigak, tahun seribu aret age kagarak.
66020005	Aa'nduk ineenik agago mippiyoorak nogo it aret~o. Ndi, it ando kambeegwaarak nogo perak, tahun seribu eeppunuk, ineenik agago mippiyoorak nduk wonogwe iigirak.
66020006	It inaa'nduk ineenik agago mippiyamenggerak nogo, maluk eeka'lek Ala ake leenak logonet, iniki ale'nggen nggwok aret logogun~o. It aa'nduk muk kambeegwaarak me, peebi kambugun lek~o. It ti, Ala unde a'nuk, Keritut Ala imbirak inake eerit nugwi, ndi, Keritut inom tiyanak logonet, wone lengganogo yorogwe, eekwi iigak, tahun seribu aret age kagarak.
66020007	-
66020008	Ti kage nagarik, tahun seribu eeppunuk, yi aakumi ndi aakumi inanebunu lombok o Magok inom, o Nggok inom, irip-irip time abok aret kuwak eeppunuk, wim eeriyak inikime nggaganogo mambiinet nege logowak nduk, Tile keele maarak mbuun ambena wonage nogo piinogo nippi wage kagarak. Piinogo nippi wage mbaki, aakumi inikime nggaganogo manabit nage kenok, aakumi mbini-kale'ngga pogom togop aret kuwak eekwi iigirak.
66020009	Iige nagarik, o kobak nonggologo pereegim time aakumi mbini negen togop aret kuwak eeppunuk, it abet mbareegwaarak Ala apuri nogo inookwi, ndi, o kota Ala inikilom mbake menggim nogo lek eerogo pugwi, eeruwok nduk, oo'nggut panggeko mbaka, kani mbogut paga nen wunuk agan wambi wage logonet, aakumi nogo tigitogon nenet nage kagarak.
66020010	Ndi, at aakumi inambokan lagangga Tile nogo, pigogo kani omoonuk wunuk mban ari menggim at nggeewo anini warak aa'nduk lagi wagaarak inom, at ore peebi lagi wagaarak pilit wone agan nege nagaarak nogo inom, imbirak wonogwe me nogome mbo nappege mbaki, liingge-kiyoma kani eyak andi nen mondok-mondok yagan yobak-nggolak wakwi iigirak.
66020011	Ti eekwi iige nagarik, wone lengganogo yorage menggim eyo nggwok ndoonak yanggwi lombok lan ari nogo paga aap ambi kwi'nage kagarak. Awo kwi'nage kagak, mbogut-nggween eenggi-iyok lek, lek age mbaki, ti'nuk, peebi obaane'me ari wage koolik mondok-mondok lek aret age kagarak.
66020012	-
66020013	Lek age mbaki, it aap inendage lek inendage warak kambeegwaarak inom, it niyo nen ndonggoninabeegerak niyo yenggenak laut inikime wonogwe inom, kambit nogogwaarak kambunuk nogo menggam wonogwe nogo inom, abok aret, wone lengganogo yorage menggim eyo nggwok ogobakkigirik yanggwi lombok lan ari nogo paga aap ambi kwi'ndak wonage nogo, owagam mi'nari wogo mbaka, at eyo ndoonak paga kwi'ndak wonage nogo nen it inalitik-inalitak eeko nogogwaarak inom, aakumi mondok-mondok ineenik aganaburak inendage inom, mbuku alitak paga mbanak wonage me, imbirak waganogo piingge nagaarik, it kangga'lek ineenik logonet eeko nogogwaarak liiru mbanak nogo pekkagak inowak loonogo onggo ndak-ndak eeppiige kagarak.
66020014	-
66020015	Ti eeke kage nagarik, it ando ineenik aganaburak mbuku nogo paga inendage mbanak lek kenok, kani omoonu'me nappiige logonet, kanggo menggaarak alom inom, kambunuk nogo menggam inom, abok aret waganogo kani omoonuk wunuk mban ari menggim nogome mbo nappiige kagarak~o. "Ne mbere kambuurak~o," yinuk, liiru mbanak nogo ti, ambi, we ineenik logonuk, laalu kanggwi, ndi, ambi, kani omoonu'me mondok-mondok nappiige, eeriyak ti nduk aret liiru mbanak~o.
66021001	Ti eeke kage nagarik, won-age me, mbogut-nggween aa'nduk wakkagagerak nogo inom, yi nggwok yenggenak laut nogo inom, lek age kagak, obaane'me mbogut-nggween ngget ogobakkigirik nogo ari wage kagarak.
66021002	Kage nagarik, kwe ambi ogonggelo kolaakit nduk, amindik-amendek li'luk eekko'nok wage menggi kwak, o kota abu alik leenak Yerutalem ngget ogobakkigirik nogo, Ala wonage me mbogut paga nen wambi wage kagarak.
66021003	Wambi wage mbaki, wone lengganogo yorage menggim time nen oone nggwok ambi ari logonet, "Ala at apuri inenggela'me logowam nogome logokit nduk, eebe wambi wage ti, kaanip~o. At eebe nogo apuri inom logonet, it nen, Kat ninogoba Ala aret~o, yinuk, yogwi, ndi, at nen, Kit an napuri aret~o, yinuk, yorage, eeko logogun~o.
66021004	Mbogut-nggween aa'nduk ogobakkigirik nogo paga logonet, iniki aaninggin kogo nogogwaarak nogo, lek agaarak me, ngget ogobakkigirik nogo paga inogoba Ala inom logonet, inale amburu mbanogo piyamenggerak me, kanggwi, tabun ndoombunuk le yogwe, iniki wakkologwe, andi kogwe, eeko logogun abu lek~o," yinuk, ari naruk konenggirak.
66021005	Ari naruk konembunuk, wonage me, at wone lengganogo yorage menggim eyo ndoonak paga kwi'ndak wonage nogo nen an yo'nege logonet, "Wone yi, liirogon karuk konengge logot~o. An nen yi mendek ndi mendek abok aret ngget ogobakkigirogo pege yi, abet aret a'me nggelok yigin me, liiru mbanu~o."
66021006	Yo'nege nagaarik, ambinom yo'nege logonet, "O maan aa'nduk togon wonagagirak alom Alpa inom, ndi, irip paga mondok logorak Omega inom, ti an aret me, yokkigirak nogo ti, muk eeke me nduk yokkigi~o. It aakumi niyo abu eeginake kenok, an nen niyo ineenik aganake menggerak eneeri wungge me nen onggo lek we aret toologo wogorage logogin~o.
66021007	It an noone mbo pega'lek inogogumbuk logonet, liirogon mugurok nogwe iinok, ineyate wogorogo mengga kwak, eeginaburak wone karuk konenggendak nogo eeginake logominggirik, an inogoba Ala aret age, ndi, it an napuri aret ogwe, eeko logogun kwe,
66021008	it Ala wone mugurok noorak inagabiti mbaka inom, abet mbariyak ineebi mbaka inom, maluk peyak wurik kagak ugun eerit nega inom, aakumi inooka inom, kumi ugun wurinaka inom, magagirak iyagalo inom, kugiwak amili kungga inom, pilit pugungga inom, it abok aret it logowam pipuk eerogo pereegim kani omoonuk wunuk mban ari menggim nogome mbo nappiyaagin~o. Aa'nduk ineenik logonuk, kambemenggaarak kwe, kani omoonu'me nappiyoorak nogo ti, peebi ne ambi kanggwi nogo kokwak aret~o," yinuk, yo'nege kagarak.
66021009	Yo'nege mbaki, malayikat ineebe 7 nogo nen aakumi andi aganaburak kugi alom 7 togolowa'na toolak porogo wonagaarak nogo, ambi nen nowagam wage nagaarik, yo'nege logonet, "Ndomba Aagaluk akwe kolegerak kolaga nogo, kenegen kaanok nduk, mok~o."
66021010	Yo'nege nagaarik, Aberiniki ninikime lik ari mbaki, neebe wo'neren puut nggwok tiyarogon nogo paga pani lagangge nagaarik, o kota abu alik leenak Yerutalem ngget ogobakkigirik Ala wonage me mbogut paga nen wambi wage, "Ti ket~o," yinuk, yo'negerak.
66021011	Yo'nege mbaki, yugum onggo nggwok pugagi pogom endage yatipit nogo mendek pindan-pindan eeke menggi kwak, o kota ngget ogobakkigirik pindan-pindan eeke ti, Ala tiyanak logonet, eya ndelenak-welenak aago menggerak nogo nen aret eeke kagarak.
66021012	Ndi, o wa'nagat wurik ti, mondok iya tiyarogon wurik me, tu pak mbanak 12, ndi, tu pak mbanak unde nogo ti, it malayikat ineebe 12 mban wonogwe iigirak. Ndi, tungga eebe paga aakumi Iterali inanebunu 12 nogo inendage liiru mbanak wonage kagarak.
66021013	O wa'nagat wurik oonegen lagi wage menggim pa'nggwe tu pak kenagan mbanak, ndi, oonegen kilu yi nage menggim pa'nggwe tu pak kenagan mbanak, ndi, o ame kwi'nari nage menggim pa'nggwe tu pak kenagan mbanak, ndi, o omarip paga kwi'nari wambi wage menggim pa'nggwe nogo ti, tu pak kenagan mbanak mban wonage kagarak.
66021014	O wa'nagat wurik ogowa pugu yugum 12 wonage nogo paga at Ndomba Aagaluk awuri nappiigak mendek ineebe 12 inendage mbanak wonage kagarak.
66021015	Ndi, at wone yo'negerak nogo nen o kota inom, tu pak mbanak nogo inom, o wa'nagat wurik inom, wakkaakit nduk, wakkagak mbuti emas paga ogobakkigirik eenggime wonage kagarak.
66021016	Nenegen neegak, at nogo nen o kota nogo wakkagak nogo paga wakkage logonet, irip agi-ogu inom, aru-ogwe inom, o eyak kirin nippugu inom, ti dua ribu dua ratus kilometer negen wakkagak wurik kagarak.
66021017	At malayikat nogo nen o kota wurik wakkage nagaarik, ti'nuk, o wa'nagat eebe wurik ambe mban wakkage mbaki, at wakkagak nogo paga wakkagagerak nogo ti, nit aakumi wakkogo monggo kwak meter 65 paga wakkagak wurik aret kagarak.
66021018	O wa'nagat nogo ti, yugum yatipit nogo paga wurik, ndi, o kota nogo ti, mbuti emas at mendek paga mban pugagi abu kin lombok pogom nogo paga wurik kagarak.
66021019	O kota nogo, yi yugum ndi yugum abe kigirikwe kenok mban obaga lu'luk eerak ogowa pugu kagarak. Yugum tabak woneemaluk abena ndoonak ti, yugum yatipit. Ndi, yugum yatipit obaga pugu nogo ti, yugum nilan, ndi, yugum nilan obaga pugu nogo ti, yugum mira, ndi, yugum mira obaga pugu nogo ti, yugum tamurut,
66021020	ndi, yugum tamurut obaga pugu nogo ti, yugum unam, ndi, yugum unam obaga pugu nogo ti, yugum taririt, ndi, yugum taririt obaga pugu nogo ti, yugum era'na tembaka, ndi, yugum era'na tembaka obaga pugu nogo ti, yugum mberin, ndi, yugum mberin obaga pugu nogo ti, yugum kiritolit, ndi, yugum kiritolit obaga pugu nogo ti, yugum kiritoparat, ndi, yugum kiritoparat obaga pugu nogo ti, yugum latuwariri, ndi, yugum latuwariri obaga pugu irip paga nogo ti, yugum ketubun, yugum etenggen abe kigirikwe paga mban ta'mban-mban aago wurik kagarak.
66021021	Tungga eebe 12 nogo ti, yugum kundali negen ambit tabak paga mban alitik-alitak ogobakkigirik kagarak. Ndi, o kota oolo tu yarak ti, mbuti emas at mendek mban pugagi abu kin lombok pogom ndoonak kagarak kwe,
66021022	at Omaawi Lombok Menggerak ninogoba Ala inom, at Ndomba Aagaluk inom, Ala awi wurik negen ineebe inenggela'me inom aret wonogwe me, it aakumi Ala ninom wonage mbaruwak nduk, awi wurik nogo lek aret kagarak.
66021023	At Ala abu tiyanak eebe eya ndelenak-welenak eeke nogo paga o kota ti, eya eeke, ndi, ndi wuninik pogom ti, Ndomba Aagaluk nen aret eya eeke, eekwi me, it aakumi nen, "Oonegen inom, tut inom, eya aruwak lak ao," yinuk, yaga'lek aret iigirak.
66021024	Yi aakumi ndi aakumi inanebunu lombok abok aret o eya ti paga nugwi, ndi, yi aap ndi aap inendagembogut nggween paga menggaarak abok aret o eya ti paga logowok nduk, inamindik-inamendek mbelenggo'nok unggwi nogwe, eekwi iigirak~o.
66021025	O kota time o kiip age, o weege, eeka'lek mondok-mondok liingge mban wonage me, tu mondok-mondok paarak aret wonage kagarak.
66021026	Yi aakumi ndi aakumi inanebunu lombok abok aret inendage abu obeelom tiyanak logonet, inamindik-inamendek mbelenggo'nok, o kota time logowok nduk, unggwi nogwe iigirak.
66021027	Ndi, it maluk inikime porogo wonogwe, maluk peyak wurik kagak ugun eerit nugwi, pilit pugunggwi, eeko menggaarak nogo kenok perak, unggwi nogwe iyoolik~o. Ata, it aakumi ineenik mondok-mondok aganaburak inendage mbuku paga liiru mbanak Ndomba Aagaluk porogo wonage kenok mban unggwi nogwe iigirak~o.
66022001	-
66022002	Ti kage nagarik wonage me, malayikat nogo nen, an yo'nege logonet, "Niyo aakumi ineenik aganaka eneeri mili lombok mbini kin nogo, Ndomba Aagaluk Ala imbirak wone lengganogo yorogo menggam abu'me nen, kilak togon wungge nagaarik, o kota tu yarak eraaninu nage ti, kenegen pekket~o," yinuk, yo'nege mbaki, pekkage me, niyo nggwok nage nogo aa'nggi yibagan-enebagan eyo aakumi ineenik aganake menggerak awi yarak me, tut ambi penengge paga ne ambit paga anggen yi'nage, tut ambi penengge paga ne ambit paga anggen yi'nage, togop aret eerit tahun ambit eerak paga ne 12 paga aret anggen yi'nage kagarak. Ndi, eyoongga nogo ti, yi aakumi ndi aakumi andi aganake kero, obeelom aganaka inake aret wonage kagarak.
66022003	Yi mendek ndi mendek pulunogo pereegerak maluk wonage nogo tigitogon obeelom eerogo pegerak me, o nogo ti, obeelom mban aret wonage kagarak. Ndi, at Ala inom, Ndomba Aagaluk inom, imbirak it wone lengganogo yorogo menggam eyo ndoonak o oolo taati wonage kagak, at Ala ayeloman mini abok aret at owagam ninggippunuk logonet, at mban alut eekwi iigirak.
66022004	At mban alut eeko logonet, etenggen liippugwi iigak, at endage inenggaawak paga liiru mbanak wonage kagarak~o.
66022005	Time o kiip age, o weege, eeka'lek o liingge mban wonage kagak, it aakumi nen Ala eya paga nugu logogun me, nugu logonet, "O eya aruwak nduk, oonegen wundi wage, ndi, ndi wuninggwi, eeruwak lak ao," mbaka'lek it aap inendagembogut negen logonet, mondok-mondok wone lengganogo yorogo logogun~o.
66022006	Ti'nuk, at wone yo'nege nogo nen ambinom yo'nege logonet, "At Aberiniki nogo it aap Ala yorage kagak yoraga inikime logonet yorage kagak, aakumi yorogo logowak nduk, nappi wagagerak ninogoba Ala nogo nen logonuk lek mbet-mbet eeriyak wone nogo, at ayeloman mini ineenu aruwak nduk, ayonggo nage menggerak malayikat ambi nappi wagaarak. Nappi wagaarak nogo nen wone yokkegerak nogo abok aret, Yi abet aret, yo'negerak me a'me nggelok yigin, mbake logot~o.
66022007	An mbet-mbet woraagin~o, yinuk, yegerak me yokkigi~o. Ndi, peebi eeriyak wone an yokkege neegak, liiru mbanggendak nogo, it aakumi liippunuk, mugurok nogwe iinok, iniki ale'nggen aret kogo logogun~o," yinuk, yo'nege kagarak.
66022008	Wone agan wagaarak naruk konengge, eerit wagaarak nenegen kage, eekirak nogo ti, an Yaya aret me, naruk konengge, nenegen kage, eeke nagarik, at peebi eeriyak wone yo'negerak malayikat nogo alut eerikit nduk, abu'me tebe ari mbaki,
66022009	at nen an yo'nege logonet, "Togop eerugun~o. It koreewi Ala nen yorage kagak yoraga inom, it wone liiru mbanggendak liippunuk mugurok nogo logomenggaarak nogo inom, kat inom, an kit pogom Ala ayeloman aret me, Ala mban alut eeke logot~o," yinuk, yo'negerak.
66022010	Yo'nege nagaarik, "Peebi eeriyak wone yokkege neegak liiru mbanggendak nogo, eeriyak abu aret panggo yi wagaarak me, wone ti, kumaapporogo logorak mage~o. Ata, yi aap ndi aap yoranet nege logot~o.
66022011	Yoranet nege keegak kwe, it maluk eeko logorak mbakwi kenok, maluk aret eekwi, ndi, eeriyak lek mendek kagak ugun-ugun eerit nogo logorak mbakwi kenok, ugun aret eerit nogwe, ndi, it ando maluk eeka'lek obeelom mban eeko logorak mbakwi kenok, obeelom mban eerit nogwe, ndi, it ando kikak naka'lek Ala ake mban leenak logorak mbakwi kenok, Ala ake leenak wonogwe, eekkologo logowak~o," yinuk, yo'nege kagarak.
66022012	-
66022013	Yo'nege kage nagarik, at Yetut nen, "O maan aa'nduk togon wonagagirak alom Alpa inom, peebi irip paga mondok logorak Omega inom, ti an mban aret me, an logonuk lek mbet-mbet wage logominggirik, yi aap ndi aap eeko logomenggaarak paga onggo wogoroorak mbakirak nogo inalitik-inalitak ndak-ndak wogora woraagin me, liippogo logowak~o," yinuk, yo'nege kagarak.
66022014	Yo'nege kage nagarik, "It ina-mbogoyum laambu kookkologo me-nggaarak nogo, Eyo ineenik aganaka anggen nunggwi, ndi, o kota tu paarak mban wonage yime nowagam unggwi wogwe, eeko logonip~o, yinuk, yorage neenok, iniki ale'nggen mbakak o kota unggwi nogwe iigak kwe,
66022015	it nggeewo pogom eeko menggaarak inom, magagirak iyagalo inom, yawukak mbabilu inom, aap inooka inom, kugi eeka inom, ndi, yi aap ndi aap pilit puguniyak inikilom mbako logonet, pilit-pilit pugungga inom, it perak, o kota time unggwi naga'lek yagat endekem logogun~o.
66022016	Kit an napuri yi awi ndi awi kuwak eerit nogo monggotak nogo, peebi eeriyak wone yi, paganogo yokkira woraawak nduk, nayonggo nege menggerak malayikat ambi nappi wagarak nogo ti, an Yetut nen aret~o. O weerikit nduk eeke kagak, laaluguragan ambiret kere ari nogo pogom anebunu Ndawut paga wiganak agarip ndarak nogo an aret~o," yinuk, yo'negerak.
66022017	Yo'nege mbaki, malayikat nogo nen ambi yo'nege logonet, "It aakumi niyo abu aganake kenok, niyo ineenik aganaka nogo mendek onggo lek we aret tookkola woraawak nduk, Aberiniki inom, Ndomba Aagaluk akwe nogo inom, imbirak nen, Wa'nip~o, yinuk, muk yorogo agaarik~o. Ndi, it wone yi, konembunuk abet mbakwi iinok, Na wa'nip~o, yinuk, wiirogo logowak nduk, yoret~o," yinuk, yo'nege kagarak.
66022018	Ti yo'nege nagaarik, ambinom yo'nege logonet, "Peebi eeriyak wone yokkege neegak liiru mbanggendak nogo, aakumi konembunuk, wone alik ambi inom nabenogo pugwi iinok, andi-pandi aganaburak kugi alom 7 porogo wonogwe iige nagandik, liiru mbanggendak nogo nen inooruwak nduk, Ala nen nappiya woraagin~o.
66022019	Ndi, at Ala nen, Ineenik aganaka anggen nunggwi, o kota obeelom alik leenak nogome unggwi nogwe, eeko logorak~o, yinuk, yereegerak mbuku yi paga liiru mbanak wonage kwe, peebi eeriyak wone yokkege neegak liiru mbanggendak yi, aakumi nen konembunuk, ando waganggo logonet, Ando ti woorak lek~o, yinuk, mbo pugwi iinok, at Ala nen it aap ti, anggen nogo nunggwi, ndi, o kota nogome unggwi nogwe, eerugun lek, Kit endekem aret logonip~o, yinuk, yoraagin.
66022020	Kat keenu a'nok nduk, wone yi, paganogo yokkegerak nogo nen, An logonuk lek mbet-mbet wagi~o, yinuk, abet aret ari kagarak me, wone ti, abu aret yokkigi~o," yinuk, yo'nege kagarak. Yo'nege mbaki, an nen, "Noweeluk Yetut mbet-mbet woraawak lak ao," yinuk, "Amin," yagarak.
66022021	Kit kinowe Yetut nogo iniki kunik en obeelom eeppinagage logonet, kinarum aret logogin~o. Amin.
